NK076(mu)002:1: // gu h+ya ma n+t+ra ba dz+ra ya na u pa
NK076(mu)002:2: de sha pa tha skra ma ra t+na b+y+au h+aa
NK076(mu)002:3: n+aam bya ny+dza nam t+ai k+aa ga ti ma ti
NK076(mu)002:4: pra k+aa sha bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK076(mu)002:5: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i man ngag lam gyi
NK076(mu)002:6: rim pa rin po che rnam par bkod pa'i 'bru
NK076(mu)002:8: ka dag dbyings las lhun grub ye shes kyi //
NK076(mu)002:9: tshogs gnyis lhun rdzogs khyad chos drug ldan cing //
NK076(mu)002:10: gdod ma'i sangs rgyas kun bzang rdo rje 'chang //
NK076(mu)002:11: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i spro bsdu khyod phyag 'tshal //
NK076(mu)002:12: nyid las mi gzhan rigs lnga gsang ba'i bdag /rigs
NK076(mu)002:13: can lnga dang skal ldan rgyal po dzah ye shes
NK076(mu)002:14: sku brnyes sangs rgyas gsang ba sogs //
NK076(mu)002:15: brgyud gsum bla ma'i tshogs la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK076(mu)002:16: sngon byon mkhas shing grub brnyes dam pa yi //
NK076(mu)002:17: gsung gi rjes 'brang 'bru 'grel bkod pa la //
NK076(mu)002:18: rtsa gsum srung mas gnang ba'i skabs dbye nas //
NK076(mu)002:19: bdag rgyud byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol //
NK076(mu)002:20: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba stong
NK076(mu)002:21: phrag brgya pa gang yin pa de dag gi snying
NK076(mu)002:22: po bsdus pa man ngag lam gyi rim pa rin
NK076(mu)002:23: po che rnam par bkod pa 'di 'chad pa la
NK076(mu)002:24: / man ngag brtsam pa la 'jug pa'i yan lag thog mar dge ba klad kyi don /
NK076(mu)002:25: chos kun khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir bar du dge ba gzhung gi don /
NK076(mu)002:26: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo zhing smon lam gdab pa tha mar dge ba mjug gi don te gsum /
NK076(mu)002:27: dang po la'ang mtshan brjod pa /
NK076(mu)002:30: brtsam par dam bca' ba bzhi las /
NK076(mu)002:32: dang po rgya gar 'phags yul du yongs su grags pa'i skad rigs bzhi las /
NK076(mu)002:33: legs sbyar sam ski ta'i skad du /
NK076(mu)002:34: gu h+ya man+t+ra badz+ra y+aa na u pa de sha ba thahkra ma rat+na bi +au ha n+aa ma /
NK076(mu)002:35: gnyis pa bod skad du bsgyur na /
NK076(mu)002:36: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i man ngag lam gyi
NK076(mu)002:37: rima pa rim po che rnam par bkod pa zhes
NK076(mu)002:40: thun mong gi spyod yul du ma gyur pa'i gsang ba dam pa de la /
NK076(mu)002:41: yid shes bde myur gyis skyob phyir sngagsa dang /
NK076(mu)002:42: rdo rje'i chos bdun dang ldan cing sangs rgyas rnams
NK076(mu)002:43: kyi sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed pa rgyu dang
NK076(mu)002:44: 'bras bu lhun grub tu spyod par byed pa'i lam
NK076(mu)002:45: 'dis 'degs par byed pas na rdo rje theg pa
NK076(mu)002:46: ste / de'ang tshegs chung ngus don chen po dpag
NK076(mu)002:47: tu med pa rtogs sla ba'i thabs su gyur pa'i
NK076(mu)002:49: de'ang rim par 'jug pas na rim pa /
NK076(mu)002:50: 'jig rten 'dir 'byung bar dkon pas na rin po che lta bu'i chos 'di nyid /
NK076(mu)002:51: gdul bya skal ldan gyi rgyud la mngon sum rnam
NK076(mu)002:52: par bkod pa zab mo'i chos zhes bya ba yon
NK076(mu)002:53: tan gyi sgo nas mtshan btags pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:55: srid pa'i dpal gyi dang zhi ba'i dpal las kyang
NK076(mu)002:56: mchog tu 'phags pa sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:57: yon tan mchog dang ldan pas na dpal dbyings dang
NK076(mu)002:58: ye shes sam stong nyid rdo rje snying rje semas
NK076(mu)002:59: dpa' chen po dbyer med pa'i rigs kun 'dus pa'i
NK076(mu)002:62: gsum pa mchod par brjod pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:63: mtshan gyi zur dang po thun mong thun min gnyis las /
NK076(mu)002:64: thun mong 'jig rten gyi 'byor ba sogs phun sum
NK076(mu)002:65: tshogs pa la dpal 'byor gyi sgras brjod pa dang
NK076(mu)002:66: / theg pa 'og ma'i rang sa'i 'bras bu la'ang dpal du btags pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:67: thun min rtogs pa bdag gi dapala dang thugs rje
NK076(mu)002:68: gzhan gyi dpal zhes gdul bya'i phyogs re la byed
NK076(mu)002:69: pa las 'phags pas na dpal gsum pa zhes te
NK076(mu)002:70: / ji ltar 'phags na 'khor 'das kyi chos kun
NK076(mu)002:71: dag mnyam chen po'i rang bzhin du gnas pa gzhi'i
NK076(mu)002:72: / dpal / sgrib gnyis dri mas ma gos shing
NK076(mu)002:73: gzhi 'bras dbyer mi phyed pa mngon du gyur pa
NK076(mu)002:75: gdul bya mtha' yas pa'i don du gzugs sku gnyis
NK076(mu)002:76: kyi phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'gro ba'i
NK076(mu)002:77: don mdzad pa thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal te /
NK076(mu)002:78: de nyid gang la ldan pa ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ste /
NK076(mu)002:79: mtshan gyi zur gnyis pa 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:80: dang po phrin las kyi sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:81: 'joms pa'i rdo rje ni rdzas kyi rdo rje pha lam lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:82: gnyis med kyi ye shes sgrib gnyis dang lta ngan 'joms pa'i ye shes rdo rje /
NK076(mu)002:83: gnyis pa ngo bo'i sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:84: rgyu rkyen gyis 'dus ma byas pa'i rdo rje /
NK076(mu)002:85: gsum pa yon tan gyi sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:86: ched du yon tan ma btsal ba ye nas 'bras
NK076(mu)002:87: chos nyer lnga ngang gis rdzogs pa btsal ba med
NK076(mu)002:88: pa'i rdo rje / bzhi pa mtshan nyid kyi sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:89: dang po rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i phyir mtha' rgyu
NK076(mu)002:90: rkyen gyis mi shigs pa ste skye 'jig med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:91: rdo rje / lnga pa rang bzhin gyi sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:92: dbyings nyid ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i phyir dbyer med rdo rje ste /
NK076(mu)002:93: de ltar rdo rje chos lnga yi sgra don bshad
NK076(mu)002:94: pa yis rdo rjer grub pa nyid snang stong dang
NK076(mu)002:95: yul sems gnyis su med pa'i rig pa rang snang
NK076(mu)002:96: bas sems byed pa po med par ngang gis rang
NK076(mu)002:97: gasla ba'i phyir sems gzhan du mi g.yo yul du
NK076(mu)002:99: de ka sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin pas na chen po zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:101: sems zhes pa la dbye na bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:102: dang po snang tshul gyi sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:103: snang stong gnyis su med pa /
NK076(mu)002:104: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:105: sems nyid ngang gis 'od gsal ba /
NK076(mu)002:106: gsum pa ngo bo'i sgo nas /
NK076(mu)002:107: rnam par rtog pas mi g.yo ba /
NK076(mu)002:109: bla na med pa'i ye shes dang ldan pa rtag chad kyi mthar ma lhung pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:111: dpa' bo ni mdzad pa'i phrin las zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhis bdud bzhi bcom pas dpa' bo ste /
NK076(mu)002:112: de yang rim par nyon mongs pa lnga nyid ye shes lngar zhi bas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK076(mu)002:113: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i ngo bor dag cing yon tan rgyas pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK076(mu)002:114: lha rtog gnyis med kyi don dbang du byas pas lha bu'i bdud bcom /
NK076(mu)002:115: skye med kyi don mngon du gyur pas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom pas na dpa' ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:116: dper na dgra dpung 'joms pa'i skyes bu la dpa' bo zer ba lta bu yin /
NK076(mu)002:119: rang nyid sangs rgyas gsang bas thun mong gi lha 'jam dbyangs yin yang /
NK076(mu)002:120: khyad par thun min gyi lha yi yang lha rdo
NK076(mu)002:121: rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal yul 'tshal mkhan dgongs
NK076(mu)002:122: pa gnyis su med par gyur kyang /
NK076(mu)002:123: rnam pa tsam du dad pa'am mos pa'i tshul gyis
NK076(mu)002:124: rang zhal mjal ba la de'i tha snyad bzhag pa'i
NK076(mu)002:125: phyir lta ba mjal ba'i phyag go //
NK076(mu)002:126: bzhi pa brtsam par dam bca' ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:127: lo rgyus kyi sgo nas brtsam par dam bca' ba'i 'thad pa /
NK076(mu)002:128: bsdus tshul gyi sgo nas bshad par dam bca' ba dngos so //
NK076(mu)002:130: gsang sngags mi yul du dar tshul /
NK076(mu)002:131: de'i tshogs sgrub kyi sgo nas 'bras bu thob pa'i tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:133: ston pa dam pa'i mdzod gsum rtogs par dka' bas gsang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:134: de la mnga' mdzad pa'i bdag po phyag na rdo
NK076(mu)002:135: rje ri ma la ya'i rtser mngon du gshegs nas
NK076(mu)002:136: / 'khor lha rgya byin klu 'jog bo gnod sbyin
NK076(mu)002:137: skar mda' gdong srin po blo gros thabs ldan dang
NK076(mu)002:138: / / mi las li tsa bi dri med grags
NK076(mu)002:139: pa skal ldan rigs can gyi 'khor 'dus pa la
NK076(mu)002:140: / / / sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang pos gsang
NK076(mu)002:141: sngags ji ltar 'byung ba mdo sde gdams ngag 'bog
NK076(mu)002:143: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK076(mu)002:144: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK076(mu)002:145: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK076(mu)002:146: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK076(mu)002:147: 'dzam gling shar lho'i phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK076(mu)002:148: mi las skal ldan rigs can de //
NK076(mu)002:149: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK076(mu)002:150: lag na rdo rje'i mthus snang 'gyur //
NK076(mu)002:152: dgongs 'dus las ji ltar lung bstan pa'i dus /
NK076(mu)002:153: sa ho ra'i yul a par ta mu dz+ny+aa'i rgyal
NK076(mu)002:154: po u ta dz+ny+aa na nyid kyi rgyal bu sngags
NK076(mu)002:155: kyi rigs cana lung bstan rdo rje la /
NK076(mu)002:157: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:158: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:159: chos kyi bgro ba byas pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:160: kun gyis dam par bsgrags pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:161: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:162: rin chen char du 'bab pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:163: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa //
NK076(mu)002:164: zhes pa'i rmi ltas bdun shar nas /
NK076(mu)002:165: de nyid sngon gyi las smon dang /
NK076(mu)002:166: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i 'brel bas snang ba'i glegs
NK076(mu)002:167: bam la rab tu dga' ba khyad par can skyes
NK076(mu)002:168: nas dbang pos mngon sum brtags pas /
NK076(mu)002:169: ma rtogs pa dang rtogs pa'i lugs gnyis kyi kun
NK076(mu)002:170: mkhyen chen pos phyi ma ltar dang kha cig gis
NK076(mu)002:173: dge slong ku ku r+aa dza la bskur bas des
NK076(mu)002:174: kyang ma 'tshal slar bsrings nas rgyal po nyid kyis
NK076(mu)002:175: gsol ba btab pas rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong
NK076(mu)002:176: gi le'u thugs kyi sgrub pa'i thabs de mngon par
NK076(mu)002:177: rtogs te / de nyid kyi sgo nas zla ba
NK076(mu)002:178: drug tu sgrub pa mdzad pas rdo rje sems dpa'
NK076(mu)002:180: rigs kyi bu rang gi phung po sbyongs dang /
NK076(mu)002:181: gsang ba'i bdag pos lung ston par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:183: de nas phyag na rdo rjes rjes su bzung gsang
NK076(mu)002:184: sngags kyi lam bstan pa'i don thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK076(mu)002:185: dngosa grub dus de nas thoba /
NK076(mu)002:186: snod ldan rgyal po dzahl don dam nges pa'i theg
NK076(mu)002:187: pa'i bcud tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad kyi tshig don kun
NK076(mu)002:188: gyis gnas ma lus pa dus de tsam nas blo
NK076(mu)002:189: gros rgyas par byas pas rtogs pa'i yon tan phul
NK076(mu)002:191: glegs bam shes pas 'dod pa'i bsam pa dus de ru grub cing /
NK076(mu)002:192: tshe rabs kun tu smon pa'i lha dpal phyag na rdo rje dang dus de ru mjal /
NK076(mu)002:193: gnyis pa tshogs sgrub kyi sgo nas dngos grub thob tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:194: de ltar gsang sngags kyi theg pa rin po che
NK076(mu)002:195: 'jig rten du byung ba'i rjes de nas spyir rgya
NK076(mu)002:196: gar rdo rje gadna steng gi shar phyogs na sa
NK076(mu)002:197: ho ra yi yul yod pa de'i byang shar /
NK076(mu)002:198: bye brag 'adzama bu gling gi sa yi char gtogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:199: ri ma la ya'i gnas yod pa'i gnas de'i shar
NK076(mu)002:200: gyi dang lho yi phyogs gnyis kyi mtshams su a
NK076(mu)002:201: su ra gsang ba'i brag phug phyag na rdo rje'i
NK076(mu)002:202: pho brang du byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas kyi dam
NK076(mu)002:203: pa rin po che zur brgyad pa'i dbyibs can rin
NK076(mu)002:204: chen sna tshogs las grub pa'i nanga du gsang ba'i
NK076(mu)002:205: bdag pos zhabs kyis bcags pas bakra shisa shing byin
NK076(mu)002:206: rlabs che bas gnas kyi dam pa'i zhes mchog gi
NK076(mu)002:208: za hor dge slong ku ku r+aa dza tshom bu 'bum dang /
NK076(mu)002:209: rgyal po dzahyi sras in+t+ra b+h+au ti tshom bu khri dang /
NK076(mu)002:210: sing+ha ra tsa tshom bu stong dang /
NK076(mu)002:211: sing+ga la'i rgyal po'i sras u pa r+aa dza tshom bu brgya zer ba'ang snang /
NK076(mu)002:214: en+t+ra b+hu ti'i sras mo go ma sa la tshom
NK076(mu)002:215: bu lnga brgya dang ro langs bde ba h'u k+aa
NK076(mu)002:217: dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor du
NK076(mu)002:218: phan nus zab mo'i dbang rnams thob nasa thos bsam
NK076(mu)002:219: gyis lta ba rtogs shing tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor
NK076(mu)002:220: bzhi mthar phyin nas sbyor lam zhi khro'i tshom bu
NK076(mu)002:221: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring sdus gsum gang rung
NK076(mu)002:223: gnas skabs lam gyur rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)002:224: mthar thug mi slob pa'i rdo rje 'chang chen po
NK076(mu)002:225: sangs rgyas kyi sar mngon sum du gshegs par mdzad
NK076(mu)002:226: do // kun mkhyen chen pos tshogs sbyor ram chos
NK076(mu)002:227: mchog nas mi slob bar rig 'dzin bzhis bgrod par
NK076(mu)002:228: do // bzhed do // gnyis pa dam bca' dngos la /
NK076(mu)002:230: thos chung gsar bu yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:231: man ngag rtsis 'go lnga yis klad nas gzhom /
NK076(mu)002:232: zhes gsungs pas dang po khungs btsun pa dang yid ches phyir sus mdzad na /
NK076(mu)002:233: bstan bcos rtsom pa'i mtshan nyid gsum de lta bu
NK076(mu)002:234: dang ldan pa'i phyir sras mo go ma de w+ais
NK076(mu)002:235: rdzes su gzung ba'i mkhas grub chen po sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)002:236: gsang bar grags pa'i sangs rgyas kyi mtshan thob pa
NK076(mu)002:237: ngas / gnyis pa 'di ltar brtsam pa la dgos ched gang gi don du na /
NK076(mu)002:238: dam pa'i rigs can gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i
NK076(mu)002:239: chos 'di lta bu nyan pa'i skal ldan ya rabs
NK076(mu)002:240: dra ma yi ngang tshul dang ldan pa /
NK076(mu)002:245: slob dpon sba khri gzher dang lnga brgyud nas de
NK076(mu)002:246: yi rjes su 'jug pa ma 'ongs pa'i skala ba
NK076(mu)002:247: dang ldan pa rnams kyi phyir du'o //
NK076(mu)002:248: gsum pa rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gar gtogs na /
NK076(mu)002:249: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag bargya pa'i rgyud
NK076(mu)002:250: dag las btus te man ngag zab mo nye bar
NK076(mu)002:251: brtsam pa'o // bzhi pa ston pa la mtshan nges
NK076(mu)002:252: shing don gyi mdo chings rtogs par bya ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:253: mtshan ci la btags pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:254: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi bgrod pa gcig
NK076(mu)002:255: pa'i gshegs shul theg pa 'og ma'i lam las 'phags
NK076(mu)002:256: pas mchog rnam mkhyen thob pa la /
NK076(mu)002:257: nye ba dang bde ba dang rdzogs pa gsum gyi
NK076(mu)002:258: yon tan ldan pa 'di la mang po nyung ngu
NK076(mu)002:259: dang 'thor ba phyogs gcig tu bsdus te /
NK076(mu)002:260: lam rnam par bkod pa zhes /
NK076(mu)002:261: don rang gi ngo bo la mtshan btags pa /
NK076(mu)002:262: nyon mongs dang dus dang tshe dang lta ba dang
NK076(mu)002:263: sems can gyi snyigsa ma lnga'i 'gro ba rgyud drag
NK076(mu)002:264: cing gnyen po gzhan spong 'gegs sbyong sgyur lam gyis
NK076(mu)002:265: thul dka' ba'i dus kyi tshe /
NK076(mu)002:266: lnga pa don ji ltar bstan na 'khor 'das dag mnyam chen po tshe 'dir mngon du gyur phyir /
NK076(mu)002:267: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa bla med kyi lam
NK076(mu)002:268: kho nas 'dul ba'i dus kyis 'gro ba kun 'dul
NK076(mu)002:269: ba'i phyir 'di bstan par bya zhes go cha gyon
NK076(mu)002:270: pa'o // de ltar rtsis 'go lngas bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:278: dgos ched ci'i bstan pa ste bdun du 'grel lo //
NK076(mu)002:279: spyi don gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:280: brgyud pa'i man ngag dang ldan pa'i bla ma bsten dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:281: snod brtag cing sbyin mi sbyin gyi dmigs bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:282: snod ldan la man ngag rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:284: brgyud pa'i man ngag med par rang nyams kyis mi
NK076(mu)002:285: rtogs pas gzhan sel gyi dpe don bstan pa dang
NK076(mu)002:286: / de nas brgyud ldan gyi man ngag dang ldan pa brten dgos pa'i don gnyer ro //
NK076(mu)002:290: 'du shes chung ba rnams la u lu tri sha
NK076(mu)002:291: ka zer ba'i spyan bzang po ste long na mi
NK076(mu)002:292: gsal bas 'gro ba'i mthu meda pa yi /
NK076(mu)002:293: dmigs bu ste long khrid pa dang bral ba de gar 'gro'i nyams med lam stor bas /
NK076(mu)002:294: lam las bgrod cing 'dod pa'i gnas su phyin par mi nus pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:295: don la tshig phyir 'brang bas blo rtsing po dug
NK076(mu)002:296: lnga ma thul bas dmu rgod de lta bus rang
NK076(mu)002:297: nyams kyis / gsang ba'i snying po rtogs par mi 'gyur ta /
NK076(mu)002:298: 'di ltar bul shing ste thang shing smug por grags
NK076(mu)002:299: pa la me tog dang 'bras bu mi 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:300: bazhana gnas skabs kyi me tog dang mthar thug gi
NK076(mu)002:301: 'bras bu med pa'i skyon yod par 'gyur /
NK076(mu)002:306: rgyu mtshan de basa na bla ma rdo rje slob
NK076(mu)002:307: dpon de nyid rgyud lung nas gsungs pa bzhin sgo
NK076(mu)002:308: gsum gyis bkur / slob bu brtag phyir spyo bar
NK076(mu)002:309: byas te mtshangs 'bru ba zhe gcod pa'i tshig ngan
NK076(mu)002:310: ji tsam smra yang bazada par byas te /
NK076(mu)002:311: gnas skabs 'jig rten gyis mthong ba'i gdung ba byung yang khur du mi blta ste /
NK076(mu)002:312: sdug bsngal de kun mthar thug yun gyi sangs rgyas thob par bya ba'i don du bzod par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:313: gnyis pa bkur ba'i yon tan la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:314: dang po bkur ba'i yon tan gyis gdams ngag gnang ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:315: de ltar sgo gsum gyi dka' bas dang du blangs nas bla ma dam pa bsten par nus na /
NK076(mu)002:316: nam zhig ston pa rdo rje rgyal po thugs mnyes
NK076(mu)002:317: nas man ngag sbyin par zhal gyis 'ches pas thugs
NK076(mu)002:318: nyamsa kyi man ngag 'di lta bu yod do zhes
NK076(mu)002:319: gsung ba lta bus gannga ba slob bus go bas
NK076(mu)002:321: thob pa de yi tshe na rgyud chen gsang ba snying po'i gzhung las /
NK076(mu)002:322: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK076(mu)002:323: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK076(mu)002:324: zhes gsungs pa bzhin yon bla ma la phul na /
NK076(mu)002:325: slob dpon gyis thugs kyi nying khu man ngag zab mo rnams ster ro //
NK076(mu)002:326: gnyis pa gdams ngag gis sangs rgyas thob pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:327: man ngag thob pa'i gang zag de yis cang shes
NK076(mu)002:328: la sogs bzhon pa bzang po myur ba dang bde
NK076(mu)002:329: ba dang brtan pa la zhon nas 'gro bas myur
NK076(mu)002:330: du gang 'dod du phyin pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:331: gsang ba bla na med pa'i rdzu 'phrul rta dang
NK076(mu)002:332: stobs glang po cher mtshungs pa'i theg pa la zhon
NK076(mu)002:333: pas / rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba mthong zhing /
NK076(mu)002:334: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:335: sbyor lam bar chad med pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub
NK076(mu)002:336: la brten nas gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK076(mu)002:337: pa rig 'dzin bzhi'i lam bgrod nas mthar thug sku
NK076(mu)002:338: dang ye shes 'phrin las la dbang 'byor ba byang
NK076(mu)002:339: chub snying po'i gnas su phyin par byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:340: gnyis pa snod brtag pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:341: dang po snod brtag pa dngos ni /
NK076(mu)002:342: dang po snod ldan gyi slob ma dang bcud man
NK076(mu)002:343: ngag zab mo 'dzom na dngos grub thob pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:344: da basa bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis slob
NK076(mu)002:345: bu yal bar mi 'dor pa'i gnyer dang ldan pas
NK076(mu)002:346: snod brtag pa gal che bas /
NK076(mu)002:348: ngang tshul bzang ngan dad pa shes rab che chung gzhan la dris pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:349: drung du sgo gsum gyi bya spyod brtson 'grus sogs brtag /
NK076(mu)002:350: kun 'dus dang rngam glog sogs las gsungs pa ltar
NK076(mu)002:351: byis pa gtsang ma'i semas la pra phab ste brtag
NK076(mu)002:352: pa dang / las kyi mkha' 'agro la gtor ma
NK076(mu)002:353: byin pas de yis gsang sngagas kyi snod du rung
NK076(mu)002:354: mi rung nyams dang rmi ltas ston pas brtag pa
NK076(mu)002:355: pa dang / dang / mtshangs 'bru sogs spyo ba
NK076(mu)002:356: byas pa yis te brtag thabs lnga'i sgo nas lan
NK076(mu)002:357: gcig min par ci nas brtags te dpyad par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:358: pa dang / dang / // gnyis pa snod lngan la man ngag sbyin pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:359: de ltar brtags pas snod bzang mtshan nyid dang ldana na /
NK076(mu)002:360: theg dman du blo mi ldog cing gsang sngags lam
NK076(mu)002:361: la yid brtan par byas pa'i ched dbang bskur cing
NK076(mu)002:362: dam tshig sdom pas rgyud smin cing brtas par byas
NK076(mu)002:363: pa yi / slob bu gang yin pa de'i lag tu zab mo'i gdams pa 'di gtad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:364: gsum pa snod ngan la mi sbyin pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:365: dang po snod ngan la man ngag mi sbyin cing 'tshams par don bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:366: dang po gal te snod ngana pa'i mtshan nyid kyi
NK076(mu)002:367: rtags rmi ltas sogs mthong ba dang mngon sum du
NK076(mu)002:368: shes pas / tshe 'di'i 'doda pa phra ma'i rgyur dmigs nas chos byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:369: 'jig rten gyi kha dang gtam snyan gragsa pa che ba'i rgyur /
NK076(mu)002:370: chos byed cinga khyad par man dag gi bcud chena
NK076(mu)002:371: brjed ngas kyi snod zhabs rdol lta bu 'dzag pa
NK076(mu)002:372: dang / rang gis ma rtogs par gzhan la 'doms
NK076(mu)002:373: pa gsang sgo yal bas gzhogs ral ba lta bu
NK076(mu)002:374: dang / 'ab ba dang / man ngag zab mo
NK076(mu)002:375: bstan kyang mi go ba ma chags pa ste kha
NK076(mu)002:377: grub mtha' gzhan dang 'dres nas rang gi chos la
NK076(mu)002:378: the tshom za ba ni ma rungs par byed pa
NK076(mu)002:379: snod dug can byed pa lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)002:380: gzhan yang zang zing ngan pa mtha' ma lta bu
NK076(mu)002:381: bla mar gtong zhing dbul ba'am dbus te bzang po
NK076(mu)002:383: sems gaya sgyu che ba can ngo nas dga' ba dang gus pa byed cing /
NK076(mu)002:384: don 'gal ba ltag pa sprad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:385: lkog nas skur ba 'debs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:386: bla mas ma mthong ba'i lkog na rang gang dag'a bar byed cing dam tshig mi srung pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:387: kha gsags che bas ngag la rigas nges pa bzang
NK076(mu)002:388: por bshad kyang bsam pa la mi nges pa gya
NK076(mu)002:389: gyu can / bud med yin yang 'doda chags kyi gzhan dbang song ba /
NK076(mu)002:390: ngo tsha med par gang 'dod rang gar shor ba'i phyal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:391: 'di nyid skyes pa la'ang mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)002:392: mun pa'i khrod dang mi med ba'i lkog gar 'phrad
NK076(mu)002:393: par 'doda pa spyod pa la don du gnyer bsnyegs
NK076(mu)002:394: pa ste / de lta bu'i pha ma gang yin
NK076(mu)002:395: yang rung tan+t+ra ste rgyud kyi rda rje'i gnas chen
NK076(mu)002:396: po rnams der snod du ma basngagasa pa rnams la
NK076(mu)002:397: pa ste / / ji ltar bskal para lus dang grib ma bzhin yang yang 'akhara bar 'gyur yang /
NK076(mu)002:398: bla med thugs kya bad ba ste dus gsum rgyal
NK076(mu)002:399: ba'i dgongs bcud mthar thug 'di rlung phyogs tsam spro
NK076(mu)002:400: bar mi bya' //de ltar na gdul bya yal bar
NK076(mu)002:401: 'dor ram snyam na ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:402: gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par lha'i sku bsgom pa tsam bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:403: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig gacana gzan gyi
NK076(mu)002:404: 'phrang dang 'dra ba sbyin cing theg pa thun mong
NK076(mu)002:405: ba'i lam nas rim par blo khrid par bya /
NK076(mu)002:406: gnyis pa byin pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK076(mu)002:407: da ltar min par zab mo'i gdams ngag byin na
NK076(mu)002:408: be'u sbrel g.yang sar gtong na gcig shos ltung na
NK076(mu)002:409: gcig shos zhar la bsgyur ba bzhin ngan song du
NK076(mu)002:410: 'gro bar 'gyur / slob dpon des zas nor gyi
NK076(mu)002:411: 'dod pa'i kha yis sems te blo phrogs shing mi
NK076(mu)002:412: chos la blo gcum zhes srab pa 'phyar bas 'chal
NK076(mu)002:414: snod kyi skyon ma rtogs par man ngag spros na /
NK076(mu)002:422: pad+ma brtsegs te gdod nas grub pa'i dur khrod kyi
NK076(mu)002:423: gling brgyad kya gnas su las las grub pa'i ma
NK076(mu)002:424: mo dang mkha' 'agro ma srin mo king thod 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:431: bsnyo byad ma rnams dur khrod kyi rol 'dus pa
NK076(mu)002:432: bzhin'dus nasa nyams pa de'i sha za zhing srog la
NK076(mu)002:433: chad pa 'bebs shing tshe bstungs phyi ma myur du
NK076(mu)002:434: ngan song du ltung ba'i phyir brtag par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:435: gsum pa snod ldan la sbyin pa'i man ngag rang gi ngo bo la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:436: dang po lus mdor bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:437: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:438: dang po gong bstan de ltar brtags pa'i gsang sngags
NK076(mu)002:439: kyi skal ba dang ldan pa'i slob ma'i phyir gang
NK076(mu)002:441: le'u dang po 'dir mdor bstan pa ltar te /
NK076(mu)002:442: gzhi bden gsum dbyer med kyi rang bzhin ma bcos
NK076(mu)002:443: pa'i ye shesa rang la gnas pa le'u dang pos
NK076(mu)002:444: ston pa dang / lam ye nas gnas pa'i don
NK076(mu)002:445: de nyid shes rab spyan gyis phyin ci ma log
NK076(mu)002:446: par mthong ba ste le'u gnyis pas dang /
NK076(mu)002:449: phyag rgya gcig /spros rnams le'u gsum pa /
NK076(mu)002:455: mthar 'bras mi slob pa dgu pas ston te /
NK076(mu)002:456: der 'jug dbang rnon cig char ba le'u gsum pa'i stod dang /
NK076(mu)002:457: dbang rtul rim gyis pa le'u gsum pa'i smad sogs
NK076(mu)002:458: kyis ston pa rim gyis 'jug pas tshogs lam stong
NK076(mu)002:459: snying gcig spros kyi rnal 'byor bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:460: sbyor lam zag med du sbyor ba la lam gzhan
NK076(mu)002:461: gyis bar chad med par tshogs sgrub byas pas sngon
NK076(mu)002:462: gyi las kyi lus kyi rnam pa ldan kyang yid
NK076(mu)002:464: rang gi tshe la mi 'chi bar dbang skur bas /
NK076(mu)002:465: sgom lam du phyag rgya chen po mngon du byed cing /
NK076(mu)002:466: mthar lam du sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rig
NK076(mu)002:467: 'dzin bzhi lam du gyur pa le'u brgyad pas ston
NK076(mu)002:468: / mthar thug 'bras bu mngona du byas pa'i rima
NK076(mu)002:469: pa le'u dgu pas rgyas par ston pas de ltar
NK076(mu)002:470: rim pa bzhin du brjod para bya /
NK076(mu)002:471: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:472: gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:473: lam rang gnas rtogs shing goms par byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK076(mu)002:474: 'bras bu rang gnas mngon du gyur pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:475: le'u dang po gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:476: dang po nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:478: dang po gzhi ye shes rang gnas nyid la'ang spros te bshad pa /
NK076(mu)002:479: ga nas lugs de nyid skal ldan da yis thog mar shes par bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:480: gnyis pa gzhung rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:481: rang bzhin ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:482: de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:483: 'khrul yang lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med par rang la gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:485: rang lugs gzhi chos kun sems nyid rang snang la
NK076(mu)002:486: 'khor 'das gnyis med lhun grub yin par bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:487: ni / gang zhe na 'khor 'das gnyis su med
NK076(mu)002:488: pa phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i rang bzhin
NK076(mu)002:489: ni / 'di chos can / ye nas de bazhana gshegas pa'i nga ba nyid yin par thal /
NK076(mu)002:490: 'khora ba semas nyid rang snang tsam yin pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:491: badga dang bdag gir 'dzin pa rdul tsam yang grub
NK076(mu)002:492: pa med pas / de yi phyir de bzhin gshegs
NK076(mu)002:493: pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa las 'gro ba'i blo'i bsam
NK076(mu)002:494: pa'i mtha' yas su shar phyir ma dag pa'i dngos
NK076(mu)002:495: por nam yang mi dmigs so //
NK076(mu)002:496: myang 'das phyogs gcig ltung ngo zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:497: rgyu 'khor ba'i rang bzhin cir yang mi dmigs ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:498: de la ltos pa'i 'bras bu chos nyid mya ngana las 'das pa yang yod pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:499: 'khor 'das dbyer med pa mtha' gnyis las grol ba gdod ma'i spyi gzhi chen po'o //
NK076(mu)002:500: gnyis pa gzhan lugs 'khor 'das tha dad du brjod pa'i skyon la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:501: dang po 'khor 'das rang bzhin tha dad pa'i skyon ni /
NK076(mu)002:502: de ltar mya ngan las 'das pa'i rigas dang 'khor
NK076(mu)002:503: ba'i rgyu gnyis ngo bo tha dad du grub pa
NK076(mu)002:504: med pas / gnas lugs byang chub kyi sems bden
NK076(mu)002:505: gnyis zung 'jug mchog gi ngo bo la 'khor 'das
NK076(mu)002:507: 'khor 'das so so'i rang bazhana rdzas tha dad du nges so zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:508: 'o na 'khor ba de yang daga pa'i lam gyisa 'khor skyon bcos su med par thal /
NK076(mu)002:509: de tha dad pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:510: gnyis pa ngo bo tha dad pa'i skyon dpe dang
NK076(mu)002:511: bcas pa ni yang dag pa'i lam la gshegs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:512: sangs rgyas dang log par rtog pa'i sems can gnyis
NK076(mu)002:513: ngo bo chos nyid kyis tha dad du gansa par
NK076(mu)002:514: gyur na / tha dad de la 'khor ba'i skyon
NK076(mu)002:515: bcos shanga mya ngan las 'das par bsgyur du meda
NK076(mu)002:516: gyur na / par thal / dper na machanga bu
NK076(mu)002:517: la phyag mchod byas na nor bu rin chen dang
NK076(mu)002:518: mtshungs pa'i dgos 'dod mi 'byung ba bzhina 'khor ba
NK076(mu)002:519: las myang 'das mi 'byung bar ragas so //
NK076(mu)002:520: gnyis pa de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:521: de bas na 'khor 'das dbyer med yin pa de
NK076(mu)002:522: lta yin na'nga glo bur gyi rnam par rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)002:523: kun dkris kyis tshul 'di bzhin 'khrul bar snang basa
NK076(mu)002:524: / 1rgyu lhan skyes ma rig pas rang ngo ma
NK076(mu)002:525: shes kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas log par
NK076(mu)002:526: rtog pa sna tshogs bzhags pa dang 'dra bas 'khor
NK076(mu)002:527: / ba'i rgyu byas / 2las dge sdig bar ma gsum dang /
NK076(mu)002:528: rtsa ba'i kun dkris nyon mongs lnga ste brgyad kyi rkyen gyis /
NK076(mu)002:529: 3'khor tshul phyi'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni /
NK076(mu)002:530: rgyu dang 'brel ba drug 'bras bu dang 'brel ba drug gis tshul du 'khor /
NK076(mu)002:531: nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis ma rig pa /
NK076(mu)002:540: rga shi'i bar du bcu gnyis po 'khor lor lta bus 'khor ba'i gnas su bskyar ro //
NK076(mu)002:541: 4'bras bu ni rten snod kyi 'jig rten dang /
NK076(mu)002:542: brten pa nang bcud sems can gyi lus longs spyod 'dod pa sogs tha dad pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:543: gnas skabs bde ba ltar snang yang skad cig gis
NK076(mu)002:544: 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal gyis gdung bas lus sems nyam
NK076(mu)002:545: thag cing rnam mkhyen gyi lam dang brala ba /
NK076(mu)002:546: 5dus 'khor ba thog ma brtsam pa med pa nas
NK076(mu)002:547: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid las dus kun tu nyams
NK076(mu)002:549: rang bzhina bde gshegs snying po nyid las gzhan du
NK076(mu)002:550: nyams pa'am dman par gyur pa nam yang med pa'o
NK076(mu)002:551: // gsum pa 'khrul yang lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med par rang la gnas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:552: dang po dpe dang sbyar te mdor bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:553: de ltar yin na'ang rgyal ba'i phrug gu dmangs su
NK076(mu)002:554: 'khyams kyang de bzhin rgyal po'i ragas la 'gyur ba
NK076(mu)002:555: med pas na / rgyu des na shul te lam dang /
NK076(mu)002:556: dona de'i 'bras bu'ang rang las gzhan na yod pa min pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:557: dper na lha 'phrul dag'i lha rnams rang gis sprul
NK076(mu)002:558: pa'i yo byad la longs spyod tshul de rang las
NK076(mu)002:560: de yang lam 'bras rang la gnas tshul la kun rdzob /
NK076(mu)002:562: dbyer med rnam pa gsum du gansa pa'i tshul du bzhag par bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:563: gnyis pa don rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:564: dang po kun rdzob las dngos po'i gnas lugs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:565: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi don rang la gnas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:568: yi ge rang la gnas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:569: gleng gzhi dang rgyud don rang la gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:571: dang po mtshon bya don gyi bstan par rang la gnas pa'i tshul /
NK076(mu)002:572: 'gro ba rgyud lnga skyed pa'i yi ge drug /spyi bor a su /
NK076(mu)002:576: rkang mthil du du ste sa bon no //
NK076(mu)002:577: de'i gnyen po 'bru lnga snying gi rtsa 'dab lnga la /
NK076(mu)002:579: yang na spyi mgrin snying lte gsang ba la /
NK076(mu)002:580: yi ge lngar gnas pa ni sku dang ye shes lnga yin pa'i phyir thabs chen pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:581: 'gro ba drug po kun la rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:582: gnyis pa mtshon byed tshig gi bstan pa gnas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:586: lte ba sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhi dang srog shing
NK076(mu)002:587: gi tshul ro rkyang dbu ma gsum gnas pa de
NK076(mu)002:588: na ka li'i ste sgra yi yi ge /
NK076(mu)002:589: +aa li ste dbyangs kyi yi ge'i phreng ba /
NK076(mu)002:590: spyi bor rtsa 'dab so gnyis kyi dbus na ham yig mgo thur bstan yod la /
NK076(mu)002:591: rtsa 'dab la k+aa li so gnyis g.yon skor /
NK076(mu)002:593: mgrin pa'i rtsa 'dab bcu drug na dbus am mthar +aa li bcu drug g.yas skor /
NK076(mu)002:594: snying ga'i dbus h'u mthar rtsa 'dab brgyad na a
NK076(mu)002:595: ka tsa ta ta pa ya sha ste ma ning
NK076(mu)002:596: yi ge brgyad / lte ba'i dbus na a shad
NK076(mu)002:597: mthar rtsa 'dab re bzhi na sgra yig so gnyis
NK076(mu)002:598: g.yas skor dang g.yon skor du ldana pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:599: gnyis pa gleng gzhi dang rgyud don rang la gnas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:600: thabs lam rang la gnas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:601: rgyud don yong shes rang la gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:603: dang po 'og sgo thal ba ltar na /
NK076(mu)002:604: esa mtshon pa'i yum gyi pad+mo sgo gru gsum /
NK076(mu)002:607: dbyings phyug gi sna rtse zlum po ste gnas /
NK076(mu)002:608: yab kyi rdo rje'i rtse mor kun rdzob kyi thig
NK076(mu)002:609: le wam yig gi gzugs su gnas pa bde ba
NK076(mu)002:610: gsal bar ston pa'i phyir ston pa /
NK076(mu)002:611: ma d+aa na ma nu zhes pa'i sgra las yid
NK076(mu)002:612: sdom byed de 'du shes gsum ldan gyi sdom pa
NK076(mu)002:613: la zhugs pas mtshan rtog sdom par byed pa gsang
NK076(mu)002:614: ba'i rnam shes kyi reg bde nyams su myong bar
NK076(mu)002:616: pa ra ma y+aa na las thabs kyi theg pa
NK076(mu)002:617: zhes bde chen dga' ba bcu drug gis lhan skyes
NK076(mu)002:618: kyi ye shes rgyud la skyes pa ni nges don
NK076(mu)002:620: de ltar ye shes de nyams su myong ba'i tshe
NK076(mu)002:621: dus 'di zhes mtshon du med pas dus phun sum
NK076(mu)002:622: tshogs pa ste de nyid yum gyi mkha' gsang du
NK076(mu)002:623: ldan pa dang / gnyis pa steng sgo bshad rgyud rgya mtsho ltar na /
NK076(mu)002:624: snying gar e sogs las bzhi'i dbyibs su gnas pa ni gnas /
NK076(mu)002:625: de'i snying po 'byung ba lnga'i rlung lnga'i dwangs ma'i sgrom bu'i gnas na ston 'khor rnams yod do //
NK076(mu)002:626: de yang dbus na thig le wam yig gi gzugs su yod pa ni ston pa /
NK076(mu)002:627: ma nu'i sgra las drangs na yed de /
NK076(mu)002:631: sgo lnga'i rnam shes rnams rtsa 'dab bzhir gnas ba 'khor /
NK076(mu)002:632: y+aa bar ma tha ya na'i sgra las drangs na
NK076(mu)002:633: steng sgo'i lam nyams su blangs pa las ye shes
NK076(mu)002:634: nam mkha'i gzugs can mngon du skyes pa ni nges
NK076(mu)002:636: de'i tshe skye 'gag gnas gsum gyi mtshan ma dang
NK076(mu)002:637: bral ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus phun sum
NK076(mu)002:638: tshogs pa'o // gleng gzhi'i nges tshig /
NK076(mu)002:639: de lta bu'i phun sum tshogs pa lnga 'dzom pa'i
NK076(mu)002:640: dus de yis tan+t+ra ste rgyud kyi don 'byin par
NK076(mu)002:642: gnyis pa rgyud don yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po ngang la gnas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:646: dang po gtso bo rang la gnas pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:647: de lta bu'i rgyud don de ni /
NK076(mu)002:648: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na gnas te /
NK076(mu)002:649: mdun du chos nyid kyi rtsa gsum dkar po zlum
NK076(mu)002:650: po'i nang du thig le mi rtog pa'i tshul du
NK076(mu)002:651: gnas pa stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin dang
NK076(mu)002:652: / g.yas su ye shes kyi rtsa gcig ser po
NK076(mu)002:653: gru bzhi'i nang du thig le ma 'gags par gnas
NK076(mu)002:655: g.yon pa yon tan gyi rtsa gcig mdog dmar po
NK076(mu)002:656: dbyibs zla gam du thig le khyab par gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:658: rgyab na rtsa gsum gnyid rmugs kyi lasa byed pa
NK076(mu)002:659: ni rang rgyud pa'i rtsa zhes dbyibs gru gsum dmar
NK076(mu)002:660: nag gi rnam par thig le sna tshogs pa'i tshul
NK076(mu)002:661: du gnas pa phyag rgya spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:662: te / de ltar rtsa 'dab brgyad po nyid kyi dngos po ni /
NK076(mu)002:663: rnal 'byor bzhi'i lam rim par rang bzhin gyis grub
NK076(mu)002:664: pas rtogs shing goms pa'i sbyor bas mngon sum du
NK076(mu)002:666: gnyis pa cha rkyen rnams rang la gnas par bstan
NK076(mu)002:667: pa la phrin las bzhi nang ltar snying ga chos
NK076(mu)002:669: steng sgo ltar na sngar smos pa'i snying ga chos
NK076(mu)002:670: kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab rigs bzhi theg le'i snod
NK076(mu)002:671: ni rtsa bzhi ste rtsa de rnams kyi g.yas chos
NK076(mu)002:674: mdun ye shes rtsa 'od ser po dbyibs gru bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:675: g.yon yon tan rtsa 'od dmar po dbyibs zla gam /
NK076(mu)002:676: rgya ba rang rgyud rtsa 'od dmar nag dbyibs gru
NK076(mu)002:677: gsum du gnas pa de phrin las bzhi ste gnas
NK076(mu)002:678: pa'o // bsnyen sgrub rang la gnas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:679: chos nyid kyi rtsa'i thig le de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo ste bsnyen pa /
NK076(mu)002:680: ye shes kyi rtsa'i thig le kun snang gi ngo bo nye bsnyen /
NK076(mu)002:681: yon tan gyi rtsa'i thig le phyag rgya gcig pa'i ngo bo ste sgrub pa /
NK076(mu)002:682: rang rgyud kyi rtsa'i thig le phyag rgya spros pa'i
NK076(mu)002:683: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo sgrub pa chen po
NK076(mu)002:684: ste / de lta rang bzhin gyis ldana pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:685: de yang ji ltar rdzogs pa'i tshul /
NK076(mu)002:686: rtsa 'dab thig les gang ba bsnyen pa /
NK076(mu)002:687: de las bde pa 'byung ba nye bsnyen /
NK076(mu)002:688: de ltar ngos zin nas nyams su blang bsgrub pa /
NK076(mu)002:689: bde ba rgyas pa de mngon sum nyams su myong ba sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK076(mu)002:691: snying ga'i rtsa 'dab bzhi'am de la phye na /
NK076(mu)002:692: de las gyes pa'i chos nyid kyi rtsa dang /
NK076(mu)002:693: yon tan gyi rtsal gsum gsum ste drug /ye shes
NK076(mu)002:694: dang rang rgyud kyi rtsa la mi phye bas gnyis
NK076(mu)002:695: te 'dab ma brgyad dang ldan pa'i shi ra na
NK076(mu)002:696: ste rtsa'i man+dala te bde chen ye shes kyi snying
NK076(mu)002:697: po 'dzin par byed pas na dkyil 'khor ro //
NK076(mu)002:698: sbyin sreg ni sum mdor ram /
NK076(mu)002:701: g.yas kyi rtsa ro ma ni dgang gzar /
NK076(mu)002:702: g.yona rkyang ma ni blugs gzar /
NK076(mu)002:703: dbus a wa d+h+au ti ni me lha /
NK076(mu)002:704: ye shes snying po ni sreg lha /
NK076(mu)002:705: nyon mongs la sogs pa'i rnam rtog tshogs ni bsreg rdzas te /
NK076(mu)002:706: de ltar sbyin sreg kyang ye nas rang la gnas shing ldan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:707: las bzhi nang ltar 'khor lo bzhi la gnas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:711: lkog ma me gru gsum mam /
NK076(mu)002:715: spyi bo rlung ste de ltar gansa bzhira 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:716: bzhi gnas pa'ang phrin lasa rnam pa bzhi gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:717: ste / las bzhi gsang ba 'og sgo ltar na /
NK076(mu)002:718: yum gyi gsang ba'i mkha' la sgo gru gsum sogs
NK076(mu)002:719: las bzhi'i dbyibs su rang bzhin gyi ldan pa'ang phrin
NK076(mu)002:722: gnas pa rten rtsa dang brten pa thig le dag la /
NK076(mu)002:724: nang nus pa 'jug pa'i dabnga lnga /
NK076(mu)002:725: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum ste dabnga rnams rang bzhin gyis ldana pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:727: dang po ni rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar gnas pa dbu rgyan /
NK076(mu)002:728: rtsa ro rkyang g.yas g.yon dar dpyangs kyi tshul du gnas pa cod pan /
NK076(mu)002:729: 'khor lo bzhir thabs shes kyi yi ge phreng ba'i tshul du spel bar gnas pa phreng ba /
NK076(mu)002:730: spyi bo'i ham las lus mgo mjug khyab pa'i rtsa'i d+r+wa bas 'brel ba go cha /
NK076(mu)002:731: rnam shes dang dbang po mi sgrib bar rang gsal brgyal mtshan /
NK076(mu)002:732: rtog tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa phyag rgya /
NK076(mu)002:733: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo'i 'dab ma ham
NK076(mu)002:734: yig la gdugs rtsibs kyi tshul du brten pa gdugs
NK076(mu)002:735: / rtsa gnas 'khor lo bzhi thig les gang ba bum pa /
NK076(mu)002:736: dam tshig lnga rang bzhin gyis gnas shing bza' btung
NK076(mu)002:737: la longs spyod pa bza' btung yig 'bru lnga rang
NK076(mu)002:738: bzhin gyis gnas pa snying po'i dbang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:740: rna ba'i rtsa'i 'dom rtsa na sgra thos pa thig le'i tshul du yod pa nyan pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:741: mgrin pa dang lce las sgra 'byung ba thig le dbyangs yig dang gnas pa 'chad pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:743: srog gi mi shigs pa'i thig le rnam par mi rtog pa bsgom pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:744: snying gi rtsa 'dab bzhir las bzhi lhun grub tu
NK076(mu)002:745: gnas shing yan lag bzhis bya ba byed pa phrin
NK076(mu)002:746: las kyi / rtsa dang thig le'i bya ba thams cad byed cing /
NK076(mu)002:747: yan lag lnga rigs lnga dang chos kun rang la
NK076(mu)002:748: rdzogs pas rdo rje rgyal po bka' rabs 'byams kyi
NK076(mu)002:751: rtsa 'dab thams cad kun byang chub sems kyis gang ba gsang ba'i /
NK076(mu)002:752: de las bde ba chen po skye bas shes rab ye shes kyi /
NK076(mu)002:753: de nyid bde stong zung du 'jug pa bzhi pa'i dbang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:754: mchod pa rang la gnas pa /
NK076(mu)002:755: gsang ba'i mchod pa thabs shes snyoms par 'jug pa'i
NK076(mu)002:756: dga' bas drangs pa'i rang bzhin gsang ba'i lha mo
NK076(mu)002:757: bcu gnyis su shar ba'i tshul /
NK076(mu)002:762: rtsa gnas na thig le chas kyis sgeg pa la s+y+aa /
NK076(mu)002:763: thig le rgyun mi chad pa thugs phreng ba m+aa l+ya /
NK076(mu)002:764: a ham gyi sgra grags pa girti /
NK076(mu)002:766: bde bas rgyud tshim pa d+hu pe /
NK076(mu)002:768: bde ba gsal bar byed pa mar me /
NK076(mu)002:769: bsal drod snyom pa gan+d+he ma'o //
NK076(mu)002:770: kha cig gis gsang ba yab yum gyi mchod pa dug gsum nang gi mchod pa'ang zer /
NK076(mu)002:771: 'doda yona dbang po drug gis nyams su myong ba'i gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya dang /
NK076(mu)002:772: dam rdzas mchod pa rang la ldan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:773: lte ba'i rtsa ba na sha chen /
NK076(mu)002:774: long kha'i rtsa ba na dri chen /
NK076(mu)002:777: ro ma na ra k+ta ste lnga po rang bzhi'i gyis ldan pa'i mchod pa sta /
NK076(mu)002:778: dam tshig rang la gnas pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:779: gong du bstan pa de dag rang la gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:780: de las mi 'da' bar lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK076(mu)002:781: ranga bzhina gzod ma nas ldan par gansa pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:782: sa ma ya ste dam tshig go //
NK076(mu)002:783: spyod pa rang la gnas pa /
NK076(mu)002:784: sgo gsum gyi ranga bazhana phyi ltar na lus ngag yid gsum dngos dang /
NK076(mu)002:785: nanga ltar na rtsa rlung thig le /
NK076(mu)002:786: gasnga ba yum gyi pad+ma dang yab kyi rdo rje sbyor ba ya gsang ba'i rnam shes sam /
NK076(mu)002:788: nang ngag /gsang ba yid kyi 'adu byed kyi spyod
NK076(mu)002:789: yul thams cad rgyal ba'i mdzad pa nyag gcig tu
NK076(mu)002:790: shar bas rang bzhin nganga gis gansa pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:791: gnyis pa thabs lam rang la gnas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:792: gzhan lus la brten pa'i 'dod chagas rang ga mar spyad pasa khamas gsum 'khor ba 'grub par byed /
NK076(mu)002:793: gciga shosa te thabs kyis zin pas ni bde stong
NK076(mu)002:794: zung 'jug gi ranga bzhina shin tu rnam par dag
NK076(mu)002:795: pa'i ya shasa 'agrub pa'i nye rgyu byed pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:796: thabs lam gazhi'ang rang la gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:797: gnyis pa 'bras bu rang la gnas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:798: dang po rtog tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor yin par khas blang ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:799: chos kun ngo bo 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes
NK076(mu)002:800: dang mi phyed par gnas pa'i phyir rdo rja phung
NK076(mu)002:801: po lnga dang de' yan lag 'byung ba lnga po
NK076(mu)002:802: kun rdzogas pa' sangas rgyas rigs lnga yab yum bcur
NK076(mu)002:803: gragsa pa sogs / rtog tshogs zhe gnyis lhar gyur
NK076(mu)002:804: tshul rgyud kyi rdo rje'i gnas las gsal ba ltar
NK076(mu)002:805: gragsa pa sogs / / de tsam ma zad dangsa
NK076(mu)002:806: por snang ba 'di kun phyi bzung ba'i yul la
NK076(mu)002:807: chagsa pa rnams rdo rje btsun mo dang /
NK076(mu)002:808: nanga 'dzin pa'i sems la chags pa rnams rdo rje sem dpa'i tshul gya 'bras bu grub pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:809: de la bsgom pa'i byed lasa dang /
NK076(mu)002:810: rang gi ngo bos kyang 'bras bur gzod nas gansa pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:811: gnyis pa dpe'i sgo nas gtan tshigs rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:812: kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid dper na chu zla sgyu ma sprul pa bazhana /
NK076(mu)002:813: dpe gsum pos 'dir ltar phung po lnga khamas bco
NK076(mu)002:814: brgyad dang skye mched bcu gnyis rnams rgyu rkyen gyis
NK076(mu)002:815: rang rgyud par grub pa med kyang rten 'brel rnams
NK076(mu)002:816: 'dus nas sgyu ma lta bur 'grub pa ni log
NK076(mu)002:817: rtog sgyu ma / yul dam tshig /byed pa las /
NK076(mu)002:819: stong pa phyag rgya chen po gzhi ye nas rdzogas
NK076(mu)002:820: pas lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyag rgya ma 'dres shing
NK076(mu)002:821: chu zla ltar gasla ba phyag rgya sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:822: de yang gdul bya'i mos pa dang mthun par cir yang 'char bas sna tshogs su 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)002:823: bsam pa ltar snang bas cir yanga 'grub kyang 'gro
NK076(mu)002:824: 'ong ma dmigs pa sprul pa lta bu ni rig
NK076(mu)002:825: pa sgyu ma'o // phung khams skye mched rnams /
NK076(mu)002:828: sprul pa bzhin du snang la rang bzhin med pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:829: gnyis pa lhag pa don dam gyi ye shes rang la gnas tshul la drug ste /
NK076(mu)002:830: dang po lhag pa'i don dam la chos kun ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:831: kun rdzob don dam dbyer med gsum du bstan pa'i bar ma don dam pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK076(mu)002:833: grub pa 'bras bu rnams rang la gnas par thal /
NK076(mu)002:834: ganga yanga rigas rgyud dang so so'i phyogs su rtag par grub pa mina pasa na /
NK076(mu)002:837: shes bya'i chos kun kyang de dang da bzhin dang mtshungs te /
NK076(mu)002:838: 'dod khams su pho mo gnyis kyi gzugsa gnyis dang ma ning matshana ma ste gsum /
NK076(mu)002:839: gzugs khams rags pa'i lus rten yoda pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:840: khams gong mar meda pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:841: de lta bu'i srid pa gsum gyi gansa mtho dman dang so so'i nang tshan gyi rasa dang /
NK076(mu)002:842: sde tshan gyi cha shas rdul tsam yang yoda pa
NK076(mu)002:843: mina te yul med rang gsal nyag gcig gi ngang
NK076(mu)002:845: gnyis pa lhag pa don dam dkor bdun kyi ngo
NK076(mu)002:846: bo chos sku nyid kyi rgyu dpe bstan pa ni
NK076(mu)002:847: / chos kun ngo bo gnyis su med pa yula
NK076(mu)002:848: can dang bral bzhina rang bzhin 'gag med da dang
NK076(mu)002:849: ldana pa'i dana dam mchoga de la sku gsung thugs
NK076(mu)002:850: yon tan phrin las lnga yi 'bras bu'i don dam
NK076(mu)002:851: / pa dang / rang bzhin ye shes don dam pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:852: ngo bo nyid dbyings don dam pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:853: rgyas par dbye na bdun dang bsdu na dbyings ye
NK076(mu)002:854: 'bras bu'i don dam pa gsum la 'khor 'das kyi
NK076(mu)002:855: chos kun rdzogs pa'i phyir lhag pa'i don dam pa
NK076(mu)002:856: yin la / dper na dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin rin chen las dgos 'dod 'byung ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:857: bdun nam gsum po de kun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:858: gsum pa lhag pa'i don dam de nyid chos skur bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:859: 'jig rten gyi khams brtan phyi snod /
NK076(mu)002:860: nang brten pa g.yo ba bcud kyi sems can la
NK076(mu)002:861: sogs pa thams cad rang byung ye shes las rang
NK076(mu)002:862: snang ba tsam nyid na ngo ba dngos por grub
NK076(mu)002:863: pa med pa / de nyid lhag pa'i chos sku chen po yin te /
NK076(mu)002:864: de yang rang bzhin nam ngang gis da ltar du gansa pa las /
NK076(mu)002:865: bcos ma glo bur ba'i 'du byed pa las gyur pa ma yin /
NK076(mu)002:866: bzhi pa lhag pa'i don dam pa de las lam
NK076(mu)002:867: dang 'bras bu gzhan na med par bstan pa ni
NK076(mu)002:868: / don de lasa gazhana pa'i 'bras bu thob bya med pas na /
NK076(mu)002:869: chos kun kyang 'bras bu'i ngo bor gdod nas smin
NK076(mu)002:870: zina pas lam gyis bgrod para bya ba'i yul meda
NK076(mu)002:871: do // 'bras bu lam du byed pa da nyid lam gya'ang ngo bo ste /
NK076(mu)002:872: de la 'ajug par byed pa'i gzhi gnas shing goms par byed pa lam /
NK076(mu)002:873: rang bzhin khams kyi yon tan mngon sum du mthar
NK076(mu)002:874: 'byin pasa gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum ldog chas sgro
NK076(mu)002:876: lnga pa lhag pa don dam de nyid chos kun
NK076(mu)002:877: gyi rang bzhin dang rgyu yin par bstan pa la
NK076(mu)002:880: 'jig rten drug gis bsdus pa'i phyogs bcu ma lus pa thams cad la /
NK076(mu)002:881: rang byung gi ye shes chen pos til dang til mar bzhin kun tu khyaba par gnas te /
NK076(mu)002:882: ranga byung gi ye shes de nyid dangsa po dang mtshan mar grub pa meda para /
NK076(mu)002:883: phyogs med kun tu snang bas kun gyi chos rnams
NK076(mu)002:884: la rgyas 'debs pa'i phyag rgya' rgya las mi 'da'
NK076(mu)002:885: ba dang rgyu yi tshul du gnas pa yina pa'i
NK076(mu)002:886: phyir ro // des na chos thams cad de lta
NK076(mu)002:887: bu yi ngang du gnas shing 'byung par ngesa so
NK076(mu)002:888: phyir ro // // bye brag tu bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:889: ji ltar gnas pa'i da bzhin nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbyingsa /
NK076(mu)002:890: rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'i ye shes ta /
NK076(mu)002:891: de nyid ma 'gags par thabas kyi phyag rgya sna
NK076(mu)002:892: tshogs su snang bas 'khor 'das kun gyi ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:893: nyid kyi rgyu'o // drug pa rgyu yi ming gi rnam grangs /
NK076(mu)002:894: bskyed bya skyed byed kyi rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi la sogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:895: don dam de la ming gi rnam grangsa su mtshan
NK076(mu)002:896: mar grub pa med pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu
NK076(mu)002:897: nyid dang 'khor 'das kyi chos kun ma 'dres pa
NK076(mu)002:898: / zad par gnas pa yangas su rdzagas pa zhes kyang brjod do //
NK076(mu)002:899: kyang gi sgras de bzhin nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:902: stong pa nyid sogs mtha' klas pa dag sdud pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:903: gsum pa bden pa dbyer med kyi ye shes rang la gnas pa'i tshul bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:904: gzhi 'khor 'das chos kun bden pa dbyer med du gcig pa'i dpe don dang /
NK076(mu)002:905: bden pa dbyer med du brjod pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK076(mu)002:906: bden pa gnyis med ye shes su rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:907: lam dang 'bras bu 'ang bden pa gnyis med las gzhan du med par bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:908: dang po ni bden pa gnyis kyi don gong du song nas /
NK076(mu)002:909: gsum pa bden pa dbyer med bstan pa la /
NK076(mu)002:910: bden pa de gnyis po tha dad pa'i dngos por zhen pa yi blos /
NK076(mu)002:912: don dam mya ngan las 'das pa dang phung po
NK076(mu)002:913: khams sogs 'khor ba'i chos zhes tha dad yod pa
NK076(mu)002:914: ma yin / ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:915: ye gdod ma nasa 'khor 'das zhes ragas rgyud so sor grub pa'i rtag pa zhig mana pas so //
NK076(mu)002:916: bye brag gnas rigs sa so'i gzugsa sgra dra ra
NK076(mu)002:917: rega bya dang chosa kyi bye braga tha snyad du
NK076(mu)002:918: btags pa kun / kun rdzob tsam du 'aja'a tshon snang ba ltar shar yang /
NK076(mu)002:919: don dam nam mkha'a ltar kha dog lnga so sor
NK076(mu)002:920: ma 'dres par snang yang nam mkhar gcig pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:921: / de ltar ma 'dres par snang ba de yang
NK076(mu)002:922: rang byung ye shes 'dus ma byas nyid kun rdzob
NK076(mu)002:923: 'dus byas su snang ba la 'dus byas su snang
NK076(mu)002:924: ba'i dus na'ang 'dus ma byas dang ngo bo dbyer
NK076(mu)002:925: mi phyed pas na rda rja nyid do //
NK076(mu)002:927: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med kyi don de rgyal
NK076(mu)002:928: 'gros zhes rgyal ba sangs rgyas sgam pos ma mdzad
NK076(mu)002:929: / 'khor ba 'gro ba sems can gyi shes pa sgrin pos ma bcos par /
NK076(mu)002:930: rang bzhin ngang gasa bden pa dbyer med par gnas pa de'nga /
NK076(mu)002:931: de ltar gnyis med min par tha dad du 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:932: pa'i zhena pa rnams kyi blo rgyud dgrola ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:933: du bden pa dbyer med du bstan pa tsam las
NK076(mu)002:934: / tha snyad kyi tshig dang bden gnyis dbyer med
NK076(mu)002:935: para 'dzin pa'i bsam brjod las ring du 'adsa pa
NK076(mu)002:936: / ste / gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:937: dang po yul shes gnyis med rang snang du bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:938: yul sems so sor snang ba 'di ci zhig cen /
NK076(mu)002:939: yul dang shes par snang ba de yang rgyu rkyen
NK076(mu)002:940: dang bral ba'i rang byung gi ye shes de rang
NK076(mu)002:942: gnyis pa rgyu 'bras gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:943: rgyu sems can las 'bras bu sangs rgyas 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:944: ltar snang yang don du gnyis su grub pa meda
NK076(mu)002:945: de / gsum pa phyi nang snod bcud gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:946: phyi snod dang nanga bcud la sogs gsal ba'ang nanga
NK076(mu)002:947: shes pa nyid ces don dam bden pa dbyer med
NK076(mu)002:950: chos kun ye shes rang la gnas bar bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:951: da ltar chos kun ye shes ranga la gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:952: de lta bu bden gnyis dbyer med kyi gnas tshul
NK076(mu)002:953: ji lta ba bzhin yin te /
NK076(mu)002:954: lam dang 'bras bu kun gyi dngosa gzhi yin pas /
NK076(mu)002:955: 'brel pa ngo bo bdag gcig gi phyir 'bras bu 'thob byed thabas chen pos /
NK076(mu)002:959: sgyur ba sogs las khyad par 'phags pa ma h+aa
NK076(mu)002:960: yo ga'i lta ba dag mnyam chen po nyams su
NK076(mu)002:961: blangs pas / gzhi 'bras dbyer med pa'i go 'phang mngon sum du byed de /
NK076(mu)002:962: de yang gzhan nas thob ba ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:963: ranga gi ngo bo nyid las 'byung bar zada do //
NK076(mu)002:965: kun rdzob don dam dbyer med pa lhag pa'i ye
NK076(mu)002:966: shes chen po ranga rgyud la lhun grub tu bzhugs
NK076(mu)002:967: pa'i gnas lugs gsal bar byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig
NK076(mu)002:968: don rnams gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don
NK076(mu)002:969: gyis na la'u zhes bya ba ste yas bgrangs ba'i
NK076(mu)002:971: spyi don gnyis pa lam rang gnas rtogs shing goms par byed pa la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:972: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:973: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:974: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med kyi rig 'dzin bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:975: de la dang po le'u gnyis pa lta ba bstan pa la /
NK076(mu)002:978: le'u'i mtshan bstan pa dang gsum /
NK076(mu)002:979: dang po ni gzhi rang byung gi ye shes la
NK076(mu)002:980: kun rdzob don dam dbyer men lhun grub tu gnas
NK076(mu)002:981: pa'i nganga la lta ba rtogs pa mjal ba'i tshul
NK076(mu)002:984: mtshan nyid gsum gyi dang pa lta ba sngon du
NK076(mu)002:985: 'gro bas lta ba ni lam gyi mchog ste de'i
NK076(mu)002:987: gnyis pa dngos kyi don bshad pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:988: dang po lus mdor bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:989: gang dag gzhi bden gsum dbyer med kyi ye shes
NK076(mu)002:990: rang la gnas pa'i don mthong bar 'dod pa la
NK076(mu)002:991: don bcu gcig gis ston te /
NK076(mu)002:997: rnam grangs dang ngo bo dngos gnyis thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1004: don de dag yan lag rgyas par bshad cing spros pa'i rtsa bar lus mdor bstan du bzhag go //
NK076(mu)002:1005: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la don bcu gcig gi /
NK076(mu)002:1006: dang po dgos ched la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1007: dang po lta ba rtogs dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1008: chos nyid mtha' bral lhun grub bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i don ma mthong bar /
NK076(mu)002:1009: sgom pa bsam med tsam gyis rang bzhin gzhi'i dkyil
NK076(mu)002:1010: 'khor gyi don la 'jug par byed pa des chos
NK076(mu)002:1011: nyid kyi gnas lugs mi shes pas blun pa yang
NK076(mu)002:1012: dag pa'i snang ba med pas mun pa the tshom
NK076(mu)002:1013: gyi blo ma nges pas sprul pa'i blo can de
NK076(mu)002:1014: / shes rab kyi spyan med pas long ba'i sems can te /
NK076(mu)002:1015: mi snang ba'i grong khyer chen por 'khor zhing 'gra bar byed pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1016: gnyis pa thos bsam gyis lta ba rtogs dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1017: lta ba ma rtogs par bsgoms kyang skyon che bas /
NK076(mu)002:1018: de bas na ma riga pa'i ling tog dang 'dra bas shes rab kyi mig ldongas pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1019: don ma rtogs pa'i slob bu la gsang sngags rdo
NK076(mu)002:1020: rja theg pa'i slob dpona ni mig nad bsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:1021: thura ma mkhan dang 'dra ba de la sgo gsum
NK076(mu)002:1022: gyis mnyes par byas nas dbang thob par sngon du
NK076(mu)002:1023: byas de nas dang por gzhung thos pas shes rab
NK076(mu)002:1025: shes bya'i rang bzhin dkyil 'khor lta ba'i don mthong bar bya dgos so //
NK076(mu)002:1026: gnyis pa dus dang snod la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1028: snod lngan gdul bya de yang sngar thun mong theg
NK076(mu)002:1029: par ma sbyangs pa'i rang bzhina gyi rnon po snod
NK076(mu)002:1030: du gyur pa dang theg par sbyangs pa yis snod
NK076(mu)002:1031: du gyur pas na dus dbang rnon nye ba dang
NK076(mu)002:1032: / dbang rtul dus ring ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1033: spyangs pa'i rnon po rim gyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1034: rang bzhin rnon po cig char ba de gnyis re
NK076(mu)002:1035: re la'ang rim dang cig char gnyis gnyis bzhi cha
NK076(mu)002:1036: yis phye bas rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo
NK076(mu)002:1037: ga'i theg pa la 'jug par byed do //
NK076(mu)002:1038: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:1039: dus ring ba sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1040: dus nye ba rang bzhin gyi snod gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1043: dus kyi yun bskal pa chen por ched sprul sku'i
NK076(mu)002:1044: zhing ga stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i rdul phra
NK076(mu)002:1045: rab kyi grangs de snyed du /
NK076(mu)002:1046: theg pa sna tshogs la shes rab gsum gyis blo shin tu sbyangsa pa la rab tu gansa pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:1047: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid shes pa
NK076(mu)002:1048: ni shes raba kyi mig dang ldana pas ma h+aa
NK076(mu)002:1050: sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur bdus ring ba'ang theg pa tha dag la sbyangs pa'i rim gyis dang /
NK076(mu)002:1051: dus mtha'i gnas skabs kyi cig char 'jug pa'a //
NK076(mu)002:1052: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:1053: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1054: rim gyis pa'i cig char ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:1056: dang po sbyangs pa sngon du 'gro ba'i lugs ni /
NK076(mu)002:1057: mdor bstan gyi snga ma dus ring ba'i rim gyis
NK076(mu)002:1058: pa la'nga tan tra ste rgyud gsang snying gi gzhung
NK076(mu)002:1060: theg 'og gi sa dang lam rnams gong 'og gi
NK076(mu)002:1061: khyad par ma 'dres par rim par bkod pa yanga
NK076(mu)002:1062: / mthar thug gsang ba'i snying por brgyud nas 'gro ba'i lam stegs yin pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1063: khyad par bkod pa gang zhen /
NK076(mu)002:1064: lha mi nyan rang byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa
NK076(mu)002:1065: bzhi yis rang rang gi gzhung bzhin ma nor bar
NK076(mu)002:1066: gang las ngesa par 'byung bar byed la /
NK076(mu)002:1068: gsang sngags theg pa gcig gis mthar thug gi 'bras bur gnas /
NK076(mu)002:1069: de ltar lam stegs nyid du pha rol phyin bcu
NK076(mu)002:1070: sogs sngon du sbyangs pa rdzogs par byas pa'i mthar
NK076(mu)002:1071: ma h+aa yo ga la sbyor bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1072: gnyis pa de'i don man ngag gis 'jug tshul la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1073: dang po 'jug gzhi so skye'i sems brgyad skye tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:1074: de'i phyir rigs ma nges pa ni mos skal yod
NK076(mu)002:1075: la rtogs skal med pa'i rigas theg pa kun gyi
NK076(mu)002:1076: sgo dang mthun par 'jug cing spyags pa'i rigs mchoga
NK076(mu)002:1077: des gzhi nas sems bskyed lugs ni /
NK076(mu)002:1079: las rgyu 'bras sogs gang yang mi shes pa'i mun
NK076(mu)002:1080: pa'i shes pa nas grub mthar blo ma bsgyur ba
NK076(mu)002:1081: phal pa de'i sems skye lugs de nyid ni rang
NK076(mu)002:1082: bzhin bde gshegs snying pa rang la gnas pa'i rgyu
NK076(mu)002:1083: yis 'khor ba la skyo ba bag tsam skye ste
NK076(mu)002:1084: smyung bar gansa pa'am bde ba 'dod mi bde spong
NK076(mu)002:1086: de ltar 'jig rten phala pa'i semas brgyad mathara phyin cing gnas pa'i tsha /
NK076(mu)002:1087: zas gcig byed pa sa bon /
NK076(mu)002:1088: gnyan 'dun la sbyin pa gtong ba myu gu /
NK076(mu)002:1089: nye ring med par gtong ba sdong po /
NK076(mu)002:1090: lhug por gtong ba yal 'dab bam lo ma /
NK076(mu)002:1091: bla ma sogs la phul ba me tog /yid dga' ba dang bcas sbyin pa 'bras bu /
NK076(mu)002:1092: mngon mtho'i phyir tshul khrims bsrung ba gsos su gyur pa /
NK076(mu)002:1093: 'jig rten pa'i lha mchod pa stobs su gyur pa ste brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:1094: de la dang po dad pa'i sems /
NK076(mu)002:1095: bar gyi lnga sbyin pa'i sems /
NK076(mu)002:1096: tha ma gnyis tshul khrims kyi sems so //
NK076(mu)002:1097: gnyis pa 'jug pa'i rgyu rkyen spyir ngos bzung ba /
NK076(mu)002:1098: spyi'i khams bde bshegs snying po rang bzhin gyis gnas
NK076(mu)002:1099: pa khyad med pa mtshungs par ldan pa'i rgyu dang
NK076(mu)002:1100: / bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen sdug bsngal las
NK076(mu)002:1101: skyob pa'i 'gro ba'i mgon po las lung gnyis thos
NK076(mu)002:1102: / te / de gang zhe na gong ma 'das
NK076(mu)002:1103: pa'i yana tan mthong ba dang 'og ma 'khor ba'i
NK076(mu)002:1105: de yi stobs kyis 'khor ba la skyo zhing rmongas
NK076(mu)002:1106: pa dang yon tan la brod cing dang ba'i sems
NK076(mu)002:1107: skye ba dang / rgyu gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ru gsungs pa yin /
NK076(mu)002:1108: rkyen bzhi ni gong gi bla ma de bdag po'i
NK076(mu)002:1109: rkyen gasnga sngags la sogs theg pa dmigas pa'i rkyen
NK076(mu)002:1110: skyon yon mthong ba'i slob bu ste snod ldan rgyu'i
NK076(mu)002:1111: rkyen / de gsum 'dzom pa'i skad cig la sems
NK076(mu)002:1112: 'phel ba de g.yo sems dang 'brel ba de ma
NK076(mu)002:1115: dang po lha mi'i theg par 'jug tshul dpe bcas /
NK076(mu)002:1116: de ltar rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi ste drug tshang ba
NK076(mu)002:1117: lasa r+ts+wa las me mched pa bzhin sems cher g.yos
NK076(mu)002:1118: te / nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi yi thog
NK076(mu)002:1119: mar lha mi'i theg pa las sems skyes nas 'jug
NK076(mu)002:1120: tshul te dang por zhogas zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1121: gnyis pa rgyu rkyen gyis theg pa la rim par 'jug tshul /
NK076(mu)002:1122: lha mi'i theg pa de nas nyan rang byang sems
NK076(mu)002:1123: gri yog gi theg pa rnams rim gyis bgrod par
NK076(mu)002:1124: byas te / ji ltar bgrod na rgyu gnyis nas
NK076(mu)002:1125: bzung ste rkyen bzhi'i stobs kyis theg pa 'og nas
NK076(mu)002:1127: gsum pa yo ga nas ma h+aa la 'jug tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1129: de yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud yo ga'i theg pa
NK076(mu)002:1130: la gnas pa la ma h+aa'i theg pa 'di ston
NK076(mu)002:1131: pa'i mgon po ste slob dpon la yo ga man
NK076(mu)002:1133: ma h+aa'i yon tan gyi lung gnyis thos pas gong
NK076(mu)002:1134: du bstan pa de ji lta ba bzhin du rgyu
NK076(mu)002:1135: gnyis dang rkyen bazha'i sgo nas 'jug pa yin /
NK076(mu)002:1136: gnyis pa sems skye ba'i rim pa bzhi'i /
NK076(mu)002:1138: bla med mchoga gi theg pa ma h+aa yo ga
NK076(mu)002:1139: la 'jug snyam du g.yo ba'i semas skye zhing 'byung
NK076(mu)002:1140: bar 'gyur ro // gnyis pa smon sems /
NK076(mu)002:1141: g.yo sems kyi gzhi da yis go phye nas ma
NK076(mu)002:1142: h+aa'i don khonga du chud na snyam pa'i smon pas
NK076(mu)002:1144: gsum pa 'jug sems las dang bya bas lhag pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1145: don mtshon pa'i gzugs bsnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du chos
NK076(mu)002:1146: bco brgyad kyis 'jug par byed de /
NK076(mu)002:1147: bzhi pa gnas pa'i sems la'ang gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1148: dang po 'jug chos kyi dam tshig 'bog nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:1149: bla med mchoga gi theg pa ma h+aa'i rtsa ba
NK076(mu)002:1150: dang yan lag gi dam tshig kyang skabs de ru
NK076(mu)002:1152: dge bsnyen nan chags kyi rigas nges par gyur ba'i slob bu la phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK076(mu)002:1153: bdag don byed nus pa la nyan bsgom dbang gnyis
NK076(mu)002:1154: kyi byin rlabs tsam slob bu'i rgyud la bzhag /gnyis
NK076(mu)002:1155: pa lta ba rtogs thabs kyi thos bsam nyams su
NK076(mu)002:1156: len pa / de nas shes rab rang ga spyan
NK076(mu)002:1157: mchog lta ba 'byed pa'i thabs thos bsam la brtson
NK076(mu)002:1158: len pa / nas / lta ba rtogs pa'i rgyu thos dang bsam pa yis /
NK076(mu)002:1159: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor mthong bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1160: ma h+aa'i gzhung las thos pa dang bsam pa'i shes
NK076(mu)002:1161: rab dam pa dang du len par byed pa ni
NK076(mu)002:1163: gnyis pa ni gang zag kha cig da lta yan
NK076(mu)002:1164: chad thun mong theg pa la sbyangs pa'i dus kyi
NK076(mu)002:1165: mtha'i tshe smad ma h+aa la cig char du zhugs
NK076(mu)002:1166: pa'o // dus nam zhugs na bskala pa zhing gi rdul rnyed dang mnyam pa sngon du song bas /
NK076(mu)002:1167: theg pa thun mong gi grangs de snyed du sbyangs
NK076(mu)002:1168: pa'i mtha' gang la zhugs na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i
NK076(mu)002:1169: don ma h+aa la zhugs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1170: ji ltar zhugs na sngar sbyangs nas lus rten 'di
NK076(mu)002:1171: yi tshe stod la nges par 'byung ba'i theg pa
NK076(mu)002:1172: bzhi la rim gyis sbyangsa la phyi rgyud sde gsum
NK076(mu)002:1173: po nas cig char du ma ha'i drod skyes nas
NK076(mu)002:1175: gnyis pa dus nye ba la'ang gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1177: sbyangs pa las gzhan ba'i la la rang bzhin gyi
NK076(mu)002:1178: shes rab kyi dbang po rnon po dag /rgyu 'bras
NK076(mu)002:1179: theg pa chen pa dang chung ngu gnyis gang rung
NK076(mu)002:1181: sngar lam stegs kyi theg pa la blo ma sbyangs par theg chen la 'jug nus te /
NK076(mu)002:1182: rang bzhin chos nyid grub pa khams dwangs mi dwangs sna tshogs yod pa /
NK076(mu)002:1183: chos can rang gi ngo bos grub pa mos pa sna tshogs yod pa /
NK076(mu)002:1184: chos tsam rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa dbang
NK076(mu)002:1185: po rno rtul sna tshogs yod pas de ltar khams
NK076(mu)002:1186: dwangs theg chen la mos dbang po rnon po gsum
NK076(mu)002:1187: yod pa'i phyir na rang bzhin gyis dbang rnon grub
NK076(mu)002:1188: ste / de yang blo 'phang mtho ba nam mkha' lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:1189: mi 'gyur bar brtan pa ri bo lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:1190: shes bya kun la myur ba glog lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:1191: shes bya'i gting 'byed pas rno ba ral gri lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:1192: thams cad shes pas rgya che ba sa gzhi lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:1193: dgag sgrub dang bral bar go bas yangas pa bar snang lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)002:1194: ming 'dogs dang bral bar go bas rgya mtsho ltar
NK076(mu)002:1195: zaba pa dang bdun ldan yod pa de theg chen
NK076(mu)002:1196: la 'jug pa'i rgyu yi gang zag de nyid kyang
NK076(mu)002:1197: bdag rkyen dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK076(mu)002:1198: rgyu'i rkyen slob bu mtshan nyid bdun ldan slob bu
NK076(mu)002:1199: de yi blo che chung 'byung bas rim pas phye
NK076(mu)002:1200: bas cig char ba'i rim gyis pa rgyu 'bras kyi
NK076(mu)002:1201: theg pa chen po rnams la /
NK076(mu)002:1202: ma ngesa par 'jug pa dang cig char ba'i cig
NK076(mu)002:1203: char dang po nas ma h+aa 'di nyid du 'jug
NK076(mu)002:1204: pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1205: cig car ba'i rim gyis pa theg chen gang mos su 'jug pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1206: cig char ba'i cig char ba gdod ma nas ma h+aar 'jug pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1208: dang po 'brel ldan theg chen mjal pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1209: cig char rim gyis pa rgyu'i theg pa la zhugs pa de dang /
NK076(mu)002:1210: 'bras bu'i theg pa la zhugs pa de'ang 'brel pa
NK076(mu)002:1211: bzhi dang ldan tshul ranga gi semsa nyid khams dwangs
NK076(mu)002:1212: ba ni brtan pa'i dngos gzhi yin cing /
NK076(mu)002:1213: de 'chad byed dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams dang sems
NK076(mu)002:1214: nyid khams dang ngo bos bdag nyid gcig par 'brel
NK076(mu)002:1215: ba dang / don de dang ldan pa shes bya
NK076(mu)002:1216: yin la rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon ni shes byed
NK076(mu)002:1217: de shes bya shes byed gyis 'brel pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1218: rang bzhin bdun ldan 'di snod dang ldan pa bcud
NK076(mu)002:1219: du theg pa chen po'i lung gnyis snod dang bcud
NK076(mu)002:1221: bla ma 'gro ba'i mgon po dang /
NK076(mu)002:1222: slob ma de la thugs rje 'jug par bya ba'i las yod /
NK076(mu)002:1223: bla ma la thugs rje skye bar byed pa'i thabs yod pas las smon thugsa rjes 'brela ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:1224: 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan pa de yi phyir theg
NK076(mu)002:1225: pa mchog gi lung dbu ma dang 'bras bu khyad
NK076(mu)002:1226: par gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa rnams dang mjal
NK076(mu)002:1227: bar byed pa'i phyir 'brel pa bzhi ldan no //
NK076(mu)002:1228: gnyis pa rgyu rkyen dang ldan pas 'jug pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1229: dang po ma nges par 'jug pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1230: gong gi rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi ste drug ldan pas
NK076(mu)002:1231: rgyu dang sngags phyi pa la ma nges par 'jug
NK076(mu)002:1232: pa ni / rang gi shes rab dbang po rno
NK076(mu)002:1233: rtul gyis rim pa ji bzhin du gang la mos
NK076(mu)002:1234: pa che chung gi dge ba'i bshes dang 'phrad pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1235: pa ni / rkyen gyis / rgyu mtshan nyid theg
NK076(mu)002:1236: pa'am bya ba kri ya'am gnyis ka u pa ya'am
NK076(mu)002:1237: pa ni / rkyen gyis / / rnal 'byor yo ga'i theg para sbyor bar byed do //
NK076(mu)002:1239: de nas gong du bstan pa de bzhina rgyu rkyen drug gis 'dir ma h+aa la 'jug pa'ang /
NK076(mu)002:1240: sngana rim gyis pa'i skabs bzhin du ma h+aa la g.yo ba'i sems /
NK076(mu)002:1241: smon pa dang 'jug pa'i sems kyis ma h+aa la sbyor nas /
NK076(mu)002:1242: ma h+aa'i don shes rab gsum gyis 'di nyid la
NK076(mu)002:1243: gnas pa'i sems ngasa don de mathara phyin par byed
NK076(mu)002:1244: pa na / cig char ba'i cig char ba la ltos pas ring ba'i dus nyid da //
NK076(mu)002:1245: gnyis pa cig char ba'i cig char ba la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1246: dang po rigs ma nges pa'i sa nas ma ha la sems skye tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:1247: gong bstan ltar rigs ma nges pa bzang shos kyis
NK076(mu)002:1248: nas las dang po nyid nas gong ltar 'brel ba
NK076(mu)002:1249: bzhi rgyu rkyen drug dang ldan pas ma bcos pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1250: don rnal ma la rtogs pa'i blo 'byor pas mchog
NK076(mu)002:1251: gi theg pa ma h+aa la sbyor ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:1252: dper na mun pa'i snang ba sel ba la nyi
NK076(mu)002:1253: ma'i zer shar ba'i tshul lam r+ts+wa la me mched
NK076(mu)002:1258: mthar phyin pa'ang sngon gong du bstan bzhin yin te /
NK076(mu)002:1259: gnyis pa snod kyi yon tan dang ldan pas thos pa don du gnyer ba /
NK076(mu)002:1260: mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pa la khyad med kyang /
NK076(mu)002:1261: yang gi sgras tan+t+ra ste rgyud gsang ba snying po
NK076(mu)002:1262: yi gzhung gi le'u gsum par bshad pa ltar snod
NK076(mu)002:1263: ldan ngang tshul bzang po dge slong gsar bu'i spyod
NK076(mu)002:1265: rang bzhin bzang ba gser lta bu sogs khong nas blo brtan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1266: lus longs spyod phangs med chos phyir btang nus pa la sogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:1267: snod kyi skyon bzhi las log pa'i yon tan du
NK076(mu)002:1268: ma dang ldan pas shes rab gsum gyi bslab pa
NK076(mu)002:1269: la gnas pa'i chos nyid rang byung gi dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:1270: chen po ru 'jug pa bazha ni /
NK076(mu)002:1271: gzhung thos pa la 'jug pa mig bye ba dang 'dra /
NK076(mu)002:1272: don rtogs pas 'jug pa dkyil 'khor mthong ba dang 'dra /
NK076(mu)002:1273: goms par byed pas 'jug pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa dang 'dra /
NK076(mu)002:1274: 'bras bu thob pas 'jug pa dbang thob pa dang
NK076(mu)002:1275: 'dra ba yi yan lag bzhi'i ni don mchoga tu
NK076(mu)002:1276: gyur pa dang po thos pa ched du gnyer bar
NK076(mu)002:1277: byed pa'o // gsum pa rgyu rkyen drug med na'ang ngang gis thos pa la 'jug tshul /
NK076(mu)002:1278: gang zag rim dang cig char de gnyis kyi thos pas lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe /
NK076(mu)002:1279: rgyu gnyis dang rkyen gyis zhes rkyen bzhis don la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1280: rgyu rkyen la rag ma las pa'i rang bzhin ngang gisa don la bzod pa thob pasa /
NK076(mu)002:1281: lta ba rtogs su ra zhing 'bras bu thob par
NK076(mu)002:1282: smon pa'i semas kyis gzhung nyan pa'i brtson 'grus la
NK076(mu)002:1283: sbyor ro // gsum pa rgyu rkyen thun mong du bstan pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1284: dang po thos bsam lta ba shes pa'i rgyu ru bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1285: snod ldan gang dag thos pa'i sgo nas mnyan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1286: yid kyi bsam pa'i shes rab kyi don gnyis ka
NK076(mu)002:1287: la dpyod pa'i tshe dang por gzhung nyan cing rna
NK076(mu)002:1288: bas thos pa'i tshig blo la 'dzin pa dang don
NK076(mu)002:1290: de ltar bsam pa'i shes rab kyi tsha na'ang don la rtog cing zhib tu dpyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:1291: de ltar rtog dpyod gnyis po 'di dag lta ba shes pa'i rgyu'o //
NK076(mu)002:1292: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen /
NK076(mu)002:1293: rgyud lung man ngag bshad pa'i mkhan po ste bla
NK076(mu)002:1294: ma dam pa rgyal ba'i lung dang bla ma dam
NK076(mu)002:1295: pa'i man ngag dang bcas ngo sprad pa de ni
NK076(mu)002:1296: lta ba rtogs pa dang lhan cig tu byed pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1298: gsum pa mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK076(mu)002:1299: slob bu'i sems kyi rang bzhin la mtho brtan myur
NK076(mu)002:1300: rno rgya che yangs pa zab pa'i mtshan nyid bdun
NK076(mu)002:1301: dang ye gdod ma nas mtshungsa par ldan pa de
NK076(mu)002:1302: ni lta ba shes pa'i rgyud las dgar bas gcig
NK076(mu)002:1303: shos rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon te mtshungs ldan gyi
NK076(mu)002:1304: rgyu ru nges pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:1305: bzhi pa lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1307: de ltar rgyu rkyen dang ldana pasa shes rab kyi spyan gyis lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe /
NK076(mu)002:1308: lta ba gtan la phab pa'i tshigs rnams kyis gzhal bya gzhig cing rmala bar byas te /
NK076(mu)002:1309: don nor ba'i lta ba ngan pa rnams shes rab
NK076(mu)002:1310: zab mos phyogs re'i lta ngan dmigas ngos bzung zhing
NK076(mu)002:1311: bsal nas / don ma nor ba ma h+aa yo
NK076(mu)002:1312: ga'i grub mtha' dmigs kyis phye nas dang du blang
NK076(mu)002:1313: zhing gtan la dbab par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1314: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1315: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste rtogs par bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:1316: gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad de don gyi dmigs bzung ba /
NK076(mu)002:1317: don ma nor bar dmigs nas grub mtha' blang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:1320: gtan tshigs kyis gzhal ba'i gzhi dang 'jal byed gtan tshigas kyis gtan la dbab pa /
NK076(mu)002:1321: des gtan la phebs pa'i grub pa'i dona lta ba de grub mtha' 'o //
NK076(mu)002:1322: de ltar rnam pa gsum po de gong gi mdor
NK076(mu)002:1323: bstan pa la gsum yod pa'i snga ma'i gtan tshigs
NK076(mu)002:1324: rnams kyi gzhal ba 'dir yan lag rgyas bshad kyi
NK076(mu)002:1325: gzhi ru mdor bstan du bzhag pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1326: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:1327: dang po sngon byung dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs de kho na nyid 'jal byed dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:1328: gzhi don phyin ci ma log par yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rang byung gi ston pa /
NK076(mu)002:1329: chos sku longs sku sprul sku mngon byang rdo rje'i
NK076(mu)002:1330: sku lngasa 'dul ba'i 'khor lhun grub rig 'dzin mthar
NK076(mu)002:1331: phyin pa'am gas lnga ye shes sems dpa' sems ma'i
NK076(mu)002:1335: brjod pa tshig /dbyer med rdo rje /
NK076(mu)002:1336: rig pa byin rlabs lhun grub tu brda' sprad nas
NK076(mu)002:1337: bstan pas gzhal bya sems nyid gsung lnga lhun grub
NK076(mu)002:1338: de kho na nyid gtan tshigs gsung lnga lhun grub
NK076(mu)002:1339: kyis gtan las 'bebs shing gsung lnga lhun grub de
NK076(mu)002:1340: nyid dang blos 'jal cing don go bar byed pa'o
NK076(mu)002:1341: // gnyis pa dngos lnga de nyid tshul tshig gi gzhi byas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:1342: sku lnga'i sangs rgyas pa de nyid kyi don dngosa lnga yin la /
NK076(mu)002:1343: de dang phyogs mtshungs tshul lnga dang tshig lnga brjod
NK076(mu)002:1344: pas dngos lnga'i don mtshon tshul tshig gi gtan tshigs
NK076(mu)002:1345: 'byung ba'i gazhi'o // gsum pa dngos lnga de nyid
NK076(mu)002:1346: tshul tshig gis gtan la phab dgos par gdams pa
NK076(mu)002:1347: 'byung ba'i gazhi'o // / tshul tshig de las dang
NK076(mu)002:1348: po don gzhal bya'i gtan tshigs dngos kyi sku des
NK076(mu)002:1349: 'khor mthar lam lhan cig pa la gsung lnga yis
NK076(mu)002:1350: don dngos su brda'a sprod pa'i rgyal ba dgongs brgyud
NK076(mu)002:1351: sngon byung du sangs rgyas pa /
NK076(mu)002:1352: de'i rjes su mthun par 'jug pa'i tshul tshig gi sgo nas bstan pa la'ang /
NK076(mu)002:1353: dper na gser yin min bsregs lhad yod med bcad
NK076(mu)002:1354: bzang ngan brdar ba'i gser rtogs pa bzhina du dngos
NK076(mu)002:1355: lngas gzhal bya'i don tshul dang tshig gis legs para
NK076(mu)002:1356: brtagsa te gtan la dabba par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1357: bzhi pa tshul tshig gis gtan la dbab tshul dngos la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1360: des gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' 'o //
NK076(mu)002:1361: dang po gzhal bya brtag gzhi bstan pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1362: gzhal bya brtag gzhi ngos bzung ba /
NK076(mu)002:1365: dang po brtag pa'i gzhi ma bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1366: dngos lnga'i don de yang tshul tshig gis yongs su brtag cing dpyad par bya ba'i gzhi ni /
NK076(mu)002:1367: mig gi dbang po la sogs drug gi rten la /
NK076(mu)002:1368: gzugs la sogs pa drug yul du snang ba rnam shes drug dang bco brgyad 'di kun chos can /
NK076(mu)002:1369: de ltar yul dang dbang po rnam shes rnams sems
NK076(mu)002:1370: nyid rang snang ma gtogs de rnams rang rgyud can
NK076(mu)002:1371: du grub nas yod pa ni ma yin te dam
NK076(mu)002:1372: bca' / gtan tshigs ci'i phyir na rnal ma don
NK076(mu)002:1373: gyi kun gzhi'i rnam pa 'gag pa med par rang
NK076(mu)002:1374: 'char ba'i shesa pa rang byung gi ye shes de
NK076(mu)002:1375: bca' / nyid / phyi nang yul dang shes pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1376: dngos po sna tshogs su ma 'gags par snang bas
NK076(mu)002:1378: rang snang ngo ma shes pas 'khora ba la ngan zhen dang /
NK076(mu)002:1379: myang 'adsa la dngos por bzang zhena gyi snang ba
NK076(mu)002:1380: gnyis la gtan tshigs kyis brtag cing dpyad par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:1381: // gnyis pa de las gzhal nas brtag dpyad byed lugs /
NK076(mu)002:1382: brtag lugs la snod 'jig pa'i rten la bcud 'jig
NK076(mu)002:1383: pa brten pas 'jig rten 'di na ci yod pa
NK076(mu)002:1384: yi dngos po ka ba la sogs ming dang /
NK076(mu)002:1385: dngos po dang dngos med kyi mtshan mara 'dzin pa yi yul tha dad rnams /
NK076(mu)002:1386: de ma yin la der 'dzin gyi log rtog dug
NK076(mu)002:1387: lnga la sogs so so'i ranga mtshan zhe sngang gi
NK076(mu)002:1388: sems 'khrugs pa / spyi'i mtshan nyid mi rtag /sdug bsngal stong bdag med matshana nyid rnams /
NK076(mu)002:1389: shes bya la ji ltar gnas pa ltar brtag cing dpyad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1390: gsum pa brtags dpyad byas pas don rig tshul /
NK076(mu)002:1391: 'khor ba dang 'das pa'i dngos po gnyis su zhen
NK076(mu)002:1392: pa'i dngos po dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chosa
NK076(mu)002:1393: thams cad kun / da lta'i shes pa skad cig
NK076(mu)002:1394: ma gcig la gang gi de kun rdzogs pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:1395: thams cad kun / ro // skad cig de nyid
NK076(mu)002:1396: kyis dngosa po'i gnas lugs kun rang snang du mthong
NK076(mu)002:1397: bas yang dag pa'i don phyin ci ma log par
NK076(mu)002:1398: rig pa bzhin shes bya'i chos kun kyang gong gi
NK076(mu)002:1399: de ltar du shes shing chud par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1400: gnyis pa rtsod pa'i skyon spang tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1401: dang po the tshom gyi dogs pa gzugs pa /
NK076(mu)002:1402: zhen yul kun brtagsa yul du byed pa'i zhen byed
NK076(mu)002:1403: kyi shes pa de ni shes rab gsum gyi bar
NK076(mu)002:1404: ma bsam byung so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK076(mu)002:1406: spyir phyi'i yul rnams yod pa ma yin te dper na lus med na grib ma med pa bzhin /
NK076(mu)002:1407: gzhal bya'i yul med pasa 'jig rten 'di na ci yod pa rnams gzhal du mi btub bo //
NK076(mu)002:1408: 'o na zhen byed kyi yid rang nyid la gzhal lo zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:1409: sems skad cig ma rang gis rang la gzhal du mi btub ste /
NK076(mu)002:1410: dper na mdzub ma rang gi rtse la rang gis mi reg pa bzhin du ste /
NK076(mu)002:1411: yul yul can gnyis gzhal mi rung ba'i dogs pa skye bas na /
NK076(mu)002:1412: gnyis pa dogs pa bsal ba /
NK076(mu)002:1413: gzhan bya zhen snang rags ba thos bsam gyis dag kyang /
NK076(mu)002:1414: zhen snang phra ba'i gnyen pa lta ba ji bzhin ma rtogs pa dang /
