NK076(mu)002:1415: bsgom byung shes rab rgyud la skyes pa med pas zhen pa dag pa min cinga /
NK076(mu)002:1416: bar ma'i zhes shes rab gsum las bsam byung gi
NK076(mu)002:1417: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis gzhal ba'i yul
NK076(mu)002:1419: des na gzhal bya'i yul yod ces bya ba'i nges tshig gam sgra don 'grub bo //
NK076(mu)002:1420: gnyis pa gtan tshigs la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:1421: dngos dang tshul mthun du rtogs tshul gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK076(mu)002:1422: dngos dang tshul gyi don tshig tu ngo sprad pa tshig gi gtan tshigs so //
NK076(mu)002:1423: dang po brtags pa'i sgo nas tshul mthun du rtogs lugs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1425: gong du bshad pa de ltar dngos lnga yis gtan la phab dgos pas /
NK076(mu)002:1426: 'khor 'das kyi dngos po de de la /
NK076(mu)002:1427: 'khor 'das kyi chos de da'i ranga bzhin nam rang spyi'i mtshan nyid brtag par bya ba'ang /
NK076(mu)002:1428: gnyis pa tshul mthun rtogs tshul dngos la drug /dang
NK076(mu)002:1429: po ngo bo nyid sku'i gsung gi tshul rang gsal
NK076(mu)002:1430: ngo bo nyid kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK076(mu)002:1431: chos nyid kyi don rtogsa pa dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK076(mu)002:1432: 'byor pa blo mchog rnamas ni 'khor gyi tshul yina
NK076(mu)002:1433: la / phyi nang gi dngos po sna tshogas su
NK076(mu)002:1434: snang ba 'di sems nyid rang snang bas gasnga sngagas
NK076(mu)002:1435: kyi ngo bo de ston pa'i tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1436: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo sgro skur bral bas ngesa pa'i lung yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1437: dngos po mthong thos thams cad kyis chos tshur la ston pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1439: tshig tu ma brjod kyang brjod pa dang 'dra bar
NK076(mu)002:1440: chos nyid kyi don brda'a sprod par byed pasa na
NK076(mu)002:1441: go tshul lo // de dag ni ngo ba nyid kyi skus bshad pa dang mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1442: ma 'ongas pa'i gang zag skal ldan gyi dana du
NK076(mu)002:1443: chos nyid gtan la pheb pa'i gtan tshigs tu nges
NK076(mu)002:1444: pa'o // gnyis pa chos sku'i gsung gi tshul skye med don gyi /
NK076(mu)002:1445: yang chos sku'i tshul ni sa la gnas pa'i byang
NK076(mu)002:1446: chub sems dpa' de dang 'dra ba'i shes rab kyi
NK076(mu)002:1447: mig dang ldan pa la ni 'khor gyi tshul lo
NK076(mu)002:1448: // rang bzhin ngang ngam shugs kyis chos nyid skye
NK076(mu)002:1449: ba med pa'i don rang gi rgyud la lhun gyis
NK076(mu)002:1450: grub pa ni ston pa'i tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1451: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis ma batsala bar
NK076(mu)002:1452: rang bzhin ngang gisa skye med kyi don snang zhing
NK076(mu)002:1453: go bar byed pas na chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK076(mu)002:1454: tshul lo // skye med kyi don tshig tu brjod
NK076(mu)002:1455: pa mada pa de nyid brjod pa dang 'dra bar
NK076(mu)002:1456: go bar byed pa ni go tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1457: gsum pa longs sku'i gsung gi tshul dgongs pa brda'i /
NK076(mu)002:1458: blo dang ldan pa'i lam pa gang zag dag ni 'khor gyi tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1459: kha dog dang dbyibs la sogs pa'i gzugs kyi brda'
NK076(mu)002:1460: dang rnal 'byor pa dgongs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK076(mu)002:1461: don gyis chos ston pa ni ston pa'i tshul lo
NK076(mu)002:1462: // mig gis gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:1464: dri ro reg bya la sagas pa thams cad kyis kyang rang bzhin gyis brda'a sprod de /
NK076(mu)002:1465: dkar po nyes skyon dang bral ba la sogs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1466: dpa' bo'i zhes bla mas gdams ngag gnang skabs phyag la sogs pa'i brda'a sna tshogs dang /
NK076(mu)002:1467: bla ma dgongas pa mnyam bzhag gis ngo sprad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1468: slob bu rang gi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i stobs
NK076(mu)002:1469: kyis go brda' sprod par byed pa ni chos 'khor
NK076(mu)002:1470: go tshul lo // bzhi pa mngon byang gsung gi tshul rig pa byin rlabs kyi /
NK076(mu)002:1471: dper na sa 'og na gser yod pa'i rlangsa pa bar snang la 'ong pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1472: me long la nyi ma'i 'od phog dus ngada rang bzhin du 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:1473: 'khor 'das chos kun kyang rang riga pa'i ye shes
NK076(mu)002:1474: rang snang ba'i phyir rang bzhin ngang gis rig pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1475: drod 'byung ba ni ston pa dang 'khor ro //
NK076(mu)002:1476: ched du ma btsal bar rang bzhin ngang gis brjod 'drar snang ste chos 'khor dang go tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1477: lnga pa rdo rje sku'i gsung gi tshul grags stong dbyer med kyi /
NK076(mu)002:1478: 'khor 'das kyi chos kyi sgra skad kun kyang grag
NK076(mu)002:1479: stong dbyer med brag cha'i sgra yi rang bazhana du
NK076(mu)002:1480: gnas pa'i phyir / sgra thams cad grag stong dbyer
NK076(mu)002:1481: med du gnas pa rdo rje sku'i gsung dang tshul
NK076(mu)002:1482: mthun pa ni ston pa dang 'khor ro //
NK076(mu)002:1483: blo rab 'gas sgra thos pa tsam nyid kyis dus
NK076(mu)002:1484: de nyid du tshig don so sara ma brtags par
NK076(mu)002:1485: sems nyid dbyer med kyi go brda' 'ajala bar byed
NK076(mu)002:1486: pa ni chos 'khor dang go tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1487: drug pa sprul sku'i gsung gi tshul brjod pa tshig gi gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:1488: 'gro ba so so'i skad du don brda' sprod pa
NK076(mu)002:1489: ltar tshig gi gsung dbyangs ni 'jig rten mes po
NK076(mu)002:1490: tshangs pa'i ngag gi lta bura snyan pas 'khor mas
NK076(mu)002:1491: pas spyod pa tshogs sbyor la tshig gi sgo nas
NK076(mu)002:1492: grol ba bzhin du ngag ges brjod pa yis /
NK076(mu)002:1493: chos nyid kyi don brda'a sprod nas bu'i rgyud yongs
NK076(mu)002:1494: su grol bar byed pa ni ston 'khor chos gsum
NK076(mu)002:1495: lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1496: gnyis pa tshig gi gtan tshigs la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:1497: dang po tshig gis mtshon pa'i dgos ched ni /
NK076(mu)002:1498: gang zag las dang po'i rigs kyi shes rgyud la blo'i bye brag tha dada yod pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1499: blo che na tshul drug gang mosa kyi sgo nas grol ba yoda pa gong du bstan mod kyang /
NK076(mu)002:1500: gang zag shes rab dang blo che ba dag /tshul lnga'i gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas grol ba yod /
NK076(mu)002:1501: blo chung ba tshig gi gtan tshigs bstan pa'i phyir thos dang /
NK076(mu)002:1503: sgom pa'i shes rab gsum gyi mnyam par sbyor thabs
NK076(mu)002:1504: kyis 'bras bu rang byung gi ye shes dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:1505: mngon du gsal bas 'khor 'das kyi chos kun la
NK076(mu)002:1506: ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba'i 'bras bu 'grub bar byed
NK076(mu)002:1507: pa'i phyir / don dam par chos nyid cir yang
NK076(mu)002:1508: mi dmigsa pa'i ngang las kun rdzob tu tshig dang
NK076(mu)002:1509: yi ge blos dmigs bar snang ba yi cho 'phrul
NK076(mu)002:1510: yi ge ngang brjod pa tshig gis don chos nyid
NK076(mu)002:1511: mtshon cing go bar bya ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:1512: gnyis pa dngos tshul tshig gis rjes su mtshon par gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:1513: sku lnga lhun grub las gsung lnga dngos su thos
NK076(mu)002:1514: pa dngos lnga de dang tshul mthun du rtogs pa
NK076(mu)002:1515: yang tshul dang / dngos tshul gnyis po de'i rjes
NK076(mu)002:1516: su mthun par blo chung rnams tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs
NK076(mu)002:1517: kyis mtshon cing gtan la dbab par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1518: gsum pa tshig gi gtan tshigs dngos de la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:1519: rgyal ba sku bdun gyi dgongs pa tshig tu ngo sprad nas gtan la dbab tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:1520: de rnams kyi don mdor bsdus nas go tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:1523: yul sems ngo bo nyid rang snang du ston pa
NK076(mu)002:1524: ngo bo nyid sku'i gsung tshig /skye med rang snang
NK076(mu)002:1525: ston pa chos sku'i tshig /ldem dgongas sam brda' yi
NK076(mu)002:1526: chos nyid mtshon pa longs sku'i tshig dang /
NK076(mu)002:1527: gang zag lam la bkri zhing drang ba'i thabs su ston pa sprul sku'i tshiga /
NK076(mu)002:1528: 'doda pa rang rkyen du ston pa gsang ba sku'i tshig dang /
NK076(mu)002:1529: chos thams cad dbyer med ston pa rdo rje'i sku'i
NK076(mu)002:1530: tshig /chos thams cad rang riga pa'i mngon sum du
NK076(mu)002:1531: gasla bar ston pa mngon byang tshig gisa don mtshon
NK076(mu)002:1532: no // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la bdun /
NK076(mu)002:1533: dang po ngo bo nyid kyi gsung mtshon pa rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyi tshig ni /
NK076(mu)002:1534: 'khor 'das kyi cho thams cad sems nyid gsang sngags kyi ngo bo'i rang bzhin mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1535: de yang yod med la sogs pa'i mtha' dang de
NK076(mu)002:1536: la ltos pa'i dbus kyang grub pa med de gnyis
NK076(mu)002:1537: su med pa de bazhana nyid du snang stong dbyer
NK076(mu)002:1538: med mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du ye nas gnas
NK076(mu)002:1539: pa la dbyer med kyis mtshon pa'i dgos pa ye
NK076(mu)002:1540: shes yin pas ye shes lnga sogs rtog tshogs ye
NK076(mu)002:1541: shes su rtogs par 'dod pa'i don bya ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:1542: / mtshon tshul ye shes de nyid phyogsa bzhi dang
NK076(mu)002:1543: dbus su yang gnas pa'i sgo nas ye shes lngar
NK076(mu)002:1544: / rtogs par bya'o // de bzhin kha dog la
NK076(mu)002:1545: sogs 'byung ba 'dod na nyon mongs pa'i chos kun
NK076(mu)002:1546: la ye shes nyid de ltar du sbyor bar shes
NK076(mu)002:1547: par gyis shig /gnyis pa chos sku'i gsung mtshon ba
NK076(mu)002:1548: skye med don gyi tshig /sprul sku'i gsung ltar yi
NK076(mu)002:1550: de 'dus pa'i tshig dang de las brjod pa'i sgra'
NK076(mu)002:1551: tha snyad spangsa pa'i phyir tshig tu brjod pa mada
NK076(mu)002:1552: pa'i skye med kyi ngang du gnas pa ni mtshon
NK076(mu)002:1553: bya'i don no // de mtshon byed tshig gi gsung
NK076(mu)002:1554: nyid snang yang rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu grub pa
NK076(mu)002:1555: med para mtshon pa yi chos rnams ma lus thams
NK076(mu)002:1556: cad ye gdod ma nas skye med du dag pas
NK076(mu)002:1557: chos thams cad rnam par mi rtog pa'i thugs stong
NK076(mu)002:1558: pa nyid kyi ye shes su gyur zin pas na
NK076(mu)002:1559: de la brjod pa'i sgra dang tshig la don ji
NK076(mu)002:1560: lta ba bzhin gnas pa min no //
NK076(mu)002:1561: gsum pa mngon byang gi sku'i gsung mtshon pa rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung /
NK076(mu)002:1562: brtag bya mya ngan las 'adsa pa dang ma 'adsa
NK076(mu)002:1563: pa 'khor ba'i chos ltar snang ba thams cad kun
NK076(mu)002:1564: la / rtog byed yang dag par mngon sum du rtogs pa'i shes pas rab tu brtags na /
NK076(mu)002:1566: 'khor 'das chos rnams rang bzhin gcig tu grub pa
NK076(mu)002:1567: med pa chos dbyings ye shes so de las me
NK076(mu)002:1568: long du gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar cir yang snang
NK076(mu)002:1569: ba ni me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK076(mu)002:1570: de ltar snang bdo ba nyid na mnyam pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:1571: kyi dbyings nyid yina ta mnyam nyid ye shes so
NK076(mu)002:1572: // mtshon byed kyi tshig gis gnyis med kyi don
NK076(mu)002:1573: de ltar rtogs par byed pa'i ye shes na dus
NK076(mu)002:1574: gsum 'khor 'das kyi chos kun la ye shes des
NK076(mu)002:1575: dbang bsgyur bas na rang dbang can ni bya grub
NK076(mu)002:1576: // ye shes so // 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK076(mu)002:1577: cad tshig gi sgra yis mtshon nas gsal ba ltar
NK076(mu)002:1578: don ma 'dres par so sor rtog par gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:1579: ni sor rtog ye shes so //
NK076(mu)002:1580: de ltar ye shes su gnas pa 'di ni rang
NK076(mu)002:1581: byung gi ye shes lnga lhun grub gyi gsung mchog
NK076(mu)002:1582: yin no // bzhi pa rdo rje'i gsung mtshon pa grag stong dbyer med kyi tshig /
NK076(mu)002:1583: 'khor 'das snang grag gi chos rnams kyi nang tshan blos bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1584: sems nyid du gcig pas mtha' dang dbus gnyis med
NK076(mu)002:1585: par 'gro 'ong bral bas kun la thams cad tu
NK076(mu)002:1586: khyab la / de ltar khyab pa'i dus na'ang /
NK076(mu)002:1587: khyab bya dang khyab byed gnyis med dbyer mi phyed
NK076(mu)002:1588: pa'i rdo rje'i sku yi gsung mtshon bya don gyi
NK076(mu)002:1589: ngo bo'o // 'byung ba dang skye 'gro'i sgra skad
NK076(mu)002:1590: mi mthun pa sna tshogas par grag pa kun yang
NK076(mu)002:1591: ngo bo'o // / don dam par dngos pora grub
NK076(mu)002:1592: pa med pa las kun rdzob tu dngos pa'i sgra
NK076(mu)002:1593: sna tshogs ma 'gags par grag ste /
NK076(mu)002:1594: dpe ji ltar na pi wam de nyid skyes bu'i lag tu thogs nas brdung na /
NK076(mu)002:1595: sgra skad kyi rnam pa ni sna tshogas par 'byung
NK076(mu)002:1596: bar 'gyur na yang sgra de rgyud dang khog pa
NK076(mu)002:1597: las byung ba'i dngosa po grub pa med de grags
NK076(mu)002:1598: stong gnyis med de bzhin nyid du ston pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1599: lnga pa longs sku'i gsung mtshon pa ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig /
NK076(mu)002:1600: 'di ni dngos don dpe ru blangs pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1601: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor
NK076(mu)002:1602: dang smin pa rgya mtsho rnams la sku gong ma
NK076(mu)002:1603: de bzhin longs skus kyang gsung mchog sprul sku ltar
NK076(mu)002:1605: ji ltar ston na sku yi sgo nas chos rnams 'khor gyi blo la 'ajala bar ston te /
NK076(mu)002:1606: dper na me langa nang du gzugs brnyan bzhin du
NK076(mu)002:1607: longs sku'i sku la bltas pas shes sgrib snang ba
NK076(mu)002:1608: de rig go // drug pa sprul sku'i gsung mtshon
NK076(mu)002:1609: pa dkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig /rnam par dkar ba'i
NK076(mu)002:1610: chos rnams lhag ma ma lus pa thams cada kun
NK076(mu)002:1611: ston pa sprul skus mos spyod gdul bya la ming
NK076(mu)002:1612: dang brjod pa'i tshig tu btagsa nas ston pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1613: chos ji snyed pa mang bo'i don sgra dang tshig tu brjod kyang /
NK076(mu)002:1614: grag stong dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung la tha dad
NK076(mu)002:1615: du spros pa rdul tsam med pa ni mtshon bya'i
NK076(mu)002:1616: don no // mtshon byed tshig spros pa med ba
NK076(mu)002:1617: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yes par gsung sna tshogas
NK076(mu)002:1619: gdul bya kun gyi blo la chos nyid kyi don
NK076(mu)002:1620: brda'a 'ajala zhing gsal bar byed pas ye shes kyi
NK076(mu)002:1621: gsung yin la / gsung dus sgra dang ming dang tshig kun las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1622: sgra smras kyang nyes pa med pa'i dpe sgra thams
NK076(mu)002:1623: cad mtha'i skyon gyis ma gos pa pad+ma 'dam gyi
NK076(mu)002:1624: skyon chags shing gos meda pa lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)002:1625: bdun pa gsang ba'i sku'i gsung mtshon pa 'dod pa
NK076(mu)002:1626: rang rkyen gyi tshig ni 'dod chags bde ba nyid
NK076(mu)002:1628: de ni yab yum gyi dbang po la bo l+la
NK076(mu)002:1629: kak+ko la rnam pa gnyis phyag rgya bzhis bsrubsa pa
NK076(mu)002:1630: yisa / yum gyi mkha' la yab yum gyi thig
NK076(mu)002:1631: le nyi zla byang sems gnyis dus gcig tu 'dzom
NK076(mu)002:1632: ba'i dus bde stong gi ye shes shar ba'am 'char
NK076(mu)002:1633: yisa / ba ni / dper na mi 'jigs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1634: seng ges gcan gzan gzhan zil gyis gnon pa'i tshul
NK076(mu)002:1635: du chags rtog zil gyis mnan cing lhan skyes ye
NK076(mu)002:1636: shes bde ba mthonga bar byed pa'i rgyu mtshan de
NK076(mu)002:1637: yi phyir lhan skyes ye shes la gtan tshigas su
NK076(mu)002:1639: don mthong bar byed pa'i las la las zhes tshig tu brjod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1640: gnyis pa mdor bsdus nas go tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1642: de lta bur phye na tshig bdun yod mod kyang
NK076(mu)002:1643: de bsdu na 'og nas 'byung ba'i go tshul gnyis
NK076(mu)002:1644: te / sku bzhi dang rjes su mthun par mi dpyod pas go ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:1645: sprul sku gcig dang rjes su mthun par dpyod pas go ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:1646: rnama pa gnyis kyi tshul gyis don rtog shing mthong bar byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1647: shes rab kyi dbang po che chung gnyis dang mthun par sbyar ba'a //
NK076(mu)002:1648: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1649: sku bzhi dpyad du med pa'i go ba /
NK076(mu)002:1650: sprul sku dpyad du yod pa'i go ba'i gtan tshigs so //
NK076(mu)002:1652: dpyad du med pa'i go ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK076(mu)002:1653: rtog dpyod kyis gtan la mi phebs par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1654: ma dpyad par go ba'i dpe don dang /
NK076(mu)002:1655: go ba'i don gyi ngo bo bcings grol dang bral bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1656: de so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis go ba mchog yin par nges tshig dang bcas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1659: gzhal bya chos kun snying po byang chub yin pas dpyad du med pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1660: mdor bstan la gnyis yod pa las de la snga mas dpyad du med pa ga bar bya ba'ang /
NK076(mu)002:1661: 'gro drug gi sems can ma lus pa thams cad
NK076(mu)002:1662: kun ye gdod ma nasa byang chub snying por gnas
NK076(mu)002:1663: pas / de yi phyir na chos nyid la dpyad
NK076(mu)002:1664: pa'i bya ba'i yul dang dpyod par byed pa'i mkhan
NK076(mu)002:1666: gnyis pa dpyad du med pa'i go ba'i rgyu mtshan /
NK076(mu)002:1667: sku bzhi'i gsung ltar skabs 'dir tshig dang yi gesa kyang mi mtshona te /
NK076(mu)002:1668: rdzogs pa'i sangas rgyas kyis kyang 'di kho na'o zhes rnyed par dka' ste /
NK076(mu)002:1669: bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i sku bzhi'i sras po 'khor bzhi la bstan pa tshig tu cang mi gsung /
NK076(mu)002:1670: tshig tu ma gsungsa pa nyid kyang don rgya chera brda' 'jal nas bshad kyang /
NK076(mu)002:1671: ston pas tshig tu bshad pa dang 'khor gyis nyan pa gnyis ka meda do //
NK076(mu)002:1672: gnyis pa rtog dpyod kyis gtan la mi phebs bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1673: yin min gyi dpyod pa zhib tu zhugs na rang
NK076(mu)002:1674: las gzhan du rnam rtog rtsing na rtog pa'i gzhi
NK076(mu)002:1676: de ltar rtog pa zhugs na yul du dmigs pa'i rten yin no //
NK076(mu)002:1677: yul du dmigas pa zhugs na bdag tu 'dzina pa'i gzungsa su 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:1678: de ltar gzung 'adzana gyi mdud pas zin pa'i phyir na 'khor ba las grol bar mi 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)002:1679: gsum pa ma dpyad par go ba'i dpe don /
NK076(mu)002:1680: rtog dpyod gnyis kyis mi grol bde bas gser lta ba la gser rang ston dgos pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:1681: chos kun rig pa bdag nyid chen po rang snang
NK076(mu)002:1682: yin pa'i phyir de ltar dpyad par bya ba'i yul
NK076(mu)002:1683: dpyod par byed pa'i shes rab gnyis mi dmigs pasa
NK076(mu)002:1684: / tshig la rtog pa ste rtsing pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1685: don la dpyod pa ste zhib pas 'di ltar yin
NK076(mu)002:1686: snyam pa'i dmigas 'dzin gyi sgo nas lta ba mi
NK076(mu)002:1687: 'tshol bar / rgyal ba sku bdun gyi dgongs pa
NK076(mu)002:1688: de tshig tu brjod pa nyid kyis rgyal ba sku
NK076(mu)002:1689: bdun de nyid kyi don mthong zhing go dgos so
NK076(mu)002:1690: 'tshol bar / // bzhi pa go ba'i don gyi ngo bo bcings grol dang bral bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1691: 'ching byed kyi dgra lta bu sus kyang ma bcingas
NK076(mu)002:1692: shing bcing bar byed pa'i dngos po zhags pa lta
NK076(mu)002:1693: bu med de / bcing bar bya ba yi yul dgra brtson lta bu'ang yoda pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:1694: de ltar bacangas pa 'khor ba mada pas rnama par grol ba po yang med pas na /
NK076(mu)002:1695: 'khor ba spangs nas 'das par rgyud grol bar yang
NK076(mu)002:1696: mi 'dod pas bcingas pa dang ngang gis brala ba
NK076(mu)002:1697: yin no // lnga pa de so sor rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1698: shes rab kyis go ba mchog yin pa'i nges tshig
NK076(mu)002:1699: yin no // bcas / so sor rtog pa'i shes
NK076(mu)002:1700: rab kyis 'khor 'das kyi dngos po ganga la'ang gzhal
NK076(mu)002:1701: bya'i yul nas rtog dpyod byas pa med pas /
NK076(mu)002:1702: 'khor 'das la sogs ma brtags par so sor snang
NK076(mu)002:1703: ba yi chos kun gyi de kho na nyid don
NK076(mu)002:1704: rtogs pa'i phyir / de nyid so sor rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1705: shes rab kyi nang nas machaga gam phul du phyin
NK076(mu)002:1706: rtogs pa'i phyir / pa yin te / so sor
NK076(mu)002:1707: rtog pa'i shes rab kyis brtagsa pa med pa'i so
NK076(mu)002:1708: sor snang ba kun rtog pas /
NK076(mu)002:1709: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab mtshon pa'i bla dgas
NK076(mu)002:1710: sam dpyad du med pa'i gtan tshigs su brjod pa
NK076(mu)002:1711: yin no // gnyis pa dpyad du yod pas go ba'i gtan tshigs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1713: dpyad du med pa song nas kha cig phyi mas
NK076(mu)002:1714: dpyad du yod pas gtan tshigs kyis rgyud grol ba'am
NK076(mu)002:1715: don go bar byeda pa'ang brtag bya gong du gzhal
NK076(mu)002:1716: bya'i skabs su brjod zin pa'i 'khor 'das kyi dngos
NK076(mu)002:1717: po'i tshogs blo'i spyod yul du gyur pa rnams la
NK076(mu)002:1718: rtog dpyod rang gi so sor rtog pa'i shes rab
NK076(mu)002:1719: kyis rgyu byas / 'og gi gtan tshigs rnams gyis rkyen byas te /
NK076(mu)002:1720: gtan la dbab pa la don dang mthun pa'i gtan
NK076(mu)002:1721: tshigs kyis gtan la dbab pa dang don dang mi
NK076(mu)002:1722: mthun pa'i gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1723: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1724: tshig don mi mthun pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1727: dang po dpe nye bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1728: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma don dang mi mthun gtan
NK076(mu)002:1729: tshigs kyi dpe yang don mtshona par byed pa ltar
NK076(mu)002:1730: / dpe me chos can yod de /
NK076(mu)002:1732: mi mthun pa'i dpe chu rlangs bzhin no //
NK076(mu)002:1733: chu rlangs nas bsgrub bya me log pas /
NK076(mu)002:1734: rtags du ba ldog pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:1735: de ka mi mthun pa'i dape'o //
NK076(mu)002:1736: gnyis pa don rgyas pa la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:1737: dang po gnas lugs mtshon pa'i yul las 'das par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1738: phyi nang 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi chos nyid
NK076(mu)002:1739: phyogs cig pa'i snang stong rtag chad la sogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1740: mtha' las 'das pa la snang stong rtag chad la
NK076(mu)002:1741: sogs pa'i mtha'i rnam pa gang yanga bkag cing dor
NK076(mu)002:1742: ba med pasa / dpe 'di ltar don 'di'o zhes phyogs gcig tu bstan du meda /
NK076(mu)002:1743: de ranga gi ngo bo tshig tu bstan pa dang blos brtags par dka' 'o //
NK076(mu)002:1744: gnyis pa ji ltar mtshon pa'i dgos ched /
NK076(mu)002:1745: 'on kyang zhes mi mthun pa mthun par ston pa'i tshig yin pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1747: snang stong sogs phyogs ris su 'dzin ba'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1748: gsum pa gtan tshigs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1749: dang po kun yin gang ma yin pa'i gtan tshigs lhun grub tu bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1751: mnyam pa nyid la 'khor 'das kyi chos nyid ji ltar ming btags pa ltar grub /
NK076(mu)002:1752: yid kyis bsam pa bzhin du snang zhing rang rig
NK076(mu)002:1753: rtsal du cir yang 'gyur bas 'khor 'das phyi nang
NK076(mu)002:1754: gi dngos po kun gyi ngo bor ston cing snang
NK076(mu)002:1755: zhing / don sems nyid da mtshon cing phyogs med
NK076(mu)002:1756: kun tu rang snang bas ci yang yin pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:1757: zhing / / dper na semas kyi chos nyid la
NK076(mu)002:1758: snang stong phyogs gcig ci yang ma grub pas ma
NK076(mu)002:1760: gtan tshigs da yi phyir phyogs gcig gang yang ma
NK076(mu)002:1761: yin phyogs med kun yin pas na ci yanga yin
NK076(mu)002:1762: na 'khor 'das chos kun lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1763: gnyis pa ma spangs mi ldan gyi gtan tshigs mtha' bral du bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1764: rang byung gi ye shes snang stong sogs mtha' kun
NK076(mu)002:1765: gyi phyogs dang ris su rgya ma chad pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:1766: / snang stong phyogs de'i mtha' kun dang brala la /
NK076(mu)002:1767: phyogs med du rang snang bas mtha' kun gyi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ma bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:1768: des na snang stong la sogs pa'i mtha' gang yang
NK076(mu)002:1769: ma spangsa pas na phyogs gcig gang yang mi ldan
NK076(mu)002:1770: pas so // mtha' kun sems nyid du rang snang
NK076(mu)002:1771: bas ma bral ba'i phyir de bas na phyogs re'i
NK076(mu)002:1772: mtha' thams cad dang bral zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1773: bzhi pa gtan tshigs kyis gtan la 'bebs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:1774: de ltar sems kyi chos nyid kyi ngo bos zhes
NK076(mu)002:1775: nges bzung gi sgo nas gtan la phebas pasa na
NK076(mu)002:1777: gnyis pa tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la spyi phyir 'jug bsdu gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1778: dang po spyir bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1779: tshig don mi mthun pa las dgar bas cig shos
NK076(mu)002:1780: su gyur pa tshig don mthun par ston pa'i tshig
NK076(mu)002:1782: bye brag tu phye na gtan tshigs bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod kyang /
NK076(mu)002:1783: mdor bsdus pas gtan tshigs kun la khyab pa ni
NK076(mu)002:1784: lung man ngag rig pa tshad ma gsum yin te
NK076(mu)002:1785: / tshad ma gsum po de dag dang ldana pa
NK076(mu)002:1786: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs kyi rnam grangs su
NK076(mu)002:1787: brjod pa bsam yas pa yod na'ang /
NK076(mu)002:1788: 'dir de dag gi cha gcig tsam tshig du brjod
NK076(mu)002:1789: pa 'og nas 'byung ba'i 'di lta bu yin moda
NK076(mu)002:1790: / gnyis pa bye brag so sor bshad pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1792: sgra mthun don spags gtan tshigs so //
NK076(mu)002:1794: dang po dag pa bzhi dang gsum gyi gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:1795: 'khor 'das bden gnyis rgyu 'bras kyi chos rnams rang
NK076(mu)002:1796: bzhin yanga gisa rnam par dag pa ya don ni
NK076(mu)002:1797: / rnam pa bzhi'i tshul gyis don rtogs shing mngona du byed do //
NK076(mu)002:1800: rgyu rnams rab tu dag pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:1801: 'bras bu yongs su dag gyur te //
NK076(mu)002:1802: don dam dmigs med rang bzhin dag /kun rdzob sgyu mar ye nas dag /ces pas /
NK076(mu)002:1803: rgyu 'byung ba lnga sems su dag pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1804: 'bras bu dam rdzas lnga rigs lngar dag pa /
NK076(mu)002:1805: don dam dmigs med du dag pa /
NK076(mu)002:1806: kun rdzob sgyu mar dag pa'i tshul lo /
NK076(mu)002:1808: snod 'byung ba lnga yum lngar dag pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1809: bcud phung po lnga rigs lngar dag pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1810: sems kyi rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyis bsdus pa
NK076(mu)002:1811: rnamas ye shes lngar dag pa la dag pa ltar
NK076(mu)002:1812: rtogsa shing gtan la phab pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1813: gnyis pa mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:1814: thun mong gi mnyam gnyis ni mdo sde dang sgo bstun pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1815: don dam skye med du mnyam /
NK076(mu)002:1817: de las lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis ni /
NK076(mu)002:1818: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes su mnyam pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1819: don dam dkor bdun du mnyam pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1820: de ltar lhag pa'i bden gnyis dbyer med kyis sku
NK076(mu)002:1821: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du spyod yul yongs
NK076(mu)002:1822: su dag pa ni kun tu bazanga po'i zhing khams
NK076(mu)002:1823: zhes bya'o // gsum pa rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs la /
NK076(mu)002:1824: rim gyi dang cig char ltar bshad pa gnyis las /
NK076(mu)002:1826: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams su zhen pa gzhal bya /
NK076(mu)002:1827: rgyu gciga pa gtan tshigs dang /
NK076(mu)002:1828: don dam skye med du rtogs pas /
NK076(mu)002:1829: dngos po'i mtshan 'dzin gyi zhen pa las grol ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:1830: gsung gi yi ge a sku'i o /
NK076(mu)002:1831: thugs kyi ste yig 'bru'i tshul du gtan la phab pa'i gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:1832: kun rdzob lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor rtogs pa grub /
NK076(mu)002:1833: des stong pa phyang chad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa grol /
NK076(mu)002:1834: rtogs pa snga ma gnyis su zhen pa gzhal bya /
NK076(mu)002:1835: phyin gyis brlabs pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK076(mu)002:1836: bden gnyis tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa grol pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1837: dbyer med du rtogs pa la zhen pa gzhal bya mngon sum pa yi gtan tshigs kyis /
NK076(mu)002:1838: bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod yul du byed pa'i zhen pa grol ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:1839: gnyis pa cig char du bshad na /
NK076(mu)002:1840: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad rgyu ma rig pa la
NK076(mu)002:1841: gcig 'das pa'i chos thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK076(mu)002:1842: su rgyu gcig /de ltar bden pa gnyis ka rang
NK076(mu)002:1843: byung ye shes su rgyu gcig pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:1844: rgyu gciga pa de nyid rang snang la don ma skyes ming 'gag med dang /
NK076(mu)002:1845: rtags sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dbyer med yiga 'abru gsum pa'i tshul du mtshon pa /
NK076(mu)002:1846: phung po rnam shes 'byung ba'i chos thams cad sku
NK076(mu)002:1847: dang ye shes su byin gyis brlabs pa'i don dang
NK076(mu)002:1848: dbyer med du rtogs pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:1849: de nyid blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba rang rig pas mangna sum du rtogs pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:1850: de ltar gtan tshigs kyis rab tu rtogsa pa rnam pa bzhi yis /
NK076(mu)002:1851: phyi nang gi chos thams cad rang rig pa'i ye
NK076(mu)002:1852: shes mngona sum du gsal bar rdzogas shing rig pa
NK076(mu)002:1853: la rang dbang bsgyur bas na rgyal po ste /
NK076(mu)002:1854: phyi rgyud man chad las khyad par 'phags pas na 'di bas che ba'i grub mtha' gzhan med do //
NK076(mu)002:1855: bzhi pa dag pa gsum dang bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:1856: chos kun rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nyid la nyid kyis dbang bsgyur /
NK076(mu)002:1857: rang byung gi ye shes nyid la nyid longs spyod pa'i phyir bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs te /
NK076(mu)002:1858: bdag gi phung po lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:1859: gzhan 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:1860: rtog pa'i rgyun ngar 'dzin pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad po rnams /
NK076(mu)002:1863: ye shes lngar rnam par daga /rang rig mngon sum
NK076(mu)002:1864: pas rtogs pa ni bla na meda pa'i gsang sngags
NK076(mu)002:1865: rdo rje theg pa'i mchog ma h+aa yo ga'i lta
NK076(mu)002:1866: ba'o // lnga pa rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:1867: dang po rang bzhin snang stong dbyer med du bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1868: mya ngan 'das pa dang ma 'das pa'i chos ma lus pa thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:1869: don dam gsum mngon du byed pa'i yang dag pa'i shes pas rab tu brtags na /
NK076(mu)002:1870: don dam par spyod yul dang bral bas rang bzhin
NK076(mu)002:1871: med pa las kun rdzob tu yul med rang gsal
NK076(mu)002:1872: bar cir yang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:1873: kun rdzob tu ji ltar snang ba yi dus nyid
NK076(mu)002:1874: na don dam mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings nyid las
NK076(mu)002:1875: g.yos ba med pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:1876: gnyis pa 'khor 'das ngo bo gnyis med du bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1877: de bzhin gshegas pa'i sku ye shes sgyu mar dag
NK076(mu)002:1878: pa'i ngo la snang ba mya ngan las 'das pa
NK076(mu)002:1879: dang / de ma yin la der 'dzin pa'i log
NK076(mu)002:1880: rtog sgyu mar snang ba gnyis ka sems nyid kyi
NK076(mu)002:1881: ngo bor brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba
NK076(mu)002:1882: med de rang bzhin gyis stong pa la mya ngan
NK076(mu)002:1883: las 'das pa'i rigas dang 'khor ba'i rgyud tha dad
NK076(mu)002:1884: du brtag tu med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:1885: gsum pa rang bzhin chos sku lhun grub tu bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1886: don dam 'khor 'das zhes so so'i rigs tha dang
NK076(mu)002:1887: dang kha daga dang dbyibs tha dad med pa lasa
NK076(mu)002:1888: / kun rdzob tu phyi nang snod bcud dang 'das
NK076(mu)002:1889: pa'i theg pa mtho dman thams cad ma 'gags par
NK076(mu)002:1890: / snang ba'o // snang ba yi dus nyid na
NK076(mu)002:1891: grub pa med pa de nyid la chos kyi sku
NK076(mu)002:1892: / snang ba'o // zhes bya'o // phyogs med cir
NK076(mu)002:1893: yang 'gyur zhing ye shes rang snang du cir snang
NK076(mu)002:1894: thams cad grub pa ste phyogs med du lhun gyis
NK076(mu)002:1895: / snang ba'o // zhes bya'o // grub pa'o // gnyis pa sgra mthun don spags la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:1896: dang po rang spyi'i gtan tshigs de'i go don ni /
NK076(mu)002:1897: de la nyon mongas pa rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:1898: spyir bstan pa yi mtshan nyid gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1899: khyad par spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid ma nor
NK076(mu)002:1900: bar don rtogs na nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par
NK076(mu)002:1901: byang ba'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam du 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:1902: ba'o // nyon mongs lam du 'gyur ba de yi phyir khyad par rang dang spyi'i gtan tshigas te /
NK076(mu)002:1903: snyigs ma'i gdul bya rnams la shin tu gces so //
NK076(mu)002:1904: gnyis pa mtha' bral gyi gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:1905: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid la yod med rtag chad la sogs pa'i mtha' ste ngan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1906: dbus te bzang po med cing gcig dang du mar brala la /
NK076(mu)002:1907: gcig dang du mar gang du yang grub ba ma
NK076(mu)002:1908: yin te gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid bden
NK076(mu)002:1909: pa dbyer med pa yi tshul de lam pas rtogsa
NK076(mu)002:1910: pa'i phyir / phyogs re ba'i mtha' dang dbus bral ba'ang sngar rang spyi bstan pa de bzhin no //
NK076(mu)002:1911: gsum pa rnam par dbye ba'i gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:1912: 'bras bu'i gzugs kyi 'byung gnas yin pas 'byung ba rags shing dbang che bas chen pa /
NK076(mu)002:1913: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' dang lnga rnams la /
NK076(mu)002:1914: rang rgyud par 'dzin pa'i rang bzhin grub pa med
NK076(mu)002:1915: par gtan tshigs kyis gzhig bar bya ba'i dgos ched
NK076(mu)002:1916: yod pa'i phyir / sa la sogs pa gcig la'ang 'byung ba lnga /
NK076(mu)002:1917: re re la'ang 'byung ba lnga lngara snang ba'i dbang gis nyi shu rtsa lngar dbya bar bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:1918: des na sems can gyi las snang phyogs gcig ma
NK076(mu)002:1919: grub pa mum gyi yi ges mtshon pa mnyam pa
NK076(mu)002:1920: nyid kyi dbyingsa dang gnyis su med pa bstim para
NK076(mu)002:1921: bya / mum gyis mtshon pa'i dbyings de nyid ngag
NK076(mu)002:1922: gi smra ba dang yid kyis bsam brjod kyi yul
NK076(mu)002:1923: bya / las 'das so // bzhi pa mtshon pa dpe'i gtan tshig la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:1925: dper na nam mkha' la dbyibs kha dog sogs ngos bzung du med de /
NK076(mu)002:1926: de dag thams cad dang bral ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:1927: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyang da dang 'dra la /
NK076(mu)002:1928: sa yi ngo bo sra zhing brtan pa sa thams cad skyed pa'i las byed pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:1929: don sems kyi chos nyid rang snang du bskyed cing thams cad kyi rten byed pa /
NK076(mu)002:1930: chu phan tshun du drang btub pas mnyen zhing /
NK076(mu)002:1931: byed las dri ma 'khru ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:1932: sems nyid rtogs pas gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma 'khru ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:1933: rlung gi ngo bo kha dog dbyibs kyi ngos gzung du med pa yangs shing g.yo ba rlung ltar /
NK076(mu)002:1934: sems nyid ngos bzung med pa cir yang 'char bar shes par bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:1935: me 'od gsal zhing byed las bud shing me yis thams cad sreg pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:1936: sems nyid gsal zhing nyon mongs rnam rtog gi mtshan ma sreg pa ma ltar shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1937: 'byung lnga'i dpe don ltar sems nyid mtshon pa de bzhina phung pa la'ang gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1941: gzugs kyis snang stong dbyer med mtshon pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1942: tshong bas myong stong mtshon pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1943: 'du shes kyis mtshan mar 'dzin stong dbyer med dang /
NK076(mu)002:1944: 'du byed kyis dran rtog dran stong dbyer med mtshon pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1945: rnam shes kyis rig stong dbyer med mtshon pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1947: gzugs phung 'jig pa ltar don kyang phyogs ris thams cad phyogs med du 'jig pa /
NK076(mu)002:1948: tshor ba nyams su myong ltar chos nyid kyang myong ba med pa'i myong ba /
NK076(mu)002:1949: 'du shes mtshan mar 'dzin pa ltar chos nyid mtshan ma med pa'i mtshan mar 'dzin pa /
NK076(mu)002:1950: 'du byed sems mngon par 'du byed pa ltar sems kyi chos nyid mngon du byed pa /
NK076(mu)002:1951: rnam shes kyis rnam par rig pa ltar chos nyid ngang gis rang rig pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1952: sems dbang po lnga dang 'dra ste /
NK076(mu)002:1953: mig gi dbang pos rang rig rang snang gi gzugs 'dzin mthong bar byed /
NK076(mu)002:1954: rna dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi sgra thos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1955: sna dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi dri tshor bar byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1956: lce dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi ro myong bar byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:1957: lus dbang gis rang rig rang snang gi reg par mtshon pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:1958: de rnams ming tsam las snang la rang rgyud pa med do //
NK076(mu)002:1959: yul lnga gzugs sgra dri ro reg sna tshogs su snang la rang bzhin med par shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1960: nyon mongas 'dod chags zhe sngang gti mug nga rgyal phrag dog lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:1961: kha dog dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ga lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:1962: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga la sogas pa thams cad
NK076(mu)002:1963: rang snang tsam du mtshon cing so sor rgyas par
NK076(mu)002:1965: gnyis pa dpe don rtogs pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1966: dpe de rnams kyang bsgrub bya'i don dang sgrub byed
NK076(mu)002:1967: kyi gtan tshigs gnyis ngo bo gcig kyang mtshon tshul
NK076(mu)002:1968: ma 'dres pas gtan tshigs de yi phyir mtshon pa
NK076(mu)002:1969: dpe'i gtan tshigs de yis chos nyid kyi don phyogs
NK076(mu)002:1970: re mtshon cing rtogsa par byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:1971: gsum pa gang nas gtan la phab kyang don gtan la phebs pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:1972: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigas dang /
NK076(mu)002:1973: sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigas brjod pa rnams
NK076(mu)002:1974: bsgrub bya grub mtha'i ngo bo gang yin pa shes
NK076(mu)002:1975: pa'i don gtan la pheb par byed pa la /
NK076(mu)002:1976: dag mnyam la sogs ngesa tshig gi sgo nas gtan dbab dang /
NK076(mu)002:1977: bdag nyid chen po la sogs ngo bo'i sgo nas dang /
NK076(mu)002:1978: rang spyi'i mtshan nyid kyi sgo nas la sogas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:1979: khongs su rang bzhin dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs dang
NK076(mu)002:1980: / de ltar gtan tshigs kyi sgo gang nas gtan
NK076(mu)002:1981: la 'bebas kyang grub mtha' mnyam pa nyid kyi don
NK076(mu)002:1982: rgyas par rtogs shing khong du chud par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1983: gsum pa mjug bsdus te bstan pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:1984: dang po lta ba shes pa'i dam tshig dang ldan dgos par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:1985: phyogs 'dzin gyi zhen pa thams cad gtan tshigs kyis
NK076(mu)002:1986: 'jig par byed pa ste dag mnyam las mi 'da'
NK076(mu)002:1988: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba rtogs thabs rnams las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshiga dang ldana para bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:1989: gnyis pa don tshig dang bral bar go bar gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:1990: mtshon bya'i chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus pa
NK076(mu)002:1991: kun gyi don go bar 'byung ba'ang gang zhe na
NK076(mu)002:1992: / mtshon byed lung man ngag gi tshiga gis don
NK076(mu)002:1993: mtshon par nus pa las don de gzhan du gud
NK076(mu)002:1995: tshig gi sgra de nyid don gyi dngos po'am ngo bo min te /
NK076(mu)002:1996: tshig blo'i yul du gyur kyang don blo'i spyod yul mi 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:1997: sgra don tha dad ce na mtshon bya'i don de nyid mtshon byed tshig gi sgra las /
NK076(mu)002:1998: mtshon dgos pas de las gzhan don gud na ci yang meda do //
NK076(mu)002:1999: don gtan la dbab tshe btags pa'i manga /
NK076(mu)002:2000: mtshon pa'i tshiga /brjod pa'i sgra tsam la mi brten para /
NK076(mu)002:2001: rang gi blo yi gting du mnyam pa nyid the
NK076(mu)002:2002: tshom med par go zhing rtogs par byos zhes so
NK076(mu)002:2003: // gsum pa grub mtha' dang 'di sngar gyi mdor
NK076(mu)002:2004: bstan snga ma'i sa bcad gnyis pa mdor bstan phyi
NK076(mu)002:2005: ma'i gsum par bsnan pa'i bzhi pa yin /
NK076(mu)002:2007: bzhi pa gol sgrib thun mong ston pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2009: gsum pa grub mtha' dang bzhi pa gol sgrib ston
NK076(mu)002:2010: pa'i lus rnams bzhag gi don brjod par bya ba
NK076(mu)002:2011: ni / gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2012: dang po rtogs pa'i grub mtha' /
NK076(mu)002:2013: gsang sngagas theg pa mchog gyur bla na meda pa ma h+aa'i grub mtha'i don ni /
NK076(mu)002:2014: yod med kyi mtshan ma bzang ngan kun tu blos
NK076(mu)002:2015: mi brtag para dbyer med chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang
NK076(mu)002:2016: du shes bya'i chos thams cad ro gcig par shes
NK076(mu)002:2017: nas / 'khor 'das chos kun kyang mnyam pa nyid yina par rtogs pasa /
NK076(mu)002:2018: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba'i yon tan dang /
NK076(mu)002:2019: 'jiga rten pa'i lta ba skyon can te so so'i
NK076(mu)002:2020: lta ba mi mthun par tha dad par brjod cing
NK076(mu)002:2022: 'og ma'i skyon dgag cing gong ma'i yon tan blang bar bya ba yang mina /
NK076(mu)002:2023: gnyis pa nor ba'i shes rab kyi dmigs bsal ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2025: spyir ni gnas lugs de ma yin pa'i der 'dzin loga rtog gi blo bsam yas pa 'di rnams /
NK076(mu)002:2026: ye gdod ma nyid nas gzhi la yod pa ma yin ta /
NK076(mu)002:2027: ci las byung na 'gro ba so so'i gzung 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:2028: gyi rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags kya phyi gzung
NK076(mu)002:2029: yul nang 'dzin gyi dra bas don la bsgribsa par
NK076(mu)002:2030: gyur te / sems nyid la phyogs ris ci yang
NK076(mu)002:2031: min pa las blo rnam rtog gis cir yang snang
NK076(mu)002:2032: gyur te / ba ni / byang chub bde gshegs
NK076(mu)002:2033: snying po'i gzhi don las rang ngo ma shes nas
NK076(mu)002:2034: gyur te / ba ni / gol ba'o // gnyis pa gol pa'i ngo bo dngos la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2039: mu stegs pa'i lta bar gol ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2042: dang po 'khrul pa sgrub byed 'thad pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:2044: bdena par grub pa min te gzung 'dzin gyis ma grol ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2045: las nyon gyis bcingas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2046: skye rga na 'chi bzhi'i dus kya dgras 'jomas pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2047: mi bden cing bslus pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2048: dang mi rtag par 'gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK076(mu)002:2049: 'phags pa'i lam thabs shes rab bral ba'i phyir dang /
NK076(mu)002:2050: thar dka' ba 'khor ba'i brtson rang chud pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2051: sdug bsngal myong yang gnyen pos mi 'jila te rigs pa gtan tshigs dgus phyir 'khrul ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2054: dgu zhes mang tshig kun la sbyor phyir na 'khrul lo //
NK076(mu)002:2055: gnyis pa lam rgyud lngar gol ba sbyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:2056: de bas na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam
NK076(mu)002:2057: pa nyid kyi don 'ga' tsam yang ma rtogsa pas
NK076(mu)002:2058: / nyon mongs dug lnga rang rgyud bar 'chola nyog spyod bas 'gro ba lam rgyud lngar 'khora ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2059: gsum pa khams gsum lha mir gol ba bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:2060: dang po 'dod khams lha mir gol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2061: mi dge bcu spangs te dge bcu dag la gtso bor dang du len cing /
NK076(mu)002:2062: dge bas mtho ris dang mi dge bas ngan song 'gro zhing dge sdig rgyu 'bras mi mnyam pas /
NK076(mu)002:2063: mi dge spangs dge bcu bsgrubs pas 'dod lha dang mi yi skye gnas su skyes te /
NK076(mu)002:2064: mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs pas 'dod khams su 'khor ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2065: gnyis pa gzugs khams gol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2066: 'khor 'das dbyer med mnyam pa'i don nyid ma rtogs
NK076(mu)002:2067: shinga ge bcu'i steng du byams snying rje dga' ba
NK076(mu)002:2068: btang snyoms te tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan bzhi
NK076(mu)002:2069: yi dang po la rtog dbyod me lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:2071: rtog pa med pa spyod pa tsam /
NK076(mu)002:2073: btang snyoms gnyis par dga' bde chu lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:2074: gsum par dbugs 'byung rdub rlung lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:2075: bzhi pa la skyon brgyad dang bral ba'i zhi gnas dwangs cha dang /
NK076(mu)002:2076: de ltar rim par so sor ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pas bdag tu 'dzin pa dang ma bral canga /
NK076(mu)002:2077: rang rang gi gzugsa gsal thog gi ting 'dzin nyams
NK076(mu)002:2078: myong rnams kun la nga'am bdag tu rtog cing 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:2079: pa bcas 'di ni tshangs gnas la sogs gnas rim
NK076(mu)002:2080: bcu bdun du rim par skye ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:2081: gsum pa gzugs med du gol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2082: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid dang gzugsa med 'khor ba'i chos yin par ma rtogs nas /
NK076(mu)002:2083: tshor 'du 'du byed rnam shes te ming bzhi pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2084: phung po cha la bdag med par ma shes te
NK076(mu)002:2088: yod min med min gyi skye mched kyi bsam gtan
NK076(mu)002:2089: bzhi la blo gnas par gyur na de dag /srid
NK076(mu)002:2090: pa'i rtse mo'i ste kun gzhi rtog med bsgoms pas
NK076(mu)002:2091: skye mched mu bzhi'i sa ru skya ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2092: gnyis pa mu stegs lta bar gol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2093: mu stegs rtag lta ba ni rang bzhin rtag par 'dod pa grangs can pa /
NK076(mu)002:2094: rig pa rtag par 'dod pa tshangs pa /
NK076(mu)002:2095: byed po rtag par 'dod pa dbang phyug dang /
NK076(mu)002:2096: khyab 'jug /rdul phran rtag par 'dod pa bye brag pa dang bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:2097: chad lta ba ni tshe snga phyi las rgyu 'bras med par 'dod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2098: rtag chad gnyis kar gang zag gi blo zhen pa de dag ni /
NK076(mu)002:2099: chos thams cad don bcud gyi snying po gzhi don
NK076(mu)002:2100: byang chub nyid las gol bar sangs rgyas kyis gsungs
NK076(mu)002:2101: so // gsum pa zhor la la bzla ba /
NK076(mu)002:2103: gzugs med bzhi ste sa dgu po de'i zhen pa dag pa'i don gnyis med kyi ya shes ni /
NK076(mu)002:2104: sa dgu'i snang ba ma spangs par chos nyid mnyam
NK076(mu)002:2105: pa nyid kyi gnas su dag pa'am dang du bacama
NK076(mu)002:2106: mo // gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg par gol ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2108: sngags phyi pa'i theg par gol pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2110: dang po nyan thos kyi theg par gol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2111: 'khor 'das sam bden bzhi gnyis su meda pa'i don
NK076(mu)002:2112: ma rtogas pa'i nyan thos ni 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK076(mu)002:2113: thams cad la 'khor ba'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal /
NK076(mu)002:2116: rgyu lam gyi bdena pa dang bzhi'i dngos pa grub par yod par lta zhing /
NK076(mu)002:2118: 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras mi spong par dang len byed bar gyur pa na /
NK076(mu)002:2119: de lta bu 'di na bden bzhi nyan cing thosa
NK076(mu)002:2120: pa'i thos sgrogs pa'i sa pa zhes par gol ba
NK076(mu)002:2121: yin no // gnyis pa rang rgyal theg par gol ba la /
NK076(mu)002:2122: dge sngig btang snyoms las gsum dang nyon mongas lnga'i
NK076(mu)002:2123: rten 'brel gyi chos thams cada la gsang sngags ltar
NK076(mu)002:2124: chos nyid mnyam pa'i don chen po nyid du mi
NK076(mu)002:2125: shes shing / nang rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni /
NK076(mu)002:2148: de ltar rten 'brel lugs 'byung ldog gnyis yoda par 'dzin pas na /
NK076(mu)002:2149: de lta bu'i gang zag 'di ni rang sangas rgyas kyi theg pa'i sa la gol ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2150: gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg par gol ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2151: dang po byang chub sems dpa' rang gi 'dod gzhung /
NK076(mu)002:2152: bden gnyis dbyer med mnyam pa'i dona chos nyid lta bas ngo mi shes shing /
NK076(mu)002:2154: so skyes snang ba log pa'i kun rdzob /
NK076(mu)002:2155: 'phags pa'i rjes snang yang dag kun rdzob dang gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2157: don byed nus ldan yang dag dang /
NK076(mu)002:2158: don byed mi nus log pa'i kun rdzob bo /
NK076(mu)002:2159: don dama pa'i bden pa la'ang /
NK076(mu)002:2160: blo rigs shes kyis don dam brtags pa /
NK076(mu)002:2161: 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag gi ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa dang gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2162: de ltar bden pa gnyis tha dad du 'byed par byed pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:2163: de yang don dam phra ba chos kyi bdag dang /
NK076(mu)002:2164: rags pa gang zag gi bdag dang gnyis ka med par 'dod pas na /
NK076(mu)002:2165: de ltar 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i sa pa zhes bya bar gol ba yina /
NK076(mu)002:2166: gnyis pa de las gsang sngags thabs kyi theg pa khyad par du spags pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2167: bden gnyis kyi khyad par spags tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:2168: lta spyod dbyer med kyi spags tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:2170: dang po byang sems kyi kun rdzob kyi 'dod gzhung /
NK076(mu)002:2171: nyan rang las 'phags pa'i bla na med pa'i theg pa'i nang nasa theg chen byang chub sems na /
NK076(mu)002:2172: chos nyid don dam stong pa'i ngang du ni yod
NK076(mu)002:2173: med sogs sngar gyi chos thams cad dbyer med de
NK076(mu)002:2174: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du snang ba thams cad
NK076(mu)002:2175: la / don byed nus pa yang dag dang don
NK076(mu)002:2176: byed mi nus pa ma dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2177: la / kar 'dzin no // gnyis pa sngags kyi bden gnyis spags tshul /
NK076(mu)002:2178: nyon mongs pa thabs kyis mi 'ching ba'i gsang sngags
NK076(mu)002:2179: thabs mkhas kyi theg pa rnal 'byor chen pa ma
NK076(mu)002:2181: rnam par byang ba mya ngan las 'das pa dang
NK076(mu)002:2182: kun nas nyon mongs shing sdug bsngal 'khor ba'i chos
NK076(mu)002:2183: dag don dam dkor bdun dang /
NK076(mu)002:2184: phung khams skye mched kun rdzob tu yang skra dang
NK076(mu)002:2185: ye shes dbyer med pa'i bdag nyid de byang sems
NK076(mu)002:2186: ma h+aa yo ga gnyis lta ba mtho dman gyi
NK076(mu)002:2188: gnyis pa lta spyod dbyer med kyi spags tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2190: nang pa thabs kyis 'phags pa gsang sngags kyi lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2191: ya mi bral ba'i spyod pa gnyis gzhan las khyad par gyur pa chen po na /
NK076(mu)002:2192: bla na med pa'i theg pa byang sems las khyad par 'aphagas pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2194: gnyis pa rgyas pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:2195: dang po lta ba chos kun dbyer med mngon sum du rtogs ba'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:2196: byang sems dbu ma'i don dam stong pa phyogs gcig pa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:2197: ma has rnam kun mchog ldan don dam du ni dkor bdun gyis 'phags pa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:2198: kun rdzob tsam du ni ma h+aas phung khams skye
NK076(mu)002:2199: mched thams cad sku dang ye shes su mnyam zhing
NK076(mu)002:2200: 'bras bu lus pa med pa rdzogs pas spags so
NK076(mu)002:2201: // de ltar dbyer med yang dag pa'i don rtogs
NK076(mu)002:2202: pa'i skyes bu mchog gam dam par gyur pa yis
NK076(mu)002:2203: // / shes bya don dam kun rdzoba gnyis tshig
NK076(mu)002:2204: tha dad la don la dbyer med par phyin ci
NK076(mu)002:2205: ma log par yang dag pa nyid du blos gteng
NK076(mu)002:2206: phyin par rab tu rtogs pas byang sems bden gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2207: // / las 'phags so // gnyis pa spyod pa
NK076(mu)002:2208: mnyam nyid las ma g.yos shing cir yang ston pa
NK076(mu)002:2210: med mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos bzhin
NK076(mu)002:2211: spyod pa'i bye brag ma 'gags pa'i thabs kyis don
NK076(mu)002:2212: las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgya spang blang las 'das
NK076(mu)002:2213: pa chena por ston pas spags so //
NK076(mu)002:2214: gsum pa lta spyod gnyis med dag pa chen por bstan pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2215: dang po thabs shes gnyis med rnam dag tu bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:2216: spyod pa thabs dang lta ba shes rab gnyis su
NK076(mu)002:2217: med cing rnam par dag pas theg pa 'og ma
NK076(mu)002:2218: las spags so // gnyis pa de nyid gnyis med rnam dag chen por la bzla ba /
NK076(mu)002:2219: phung khams sogs chos thams cad rnam par dag cesa bya ba de yang /
NK076(mu)002:2220: snang ba'i dngos pa spang 'gog sbyong ba'i thabs kyis bsal nas dag pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2221: snang bdo ba spyod bdo ba'i dus nyid na sku dang ye shes su rnam par dag pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2222: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir na kun rdzoba kyi snang ba
NK076(mu)002:2223: rdzun pa kho na yang mi blta ba ste snang
NK076(mu)002:2224: ba mi spar phyir spags pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2225: gnyis pa sngags phyi par gol ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2226: dang po kri yar gol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2227: 'khor 'das gnyis meda mnyam par lhun grub kyi don ma shesa pas /
NK076(mu)002:2228: don dam du skye 'gag dang gcig du ma mtha'
NK076(mu)002:2229: bzhi'i dri ma dag pa chosa nyid tsam de nyid
NK076(mu)002:2232: sor rtog bya grub ye shes bzhi ru shar ba'i
NK076(mu)002:2233: yona tan la kun rdzob rigs gsum lha yi dkyil
NK076(mu)002:2235: ye shes pa la dngos grub res 'jog bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:2236: byed cing lus ngag gi khrus dang gtsang sbra'i bya
NK076(mu)002:2237: ba las kyi sgo nas 'bras bu grub par 'dod
NK076(mu)002:2238: pa kri ya'i sa ste der gol ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2239: gnyis pa yo gar gol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2240: 'khor 'das dbyer med lhun grub mnyam pa chen po'i don ma mthong bas /
NK076(mu)002:2241: 'khor 'das chosa kun skye 'gag med pa'i rnam dag ste /
NK076(mu)002:2242: de rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi byin rlabs kun rdzob
NK076(mu)002:2243: lha rdo rje dbyings kyi lha so bdun sogs sprul
NK076(mu)002:2245: lha rtog gam dkar gsum sogs dam rdzas la blang
NK076(mu)002:2246: dor byed cing dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gtsor ston
NK076(mu)002:2247: pas rnal 'byor te yo ga'i sa la gol ba'o
NK076(mu)002:2248: // chos rnams kun gyi gzhi ma lus pa thams cad la /
NK076(mu)002:2249: lta bas bya lam rjes med ltar nam mkha' la rgyun du gacada bzhina gyis /
NK076(mu)002:2250: nyon mongs nyid dam spyod pas 'dzin chags ma lus thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:2251: thogs pa med pa mkha' la rlung chena po 'phya ba bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:2252: bsgom bas yid kyi rtog tshogs chags pa ma lus pa /
NK076(mu)002:2253: nyam nga med pas chu bo la nya chen 'phya ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:2254: rnal 'byor pas lta ba sgom pa spyod pa de ltar ltos zhes pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2255: gsum pa don ma nor bar dmigs nas grub mtha' blang ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2257: gong du bstan pa da ltar gzhal bya 'khor 'das
NK076(mu)002:2258: kyi dngos po gtan tshigs kyis brtags shing rnal 'byor
NK076(mu)002:2259: pa'i shes rab kyis dmigs phye ste bsal nas /
NK076(mu)002:2260: rang gzhung ma nor ba'i don gyi grub mtha' dmigs nas blang bar bya ba na 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:2261: gnyis par rgyas bshad la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:2262: gsang sngags bla med kyi grub mtha' mnyam pa nyid kyi ngo bo dang /
NK076(mu)002:2263: lta ba yod med phyogs rer 'dzin pas mnyam nyid las gol tshul dpe bcas /
NK076(mu)002:2264: yod med sgra tsam brtag tu rung yang don la yod med kyi mtha' las grol tshul /
NK076(mu)002:2265: de skyes bu mchog gi spyod yul yin pas rtogs par gdams pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2267: dang po lta ba rtogs pa'i ngo bo la 'khor
NK076(mu)002:2268: 'das kyi lta ba thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK076(mu)002:2270: gong bstan ltar 'das pa'i theg pa mthon po gsang sngags /
NK076(mu)002:2271: man pa theg dman thams cad kyi lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2273: mu stegs rtag chad gnyis te 'jiga rten pa'i lta ba ma lus pa thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:2274: don rang byung gi ye shes chen po nas /
NK076(mu)002:2275: rtog pa'i ngo bor rab tu brtags na /
NK076(mu)002:2276: don dam par lta ba dang theg pa rang bzhin
NK076(mu)002:2277: med pa las kun rdzob tu lta ba dang theg
NK076(mu)002:2278: pa cir yang snang zhing sgrub bo //
NK076(mu)002:2279: lta ba dang theg pa ji ltar snang yang /
NK076(mu)002:2280: de dag gi rang bzhin chos nyid mnyam pa'i dbyings
NK076(mu)002:2281: las nyamsa shing g.yos pa med pas na snang stong
NK076(mu)002:2283: gnyis pa mnyam dus lta ba phyogs 'dzin gyi rtog pa med tshul /
NK076(mu)002:2284: 'o na chos nyid mnyam pa'i don nyid rang bzhin ji lta bu zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:2285: don skye ba med par manyama pa nyid kyi ranga
NK076(mu)002:2286: bzhin phyogs gcig tu gang du yang grub pa min
NK076(mu)002:2287: de / phyogs med du chos kun tu 'char ba
NK076(mu)002:2288: yin pa la mnyam pa de'i ngo bo nyid 'di
NK076(mu)002:2290: de la mnyam pa dang mi mnyam pa'i rtog pa gang yang med do //
NK076(mu)002:2291: gsum pa de gzhi don byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid yin par bstan pa de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:2292: dang po byang chub sems la 'gro 'ong med cing
NK076(mu)002:2293: rang rig pa yin par bstan pa 'khor 'das mnyam
NK076(mu)002:2294: nyid kyi don byang chub kyi sems yin no zhes
NK076(mu)002:2295: tshig tu brjod pa yi don ni ci lta bu
NK076(mu)002:2296: zhe na / dang po gang nas kyang ma 'angas pas skye ba med pa /
NK076(mu)002:2297: mthar gar yang mi 'gra bas 'gag pa med pa /
NK076(mu)002:2298: da ltar gang na'ang mi gnas te yul yul can
NK076(mu)002:2299: gyi rtog pa gang yang med pas rang rig pa
NK076(mu)002:2301: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang khams gsum gyi sems
NK076(mu)002:2302: can thams cad rang rig pa byang chub kyi samas
NK076(mu)002:2303: la gnas pa'o // gnyis pa de dmigs su med tshul /
NK076(mu)002:2304: byang chub sems rnams rang bzhin thams cad kyi don ni /
NK076(mu)002:2305: ngos bzung bral bas shin tublos brtaga dka' zhing rgya mtsho ltar gting zab pas /
NK076(mu)002:2306: dngos po'i chos su ma dmigs pas byang /
NK076(mu)002:2307: dngos med kyi chos su mi dmigs pas chub /
NK076(mu)002:2308: tha dad kyi chos su dmigas su med pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2309: gsum pa dbyer med byang chub sems ni chos thams cad kyi ngo bo yin par bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:2310: sems nyid de ni don ci lta bu zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:2311: chos nyid byang chub da nyid ni sems nyid rang snang ba yin no //
NK076(mu)002:2312: des na sems dang byang chub gnyis su dbyer med pas na /
NK076(mu)002:2313: khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad dang /
NK076(mu)002:2314: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams thams cada sems kyi rang bazha na 'ba' zhig yina no //
NK076(mu)002:2316: 'khor 'das kyi lta ba dngos por yoda pa lasa
NK076(mu)002:2317: btsal na mnyam nyid la sgro btagsa pa yin te
NK076(mu)002:2319: dge sdig gi las dngos por 'dzin nas 'dod khams pas sgro btags /
NK076(mu)002:2320: mi g.yo ba'i las yod par 'dzin nas bsgoms pas khams gong ma gnyis kyis sgro btags /
NK076(mu)002:2321: rtag chad yod par 'dzin nas mu stegs pas sgro btags /
NK076(mu)002:2322: bden bzhi'i dngos po yod par 'dzin nas nyan thos kyis sgro btags /
NK076(mu)002:2323: rten 'brel rgyu 'bras lugs 'byung ldog yod par 'dzin nas rang rgyal gyis sgro btags /
NK076(mu)002:2324: bden pa gnyis tha dad du 'dod nas byang sems kyis sgro btags /
NK076(mu)002:2325: don dam chos nyid dang kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor res bsgom byed nas kri yas sgro btags /
NK076(mu)002:2326: chos kun rnam par dag pa'i cha ye shes kyi
NK076(mu)002:2327: byin rlabs las rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor sprul
NK076(mu)002:2328: bar 'dod nas yo gas sgro btagsa pa dang brgyad
NK076(mu)002:2330: phyogs med du 'khor 'das kyi lta ba thams cad
NK076(mu)002:2331: mnyam pa nyid du gcig kyang rang gi lta ba
NK076(mu)002:2332: las gzhan pa'i chos batsala na /
NK076(mu)002:2333: mnyam pa nyid la skur ba btab pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2334: gang zhe na dug lnga rang gzhan gyi lta ba
NK076(mu)002:2335: mi mnyam pas rgyud lnga'i sems can gyis skur pa
NK076(mu)002:2336: btab / dge sdig dang gzhan gyi lta ba mi
NK076(mu)002:2337: mnyam pas 'dod khams pas tshad med bzhi dang bsam
NK076(mu)002:2338: gtan bzhi mi mnyam pas gzugs khams skye mched mu
NK076(mu)002:2339: bzhi dang mi mnyam pas gzugs med rtag chad dang
NK076(mu)002:2340: mi mnyam pas mu stegs kyis bden bzhi dang mi
NK076(mu)002:2341: mnyam pas nyan thos kyis rten 'brel dang mi mnyam
NK076(mu)002:2342: bas rang rgyal gyis bden gnyis dang mi mnyam pas
NK076(mu)002:2343: byang sems kyis gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas
NK076(mu)002:2344: kri yas lhun grub mnyam par ma shes pas yo
NK076(mu)002:2345: gas skur ba btab pa dang bcu yi gnas su
NK076(mu)002:2346: btab / ltung ngo // yang na chad par /
NK076(mu)002:2353: don dam par rang bzhin med pa /
NK076(mu)002:2354: sems dag pa mtha'i dri ma med pa /
NK076(mu)002:2355: sems 'od gsal ma rig med pa 10snang /
NK076(mu)002:2356: de ltar yod pa dang med pa gnyis las btsal
NK076(mu)002:2357: bar byas na sgro skur gyi grangs de snyed kyi
NK076(mu)002:2358: skyon gyis mnyam pa nyid kyi don mi rtogs nas
NK076(mu)002:2359: lung ma bstan du lus par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:2360: yod med gnyis las btsal na skyon yod pa de
NK076(mu)002:2361: yi phyir dper na nam mkha' yoda ces bya ba
NK076(mu)002:2362: dang med ces bya bar gang zag blun po rnams
NK076(mu)002:2363: ni rtsod pa byed par byed do //
NK076(mu)002:2366: de yang gang zag nam mkha'i mtshan nyid la mkhas
NK076(mu)002:2367: pas nam mkha'i rang bzhin yod med kyi mtha' las
NK076(mu)002:2369: kun gyi go skabs 'byed pas med par kho na yang mi 'adzana /
NK076(mu)002:2370: kha dog dbyibs su ma grub pas yoda pa kho nar yang mi 'dzin te /
NK076(mu)002:2371: yod med gnyis kyi mtha' kun dang bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2372: gnyis pa don de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2374: de bzhin du sems nyid rig rtsal 'gag med du
NK076(mu)002:2375: cir yang snang bas yoda pa kun gyi ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:2376: dang / snang dus rang rgyud can du ma grub
NK076(mu)002:2377: pas med pa kun gyi ngo bo yin pas gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2378: dang / su med do // yod med sogs sgra
NK076(mu)002:2379: tsam du brjod du rung mod kyis don sems nyid
NK076(mu)002:2380: kyi nga bo la snang stong phyogs re ba 'ad
NK076(mu)002:2381: dang / su med do // kho na'o // zhasa
NK076(mu)002:2382: rgyal bas kyang gzhan la bstan cing rang gis brtags
NK076(mu)002:2384: yoda ces bya ba dang meda casa sogs brjod pa ca byar yoda /
NK076(mu)002:2385: tha dad med cing mnyam pa nyid do //
NK076(mu)002:2386: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2387: dang po dgos ched kyi sgo nas de kho na nyid kyi ming gi rnam grangs bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:2388: 'o na sems nyid ces tshig tu mtshon pa la dgos pa med dam zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:2389: semas nyid ya gdod ma nyid nas phyogs zhen dang bral bas sangas la /
NK076(mu)002:2390: ye shes phyogs med rgyas pa'i phyir sangs rgyas yin la /
NK076(mu)002:2391: de ltar min par 'dzin pa'i lta ba ngan pa'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2392: gnyis su med pa bzang ngan sogs zhen pa zlog phyir mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:2393: sems can gyi zhen pa zlog phyir sangas rgyas dang
NK076(mu)002:2394: gzhan du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa bzlog phyir bdag nyid
NK076(mu)002:2395: chen po dang / rtsol sgrub zhen pa zlog phyir lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2396: mu mthar 'dzin pa zlog phyir chosa kyi dbyings su dag pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2397: nyon mongs 'dzin pa zlog phyir byang chub /
NK076(mu)002:2398: chos can du 'dzin zhen zlog phyir chos nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:2399: dngos 'dzin zlog phyir stong pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2400: yid yul du 'dzin pa zlog phyir bsam pa las 'das pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2401: bcos pa'i 'dzin pa zlog phyir ma bcos de bzhin nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:2402: rgyu rkyen du 'dzin pa zlog phyir skye 'agga med pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2403: phyogs re'i mtha' 'dzin zlog phyir mtha' bral dang /
NK076(mu)002:2404: 'khor ba'i 'dzin pa zlog phyir mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2405: 'khrul rtog gis bcing bar 'dzin pa zlog phyir rang grol ba la sogas su /
NK076(mu)002:2406: don sems nyid phyogs med las rgyu mtshan phyogs re
NK076(mu)002:2407: nas gang yang mi 'gag par gdul bya'i ngo la
NK076(mu)002:2408: bla dwagsa tsam du brjod pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:2409: gnyis pa don tshig la mi gnas par la bzla ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:2410: gshis ye gdod ma nas tshaga gi dngos pos mtshon
NK076(mu)002:2411: pa'i don de tshig la mi gnas pas tshig gi
NK076(mu)002:2412: lam rnam par chad pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2413: ci'i phyir zhe na sems nyid de ni chos kun gyi rang bzhin yin pa la /
NK076(mu)002:2414: tha snyad de daga sgra ru brjod cing tshig tu bsnyad du ca yoda de med /
NK076(mu)002:2415: 'di zhes gzhan la bstan cing rang blos brtag par dka' bar rgyal bas gsungsa so //
NK076(mu)002:2416: bzhi pa ni sangs rgyas la sgrib gnyis gyis ma
NK076(mu)002:2417: gos bas ma chags pa ste me tog pad+ma la
NK076(mu)002:2418: 'dam gyis ma gos pa dang 'dra ba yi thams
NK076(mu)002:2419: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes can rgyal ba kun gyi
NK076(mu)002:2421: gang zag kun dang spyod yul thun manga du gyur
NK076(mu)002:2422: pa ni don de ma yin pa'i phyir su yis
NK076(mu)002:2423: rtogs nas mthar thug gis de da bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2424: dgongs pa'i spyod yul du gyur ta /
NK076(mu)002:2425: te zhes lhag ma can gyi tshig ste gzhan sus kyang mi rtogs sam zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:2426: gsang sngags kyi rigs can snod ldan skyes bu shes
NK076(mu)002:2427: rab kyi blo rtsal dang ldan pa dbang rnon rab
NK076(mu)002:2428: kyis rtogsa so // rgyu mtshan de yi phyir skal
NK076(mu)002:2429: ldan blo rtsal cana lam pa rnams kyis brtsona cig
NK076(mu)002:2430: kyis rtogsa so // pa'o // lnga pa ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:2431: dang rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2432: kyis rtogsa so // pa'o // / dang po mdor bstan /
NK076(mu)002:2433: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba'i ngo bo dngos
NK076(mu)002:2434: dang minga gi rnam grangsa grags pa de lta bu'i
NK076(mu)002:2435: nga bo ngos bzung ba'i rim pas rnam grangs phye
NK076(mu)002:2436: ba yin no // gnyis pa rgyas bshad de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2437: lta ba'i ngo bo'i rnam grangs dang /
NK076(mu)002:2441: mdor bstan gyi snga ma lta bu rtogs nus pa
NK076(mu)002:2442: kha cig rang rig mngona sum la rnam shes tshogs
NK076(mu)002:2443: drug gama tshogs brgyad nyid ye shes su gnas 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:2444: phyir / gyur tshul shes rab kyi rnam shes drug
NK076(mu)002:2445: dbang po drug yul drug dbyer med tshul du yul
NK076(mu)002:2446: yul can nas gnas su gyur par brjod pa /
NK076(mu)002:2447: brjod pa'i don nges par ma nor bar mngon sum du mthong ba de yanga /
NK076(mu)002:2448: tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga ru rang gsal ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2449: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi ngo bo'ang ye shes lnga de nyid yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2450: gnyis pa rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2451: dang po tshogs drug lta ba'i ngo bo'i rnam grangs la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:2452: dang po sgo lnga yul med rang gsal gyi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2453: mig rna ba sna lce lus kyi dbang po ste lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:2454: dmigs bya gzugs sgra dri ro reg lnga /
NK076(mu)002:2455: dmigs byed sgo lnga'i rnam shes lnga ste bco lnga rnams rang rig tu dbyer med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2456: gtan tshigs de bas na sgo lnga yul dang yul
NK076(mu)002:2457: can med par rang rig par gsal bar rtogs pa'o
NK076(mu)002:2458: // gnyis pa yid kyi shes pa dbyings rig dbyer med kyi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2459: shes bya chos kyi dbyings dang shes byed rig pa gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i don no //
NK076(mu)002:2460: de nyid bcos slad bral nas de bzhina nyid du dbyer med pas rdo rje'i ragas zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:2461: gsum pa yid kyi dbang po gzung 'dzin gnyis med rang snang gi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2462: phyi gzung pa'i yul gyi gsal cha la nang yid
NK076(mu)002:2463: kyi 'dzin pa'i rnam pa dang bral ba'i rang gi
NK076(mu)002:2464: mtshan nyid rang gis rig pa de nyid dmigs bya
NK076(mu)002:2465: dmigs byed med pa'i tshul du rang gsal bas der
NK076(mu)002:2466: snang ngo // bzhi pa yid kyi yul chos kun
NK076(mu)002:2467: lhun grub phyi nang rnam dag mnyam nyid chen po'i
NK076(mu)002:2468: snang ngo // lta ba / sems nyid phyogs ris
NK076(mu)002:2469: med pa yangs shing kun la khyab pas rgya che
NK076(mu)002:2470: ba 'khor 'das lhun grub tu gnas pa de ni
NK076(mu)002:2471: thams cad kyi 'byung gzhir snang ba de bas /
NK076(mu)002:2472: yid kyi yul 'dus byas kyi phyi nang zhes snod
NK076(mu)002:2473: kyi 'jig rten bcud kyi sems can thams cad ye
NK076(mu)002:2474: nas rnam par dag pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2475: de ltar 'dus ma byas su dag pa'i rang rig
NK076(mu)002:2476: mngon sum rtogs pa de nyid kyang dbyer med mnyam
NK076(mu)002:2478: de rtogs pa'i don 'di ni dbyings ye dbyer med
NK076(mu)002:2479: rdo rje ste bzang ngan med par mnyam pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:2480: yin no // lnga pa bsdu na shes yul gnyis med kyi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2481: nang rnam par shes pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2482: des longs spyod pa'i phyi'i yul gyi bye brag rnams dbyings ye ngo bor gnyis su med pas /
NK076(mu)002:2483: yul shes kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ma lus
NK076(mu)002:2484: pa byang chub sems su ro gcig pa'i ngang du
NK076(mu)002:2486: gnyis pa tshogs brgyad lta ba'i ngo bo'i rnam grangs la brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:2487: dang po gzugs dang gsal stong dbyer med ye shes rang snang du bstan pa spyan gyi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2488: chos kun ma 'dres la rang snang du yongas su
NK076(mu)002:2489: rdzogsa par gsal stong gnyis med ni don shes bya
NK076(mu)002:2490: yul gzugsa kyi lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2491: blta bar bya ba'i yul dang lta ba shes pa dang gnyis su byar med pas /
NK076(mu)002:2492: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba'i zhing khams thams cad gnyis med rang snang du mthonga nas /
NK076(mu)002:2493: yul yul can ganga du'ang ma mthong ba ni shes rab spyan gyi lta ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:2494: yul yul can du mthong ba'i machaga go //
NK076(mu)002:2495: gnyis pa don sgra dang grag stong dbyer med snyan gyi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2496: chos nyid khyab brdal chen po yul med rang gsal
NK076(mu)002:2497: ba rang bzhin go ba'i don ni shes bya'i yul
NK076(mu)002:2499: thos pa de yang bya ba dang byed pa gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2500: med par rang snang du thos pa'i phul du byung
NK076(mu)002:2501: ba ste shes rab snyan gyi lta ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2502: gsum pa don dri dang tshor stong dbyer med de shangs kyi lta pa /
NK076(mu)002:2503: gzung 'dzin dri ma med pas dang bas shes rab
NK076(mu)002:2504: kyi dbang po tshim par byed pa'i chos nyid kyi
NK076(mu)002:2505: don ni shes bya'i yul dri yi lta ba dang
NK076(mu)002:2506: / de yang bsnam bya snom byed med para rang
NK076(mu)002:2507: ga ma gnyis med rang snang du tshor ba'i shes
NK076(mu)002:2509: bzhi pa don ro dang myong stong dbyer med lce'i lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2510: chos nyid kyi don bcud gnyis med kyi ye shes
NK076(mu)002:2511: nyams su myong ba'i don ni shes bya'i yul ro'i
NK076(mu)002:2512: lta ba dang / de nyid myong ba'i bya ba yi yul dang /
NK076(mu)002:2513: myod bar byed pa'i sems gnyis su med pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:2514: du myong ba ni shes rab ljags kyi lta ba'o
NK076(mu)002:2515: // lnga pa reg bya dang reg stong dbyer med lus kyi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2516: de tsam na yang dag pa'i chos nyid kyi don
NK076(mu)002:2517: la reg pa yi don ni shes bya'i yul la
NK076(mu)002:2518: reg pa'i lta ba dang de nyid reg pa kun
NK076(mu)002:2520: rega bya reg byed dang bral ba shes rab lus kyi lta ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2521: drug pa yid phyogs med ye shes rang snang du lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2522: yul chosa 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi khamas sna tshogas pa kun mkhyen pa la /
NK076(mu)002:2523: yid rang rig ye shes su dbang bsgyur ba'i rgyal
NK076(mu)002:2524: po ltar rang snang nga zhes shes rab yid kyi
NK076(mu)002:2525: lta ba'o // bdun pa nyon yid bdag med rang gsal ba /
NK076(mu)002:2526: thams cad rang snang yin pa de bas kun gzhi
NK076(mu)002:2527: la bdag tu 'dzin pa'i nyon yid kyang rig pa
NK076(mu)002:2529: badga 'dzin dang bcas dus badga rang rgyud pa dang
NK076(mu)002:2530: bral ba'i nyon yid bdag med par rtogs pa'i lta
NK076(mu)002:2531: ba'o // brgyad pa kun gzhi ye shes rang gsal thams cad mkhyen pa'i lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2532: phyi rol gyi don yul dang sems can thams cad
NK076(mu)002:2533: kyi kun gzhi rtog med kyi ngang du gsal ba
NK076(mu)002:2534: / kun gzhi rang byung gi ye shes thams cad mkhyen pa'i lta ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2535: gnyis pa rim pa'i don grangs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:2536: dang po mdor bstan gong du ngo bo'i rnam grangs song nas yang lta ba'i rnam grangs dngos ni /
NK076(mu)002:2537: lam gyi lta ba mtho dman gyi rim pas /
NK076(mu)002:2538: don gyi rnam grangs rgyud don ming gi rnam grangs brjod pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:2539: gnyis pa rgyas pa la'ang gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2540: don lam gyi lta grangs dang /
NK076(mu)002:2541: rgyud don ming gi lta grangs so //
NK076(mu)002:2543: dang po lta ba gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phebs pa'i 'phel rim gyi lta grangs /
NK076(mu)002:2544: don dama rang bzhin med pa dang kun rdzob sgyu
NK076(mu)002:2545: ma'i ye shes dang de gnyis med du mthong zhing
NK076(mu)002:2546: rtogs pa dang / spyod yul dang bral bar rang
NK076(mu)002:2547: rig pa'i mngona sum du byas pa bzhi rim pas
NK076(mu)002:2548: rtogs pa dang / / rgyu gcig pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2551: mngon sum du rtogs pa bzhi go rim dang spyar bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:2555: spros pa dang rnam bzhi'i ste tshogs lam dang /
NK076(mu)002:2559: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi dang rim par sbyar bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:2563: sgrub pa chen po bzhi dang sbyor lam sbyar zhing tshogs lam gyi grangs re re'ang dbye na /
NK076(mu)002:2568: mathara phyin pa'i nyams kyis rima para 'phar ba rnams dang sbyar ro //
NK076(mu)002:2569: gnyis pa lam gyi lta grangs de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2570: dang po lam gyi lta grangs ngos bzung ba /
NK076(mu)002:2571: chos nyid bden pa dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK076(mu)002:2572: ngang las mi skrag pas rang rig mngon sum du
NK076(mu)002:2574: yid ches nges pa'i gdengs rnyed pa'i shes rab ste rgyu shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2575: snang ba'i rnam pa kun ma spangs bar ldan pa
NK076(mu)002:2576: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa chen por gyur
NK076(mu)002:2577: ba de mthong zhing go ba'i ngang nas gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:2578: de ting stong chen lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2579: yul yul can gnyis su med par rang rig pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2580: snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ye shes
NK076(mu)002:2581: sgyu ma'i ngo bo shar ba 'di kun snang gi
NK076(mu)002:2582: ting nge 'dzin snying rjera gzigas pa'i lta ba dang
NK076(mu)002:2583: / yi dam lha'i phyag rgya gcig pa'i sku ru
NK076(mu)002:2584: dbyer med rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba 'bras
NK076(mu)002:2586: rtog tshogs thams cad lha du ma'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba'i phyag rgya rgyas spros lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2587: sbyor lam bar chad mada pa'i lam du yo byad
NK076(mu)002:2588: lnga la rang bzhin med par spyad pas tshogas gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2589: chena po rdzogs par mathanga ba sbyor lam tshogs sgrub
NK076(mu)002:2590: lta ba dang / tshe la dbang bsgyur ba mthong lam tshe dbang gi lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2591: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid kyi don las mi g.yo
NK076(mu)002:2592: ba sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i lta ba dang
NK076(mu)002:2593: / yab yum gyi dga' ba sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK076(mu)002:2594: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug la ye shes lnga'i
NK076(mu)002:2595: rtsal du kun mkhyen pa lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi
NK076(mu)002:2597: gnyis pa de nyid shes rab gsum las byung bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:2598: lta ba'i rnam grangs de nyid rgyu gang las byung na /
NK076(mu)002:2599: dang po gzhung zab mo thos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2600: tshig des mtshon pa'i don la bsam byung so sor
NK076(mu)002:2601: rtog pa'i shes rab kyi rtog dpyod kyis gomas pa
NK076(mu)002:2602: dang / de yang tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:2603: sbyor lam rima par bsgom pa'i rgyu lasa mthong sgom mthar lam gyi lta ba skye ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2604: de lta basa na thos bsam sgom pa'i shes raba
NK076(mu)002:2605: gsum gyi rgyu las lta ba skyes pa'i phyir shes
NK076(mu)002:2606: rab gsum la 'boda cig ces gdams pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2607: gnyis pa rgyud don ming gi lta grangs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2609: yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po rgyud don
NK076(mu)002:2610: dgu po lta ba'i gzungs kyis zin pa'i ngos nas
NK076(mu)002:2611: lta grangs dgur bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:2613: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la dgu /
NK076(mu)002:2614: dang po mi 'da' ba dam tshig gi lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2615: rgyud gzhung rnams las rtsa ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK076(mu)002:2616: yan lag gi dam tshig cesa bya ba bshad pa de la'ang /
NK076(mu)002:2617: gud dam log na yod pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2618: khyad par du lam pa rang ga chos nyid lta
NK076(mu)002:2619: ba rtogs pa'i ngang las mi 'da' ba de ka
NK076(mu)002:2621: sgo gsum gyis sgrub cing bsrung ba las mi 'da' bas sdom pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:2622: dang blang mi spang lnga ste rnam pa bcu dang
NK076(mu)002:2623: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi sdom pa gsum dang
NK076(mu)002:2624: bcu gsum / thun mong spyi'a dam tshig yo ga man chad kyi bsrung bya mtha'a yasa pa rnams /
NK076(mu)002:2625: chos nyid thig le chen po'i zhes mnyam pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:2626: du lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang du thams cad 'du
NK076(mu)002:2628: sgo gsum gyis ji ltar spyad kyang dam tshig sdom pa las mi 'ad'a ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2629: gnyis pa blang dor med pa spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:2630: rang gzhan gyi sgo gsum gyi spyod pa rang gzhan
NK076(mu)002:2631: rnam pa gnyis po yi bye brag ji snyed pa
NK076(mu)002:2632: yang // chos nyid thig le chen po'i ngang du dbyer med par nges par rtogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:2633: spyad bya spyod byed phyogs gcig pa ci la'ang blo
NK076(mu)002:2634: mi gansa par rang gzhan gyi don kun la ma
NK076(mu)002:2636: de ka'i dus na spyod par byed pa'i mkhan po dang /
NK076(mu)002:2637: spyad par bya ba'i yul gnyis med par thams cad rig pa rang snang du mthonga ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:2639: gsum pa rol pa phrin las kyi /
NK076(mu)002:2640: phrin las bya ba'i yul dang byed pa'i mkhan po
NK076(mu)002:2641: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis su las rnams kun
NK076(mu)002:2642: la thogas pa med par spyod cing /
NK076(mu)002:2643: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi yi lasa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2644: gcig pu gcig la kun lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin
NK076(mu)002:2645: las lnga yanga sems nyid spros bral thiga le chen
NK076(mu)002:2646: pa'i ngang du gnyis su med par gasla bar rtogs
NK076(mu)002:2647: pa ni phrin las kyi lta ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2648: bzhi pa gnas su stobs pa mchod pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:2649: mchoda pa'i yo byad steng 'og gi rgyan rin po
NK076(mu)002:2650: che dang dar zab phyi nang gsang ba'i longsa spyod
NK076(mu)002:2651: ma lus pa kun gzhan na med de /
NK076(mu)002:2652: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems chana po cha
NK076(mu)002:2653: 'phrul chana pa'i zhes lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang du
NK076(mu)002:2654: 'dus pas / mchod pa gzhan du phul ba meda
NK076(mu)002:2655: par 'khor gsum yongs dag gis dus gsum gyi rgyal
NK076(mu)002:2656: ba thams cad mnyes pa ste mchod pa'i lta ba'o
NK076(mu)002:2657: 'dus pas / // lnga pa bkod pa dkyil 'khor /
NK076(mu)002:2658: rten gzhal yas khanga dang brten pa zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK076(mu)002:2659: 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogas kyi pho nya nang
NK076(mu)002:2660: du 'adu ba dang phyi rol du 'aphro ba mang
NK076(mu)002:2661: pa de yanga / logs na med de rang rig
NK076(mu)002:2662: byang chub semas kyi cha 'phrul chen pa yin pas
NK076(mu)002:2663: pa de yanga / / gtan tshigs de lta bas /
NK076(mu)002:2670: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang rnam pa bdun po thams
NK076(mu)002:2671: cad kyang rig pa rang snang lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2672: nganga du 'du zhing gsal ba ni dkyil 'khor gyi
NK076(mu)002:2673: lta ba'o // drug pa rim pa dbang /
NK076(mu)002:2674: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams ma lus pa
NK076(mu)002:2675: thams cad kun gyi ranga bzhin nam ngang gisa sems
NK076(mu)002:2676: nyid rig pa bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:2677: / phyi nang gsang ba'i dabnga la /
NK076(mu)002:2680: zab dbang gsum bcas logs nas ma batsala bar /
NK076(mu)002:2681: rig pa sems nyid la lhun gyis grub cing rdzogsa te /
NK076(mu)002:2682: de ltar phan nus zab dbang baca brgyad kyang rang
NK076(mu)002:2683: rig pa'i sems kyi cho 'phrul du rang snang bar
NK076(mu)002:2684: rtogs pa'i dbang gi lta ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2685: bdun pa don du gnyer ba sgrub pa'i //
NK076(mu)002:2686: dngos grub 'bras bu rang la yod pa la ngo
NK076(mu)002:2687: mtshar zhing ngom pas e ma ha rgyu rkyen gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2688: kyis ma bsgrubsa par rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa
NK076(mu)002:2689: chena po ste / grub pa chen po gang zhe
NK076(mu)002:2690: na rang byung gi ye shes chena po yin te
NK076(mu)002:2691: chena po ste / / de bas na lam pas
NK076(mu)002:2692: don du gnyer bar bya ba'i sgrub pa'i rnam grangsa
NK076(mu)002:2693: mchog thun gyi dngos grub thams cad kun kyang rang
NK076(mu)002:2694: rig pa byang chub kyi sems chen pa lta ba
NK076(mu)002:2695: rtogs pa'i ngang du 'du zhing gsal ba ni sgrub
NK076(mu)002:2696: chena po ste / / pa'i lta ba'o // brgyad pa nyams su len pa ting nge 'dzin /
NK076(mu)002:2697: ting nge 'dzina gyi ngang la gnas pa lta ba'i
NK076(mu)002:2698: bye brag mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi ting 'dzin kun
NK076(mu)002:2699: gzhan na min te ranga rig pa nyid lhar snang
NK076(mu)002:2700: ba'i phyir / mtshan bcas rnams chu yi chu bur lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)002:2701: mtshan med nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhina du rtogs pas /
NK076(mu)002:2702: rang rig pa'i ya shes nyid du 'du zhing gsal
NK076(mu)002:2703: ba las gzhan du btsal zhing bsgom pa min no
NK076(mu)002:2704: // de ni ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:2705: dgu pa bcings grol med pa sngags dang phyag rgya'i lta ba /
NK076(mu)002:2706: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i /
NK076(mu)002:2708: bzlas pa las rim gyi sngagas gsum brjod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2711: dam tshig las kyi phyag rgya bzhi 'ang rang gi sems nyid rang snang yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2712: sngags grag stong brag cha lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)002:2713: phyag rgya snang stong chu zla dang 'dra bar snang
NK076(mu)002:2714: la rang bzhin ma grub par shes pa'i dus na
NK076(mu)002:2715: / phyag rgya 'ching grol dang sngags brjod pa'i las
NK076(mu)002:2716: nyid gang ltar yang mya ngan las 'das pa ni
NK076(mu)002:2717: / / de bas phyag rgya bsgom bya sgom byed
NK076(mu)002:2718: dang sngags bzla bya zlo byed gnyis su med par
NK076(mu)002:2719: mnyam pa nyid kyi don lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang
NK076(mu)002:2720: du 'du zhing gsal ba ni sngags dang phyag rgya'i
NK076(mu)002:2721: / / lta ba'o // gsum pa lta ba kun 'dir shes dgos par gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:2722: de ltar lam gyi lta ba dang rgyud kyi lta
