NK076(mu)002:2723: ba zhes lam dang rgyud don gyi gtso bor ming
NK076(mu)002:2724: tshig tu lta ba brjod mod kyang nges pa'i don
NK076(mu)002:2725: du na shes rab kyi mchog chos kun ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:2726: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs par byed pa ni lta
NK076(mu)002:2728: de ni dper na tshong ba'i ded dpon rgya mtshor
NK076(mu)002:2729: rin chen len pa'i thabs la mkhas dgos pa'i dpe
NK076(mu)002:2730: ji bzhin du / thog mar gdod ma rgyu shes
NK076(mu)002:2731: ba'i lta ba nas tha ma lhun grub kyi 'bras
NK076(mu)002:2732: bu ma thob ba'i bar gyi skyon yon /
NK076(mu)002:2733: bye brag thams cad lta ba'i skabs 'dir phyin ci ma log par shes dgos pas 'dir gdams pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2734: drug pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2736: thos bsam gyi shes rab kyis lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2737: thabs la don du gnyer zhing blo chub nas rtogs
NK076(mu)002:2738: pa'i tshe / bdag don dang gzhan gyi don phyir
NK076(mu)002:2739: du sgo gsum gyis spyad par bya ba spyod pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2740: bye brag rnams ni 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:2741: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:2742: bdag don dang gzhan don spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2744: dang po thos bsam la brten nas rgyud don bcu la spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:2745: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba'i gzhi la spyod pa kun
NK076(mu)002:2746: kyang bdag gzhan don du spyod la de yang 'dir
NK076(mu)002:2747: thos bsam gnyis kyi sgo nas bslab pa'i gnas bcu
NK076(mu)002:2748: 'am / yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po
NK076(mu)002:2749: bcu la spyod cing don ched du gnyer bar byed
NK076(mu)002:2750: 'am / pa'o // gnyis pa lta ba rtogs tshab
NK076(mu)002:2751: che chung gi dbye bas spyod pa la khyad par
NK076(mu)002:2752: 'am / pa'o // yod tshul / rgyu shes pa lta ba'i spyod pa 'adi la yang /
NK076(mu)002:2753: khyad yod tshul gyi dpe 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal
NK076(mu)002:2754: po'i ming tsam 'dra yang 'dul zhing sa la khams
NK076(mu)002:2755: rgya che chung yod pa bzhin dang /
NK076(mu)002:2756: thabs kyi spyod pa nyon mongs pa thad gcod nus mi nus kyi dpe /
NK076(mu)002:2757: stobs chen glang po tsam du 'dra yang /
NK076(mu)002:2758: rtsal che chung sgyid drag zhan yod pa lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)002:2759: bdag don ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod pa la stobs che chung yod pa'i dpe /
NK076(mu)002:2760: lung pa rgya che chung gis phye ba'i nas mkha'
NK076(mu)002:2761: yi zhing gi yul cha chung ji lta bar gzhi
NK076(mu)002:2762: shes pa lta ba'i spyod par gcig kyang /
NK076(mu)002:2763: gzhan don la rgya che chung /
NK076(mu)002:2764: nyon mongs pa thang gcod nus mi nus /
NK076(mu)002:2765: bdag don ting nge 'dzin stobs che chung gi stobsa
NK076(mu)002:2766: kyis spyod pa la khyad par yod par 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)002:2767: // gsum pa lta ba rtogs pa ngo bo'i spyod thabs bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:2768: chos thams cad ye nas mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su ro gcig pas /
NK076(mu)002:2769: de la'ang bdag tu 'dzin pa gang zag gi nga bdag dang /
NK076(mu)002:2770: chos kyi bdag rang rgyud par ma rtogs par spyod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2771: dam rdzas sogs chos thams cad ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa yin pa la /
NK076(mu)002:2772: dkar gsum gtsang ba dang dam ye lnga sogs dme
NK076(mu)002:2773: ba mi gtsang ba'i blo gnyis su 'dzin par ma
NK076(mu)002:2776: sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying pa gcig pa yin pas na /
NK076(mu)002:2777: gang ltar spyad kyang bag chags kyi rkyen gyis dri
NK076(mu)002:2778: ma ngan pa'i rdul gyis ga la 'go ste mi
NK076(mu)002:2779: gos so // de sus spyod na /
NK076(mu)002:2780: gang zag shes raba mchog gyur dag gis tshul de
NK076(mu)002:2781: ltar rtogs shing spyad bya'i yul gyi chos ma lus
NK076(mu)002:2782: pa kun sems su 'dus la sems mnyam nyid dbyings
NK076(mu)002:2783: su shes par byos zhes gdams so //
NK076(mu)002:2784: bzhi pa spyod pa'i dam tshig dang slob rim bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:2785: gdams pa'i tshul de bas na rgyu shes par bya ba yi lta ba rnams rtogs thabs /
NK076(mu)002:2786: lta ba las mi 'da' bas dam tshig dang sdom pa'i ngo bor byed de /
NK076(mu)002:2787: dgos pa bdag dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir du lta ba la gtsor byeda kyi /
NK076(mu)002:2788: lam gyi dang po'i lta ba shes 'jug dus su
NK076(mu)002:2789: sdom pa dam tshig kun kyang slob cing spyod par
NK076(mu)002:2790: byed pa'o // gnyis pa gzhan don gyi spyod pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:2791: dang po rtogs pas rang grol nas thugs rjes gzhan grol ba /
NK076(mu)002:2792: chos kun mnyam nyid shes pa'i shes rab chen po'i lta ba'am /
NK076(mu)002:2793: mi 'dzin pa'i sbyin pas rtog pa sreg pa'i sbyin sreg gis /
NK076(mu)002:2794: bsreg bya srid pa khams gsum gyi rtog pa bsreg
NK076(mu)002:2795: rdzas lta bu sreg pa'i me ni lta ba rtogs
NK076(mu)002:2796: pa yina te / bsregs tshul ni yida kyi rtog
NK076(mu)002:2797: pa rang byung gi ye shes rang gsal bas me
NK076(mu)002:2798: pa yina te / ru 'abra ba / ram ni me yi sa bon te /
NK076(mu)002:2799: rtog pa ye shes kyi mes bdag bsgral nas /
NK076(mu)002:2800: de nas thugs rjes 'gro drug gi rtog pa kun
NK076(mu)002:2801: kyang chosa nyid mi dmigs pa'i ngang du bsregs pa
NK076(mu)002:2803: gnyis pa bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:2804: gdod ma rgyu shes lta ba nas bzung mathara 'bras
NK076(mu)002:2805: bu ma thob bar du lam don gnyer gyi thos
NK076(mu)002:2806: bsam gyis spros pa'i sgro 'dogs gcod cing /
NK076(mu)002:2807: 'bras bu grub para byed pa'i lam bgrod nas /
NK076(mu)002:2808: lam du 'jug pa yi dus der yang /
NK076(mu)002:2811: chos kyi don te don gsum gyi phyir byang chub bsgrub par dam bcas shing sems bskyed pas /
NK076(mu)002:2812: dngos su bdag nyid kyis lam bgrod pa'i spyod pa la yang /
NK076(mu)002:2813: gdul bya gzhan gyi don shugs kyis rdzogas pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:2814: gsum pa de theg chung la mi 'tshams pas khyad par gyi spyod pa yin tshul /
NK076(mu)002:2815: de bas na byis pa nyan rang rang don byed pa dang 'di gnyis mi mtshungs te /
NK076(mu)002:2816: theg chen kun gyi lam skabsa lasa bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:2817: bdun pa phan yon la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:2818: dang po lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan 'khor bar mi ltung zhing yon tan tshad las 'das pa /
NK076(mu)002:2819: lam pa gang zhig gis yon tan gong bstan 'di
NK076(mu)002:2820: 'drar thos bsam la brten nas rang rig pa'i mngon
NK076(mu)002:2821: sum du mthong zhing rtogsa pa de ni /
NK076(mu)002:2822: dngos grub rnam gnyis las machaga gi dngos grub kyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po ni yin te /
NK076(mu)002:2823: dper na chu srin gyi gre bar dngos po tshud
NK076(mu)002:2824: pa phyir mi gtong pa'i phyag rgya ji bzhina du
NK076(mu)002:2825: / dang po chos nyid lta ba'i don rtogsa na /
NK076(mu)002:2826: mtha' 'bras bum thob par 'khor bar mi gtong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2827: dbang po'i spyod yul kun tu ye shes 'char bas yon tan gyi tshad blos dpag tu med do //
NK076(mu)002:2828: gnyis pa ci ltar spyad kyang rnam smin med cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:2829: lta bas zin na kun nas nyon mongas pa 'khor
NK076(mu)002:2830: ba'i chos la spyod pa'ang rtogs pas grol bar 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:2831: bas thun mong gi lam theg pa che chung gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2832: sam / sngags phyi ba dang mtshan nyid gnyis la spyod pa'ang grol ba de bzhin yin pasa na /
NK076(mu)002:2833: rgyu dge sdig gi 'bras bu rnam smin la mtho ris bde ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2834: ngan song gi sdug bsngal gnyis med de slar ci
NK076(mu)002:2835: spyod kyang bsod nams kyi tshogas chen gnyis rdzogas par
NK076(mu)002:2836: 'gyur ro // gsum pa mtha' gsum bral zhing don gsum rdzogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:2837: rnal 'byor pa gang gis gong gi don de ltar
NK076(mu)002:2838: lta ba mnyam pa nyid dbyer med rtogs par gyur
NK076(mu)002:2840: med par skur pa 'debs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2841: mnyam nyid lung ma bstan gyi mtha' dang gsum las yongs su grol ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:2843: de'i don 'bras bu rnams mngon du 'byin cing 'thob bar byed do //
NK076(mu)002:2844: gtan tshigs de lta bas na bdag don thob pa dang gzhan don nus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2845: chos dang mthun pa'i chos don te /
NK076(mu)002:2847: bzhi pa shes rab chen pos 'khor bar mi gtong
NK076(mu)002:2848: zhing bde ba dang ldan pa ni blos thug pa
NK076(mu)002:2850: rgya mtsho ltar gting zab pa /
NK076(mu)002:2852: glog ltar shes rab myur bas /
NK076(mu)002:2853: chos nyid zab pa'i don rtogs shing lta ba de dang ma bral na /
NK076(mu)002:2854: ngan song du ma ldog sdug bsngal med pas bde ba dang //
NK076(mu)002:2855: sems nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pas meda pas blo
NK076(mu)002:2856: gros bas yangas pa'i don dang ldan pas bde ba'o
NK076(mu)002:2857: // brgyad pa drod la dbye ba med de /
NK076(mu)002:2858: rnal 'byor pa brtson 'grus dang ldan pasa lta ba
NK076(mu)002:2859: rtogs pa de lhur len par byed na kun 'dus
NK076(mu)002:2861: chos la dbang thoba pa'i ltas ni /
NK076(mu)002:2862: rin po che'i gling du phyin pa dang me rtog 'bras bu'i char 'bab pa sogs /
NK076(mu)002:2863: bden pa mthonga ba'i rmi ltas ni /
NK076(mu)002:2864: sngar ma mthong ba'i yul khams chen po mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2865: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten la 'dzin cing thams
NK076(mu)002:2866: cad mthong ba sogs gzhan yang matshana ma bzang po
NK076(mu)002:2867: mthong zhing / rtsa ba'i drod chos nyid rtogs pa
NK076(mu)002:2868: lasa phyi nang gsang ba'i yan lag gi drod kun
NK076(mu)002:2870: lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i shugs kyis 'byung bar tha tshom med do //
NK076(mu)002:2871: dgu pa lta ba rtogs pa'i rtags bstan pa la dbye ba med de /
NK076(mu)002:2872: lta ba rtogs pa de la rtags kyi mtshan ma mngon du 'byung ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:2873: shes rab kyi stobsa kyis lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang
NK076(mu)002:2874: la rig pa klung du phebs pa'i don dang ldana
NK076(mu)002:2875: la / rnal 'byor ba des rang tshe 'pho zhing
NK076(mu)002:2876: spyod yul 'gyur bar mthong yang skye 'chi med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2877: don rtogs pas de la 'ajagas pa mada canga snang
NK076(mu)002:2878: srid chos skur shes pas 'khrul pa'i khamas la skyo
NK076(mu)002:2879: la / ba meda la / 'bras bu sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)002:2880: grub pa'i gnas 'og min sogs la skye bar mi
NK076(mu)002:2881: la / ba meda la / smon te / 'dod
NK076(mu)002:2882: pa'i yon tan lnga'i longas spyod la gtsang smre med
NK076(mu)002:2883: par rol cing chos nyid la mnyam par sbyor ba
NK076(mu)002:2884: la / ba meda la / smon te / dang / lus sems la sdug bsngal drag po dang /
NK076(mu)002:2885: nyon mongas chags sdang sogs skye dus lta ba las ma g.yos pas bzoda pa chen po thob sta /
NK076(mu)002:2886: dge ba'i las rlabs po che rnams dang gzhan don gang la'ang /
NK076(mu)002:2887: dka' bas khur du mi blta zhing rtsol med grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2888: rgyud tan+t+ra'i lugsa rnams dang rang gi bya spyod 'gal ba med par spyod pas /
NK076(mu)002:2889: so skye tha mala pa'i spyod pa bas khyad par du lhag par 'gyur ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:2890: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa rgyun gyi ma 'gags par
NK076(mu)002:2891: spyod pas bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis
NK076(mu)002:2893: lta ba rtogs pa'i yon tan rnams mad tsam du
NK076(mu)002:2894: smos kyi tha dada spros na brjod kyis mi long
NK076(mu)002:2895: pa yod do // bcu pa tshad la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:2896: dang po thos bas ma gyi sgo nas tshul mthun du rtogs shing mthar phyin pa'i tshad /
NK076(mu)002:2897: dper na rgya mtsho rnyogs ma dwangsa pa'i nang du
NK076(mu)002:2898: nyi zla gza' skar gyi gzugs brnyana 'char ba ltar
NK076(mu)002:2899: / rang rig pa'i chos nyid mngon sum du gsal bar mthong ba'i tshe /
NK076(mu)002:2900: chos nyid de mtshon byed kyi ngo bo gsum dang
NK076(mu)002:2901: bral te sgra tshig tsam la brten nas don spyi
NK076(mu)002:2902: yid la byed pa min para /
NK076(mu)002:2903: mngon sum bzhi las rang rig pa'i mangna sum du dmigas pa'i yul dang brala bar /
NK076(mu)002:2904: yul med rang gsal du mthong ba la blta bya
NK076(mu)002:2905: lta byed lta ba'i ngo bo gsum dang bral te
NK076(mu)002:2906: / grub mtha' gzhan gyi rkyen gyis ma bsgul bar /
NK076(mu)002:2907: don ngasa par rang rig pa'i gdeng du chud par gang byas pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:2908: thosa bsam la brten nas tshul mthun du rtogs pa'i lta ba mathara phyin pa'i tshad do //
NK076(mu)002:2909: gnyis pa tshig tu go na ngo bo gcig kyang
NK076(mu)002:2910: gsal du 'gro ba'i dpe dang bcas pa 'on kyang
NK076(mu)002:2911: zhes pa mi mthun pa mthun par ston pa'i tshig
NK076(mu)002:2912: ste / thos bsam la brten nas lta ba rtogs
NK076(mu)002:2913: ma nus kyang rtogs bya lta ba tsam du mthun
NK076(mu)002:2914: ste / pa'o // de yang sa gong ma gong
NK076(mu)002:2915: ma dang sa 'og ma 'og ma yi rima pa
NK076(mu)002:2916: bzhin du lta ba'i khyad yod ces pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2917: gang gis khyad ce na gsal mi gsal gyi khyad ston te /
NK076(mu)002:2918: dper na mig gi dabnga po shin tu dang ba'i spyod yul du gzugs mthong ba la /
NK076(mu)002:2919: nye ba gsal ring na mi gsal drung na shin
NK076(mu)002:2920: tu gsal ba bzhin bsgom byung gi stobsa lta pa
NK076(mu)002:2922: de nas rgyu shes pa'i lta ba dang rkyen 'jug
NK076(mu)002:2923: pa ting nge 'dzin gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu re
NK076(mu)002:2924: re la'ang / lam dus kyi gonga ma rgyu dang 'oga ma 'bras bur 'brel yang /
NK076(mu)002:2925: lta ba'i don nyid lam snga ma bas phyi ma
NK076(mu)002:2926: gasla du song ba'i bye brag lam gyi rim par
NK076(mu)002:2928: lta ba gsal mi gsal yod pa de yis chas
NK076(mu)002:2929: phye bas lam gong 'og gi gnas skabs kyi lta
NK076(mu)002:2930: ba la / de bzhin nyid kyi lta ba la sogs ming so sor brjod kyi /
NK076(mu)002:2931: lta ba rang gi dngos na ngo bo gcig pa ste sems kyi gnas lugs yin pas so //
NK076(mu)002:2932: bcu gcig pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:2933: ma rtogs pa'i skyon dngos dang /
NK076(mu)002:2934: rtogs pa'i don la brtson par gyis shig gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:2935: ting nge 'dzin rnams dang rgyu 'bras su 'brel tshul bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2937: dang po blo ngan gyis ma rtogs par le lo byas pa'i skyon gyis ngan song du ltung ba /
NK076(mu)002:2938: gong ga lta ba'i tshad kyi don ltar ma rtogs par shes rab med pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:2939: shes rab dman pa'i blo ngana tshig gis chos thams
NK076(mu)002:2940: cad mnyam para bshad pa'i lung khungs bzang po rnams
NK076(mu)002:2942: lta ba mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs pa dman pa'i le lo dang /
NK076(mu)002:2943: spyod pa rang ga mar snyom las byas pas tshe
NK076(mu)002:2944: 'dir dgos pa'i don ma grub par phyi mar ngana
NK076(mu)002:2946: gnyis pa tshig gi lta bas 'tshang mi rgya bas tshig don ldan par gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:2947: sems kyi chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don gcig gting 'byin par ma rtogs na /
NK076(mu)002:2948: kha tshaga ga sgo nas chos thams cad mnyam pa
NK076(mu)002:2949: nyid yin ces brjod pas 'bras bu mngon par 'atshanga
NK076(mu)002:2950: mi rgya'o // don ma rtogs na skyon yod pa
NK076(mu)002:2951: de bas na don dang tshig tu 'brel cing ldan
NK076(mu)002:2952: par gyis la go bar byos shig /
NK076(mu)002:2953: 'o na lta ba ma rtogs pas lam la 'jug
NK076(mu)002:2954: pa la dgos pa med do zhe na ma yin
NK076(mu)002:2955: te / 'on kyang tshig don 'brel bar gyur nas
NK076(mu)002:2956: the tshom med para go na don gyi 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:2958: gsum pa lta ba med na lam kun zag cing
NK076(mu)002:2959: 'ching bas lta ba rtogs shig par gdams pa dang
NK076(mu)002:2960: bcas pa ni / dper na spyan bzang ste long
NK076(mu)002:2961: ba lam du zhugs kyang 'gro sar mi phyin pa
NK076(mu)002:2962: ji lta ba bzhin gyi phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2963: lta ba ma rtogs par lam du zhugs na lam
NK076(mu)002:2964: kun 'khor bar zag cinga 'ching ba'i rgyu ru 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:2965: bas / bdag gzhan gyi 'bras bu thob pa'i don
NK076(mu)002:2966: du ma 'gyur ba'i phyir na sems ngan song du
NK076(mu)002:2967: brlag par 'gyur ba'i skyon yod do //
NK076(mu)002:2968: de basa na lta ba'i don la brtson zhing 'grus par gyis shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:2969: gnyis pa rtogs pa'i don la brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:2970: gong du lta ba rtogs pa'i tshad bstan pa da
NK076(mu)002:2971: ltar rang gsal gsum bral gyi chos nyid lta ba'i
NK076(mu)002:2972: don phyin ci ma log par mthong ba'i gang zag
NK076(mu)002:2973: rang gang dang gzhan gang dag gisa /
NK076(mu)002:2974: 'grel pa kha gcig gis de ltar lta ba'i don mthong ba'i mi ganga zhig gis /
NK076(mu)002:2977: lta ba'i don las gzhan du mi bsam par lta
NK076(mu)002:2978: ba'i don de kho na la blo 'dris shing goms
NK076(mu)002:2979: par bya'o // skyes bu dama pa 'bras bu machaga
NK076(mu)002:2980: gi dngos grub rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par 'dod
NK076(mu)002:2981: par bya'o // pasa / lta ba de la dus
NK076(mu)002:2982: rtag tu brtsona 'grus kyis don gasla bar gyis la
NK076(mu)002:2983: sgoms shig ces gdams pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:2984: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin rnams dang rgyu 'bras su 'brel tshul bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:2985: dper na mgron po rnams lam rgyus shes nas lam
NK076(mu)002:2986: du 'jug pa ji lta ba bzhin du lta ba
NK076(mu)002:2987: rtogs nas bsgom dgos pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:2988: rgyu shes pa lta ba dang rkyen 'jug pa ting
NK076(mu)002:2989: nge 'dzin rnams dang snga ma rgyu dang phyi ma
NK076(mu)002:2992: gzhi gnas lugs don dam kun rdzob dbyer med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:2993: ye shes ye nas rang la rang chas su gansa
NK076(mu)002:2994: pa'i don rang rig pa'i mngon sum du mthong ba
NK076(mu)002:2995: lta ba ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don
NK076(mu)002:2996: rnams / mtshams dang ris su gcod cing 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis ni le'u zhes bya sta /
NK076(mu)002:2997: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK076(mu)002:2998: yas bgrangs gnyis pa'i don du gda' 'o //
NK076(mu)002:2999: spyi don gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3000: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:3001: de'ang le'u gong mar chos kun sems nyid rig pa
NK076(mu)002:3002: badga nyid lhun grub kyi ngang chen po de la
NK076(mu)002:3003: lta ba rtogsa pas mos zhes thun mong ma yin
NK076(mu)002:3004: pa rtogs pa 'jal ba'i sgo nas le'u gsum pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3006: lta ba rtogs pa de yi rjes su goms par byed pa'i lam /
NK076(mu)002:3007: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin bshad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3008: gnyis pa don rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3009: dang po lam gong 'og gi 'brel ba /
NK076(mu)002:3010: de yang lam grangs sam dus kyi snga ma snga
NK076(mu)002:3011: ma de ting la sogs gang dang gang yin pa
NK076(mu)002:3012: de / lam grangs sam dus kyi phyi ma phyi
NK076(mu)002:3013: ma'i gcig spros la sogs gang yin re bskyed pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3015: snga ma snga ma thabs sam rgyu yin pa de bzhina du /
NK076(mu)002:3016: lam phyi ma phyi ma gcig spros la sogs ganga yin pa de /
NK076(mu)002:3017: lam snga ma snga ma de ting la sogs pa'i thabs las byung ba de'i 'bras bu yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3018: gnyis pa lam gyi dmigs rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3019: dang po mdor bstan gong du bstan pa da ltar lam snga phyi la rgyu dang 'bras bu'ang /
NK076(mu)002:3020: thabas dang thabs las byung ba'i 'brel la yod pa'i lam pa de'ang /
NK076(mu)002:3021: dpe na srid pa 'khor ba'i skye gnas kyi 'khor
NK076(mu)002:3022: la'i rang bzhin bardzusa skyes mngal skye la myur bul
NK076(mu)002:3023: yod pa'i tshul bzhin du shes rab dbang po dang
NK076(mu)002:3024: / brtsona 'grus bzang ba cig char ba bardzusa skyes dang /
NK076(mu)002:3025: ngan pa rim gyis pa mngal skyes kyis phye ba
NK076(mu)002:3026: lta bu'i rnam par dbye ba'i lus gnyis su bstan
NK076(mu)002:3027: par bya'o // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3031: dang po cig char ba'i ting 'dzin bsgom tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:3032: cig char ba ni srid par bardzusa nas skye ba de lus rdzogs par smin pa'i tshul bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:3033: rim gyis pa'i lta sgom las lhag par bden gsum
NK076(mu)002:3034: dbyer med rtogs pa'i gdings dang ldan ba'i skyes bu
NK076(mu)002:3035: de yis / de ting kun snang phyag rgya gcig spros kyi bsgom pa rnam pa bzhi las /
NK076(mu)002:3036: bzhi po zung 'brel gnyis med du ldan par /
NK076(mu)002:3037: dus gdod ma na lta ba rtogs ma thag nyid
NK076(mu)002:3038: nas bden bzhi cig chod du goms par byed pa'o
NK076(mu)002:3039: // lta ba rang byung mtha' dbus med pa'i thig
NK076(mu)002:3040: le chen po'i ranga bzhin du gsal ba de la
NK076(mu)002:3041: // / rim gyis bsgom pa stong chen /
NK076(mu)002:3043: dbyer med rgyu'i ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum ka dus
NK076(mu)002:3044: gcig la tha dad med par gnyis med thig le
NK076(mu)002:3045: chen por rdzogs la de ni bcos slad med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3046: de bzhin nyid kyi don ni mnyam pa'i dbyings dang
NK076(mu)002:3047: / de ni ma 'gags gsal bas kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK076(mu)002:3048: thig le chen po de ni sku dang ye shes su gsal bas rgyu yi ting 'dzin no //
NK076(mu)002:3049: rim gyis pa'i ting 'dzin gsum rim para bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:3050: rnams 'dir cig car dus gcig tu ldan pa yin
NK076(mu)002:3051: no // gnyis pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogsa shing bsgom pa las mi 'da' bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3052: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad nyid ya shes
NK076(mu)002:3053: lngar gsal ba rtogs pas lta ba rtogs pa'i don
NK076(mu)002:3054: de la bsgom pa ting nge 'dzina gyis rig pa
NK076(mu)002:3055: la dbang bsgyur nasa bsgom pa'i don ni /
NK076(mu)002:3056: tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga ru ngo bo yul med
NK076(mu)002:3057: rang gsal ba nyid ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3058: thugs ye shes lnga'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa
NK076(mu)002:3059: las mi 'da' bas phyag rgya chen pa'a //
NK076(mu)002:3060: gsum pa bye brag phye ste bshad pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3062: rab zag med kyi bden pa rtogs nas sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)002:3063: par bstan pa 'bring zag bcas kyi bden pa cig
NK076(mu)002:3066: mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig /de dang mthun par spyod pas sangs rgyas tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:3068: dang po mnyam pa nyid kyi don lta sgom las mi 'da' bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3069: gzhi don mnyam pa nyid la lta bas mnyam par rtogs nas sbyor ba yi /
NK076(mu)002:3070: sgom pas mnyam pa'i don las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshiga de'i don la mi 'da' bar gnas na /
NK076(mu)002:3071: gang yang ma spangs par 'bras bu mnyam rdzogsa bdag
NK076(mu)002:3072: nyid chen po sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po dang
NK076(mu)002:3073: dbye ba med pa'i sa thob par 'gyur bas so
NK076(mu)002:3074: // mnyam nyid de las 'das na sangs rgyas thob pa ma yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3075: gnyis pa spyod pa las mi 'da' zhing tshogs gnyis rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3076: yang na zhes 'dam ka'i tshig yin te bsrung du
NK076(mu)002:3077: med pa spyod pa'i dam tshig 'og nas 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:3078: 'ad lta bu / lta sgom gyi ngang nas ja
NK076(mu)002:3079: ltar spyad kyang bdag nyid chen po mnyam pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:3080: kyi sdom pa'i don las mi 'ad'a ba'i steng /
NK076(mu)002:3081: sgo gsum gyi byed spyod thams cad bsod nams dang
NK076(mu)002:3082: ye shes kyi tshagas chen po gnyis su rdzogs par
NK076(mu)002:3083: 'gyur ro // gnyis pa spyod pas sangs rgyas tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3084: dang po spyod lam mnyam pa nyid las mi 'da' ba /
NK076(mu)002:3085: rnal 'byong pa de 'gro 'ong gi spyod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3087: nyal zhing gnyid log pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3088: za zhing longs spyod pa'i dus na /
NK076(mu)002:3089: lta sgom gyi don las ma nyams pa mnyam pa
NK076(mu)002:3090: nyid de yi dbyings su gnas par gang gis spyod
NK076(mu)002:3091: na / rnal 'byor pa shes rab mchog tu gyur
NK076(mu)002:3092: pa cig char ba dag gis dus rtag tu de
NK076(mu)002:3094: gnyis pa de'i lta spyod ldan pas sangs rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3095: dbyingsa nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don gnas pa la
NK076(mu)002:3096: ni blos rtogs par byas nas dbyings de nyid la
NK076(mu)002:3097: spyod pa'i phyir / dbyings gang la spyod na skye
NK076(mu)002:3098: ba med pa'i dbyingsa nyid la lhag pa'i 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:3099: mchoga ga 'byung gnas gnyis med mnyam nyid la spyod
NK076(mu)002:3100: spyod pa'i phyir / pas / gnyis med mnyam pa
NK076(mu)002:3101: nyid de nyid rang yang mi gnas pa'i mya ngana
NK076(mu)002:3103: gnyis pa 'bring zag bcas kyi bden mthong cig char ba la chos gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:3104: dang po lta ba yul sems dbyer med du rtogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:3105: lta ba rtogs pa'i rang rig gi ye shes ni
NK076(mu)002:3106: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i gter ltar dgos
NK076(mu)002:3108: de chos thams cad la bltas na yanga /
NK076(mu)002:3109: me longa gi gzugs brnyan snang la rang bzhin med pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:3110: phyi nang chos kun la bltas kyang gzugs brnyan rang rgyud par mi snang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:3111: gnyis pa bzhag thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3115: dang po rtogs pa'i don la bzhag pas 'bras bu thob tshul /
NK076(mu)002:3116: rang gi shes pa'i rgyud kyi chos nyid ci yin
NK076(mu)002:3117: pa rnal 'byor pa ganga gis ye shes su ngo
NK076(mu)002:3118: shes shing / de'i ngang la bsgom bya sgom byed
NK076(mu)002:3119: gnyis su 'dzin pa las 'phags te blo gyen 'dar
NK076(mu)002:3120: rtsol med du 'dug par byed pa rnal 'byor ba
NK076(mu)002:3121: gang zhig chos nyid rtogs pa'i blo la rtsol med
NK076(mu)002:3122: du longs spyod pas byang chub 'thob bo //
NK076(mu)002:3123: gnyis pa dgongs pa'i ngo bo /
NK076(mu)002:3124: gdod nas rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid 'gyur med
NK076(mu)002:3125: g.yung drung lta bur ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don
NK076(mu)002:3126: la / lta ba 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK076(mu)002:3127: ya gdod ma nasa bden gsum mnyam pa nyid du
NK076(mu)002:3128: ngo bo rnama par dag pa rtogs nas mngon du
NK076(mu)002:3129: la / gyur cinga / ting nge 'dzin yul du
NK076(mu)002:3130: ma rtog pa zhi gnas dang sa lara gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:3131: la / gyur cinga / lhag mthong dang / de
NK076(mu)002:3132: gnyis zung 'jug la yang dag pa'i rtogs pa zhes
NK076(mu)002:3133: la / gyur cinga / lhag mthong dang / madzada pa'o // gsum pa yon tan 'byung tshul /
NK076(mu)002:3134: de'i nyams 'di 'drar bstan du med pas drod rtags
NK076(mu)002:3135: kyi yon tan sna tshagas pa 'byung ba yina pas
NK076(mu)002:3136: / de dang chos kyi bdag gnyis med pa'i sems
NK076(mu)002:3137: nyid snang stong tha dad med cing bdag nyid chen
NK076(mu)002:3138: po la yon tan nam 'bras bu thams cad zad
NK076(mu)002:3140: gnyis pa skyon bcos thabs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3141: dang po rnam rtog ye shes yin pas gnyen po mi bsten pa /
NK076(mu)002:3142: tshogs drug ma bkag pa las rnam rtog sna tshog
NK076(mu)002:3143: rgyu zhing 'byung yang 'byung dus rang bzhin med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3144: ngo bor rnam rtog skye pa'i dus nyid ngo shes
NK076(mu)002:3145: na ye shes kyi rang bzhin yin te /
NK076(mu)002:3146: yul sems dbang po rnam pa gsum du ma 'gags
NK076(mu)002:3147: par snang zhing snang dus rang rgyud pa med pas
NK076(mu)002:3148: rnam kun mchog ldan stong pa nyid yin pasa /
NK076(mu)002:3149: des na rnam par rtog pa'i rkyen rang ga ma ma skya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:3150: de las gzhan du ye shes bya ba bzang po
NK076(mu)002:3151: zhig brjod du med de gnyis med du rang grol
NK076(mu)002:3152: lo // gnyis pa blo thams cad 'dzin rtsol med par rang byung rang zhi ba /
NK076(mu)002:3154: chos thams cad semas nyid kyi nganga du 'du ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:3155: de'i ngo bo sems zhesa bya ba phyogs gcig tu gdags su meda de /
NK076(mu)002:3156: de nyid byed pa pos ma bcosa 'khor 'das lhun
NK076(mu)002:3157: grub tu gansa pas ya gdod ma nas byang chub
NK076(mu)002:3158: yin cing / de nyid ma rtogs pa'i 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:3159: thob par bya rgyu zhig gzhan na meda pas ya
NK076(mu)002:3160: gdod ma nas bade bar gshegs pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3161: dper na kha tog sngon po la nam mkha' zhes
NK076(mu)002:3162: par rang rgyud pas bzung basa na de la sprin
NK076(mu)002:3164: nam mkha'a yi ngo bo grub pa meda para mkhas pa ganga gisa shes pa de la na /
NK076(mu)002:3165: sgrib byed kyi sprin zhiga 'byung zhing sprin des nam mkha' khebas para mi srid pa de bazhana du /
NK076(mu)002:3166: rnal 'byor pas bsgom pa'i sems kyang rang grol du
NK076(mu)002:3167: 'gro bas gong gi dpe da ltar blta bar bya'o
NK076(mu)002:3168: // gsum pa bcos bslad med par bzhag pas 'bras bu rang byung tshul /
NK076(mu)002:3169: rtogs pa'i don la blo ma bcos rtsol med lhun
NK076(mu)002:3170: grub tu mnyam pa ja bzhin pa'i nganga du mnyam
NK076(mu)002:3172: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3173: dkyil 'khor mthar thug gi 'bras bu rang snang du
NK076(mu)002:3174: 'byung ba'o // gsum pa ji bzhin mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:3175: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid la ting nge 'dzin gyi gnas bacasa shing bsgoms na /
NK076(mu)002:3176: yon tan ni 'khor bar byed pa'i rgyu nyon mongas
NK076(mu)002:3177: pa dang 'bras bu sdug bsngal rnams mi 'byung sta
NK076(mu)002:3178: / dus rtag tu zag med bde ba la gnas shing /
NK076(mu)002:3179: 'bras bu bdag don byang chub chen po nyid thob cing /
NK076(mu)002:3180: gzhan don thun mong thun min gyi mtshan bzang po
NK076(mu)002:3181: sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dapa byad bzang po brgyad
NK076(mu)002:3182: cu kun dang ldana pa'i gzugs sku gnyis su snang
NK076(mu)002:3184: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis non pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3185: des 'bras bu sku gnyis thob pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3186: gnyis pa rim gyis pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3188: dper na srid pa bcud kyi 'gro ba rima para mngal nas smin pa'i tshul gyis /
NK076(mu)002:3189: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i yan lag la /
NK076(mu)002:3190: stong chen sogs lam lnga ru lus rnam par bzhag na /
NK076(mu)002:3191: lam pa gang dag phyi nang gi dangsa po'i chos
NK076(mu)002:3192: kun ranga gi rig pa byang chub yin pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:3193: / rtog pa 'gags te sha ba yi tshe gzung
NK076(mu)002:3194: 'dzin gyi rtog pa dang bral bas dona dama bden
NK076(mu)002:3196: stong pa chen po dang 'dra ba'i dper brjod pa'am sbyang gzhi 'am bslab bya yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3197: de nas 'di phyi gnyis kyi skye ba bar ma ste /
NK076(mu)002:3198: dbang po kun tshang thogs med du 'gro bas kun rdzoba bden pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3199: snying rje sgyu ma dang 'dra ba'i dape'am sbyang gazhi'am bslab bya yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3200: mngon byang lnga dang mtshungs par mngal nas skyes pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3201: dus lo bcu gnyis man chad gzhon nu ste phyag
NK076(mu)002:3202: rgya gcig pa / nyer lnga khyim thabs bzung zhing
NK076(mu)002:3203: bu tsha dang ldan pa ni phyag rgya spros pa
NK076(mu)002:3204: rgya gcig pa / / yo byad sna tshogs bsgrub pa tshogs sgrub dang 'dra ste rim pa gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3205: gcig spros tshogs sgrub gsum bden gnyis dbyer mada du bsgom pa'i lam zhes brjod da //
NK076(mu)002:3206: gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3208: sbyor lam bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3209: dang po la le'u bzhis ston te /
NK076(mu)002:3210: de la le'u gsum pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3212: de la dang pa don dam stong pa chen po'i
NK076(mu)002:3213: lam la barten par byed pa'i rnal 'byor pasa chos
NK076(mu)002:3214: rnams da bzhina nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin du gomsa
NK076(mu)002:3215: par bya ba yi thabs bstan pa la don bco
NK076(mu)002:3216: lnga ste / spyi dang khyad par sngon du bya
NK076(mu)002:3217: ba dang gcig bsgoms pa'i dagsa ched dang gnyis rton
NK076(mu)002:3218: yang snang mchan bsgom pa blo la bzhag pa'i thabas
NK076(mu)002:3219: lnga ste / dang gsum / bsgom pa'i ngo bo rnam grangs nges tshig dang bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:3220: ting 'dzin gyi mi mthun pa'i skyon ngos bzung ba dang lnga /
NK076(mu)002:3221: skyon de bcos thabs dang drug /bsgom pa'i nyams kyi rim pa dang bdun /
NK076(mu)002:3225: rtags dang bcu gcig rmis ltas kyi matshana ma dang bcu gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3226: ting 'dzin gyi yon tan dang bcu gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3227: 'da' ka ma'i man ngag dang bcu bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:3228: de ting ranga gi 'bras bu dang bco lnga yis
NK076(mu)002:3229: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor yongs su rdzogsa para
NK076(mu)002:3230: 'gyur ra // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la don bco lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:3233: khyad par gyi sngon du bya ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3235: dang po sngon du dbang thob dgos par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3236: gsang sngags kyi rigs can skyes bu gang zhig dper na senga ge gcig pur gnas pa /
NK076(mu)002:3238: gzhan zil gyis gnon pa bzhina du grogs ngan spangs
NK076(mu)002:3239: nas gcig pur rgyu bas de bzhin nyid kyi ting
NK076(mu)002:3240: 'dzin la 'jug pa'i sngona du lhag pa gzugs brnyan
NK076(mu)002:3241: gyi dkyil 'khor gyi ri mor phyi nang gsang gsum
NK076(mu)002:3242: gyi dbang rnams rim pa bzhin du rdzogs par mnos
NK076(mu)002:3243: shing / gnyis pa lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs par bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:3244: rgyud lung man ngag gi don ma nor par ston pa'i rdo rje slob dpon /
NK076(mu)002:3245: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs /
NK076(mu)002:3246: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK076(mu)002:3248: zhes yon tan brgyad ldan de lta bu la sgo
NK076(mu)002:3249: gsum gus pas mchod cing brtson 'grus kyis rang rgyud
NK076(mu)002:3250: yongs su sbyangs pa'i sgo nas rtogs pa zhes lta
NK076(mu)002:3251: ba dag mnyam chen po mngon sum gsal bar byas
NK076(mu)002:3252: nas / rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshaga dang
NK076(mu)002:3253: /1 bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin /2 spyi dang rang
NK076(mu)002:3254: gi mtshan nyid shes pa'i shes rab 3lta ba'i gding
NK076(mu)002:3255: nas / dang / bden gnyis byang chub kyi sems 4bskyed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3256: snying rja 5che ba dang lnga ni /
NK076(mu)002:3257: 'jig rten pa'i yo byad las lhag pa'i yo byad gong gi lnga rgyud la rdzogs par bya /
NK076(mu)002:3258: gsum pa yo byad lnga'i nang nas khyad par gzhan
NK076(mu)002:3259: don du sems bskyed nas sgom par dam bca' ba
NK076(mu)002:3260: / gong gi yo byad lnga rdzogs pa de yi
NK076(mu)002:3261: nang nasa bu gcig pa la ma yi byams sems
NK076(mu)002:3262: / ldan pasa / khams gsum 'khor ba na gansa
NK076(mu)002:3263: pa'i rigs drug gi sems can thams cad thar ba
NK076(mu)002:3264: myang 'das kyi sar 'agda par dam bca' ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3265: bzhi pa tshad med bzhi sngon du song bas sa bslang ba /
NK076(mu)002:3266: sems bskyed mi nyams pa'i thabs la tshangas pa la
NK076(mu)002:3267: sogs pa'i gansa su skye bar byed pa'i tshad med
NK076(mu)002:3268: pa bzhi sngon du song bas /
NK076(mu)002:3269: rang gi yid du 'ong zhing sa dgra sogs skyon
NK076(mu)002:3270: med pa'i sa btsal nas sa bslang ste sa chog
NK076(mu)002:3271: bya / lnga pa gnas khang brtsigs shing gdan bsham pa /
NK076(mu)002:3272: gnas khang che chung ran cing 'tshams par byas te zhal ba'i byi dor dang ldan par byas la /
NK076(mu)002:3274: sman gla rtsi sogs kyis sa'i skyon dang nad dang
NK076(mu)002:3275: dug sbrul sogs kyi gnod pa bsrung bar byas nas
NK076(mu)002:3276: / yul pi par ta'i ras kyi stan nang tshangs can dang ldan para bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3277: drug pa tshogs bsag cing 'brel thag bcad pa /
NK076(mu)002:3278: byang chub sgrub pa'i 'gal rkyen bar chad thams cad
NK076(mu)002:3279: bsal zhing lam gyi cha rkyen tshogs gnyis rdzogsa par
NK076(mu)002:3280: bya phyir / tshagas 'khor dang sbyin sreg brgya rtsa la sogs bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3286: bskor ba la sogs dge ba'i dpung tshogas la 'bad par bya /
NK076(mu)002:3288: nang slob dpon dang mched lcam rnams kyi bu lon
NK076(mu)002:3289: dang 'brel chags pa thams cad kun ting nge 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:3290: las gzhan pa rnams gegs yin pa'i phyir dur rkun
NK076(mu)002:3291: gyi wa sngar ma lta bu'i sems kyis gong gi
NK076(mu)002:3293: bdun pa cha rkyen bsdu zhing grogs btsal ba /
NK076(mu)002:3294: khamas gso ba'i cha rkyen sman zas rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:3295: ting nge 'dzin skye ba'i cha rkyen bla ma'i gdams ngag zab mo'i dpe cha dang /
NK076(mu)002:3296: grogs nyams can la sogs 'khor ba'i cha rkyen rnams bsdus la /
NK076(mu)002:3297: lam gyi bar chad bgegs dang nad bsrung ba yi cha rkyen nam /
NK076(mu)002:3298: cho ga rnams sngona du rdzogsa par byas nas phyi 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga'am /
NK076(mu)002:3299: gsang ba'i longs spyod rig ma'ang mtshan nyid dang ldan pa 'du byas la /
NK076(mu)002:3300: dgra bgegs nad gsum gyi 'atsha ba bzlog pa'i cha rkyen /
NK076(mu)002:3301: go mtshon phur pa yungs dkar gu gul la sogs pa'ang nyer rdzogs su bzhag go //
NK076(mu)002:3302: gnyis pa khyad par gyi sngon du bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:3303: de ltar thun mong du kun gyi spyi yi sngon du 'gro ba rnams rdzogs par byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:3304: khyad par de ting 'di nyid kyi sngon du bya
NK076(mu)002:3305: ba ni mchoda pa 'bul ba'i rten du dngos grub
NK076(mu)002:3306: nye ba'i lha yi dam gyi lha'i sku'i gzugs brnyan
NK076(mu)002:3307: rab gnas can rang gi mdun du bzhugs su gsol
NK076(mu)002:3315: bsngo ba'i yan lag brgyad pa'i tshul yongs su bzung la de tshar nasa /
NK076(mu)002:3316: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal pos /
NK076(mu)002:3317: stong pa nyid kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)002:3318: de'i ngang las snying rje chen po'i tshad med bzhi ste yan lag brgyad du bzhed do //
NK076(mu)002:3319: tshogs shing rnams 'od du zhu yongs su gyur te
NK076(mu)002:3320: bdag gi spyi gtsug tu thim par byas pas sgrib
NK076(mu)002:3321: kun dag / rang nyid 'od du zhu ba'i rjes la ting nge 'dzin la 'jug par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3322: gnyis pa dgos ched la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3323: lam rim par bgrod nas sangs rgyas pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK076(mu)002:3324: de ting rang la 'jug pa'i dgos ched do //
NK076(mu)002:3328: ye shes lngar dag pa rnam pa gsum ma nor bar rtogs shing /
NK076(mu)002:3329: ting nge 'dzin gyis rang rig pa'i rgyal po la
NK076(mu)002:3330: dbang bsgyur nas cig char du goms pa'am bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:3331: yis / 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK076(mu)002:3332: kyi mchog chos sku 'di nyid rnyed par 'gyur ba'o
NK076(mu)002:3333: yis / // gnyis pa des grub pa'i don /
NK076(mu)002:3334: gong gi gtan tshigs de yi phyir lta ba mthong
NK076(mu)002:3335: ba'i rjes la de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:3336: bsgom mo // de ni snying rja chen po kun
NK076(mu)002:3337: snang gi ting nge 'dzin 'byung ba'i gzhi'am rgyu ru
NK076(mu)002:3338: bsgom mo // bzhag ces bya / lam gong 'og
NK076(mu)002:3339: gi go rima 'byung ba'ang snga ma'i ting 'dzin gyis
NK076(mu)002:3340: rjes la phyi ma 'byung ba de bzhin du nges
NK076(mu)002:3341: bsgom mo // bzhag ces bya / so // gnyis pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3346: lam pa gang dag sngags kyi skal ba dang ldan yang blo cung zad dman pa rim gyis pas /
NK076(mu)002:3347: mi mthun pa'i phyogs gzhan sala ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK076(mu)002:3348: mthun pa'i phyogs sgrub bya chos sku don du gnyer ba'i dgos ched gnyis yod pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:3349: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3351: ting 'dzin la snyoms par 'jug par byed pa de'ang
NK076(mu)002:3352: dkyus kyi snga ma gzhan sel ba'ang bdag gzhan gnyis
NK076(mu)002:3353: kyi don du bsgom pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3354: bsal bya lhan skyes kun brtags kyi ma rig pas
NK076(mu)002:3355: phyin ci log tu 'khrul pa'i snang ba thar dka'
NK076(mu)002:3356: ba 'dam rdzab 'dra ba'i dbyings su chud pa /
NK076(mu)002:3357: bsal phyir ye shes kyi yul du gsal bas sgron
NK076(mu)002:3358: ma'i 'od dang 'dra ba'i mda' lta bu ting nge
NK076(mu)002:3360: de'i yon tan gyis rang rgyud la yod pa'i gti mug gi mun pa rnam par bsal te /
NK076(mu)002:3361: don dam rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i nyonamongasa pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3362: zug rngu med pas bde ba'i mchoga tu gyur pa
NK076(mu)002:3363: de nyid snang bar byas so //
NK076(mu)002:3364: de yang madra bsdu na sgrib pa'i tshogas rnams ting
NK076(mu)002:3365: 'dzin bsgoms pas mun pa la sgron me btegs pas
NK076(mu)002:3366: gsal ba'i snang bar song ba'i tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:3367: gnyis pa don gnyer la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3368: dang po chos nyid don du gnyer ba /
NK076(mu)002:3369: chos nyid kyi dbyings nam mkha' lta bu'i thog tu
NK076(mu)002:3370: phebs pas dkyil phyogs su thug ba med pas yangas
NK076(mu)002:3371: pa la / chos nyid rtogs pa'i blo shes rab
NK076(mu)002:3372: kyis dus myur ba cig chod du don chos nyid
NK076(mu)002:3373: pa la / la 'gro ba'ang / don la 'agro
NK076(mu)002:3374: ba med cing 'ong ba med de mtha' gang la
NK076(mu)002:3375: mi gnas pa gnas lugs byanga chub kyi sems mchog
NK076(mu)002:3376: gnyis su ma skyes pas a zug rngu med pas
NK076(mu)002:3378: gnyis pa dngos grub don du gnyer ba'i dgos ched /
NK076(mu)002:3379: dper na nyi ma shar dus mun pa snang bar gyur pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3380: dug ha la dug nad la rtsi'i mchog gi tshul bzhina du /
NK076(mu)002:3381: rtog pa'i ngo bo ma spangs par chos nyid du
NK076(mu)002:3382: dbang bsgyur bar byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin te
NK076(mu)002:3383: lam pa kun gyi don du gnyer ba yi mchog
NK076(mu)002:3384: thun gang dag ma lus kun /
NK076(mu)002:3385: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'ad yisa thob pa'i grogs byed par 'gyura ro //
NK076(mu)002:3386: gnyis pa ni gal te de ting stong pa chen
NK076(mu)002:3387: po'i rnal 'byor 'di med pas skyon ci yod ce
NK076(mu)002:3388: na / dper na rgya mtsho'i 'jing gi pha bong
NK076(mu)002:3389: de steng du mi thon zhing dkyil skam por yod
NK076(mu)002:3390: na / pa ltar / yun bskal bar dngos por
NK076(mu)002:3391: 'dzin pa'i lam la 'bad nas 'bras bu btsal bar
NK076(mu)002:3392: na / pa ltar / byas kyang / gnas lugs
NK076(mu)002:3393: de bzhin nyid kyi don gyi rlan med na bla
NK076(mu)002:3394: na med pa'i byang chub snying po yi myu gu
NK076(mu)002:3395: bskams pa yin te 'bras bu sangs rgyas mi 'byung
NK076(mu)002:3396: na / pa ltar / byas kyang / ngo // gsum pa bsgom pa'i thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3398: de ting bsgom pa de yi phyir lhag ma yi lus cha snyomsa pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:3399: lus bad ba dang ldana zhing sems thar pa la
NK076(mu)002:3400: brod pasa lus chosa bdun gyi tshul du ldana par
NK076(mu)002:3401: byas pa ni rja btsun rnam par snang mdzad bazhana
NK076(mu)002:3402: no // gnyis pa sems kyi bzhag thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3404: lus su 'adzana pa dang rtsol ba'i rtog pa meda
NK076(mu)002:3405: pa'i semas kyis ting nga 'dzin la 'dug par bya
NK076(mu)002:3406: ba da yanga blo chung ba bla ma'i gadmas ngaga
NK076(mu)002:3407: la brten nas mnyam par 'jog /blo che ba rang
NK076(mu)002:3408: gi shes raba kya stobsa kyis lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3409: ngang la blo bazhaga pasa ting nge 'dzin la gomsa
NK076(mu)002:3411: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3412: dang po blo chung ba gdams ngag gi stobs kyis bzhag pa /
NK076(mu)002:3413: mdor bstan gyi sngona du brjod pa'i gdams ngag gi
NK076(mu)002:3414: stobs kyis bzhag pa'i slob bu des yul 'du 'dzis
NK076(mu)002:3415: dben pa'i sara / gser g.yu la sogs rin chen dang lhab lhub dar zab dang /
NK076(mu)002:3416: bza' btung la sogs pa'i longs spyod kyis bla ma
NK076(mu)002:3417: dam pa mnyes par byas nas slob bu da slob
NK076(mu)002:3418: dpon gyi pang du ste mdun du drang bor bazhaga
NK076(mu)002:3419: la / mkha' 'gro dang rna nyan la sogs bgegs
NK076(mu)002:3420: rnams drag sngags kyis bskrad la rat+na'i sbubs mchus rna
NK076(mu)002:3422: gzhan gyis ma thos par gdams ngag zhib par shub
NK076(mu)002:3423: bur rna ba g.yon par bsgrag cing sems su bstim
NK076(mu)002:3424: / gdams ngag dngos ni mchog thun gyi dngos grub
NK076(mu)002:3425: dus myur du tshe 'di la 'grub par 'dod na
NK076(mu)002:3426: / / bsgom bya sgom byed shin tu mi damgas
NK076(mu)002:3427: par chos nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyings su bsgom
NK076(mu)002:3428: / / para bya / gnyis pa blo che ba
NK076(mu)002:3429: shes rab kyi stobs kyis bsgom pa de la gnyis
NK076(mu)002:3430: / / para bya / / dang po mdor bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3431: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma shes rab stobs kyis bzhag pa la'ang /
NK076(mu)002:3432: rig pa gsal stong gi ting nge 'dzin spya blugs
NK076(mu)002:3433: dang sngar gyi lta ba dran par byas shing mthong
NK076(mu)002:3434: pa'i rjes su gsal stong ngang du bzhag pa dang
NK076(mu)002:3435: gnyis so // gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3437: lta ba rtogs rjes su bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3439: dang po bdag dang bdag gir med par rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:3440: bdag ngar 'dzin pa rnam shes dang bdag gisa myong ba'i phung po dang /
NK076(mu)002:3441: gzhan 'byung ba yul du snang ba rnams ni bsgom
NK076(mu)002:3442: bya'i yul mi dmigs gsum las shin tu blos ma
NK076(mu)002:3443: dmigs te skye med dbyings su grol bar bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:3444: dran pa tsam yul gyis ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo
NK076(mu)002:3445: bo yul med rang gsal du bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3446: de'i rgyu mtshan ni rnal 'byor pa rang gi rig
NK076(mu)002:3447: pa chos nyid gsal stong gi ngang la gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:3448: yi don ni de byed pa po sus kyang ma
NK076(mu)002:3449: byas zhing rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung ba ste
NK076(mu)002:3450: / des phyi nang gi chos thams cad skyes med
NK076(mu)002:3451: de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gsal bar sbyor ba
NK076(mu)002:3452: ni bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis su 'dzin pa meda
NK076(mu)002:3454: skye med chos dbyings kya ngang du rig pa'am ngo
NK076(mu)002:3455: bo ma grub pas chos thams cad thima ste yul
NK076(mu)002:3456: sems gnyis med du gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3457: gnyis par rang byung spro bsdu med par rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:3458: rgyu rkyen med pa rang byung gsal bas ye shes ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khora gyis /
NK076(mu)002:3459: shes bya phyi nang gi chos ma lus pa thams
NK076(mu)002:3460: cad chos nyid da bzhin nyid kyi nganga du gsal
NK076(mu)002:3462: 'on kyang sdud par byed pa dang ma sdud par 'jog pa gnyis ka grub pa mina te /
NK076(mu)002:3464: de nyid ma nor zhing mi bslu bas na yang
NK076(mu)002:3465: daga pa'i don ma bcos ba'i de kho na nyid
NK076(mu)002:3466: rig pa yul med du rang gsal bar 'dug pa'
NK076(mu)002:3467: //gsum pa bsgom bya sgom byed med pa rig pa
NK076(mu)002:3469: bsgom bar bya ba'i yul chos nyid dang bsgom par
NK076(mu)002:3470: byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis ka don dam par ma
NK076(mu)002:3472: don chosa nyid yid kyi yul du bsgom para bya ba'ang med de /
NK076(mu)002:3473: de ltar don dama par bsgom para bya ba'i yul meda pasa na /
NK076(mu)002:3474: bsgom bya'i yul gang la'ang blo'i yul du mi 'jug
NK076(mu)002:3475: pa ste gnyis su med par gsal ba de ka
NK076(mu)002:3476: ting 'dzin la zhugs pa'i machaga yin te /
NK076(mu)002:3477: bzhag tu med pa'i bzhag thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:3478: bzhi pa bsam bya bsam byed med par rig pa spyi blugs su bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:3479: chos nyid blo'i yul du bsam par bya rgyu cir med pas yang bsam par mi bya sta /
NK076(mu)002:3480: 'o na mi bsam pa nyid bsam mo zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:3481: ched du bsam pa dgag pa'i phyir mi bsam par yang /
NK076(mu)002:3483: de nyid yong yer bcad du med pas bsam mi
NK076(mu)002:3484: bsam gyi yul gang la blo rnam par mi sems
NK076(mu)002:3485: pa yi ting 'dzin de ni yul med rang gsal
NK076(mu)002:3486: bas rang rig mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du gnas
NK076(mu)002:3487: pa nyid do // gnyis pa lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes su bsgom pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3491: dang po shes rab mchog gis rtogs pa'i lta ba
NK076(mu)002:3492: 'dir go ba lhag pa don dam pa'i byang chub
NK076(mu)002:3493: samas kyi de bzhin nyid ni /
NK076(mu)002:3494: dngos por shin tu ma dmigas shing blo yis brtag par dka' ba de ni /
NK076(mu)002:3495: bar snang ltar yangs las gzhi ltar rgya che rgya mtsho ltar gting zab pasa /
NK076(mu)002:3496: de'i ting de'i sngon du shes raba dang ldan pas
NK076(mu)002:3497: gsang sngags zab pas de'i don lta ba rtogs par
NK076(mu)002:3498: 'gyur te / rtog dpyod kyis lta ba'i don dran
NK076(mu)002:3499: bar byas te de'i rjes su ngang ma shor ba'i
NK076(mu)002:3501: gnyis pa rang gi rtogs pa'i ngo bo la 'gro 'ong dang mtha' dbus med pa /
NK076(mu)002:3502: byang chub kyi sems de dang por gang nas kyang ma 'ongs mthar gar yang ma 'gro bas /
NK076(mu)002:3503: des na 'gro ba dang 'ong bar bya ba gnyis su grub pa min no //
NK076(mu)002:3504: don de shin tu blos brtag par dka' zhing yul du mi dmigs pas na /
NK076(mu)002:3505: spros pa'i mtha' dang bral bas dbus kyang 'di zhes brtag tu med do //
NK076(mu)002:3506: gnyis pa sgoms pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3507: dang po rtogs pa'i don la gnyis su med par rang snang gi sgom pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3508: 'o na ji ltar yin na gzung 'dzin gnyis dang
NK076(mu)002:3509: brala ba'i rang gi rig pa nyid dmigs bya dmigs
NK076(mu)002:3510: byed med pa'i tshul du rang gsal bas der snang
NK076(mu)002:3511: ngo // bsgom bya chos kyi dbyings dang dbyings de
NK076(mu)002:3512: rtogs byed kyi ye shes gnyis kyang gzhan na yod
NK076(mu)002:3513: ngo // pa min te / rang gi rig pa
NK076(mu)002:3514: gsal stong de kho na tsam du zada pas yul
NK076(mu)002:3516: gnyis pa bsgom thabs de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3517: dang po dmigs pas gol la dmigs med sangs rgyas yin par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3518: blo chung ba gang zhiga gis bsgom bya dmigas nasa ting 'dzin la blo 'jug pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3519: dmigs pa yod pa da srid du 'jiga rten rgyang 'phena pa dang 'dra la /
NK076(mu)002:3520: stong pa yul du dmigs nas blos 'ajug tu meda
NK076(mu)002:3521: cing yul med rang gsal ba de ni sangsa rgyas
NK076(mu)002:3522: kyi dgongs pa yina para na /
NK076(mu)002:3523: thub pa'i dabnga pa nyid dang rgyal ba kun gyis gsungsa pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3524: gnyis pa dmigs pas dmigs med mi mthong ba dpe dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:3525: blos nges par bsgom bya chos nyid cig blo yul
NK076(mu)002:3526: du bsam zhing de la yul du byas shing dmigs
NK076(mu)002:3528: dper na phra rab khab mig tu 'then thag skud pa 'dzud pa lta bus /
NK076(mu)002:3529: don chos nyid da bzhin nyid dmigs su med pa de'i don mi mthong ste /
NK076(mu)002:3530: 'then thag skud pa khab mig tu 'dzud pas nam mkha' chen po mi mthong ba bzhin na //
NK076(mu)002:3531: bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3533: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor skye med mnyam pa
NK076(mu)002:3534: de bzhin nyid la ngo bo tha dad du ngos
NK076(mu)002:3535: bzung ba bzhi na du rnam grangsa kyang 'jug cinga
NK076(mu)002:3536: / zhor la ngesa tshiga dang rnama pa gsum nges par 'byung ba yin /
NK076(mu)002:3537: de bas kun snang la sogs lam kun la ngo
NK076(mu)002:3538: bo nges tshig rnam grangs gsum 'byor bar gyis shig
NK076(mu)002:3539: /gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3540: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi don gyi rnam grangs
NK076(mu)002:3541: spyir bstan pa nyan rang la ltos na chen pa
NK076(mu)002:3542: gsang sngags la ltos na damna pas na dbu ma
NK076(mu)002:3543: pas spros pa'i mtha' brgyad po bkag cing bsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:3544: don / rgyu rkyen las ma skyes shing /
NK076(mu)002:3545: ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i stong pa nyid du 'dod do //
NK076(mu)002:3546: sngar ma stong pa 'phral du stong pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:3547: ye gdod ma nas stong pa la stong pa'i tha snyad tsam yang bral bas /
NK076(mu)002:3548: skye 'gag rtag chad 'gro 'ong gcig dang du ma'i
NK076(mu)002:3549: spros pa yi mtha' brgyad dang bral bar 'doda la
NK076(mu)002:3550: bral ba tsam 'dzin pa yang ma yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3551: sngags kri ya pa ganga gis ranga gi samas nyid
NK076(mu)002:3552: dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma meda pa'i de bazhana
NK076(mu)002:3553: nyid rnam par dag pa chos nyid 'gyu stong du
NK076(mu)002:3554: 'dod pa dang / rnal 'byor yo ga pas chos
NK076(mu)002:3555: dbyings mnyam pa nyid la spros pa'i matshana ma meda
NK076(mu)002:3556: pa'i de bzhin nyid snang stong du 'dod pa dang
NK076(mu)002:3557: 'dod pa dang / / ma h+aa yo gas 'khor
NK076(mu)002:3558: 'das gnyis med lhun grub mnyam pa chen po'i de
NK076(mu)002:3559: 'dod pa dang / / bzhin nyid do // gnyis
NK076(mu)002:3560: pa khyad par du ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid rgyas
NK076(mu)002:3561: par bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:3562: dang po ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid spags tshul /
NK076(mu)002:3563: de bzhin nyid kyi rnam grangsa bzhi'i rim pa tha
NK076(mu)002:3564: ma ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid ni byin brlabs cir
NK076(mu)002:3566: yod tan mthar thug gi 'bras bu lhun grub thob pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:3567: ngo bo don dam dkor bdun snang stong gnyis su med pas na kun gyi bla mar gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3568: gnyis pa rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:3569: dang po rnam grangs ma 'dres par yon tan gyi cha nas ming grangs bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3570: bla mar gyur pa de la'nga gnas skabsa kyi ming gi rnams grangs su phyes na /
NK076(mu)002:3571: chos rnams bzang ngan spang blang bral ba mnyam nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:3572: chos kun yon tan lhun grub dang /
NK076(mu)002:3573: mtha' gang yang ma grub pas mtha'a bral /
NK076(mu)002:3574: mtshon pa dang bral bas tha snyad meda /
NK076(mu)002:3575: rnam kun mchog dang ldan pasa stong chen /
NK076(mu)002:3576: rgyu rkyen dang bral bas ma skyes /
NK076(mu)002:3577: gang yang 'byung ba med pas chos dbyings la sogs
NK076(mu)002:3578: ngo bo'i yon tan gyi bye brag cha re nas
NK076(mu)002:3579: ming re brjod para zad do //
NK076(mu)002:3580: gnyis pa de gang yang mi 'gal bar gtan tshigs ting nge gsum dang ldan par gnas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:3581: de ltar mnyam nyid la sogs bdun po de re
NK076(mu)002:3582: re'ang gnas skabs kyi dbye bas gong bstan ltar ngo
NK076(mu)002:3583: bo thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3584: sgra'i ming gi don mtshon pa'i nges tshiga thun mong du brjod pa yang /
NK076(mu)002:3585: sgrub par byed pa'i gtan tshigs kyi yan lag tu ldan pa yin nam zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:3586: lung man ngag rigs pa rnam pa gsum thams cad
NK076(mu)002:3587: la phrugs para sbyor ba rgyud las 'byung ba yin
NK076(mu)002:3588: te / gsum pa bsgom gyi ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:3589: don dang ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo /
NK076(mu)002:3590: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyi 'bras bu /
NK076(mu)002:3593: dang po don dang ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo dngos /
NK076(mu)002:3594: theg pa 'og ma las lhag pa'i ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid kyi don mchog gang yin pa de /
NK076(mu)002:3595: 'khor 'das kyi dngosa po rnams su snang ba'i dus
NK076(mu)002:3596: nyid na sems dngos po rang rgyud par grub med
NK076(mu)002:3597: pas na / rtog pa'i blo gang du'ang smra bsam gyi yul lasa 'das pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:3598: ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK076(mu)002:3599: mu mtha' med pa'i dbyings dang /
NK076(mu)002:3600: sgrib g.yogs dang bral bar gsal bas ye shes don dam ste /
NK076(mu)002:3601: gnyis pa de nyid zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3602: don dam ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi rang
NK076(mu)002:3603: bzhin gsal bar rtogs pa'i mthar mi gaya ba ste
NK076(mu)002:3604: / spros pa'i mtshan ma zhi gansa mi rtog pa'i ngang la gnas pa /
NK076(mu)002:3605: rig pa rang gsal mngon sum lhag gis mthong bas lhag mthong /
NK076(mu)002:3606: de gnyis tha dad med pas zung du 'brel bas gsal bar zung du 'brel lo //
NK076(mu)002:3607: gnyis pa ni de tsam na chos thams cad rang
NK076(mu)002:3608: bzhin med pas shes rab mu mtha' med pas dbyings
NK076(mu)002:3609: nyid du dbyer med pa de la /
NK076(mu)002:3610: bsgom bya chos kyi dbyings la sgom byed blo'i shes
NK076(mu)002:3611: rab kyis rtogs pa'i dbyings de gnyis na tha dad
NK076(mu)002:3612: med par rnam par sbyar ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3613: de ltar blo'i shes rab dang chos kyi dbyings nyid tha dad med par sbyor ba yis /
NK076(mu)002:3614: byang ba stong pa chub pa snang ba dbyer med
NK076(mu)002:3615: pas rda rje spros pa med pa'i thig le yin
NK076(mu)002:3617: bsgom pa de yang so sor rtog pa'i shes rab
NK076(mu)002:3618: kyis lta ba mthong ba'i rjes su bsgom pa dang
NK076(mu)002:3619: / mnyam gzhag gi yul mi dmigs bsgom pa'i ting
NK076(mu)002:3620: 'dzin gyi ngo bo shin tu'ang mi dmigs pa dang
NK076(mu)002:3621: / / rjes su thob pa'i shes pa'ang mi dmigs pa'i rim pa yisa /
NK076(mu)002:3622: bsgom bya'i yul du mi gnas shing /
NK076(mu)002:3623: bsgom pa'i ngo bor mi rtog /rjes bdag gis bsgom so so'i nga rgyal gyis rlom semas med pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3624: bzhi pa nges tshig la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:3625: dang po bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi nges tshig
NK076(mu)002:3626: /stong pa'i ngang las rang bzhin ngang gis chos dang
NK076(mu)002:3627: gang zag gi bdag gnyis su grub pa med pas
NK076(mu)002:3628: na / bsgom bya yi yul dang sgom byed kyi
NK076(mu)002:3629: shes pa gnyis ka rang bzhin mi dmigs pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:3630: na / / nam mkha' ltar blo'i yul gyis bsgom
NK076(mu)002:3631: bya sgom byed kyi 'adu byed kun dang bral ba
NK076(mu)002:3632: na / / / blo gang du'ang bsam du med
NK076(mu)002:3633: pa'i ngang la 'dug pa tsam la bsgom zhes tha
NK076(mu)002:3635: gnyis pa 'du 'bral med par bsgom pa'i nges tshig
NK076(mu)002:3636: /bsgom bya sgom byed kyi 'adu shes kyis yul snang
NK076(mu)002:3637: stong la sogs pa gang du'ang 'dzin pa ma zhugs
NK076(mu)002:3638: na / chos nyid bsgom pa'i ro la 'dod cing
NK076(mu)002:3639: chags pa med pas rang gi blo dang don gnyis
NK076(mu)002:3641: lnga pa skyon la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:3643: de lta gdams ngag gi stobs dang /
NK076(mu)002:3644: de ltar shes rab kyi stobs kyis mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe /
NK076(mu)002:3645: ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i dus kyi skyon dang /
NK076(mu)002:3646: rjes spyod lam gyis ting 'dzin la sgrib pa yi skyon /
NK076(mu)002:3647: khams kyi skyon rnams nor bar skyon ngos zin nasa
NK076(mu)002:3648: bcos na ting 'dzin mi 'phrog par bya ba'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:3649: skyon gyi rnam grangs mdo tsam zhig brjod par bya
NK076(mu)002:3650: ba ni / gnyis pa rgyas pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3651: ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i dus kyi skyon /
NK076(mu)002:3653: spyod lam sgom chen gyi skyon drug go //
NK076(mu)002:3655: dang po thun mong dang dogs log gi skyon bco brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:3656: las dang po pas bla ma'i gdams ngag gi dmigs pa brjed pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3657: g.yo nyams sems bying ba'i skyon gyis mi gsal ba des zhi lhag zung 'brel spyir sgrib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3658: bying ba ni rang bzhin gyis bying ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3660: ched du bya bas bying ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3661: dang po bad kan 'du ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3663: gnyis pa lus ngal dub kyi las byas pa /
NK076(mu)002:3666: gsum pa lus snyes mig btsum khang pa mun nag gos 'thug pa sogs kyis lhag mthong la sgrib /
NK076(mu)002:3667: rgod pa ni rang bzhin dang /
NK076(mu)002:3670: dang po rlung shas che ba dang 'dod chags che ba /
NK076(mu)002:3671: ting 'dzin la blo gnas su mi 'dod yul sna tshogs la 'phro ba /
NK076(mu)002:3672: gnyis par bar chad 'byung ba ni rang dbang med par 'gal rkyen sna tshogs kyis g.yeng ba /
NK076(mu)002:3675: gsum pa dgong mo gos srab pa /
NK076(mu)002:3676: snang g.yeng che sar sdod pa /
NK076(mu)002:3677: lta stangs bstod pa sogs kyis zhi gnas la sgrib ste drug go //
NK076(mu)002:3678: de rnams rgyu gang las byung na blo ched du rtsol bas rgod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3679: gnyen pos ched du ma rtsol bar byed pa las bying ba 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3680: khams gsum sa dgur gol du dogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3681: rtag chad du log pa yi dogs ba ste bcu gcig dang /
NK076(mu)002:3682: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi bo kun gyi thun mong gi skyon ni /
NK076(mu)002:3683: gong gi brjed dang bying rgod drug dang bdun te rnam grangs bco brgyad da //
NK076(mu)002:3684: gnyis pa g.yeng ba'i skyon drug /gong gi sgrib pa
NK076(mu)002:3685: da bzhin ting 'dzin la g.yenga ba yi skyon rnam
NK076(mu)002:3686: pa drug sta gang zhen rang bzhin nam ngo bosa
NK076(mu)002:3687: 1g.yeng ba ni sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa snang
NK076(mu)002:3688: rkyang la sogs lnga'i thog tu lung ma bstan sdod
NK076(mu)002:3689: pa'o // phyi rol 'dod yon gyi yul lngar shes pa 'phro bas phyi rol gyi g.yeng ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3691: rgod pa med pa ting 'dzin gyis ro myong nas zhen na nang 2gi g.yeng ba yin te /
NK076(mu)002:3693: gdul bya gzhan dad par bya ba'i phyir mtshan bcas
NK076(mu)002:3694: kyi dge sbyor byed pa ni mtshan ma 4yi g.yeng
NK076(mu)002:3695: ba'o // rang gi ting 'dzin las 'jig rten pa'i 'gog pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa sogs gzhan nam /
NK076(mu)002:3696: theg pa 'og ma gazhana gyi gzhung de yi lugs
NK076(mu)002:3697: kyis ting nge 'dzin la sems 'phro ba ni yida
NK076(mu)002:3699: sgom pa bzang po nga la yod pa' snyam pasa
NK076(mu)002:3700: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i ting 'dzin la snyoms par 'jug
NK076(mu)002:3701: pa ni snyoms 'jug 6 gi g.yeng ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3702: de drug gi dbang du song ba /
NK076(mu)002:3703: gnas ngan pa 'khor ba'i skye ba len par the tshom med do //
NK076(mu)002:3704: gsum pa bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu /
NK076(mu)002:3705: sngar gyi yul la ma rtog pa'i dran pa byung
NK076(mu)002:3706: nas de'i rjes su rtog pa 'brang ba ste nyams
NK076(mu)002:3707: g.yo thob la sgrib pa dang gcig /skyon ched du
NK076(mu)002:3708: 'gog pa zung 'brel la sgrib pa dang gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3709: ting 'dzin gyi nyams myong 'thas pa bdag tu ther zug pa dang gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3710: bsgom mi shes par don med phyal pa dang bzhis lhag mthong la sgrib /
NK076(mu)002:3711: ched du lus ngag yid gsum 'chos nas chos nyid
NK076(mu)002:3712: ci gsal du yid la byed pas zhi gnas la
NK076(mu)002:3714: ting 'dzin gyi ro nyams su myong bar re ba
NK076(mu)002:3715: dang drug /bdag tu 'du shes pas bsgom pa la
NK076(mu)002:3716: gnas shing yul du dmigas pas zung 'brel la sgrib
NK076(mu)002:3717: pa dang bdun / shes pa nang du sdud pas lhag mthong la sgrib pa dang brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:3718: ting 'dzin gyi don ci snga mngona du byed 'dod pa dang dgu /
NK076(mu)002:3719: yon tan 'ong bar 'dod pa'i re ba manga bar 'dod pa dang bcu ste /
NK076(mu)002:3720: de gnyis kyis zhi lhag spyir sgrib pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3722: de yang sgrib pa yi skyon la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3730: yod 1 med dang yin min sogs /
NK076(mu)002:3732: de'i rjes 3su dran pa'i rgyun ring thung rgyu ba /
NK076(mu)002:3734: rtog pa'i 5 'byung 'jug dus myur bul ba ltos pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3736: rtsa ba lnga po de dag re re la yang yan lag gnyis gnyis te bcu'o //
NK076(mu)002:3737: dbye na rtogs pa la rags phra /
NK076(mu)002:3742: lnga pa dogs pas dgu dang log pa rtag chad kyi dmigs bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3743: 'jiga rten gsum gyi dang po 'o zhes 'dod khams kyi lha drug /gnyis pa bsam gtan bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:3746: 'byin 'jug rlung ngam bde ba'i ngang du rtse gcig pa'i sa pa /
NK076(mu)002:3747: kun gzhi'i ngang la snyoms par 'jug pa skye mched mu bzhir gol ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:3751: yod min med min te bzhi'o //
NK076(mu)002:3752: de ltar khamas gsum sa dagu ste de dag tu gol ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3753: thera zug pa rtag par lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3754: snga phyi'i mtha' chad para lta ba gnyis ni phyin ca lag gi lta bar gol ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3756: sgo gsum gyis 'jig rten gyi bya ba mang po byed la /
NK076(mu)002:3757: ting nge 'dzin la blo mi 'byung ba'i rkyen byas shing /
NK076(mu)002:3758: nyams su len pa'ang ngang thung ba /
NK076(mu)002:3760: rna bas dug shad kyi sgra thos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3763: rang gi mgo bo 'khor zhing rlung gi sngo /
NK076(mu)002:3766: bad kan skya ba la sogs pa'i kha doga mathanga ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3767: nad khamas 'khrug pa las gyur pa'i skyon gyi cha yanga brtag cing shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3768: gsum pa spyod lam sgom chen gyi skyon drug /rnal 'byor pa de yi 'agro ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3771: zas nor la longs spyod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3772: lam du 'jug pa'i tsha na yanga /
NK076(mu)002:3773: stong pa chen bo'i rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin dang brala ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:3774: gnas su ye sdod tshe bya ra khra lta bu'i sgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:3775: 'gro ba'i sems tshol dur rkun wa'i sgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:3776: sgom khang du gnas tshe nya lta bu'i sgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:3777: nyal ba'i tshe 'tham yor glang gnyid kyi sgom pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3778: zas nor longs spyod pa brkam chagas che ba tshonga ba'i sems kyi bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:3779: bya byed mang po pa spre'u yi spyod pa rnams sgom gyi skyon yin no //
NK076(mu)002:3780: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:3781: ting 'dzin la gnas pa'i dus kyi skyon bcos thabs /
NK076(mu)002:3785: dang po blo che chung ngam nyams kyi rim pa dang sbyar te bcos thabs so sor bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:3786: gong gi de ltar skyon ngo shes pa'i rnal 'byor
NK076(mu)002:3787: pas skyon de dag spong bar byed ba'i gnyen po
NK076(mu)002:3789: mngon par 'adu byed grangs yan lag brgyad bsten pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3798: de dag ni blo chung ba'am /
NK076(mu)002:3799: nyams g.yo thob kyi bcos thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:3800: skyon gang yin gang las byung so sor cung zad tsam blta bar bya'am /
NK076(mu)002:3801: zhes blo tha ma'i bcos so //
NK076(mu)002:3802: yang na skyon byung yang sems nyid rang byung rang zhir bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:3804: nyams goms brtan gyi bcos thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:3805: gnyis pa mthar phyin pa'i dus su dgag sgrub med pa'i bcos thabs /
NK076(mu)002:3806: dpe ji ltar na byis pa brda' don gnyis ka
NK076(mu)002:3807: la blo shed ma bye pa dag /rtsed mo'i bya
NK076(mu)002:3808: byed mang po yis sems g.yeng bar gnas pa ltar
NK076(mu)002:3809: / lam pas sgo gsum gyi bya byed mang pos
NK076(mu)002:3810: sems g.yeng ba de lta bas na bdag med par
NK076(mu)002:3811: rtogs pa'i ngang la stong pa chen po'i ting nga
NK076(mu)002:3812: 'dzin gyi rang dbang du bsgyur nasa /
NK076(mu)002:3813: rtog pa'i mtshan ma thams cad sems mnyam pa'i dbyings su zil gyis mnan pas /
NK076(mu)002:3814: skyon dgag pa dang yon tan sgrub pa mi bya ba ga la yin te min no //
NK076(mu)002:3815: blo rab bam nyams mthar phyin pa'i bcos thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:3817: cung zad khams las gyur pa'i skyon rnams kya cha mnyam pas /
NK076(mu)002:3818: bsgom bya'i don mi gsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3820: ting 'dzin la blo mi 'jug pa la sogs khams
NK076(mu)002:3821: kyi skyon ngos zin par byas nas khams 'khrugs na
NK076(mu)002:3822: spyod lam du rang rang gang dag'a ba brten pa
NK076(mu)002:3823: dang / nad khams la mthun pa'i zas sman dpyad kyi cho gasa khams gso bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3825: spyod lam bzhir ting 'dzin rnal du ma 'byor pasa /
NK076(mu)002:3826: dus su shes bzhin gyi bya ra ba'i so mthas
NK076(mu)002:3827: chod cing ngos zin nas skyon de dag dor bar
NK076(mu)002:3828: bya zhing ting 'dzin la dran pa ma yengs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3829: thag pas sdams par byas ta /
NK076(mu)002:3830: spyod lam gyi dus dang rnam pa kun tu ting 'dzin gyi don la nyams par mi bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3833: de ltar skyon bcos shing don la nogs thub cing
NK076(mu)002:3834: brtson 'grus kyis yun ringa bar ting 'dzin la gnas
NK076(mu)002:3835: pa'i dus gdod mar 'jug pa nas mthar ma phyin
NK076(mu)002:3836: bar du nyams rim par 'phel ba yanga /
NK076(mu)002:3841: mathara phyin pa'i nyams ste mu lngas de ting yongs su rdzogs para 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:3842: gnyis pa rgyas pa la lnga /
NK076(mu)002:3843: dang po g.yo ba'i nyamsa la brtson 'grus bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:3844: rnal 'byor ba gang daga dper na ri gazara po'i chur 'bab pa de dag tu rgyug pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:3845: mnyam bzhag la gnas pa'i tshe /
NK076(mu)002:3846: rnam rtog byung ma thag /sngar kun brtags kyi 'khrul
NK076(mu)002:3847: ba la goms pa'i dpe rdza makhana gyis 'khor lo
NK076(mu)002:3848: bskor ba mi sdong pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:3849: ting 'dzin gyi thog tu ma sdod par rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3850: dbang du 'gra bas ting 'dzin la skya bar byed
NK076(mu)002:3851: pa da tshe mago la me 'abra ba myur du
NK076(mu)002:3852: gsod pa bazhana du brtson 'grus bskyed la ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:3853: 'bad do // gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams la 'byung 'jug bsring ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3854: dang po skyon gyi rgyu brtags te dor ba /
NK076(mu)002:3855: gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams kyi skabs su bar 'ag'a
NK076(mu)002:3856: ting 'dzin skyon dbang 'chora bar 'ga' ting nge 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:3857: thob pa la khams dang spyod lam sogs ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:3858: 'chora ba'i rgyu brtags te khams gso ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3859: spyod lam log pa'i skyon dor bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3861: ting 'dzin cung zada yoda la rtog pa de dag sngar bas nyung bar 'byung bas /
NK076(mu)002:3862: de yi tshe ting 'dzin la dal bus 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:3863: dang 'jug par bya ste thun sngar pas bsring bar
NK076(mu)002:3864: bya'o // gsum pa goms pa'i nyams la btang snyoms bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:3865: de ltar thob pa'i nyams de goms nas ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:3866: la brod pas blos ched du bsgom par bya ba
NK076(mu)002:3868: dang po rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang snyoms dang po dang du blang bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3869: bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams la mi sun par bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:3870: dper na ri bo rlung gis mi 'gul ba lta
NK076(mu)002:3871: bura rnam rtog gis mi 'gul ba brtan pa thob
NK076(mu)002:3872: ste / nyin zhag gcig la thun gcig tu brkyang
NK076(mu)002:3873: nas nyin mtshan 'brel bar bsgom nus na yang ha
NK076(mu)002:3874: cang sems sun par bsgom par ma bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3875: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams la dga' brod mi bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:3876: gnyen pos zin pa'i ting 'dzin gyi ro myong ba'i
NK076(mu)002:3877: zhen pa dor bas rtsol med blo 'das de mthar
NK076(mu)002:3878: phyin pa'o // mthar phyin pa'i shugs las snang ba
NK076(mu)002:3879: brgyad mthong ba la dga' ba dang broda med par
NK076(mu)002:3880: phyin pa'o // bya'o // snang ba brgyad ni /
NK076(mu)002:3881: me long skar mdas brgyan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3882: snang srid rdul phra rab tu mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3884: kun dga' ra ba mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3885: skyed mos tshal mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:3886: glang po che la zhon pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3888: stod gsum lag mthil ltar mnyam par mthong ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:3889: gsum pa brtson pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:3890: ting nge 'dzin la shin tu ngang bsrings nas yun
NK076(mu)002:3891: ring du brtson pa yis nyams gong nas gong du
NK076(mu)002:3892: bogs chen po skye zhing 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:3893: brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3895: stong chen bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas bdag gi don
NK076(mu)002:3896: dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir du sgo gsum
NK076(mu)002:3897: gyi bya ba yi spyod pa kun ji lta bu
NK076(mu)002:3898: zhe na / gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3902: dang po nyams lnga char mi dmigs pa'i spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:3903: dang po ting nge 'dzin gyi 'go slob pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:3904: nyams dang po g.yo ba'i nyams nas 'go bzung nas
NK076(mu)002:3905: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams kyi bar thams cad
NK076(mu)002:3906: du / gnyis 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa med pa'i tshul gyis ni /
NK076(mu)002:3907: spyad bya'i yul gang yang rung ba thams cad kun la 'dzin zhen dang /
NK076(mu)002:3908: thogs chags med par rol par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:3909: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin dang mthun pa'i spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:3910: de ting nyams su len pa'i tshe chos spyod bcu
NK076(mu)002:3911: yod pa la dgu dor ba'i gcig la cha ste
NK076(mu)002:3912: rtse gcig ting 'dzin sgom par byed pa de yang
NK076(mu)002:3915: yi ge bri mchod sbyin pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3916: nyan dang 'dzin dang klog pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3918: de sems pa dang sgom pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3919: chos spyod bcu yi bdag nyid do //
NK076(mu)002:3921: 'dir mtshan ma med pa mi dmigs par bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:3922: ni de ting dang mthun pas spyod pa zhes bya'o
NK076(mu)002:3923: // gsum pa spyod lam bzhi la spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:3924: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du 'gra ba
NK076(mu)002:3925: dang 'ong ba meda pa lasa spyod lam 'gra ba
NK076(mu)002:3926: dang 'onga ba ma 'gags par snang la /
NK076(mu)002:3927: de ltar 'gro 'ong gi spyad par snang ba'i dus
NK076(mu)002:3928: de nyid na chos nyid 'gro 'ong meda pa las
NK076(mu)002:3930: chos nyid la gnas bya dang gnas byed kyi zhen pa med pa'i ngang las /
NK076(mu)002:3931: spyod lam nyal 'dug thams cad du gnas pa ltar ma 'gags par snang la /
NK076(mu)002:3932: de ltar nyal 'dug gnas pa yi dus nyid na gnas pa med pa las mi 'da' 'o //
NK076(mu)002:3933: chos nyid de bzhin nyid longs spyod bya spyod byed
NK076(mu)002:3934: med pa'i ngang las bza' btung sogs 'dod yon thams
NK076(mu)002:3935: cad ma 'gags par longs spyod la /
NK076(mu)002:3936: de ltar longs spyod pa de nyid na longs spyad
NK076(mu)002:3937: bya spyod byed med pa'i ngang las mi 'da' ba'i
NK076(mu)002:3938: ting nge 'dzin la nyams pa med par longs spyod
NK076(mu)002:3939: cing spyad bya la chags shing zhen par mi bya'o
NK076(mu)002:3940: // bzhi pa spyod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK076(mu)002:3941: de ltar spyod lam rnam bzhir snang ba mi 'goga
NK076(mu)002:3942: pa bsod nams dang mi 'dzin pa ye shes kyi
NK076(mu)002:3943: tshogs gnyis zung 'brel du ldan par spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:3944: bdag gi don gyi phyir spyod lam kun la yul yul can mi dmigas para spyod pas /
NK076(mu)002:3945: 'bras bu stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor myur du thob pa la the tshom med do //
NK076(mu)002:3946: gnyis pa gzhan don gyi spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:3947: dang po spyod lam chos nyid du slong zhing gzhan
NK076(mu)002:3948: don rdzogs pa de yang rnal 'byor pas 'gro zhing
NK076(mu)002:3949: 'ong ba dang / nyal zhing gnyid log pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:3951: bza' btung la longas spyod pa'i dus kyi tshe /
NK076(mu)002:3952: da ltar bdag don gyi spyod pas ci spyad chosa
NK076(mu)002:3953: nyid du khyer nas spyod pa'i byin rlabsa las 'gro
NK076(mu)002:3954: ba sgrol bas gcig shos gzhan don yin te /
NK076(mu)002:3955: de'ang bdag don ganga ltar nyamsa su blang yang gzhan gyi don du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:3956: de'i rgyu mtshan lam gyi sngon du sems bskyed dgos pas /
NK076(mu)002:3957: bdag don de ting bsgom pa la gzhan don rdzogas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:3958: gnyis pa thugs rje thabs kyi spyod pas gzhan don bab de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:3959: dang po skabs min kyang gzhan don bya bar gsung pa /
NK076(mu)002:3960: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i gzhung las grags pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:3961: spyad bya dang mi spang ba 'dod yon lnga /
NK076(mu)002:3963: rtogs kyang dbang ma thob pas /
NK076(mu)002:3964: skye bo tshogs sbyor ba kun gyis 'chol nyog tu spyad par gsungs pas /
NK076(mu)002:3965: 'dir de dag la mos pa'i sgo nas slob pa
NK076(mu)002:3966: lta ci smos sbyor sgrol la sogs pa gdul bya'i
NK076(mu)002:3967: don du 'gyur ba'i rkyen mthong na /
NK076(mu)002:3968: lnga bzhi'i smad spyod de dag kun rgyu shesa pa
NK076(mu)002:3969: lta ba stong chen bsgom gyi gzhi ma de ting
NK076(mu)002:3971: gnyis pa phrin las la sogs gzhan don bya ba'i thabs ni /
NK076(mu)002:3972: rgyu shes pa lta ba dang rkyen 'jug pa ting
NK076(mu)002:3973: 'dzin man chad kun gyis kyang gdul bya gzhan gyi
NK076(mu)002:3975: phrin las bzhi spyod cing mchog thun dngos grub sgrub pa dang dbang bskur ba'i tshe /
NK076(mu)002:3976: phyag rgya gcig pa man chad kyi lam kun skad
NK076(mu)002:3977: ciga tsam gyi rgyus rdzogs par bsgomsa nasa mthar zhi
NK076(mu)002:3978: khro phyag rgya spros pa'i 'khora lo gang yin dngos
NK076(mu)002:3979: su bsgom pa'i spyod yul min kyang /
NK076(mu)002:3980: mosa pa tsam gyis bsgom bar bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:3981: rang bazhana lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor 'og min nas snyan gsan phab /
NK076(mu)002:3984: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchoda pa 'bul /
NK076(mu)002:3986: phrin las sgrub pa'i dbang sogs gang byed nus pa'i
NK076(mu)002:3987: gzi byin dang ldan par byas nas gzhan don rdzogsa
NK076(mu)002:3988: par de ting gi skabs su 'ang byed do //
NK076(mu)002:3989: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:3990: khyad par de ting rang gi dam tshig dang /
NK076(mu)002:3991: lam spyi'i dam tshig ji ltar bsrung tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:3993: bsrung bya dam tshig gi ngo bo /
NK076(mu)002:3997: dang po de ting 'dir dam tshig kun dang khyad par ting 'dzin ldan dgos pa /
NK076(mu)002:3998: de ting stong chen la gnas pa de tsha lam
NK076(mu)002:3999: gong ma'i dam tshig dang sdom pa thams cad kun
NK076(mu)002:4000: / mos pa'i sgo nas slob cing mi gtong bar bsrung mod kyang /
NK076(mu)002:4001: khyad para ting nge 'dzin las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshiga dang ldan par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:4002: gnyis pa lta ba dam tshig gi ngo bo yin pas lta ba'i don 'dir dgos par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4003: spyi dang khyad par ram rtsa ba'i dam tshig dang
NK076(mu)002:4004: yan lag gi dam tshiga ces bya ba de yang
NK076(mu)002:4005: sems las logas na yod pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:4006: gang zhe na rang gi sems lta ba yi rtogs
NK076(mu)002:4007: pa'i don las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig yin te
NK076(mu)002:4008: / lta bas zin na 'khor ba ngan song du mi gtong ba'i phyir yang ngam zhes bya /
NK076(mu)002:4009: bla med byang chub kyi gzungs su gyur pas kyang ngam zhes bya /
NK076(mu)002:4010: lta ba rtogs pa'i don sngar nas ldan pa de yang 'dir de ting gis goms par byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4012: lta ba dam tshig gi mchog yin pa de bas
NK076(mu)002:4013: na rang gi sems nyid lta bas rdzogs par byas
NK076(mu)002:4014: te / snyom las su gyur pa la le lo
NK076(mu)002:4015: g.yeng ba yi skyon drug la sogs pa'i skyon rnams
NK076(mu)002:4017: gang zag gi nga dang chos kyi bdag med cing
NK076(mu)002:4018: mnyam pa'i don la mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dang
NK076(mu)002:4020: gsum pa mi 'da' ba'i nges tshig chos nyid da
NK076(mu)002:4021: bzhina nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin las dus thams cad
NK076(mu)002:4023: de bzhin nyid kyi don rtogs pa dang goms pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4024: ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa dam pa yin te
NK076(mu)002:4025: / de bzhin nyid de las 'das na rang gi
NK076(mu)002:4026: bde 'bras thams cad 'tshig par 'gyur te 'khor bar
NK076(mu)002:4027: / lhung la / de las ma 'das na rang
NK076(mu)002:4028: rgyud kyi nyes skyon thams cad tshig par gyur pas
NK076(mu)002:4030: gnyis pa lam spyi'i dam tshig ji ltar bsrung tshul la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:4031: dang po lam snga ma mthar phyin dus gong ma'i
NK076(mu)002:4032: dam tshig ldan kyang spyod pa min par bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:4033: / de yang lam snga ma snga mara lta ba'i
NK076(mu)002:4034: skabs sogs rang rang gi dam tshig rdzogs par byas
NK076(mu)002:4035: / pas / lam gong ma gong ma'i rgyud la yar ldan du yod pasa /
NK076(mu)002:4036: snga ma lta ba la spyod pa'i de ting yongas
NK076(mu)002:4037: su 'phar ba'i rgyu byas kyis de ting skabs su
NK076(mu)002:4038: lta ba'i dam tshig la mngon du spyod pa min
NK076(mu)002:4039: no // de bas lam gong ma la na 'phar
NK076(mu)002:4040: bas thabs 'og ma'i spyod pa kun gong ma la
NK076(mu)002:4041: mngon du 'gro ba'i rgyu ru spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4042: gnyis pa de bas lam gong 'og gi dam tshig
NK076(mu)002:4043: dang spyod pa la khyad yod par dpes bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:4044: / khyad yod pa de bas na lam so so'i
NK076(mu)002:4045: lta ba rtogs tshab che chung gi gzhi yis phye
NK076(mu)002:4046: / ba las / bdag don ting 'dzin dbang bsgyur
NK076(mu)002:4047: gyi spyod pa la sogs pa kun la khyad yod
NK076(mu)002:4048: bar ni lung pa che chung gis nam mkha'a yi
NK076(mu)002:4049: yul la rgya che chung yod pa dang 'dra bar
NK076(mu)002:4050: / ba las / / gzhan don byin rlabs kyi
NK076(mu)002:4051: spyod pa'i zhing khams rgya che chung ni mi'i dbang
NK076(mu)002:4052: po'i gser dngul zangs lcags kyi 'khor sgyur la 'dul
NK076(mu)002:4053: zhing gis khams rgya che chung yod pa bzhin /
NK076(mu)002:4054: nus ba'i stobs che chung gi khyad par ni stobsa
NK076(mu)002:4055: ldan glang po che tsam du gcig kyang rtsal che
NK076(mu)002:4056: chung dang sgyid drag gzhan gyis chu la thang gcod
NK076(mu)002:4057: dang gzhol gcod byed pa dang 'dra ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:4060: bzhag thabs gong bstan de ltar bsgom bya sgom byed
NK076(mu)002:4061: dang g.yeng ba drug la sogs bya byed med par
NK076(mu)002:4063: phyi lus dang nang ngag dang gsang ba sems la
NK076(mu)002:4064: myong ba'i drod gsum 'byung ba ni 'di lta ste
NK076(mu)002:4065: / gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:4066: dang po drod gsum spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4067: phyi lus la na tsha med pa sogs bzod pa phra mo thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4068: nang ngag gi rgyu 'gyu ba'i dbugsa mi tshor te btang bzung la rang dbang thoba pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4069: gsang ba'i drod don chos nyid la sems rnal du phebas pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:4070: the tshom med cing ngesa para phyi nang gsang ba'i drod gsum rang gis nyams su myong ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:4071: gnyis pa de las gzhan pa'i phyi nang gi drod 'byung bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4072: drod gsum po de las gzhan du drod 'byung tshul /
NK076(mu)002:4073: phyi rol gyi snang ba rdul phran tsam du mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4076: pad+ma dang kun da'i 'od la sagas pa'i mtshan ma mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4077: nang sems la snang ba'i drod ni /
NK076(mu)002:4078: ma bsgoms par rig pa rang shugs kyis chos nyid kyi klong du phebas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4079: phyi 'dod pa'i yul 'dod yon lnga la sems mi 'phro zhing mi 'gro ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4080: 'di nas 'chi 'pho ba dang phyi mar 'gyur zhing
NK076(mu)002:4081: skye ba len pa dag la nyam mi nga ba
NK076(mu)002:4082: dang / phyi zas nor dang nang 'khrig pa'i 'dod
