NK076(mu)002:4083: chags kyi yul la sngar bas zhen pa chung ba
NK076(mu)002:4084: dang / dang / de yang tha mal pa 'am
NK076(mu)002:4085: snga ma lta ba'i dus pas drod khyad par du
NK076(mu)002:4086: spags pa nyamsa su myong bas 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4087: gzhan sems can sdug bsngal snying rje'i yul mthong ba
NK076(mu)002:4088: thugs rjes rang dbang med par sems 'phrog pa dang
NK076(mu)002:4089: / 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad sngar bas grangs nyung
NK076(mu)002:4090: la ngo bo'i cha phra bas na mnyam par snyoms
NK076(mu)002:4091: pa la sogas pa'i yon tan phal cher 'byung ba'o
NK076(mu)002:4092: / // gsum pa drod nyams lnga kun tu 'khor bar 'byung tshul /
NK076(mu)002:4093: de ltar drod kyi rnam pa de kun yang nyams
NK076(mu)002:4094: dang sbyar na g.yo ba'i nyams kyi skabs su res
NK076(mu)002:4096: thoba pa'i skabs su phal cher yod la /
NK076(mu)002:4097: goms brtan gyi skabs su mi 'gyur bar yod pa'i go rim kyis /
NK076(mu)002:4098: nyams kun tu drod 'khor bar 'byung ba yin no //
NK076(mu)002:4099: bcu gcig pa rtags la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4100: dang po dpe don gnyis kyis drod rtags spyir bstan pa'i dgos pa /
NK076(mu)002:4101: bru sha'i skad du gu ljo bod skad du byis pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:4102: de yang smin te nar son pa lo nyer lnga
NK076(mu)002:4103: tsam lon pa'i rigs da la pha mas khyed la
NK076(mu)002:4104: khyim thabs len pa'i ltas bstan na /
NK076(mu)002:4105: byis pa de khyim thabs la dprod pas mdun bsu
NK076(mu)002:4106: zhing zang zinga gi nor mang dag /don du gnyer
NK076(mu)002:4107: ba la brtson par byeda pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4108: dpe de bzhina du stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK076(mu)002:4109: bas 'bras bu byang chub kyi bde ba chen po
NK076(mu)002:4111: droda dang rtags kyi yon tan mngon du mthong ba'i 'bras bu la blo broda pa'i tshul gyis /
NK076(mu)002:4112: drod rtags mthong ba des shin tu thar pa'i lam la brtson 'grus byed par 'gyur bas /
NK076(mu)002:4113: rgyu mtshan da yi phyir rtags 'di dag drod kyi rjes su bstan par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:4114: gnyis pa rtags bye brag tu bshad pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4116: drod song nas phyi ma rtags la'ang lam gyi lta
NK076(mu)002:4117: sgom gyi nus pa'i stobs che chung gi cha las
NK076(mu)002:4119: rdzu 'phrul lam cho 'phrul snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:4120: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:4126: de la snga ma rtags la'ang phyi rtags dang nang rtags gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:4127: gnyis pa rgyas bshad de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4129: phyi rol gyi yul chu gcig la gzhan zad pas na zad para skye mched de me dang /
NK076(mu)002:4133: kha dog bzhi ste brgyad sogs dngos su mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4134: nyi zla dang pad+ma'i 'od dang mdog sogs dang /
NK076(mu)002:4135: phyag mtshan la sogs pas gang bar mthong ngo //
NK076(mu)002:4137: nang du lus kyi na tsha la bzod pa thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4138: ting nge 'dzin gyi bye brag shes pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4139: nyon mongs pa'i chu bo lnga ste 'khor ba'i rgyun
NK076(mu)002:4140: lam la mngon zhen shas che ba ting 'dzin stobs
NK076(mu)002:4141: kyis bgas kyis bcud de shas chung du 'gro ba
NK076(mu)002:4142: dang / rnam rtog gis ting 'dzin mi 'phrog /srin po mthong yang myos shing skrag pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4143: lha'i bu mo mthong yang dga' zhing brod ba med do //
NK076(mu)002:4144: ched du ma byas kyang ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i shugs las snang ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:4147: me long skar mdas brgyan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4148: nam mkha' rdul gyis gang ba /
NK076(mu)002:4150: kun dga' ra ba mthong ba /
NK076(mu)002:4151: zad par skye mched mthong ba /
NK076(mu)002:4152: stong gsum lag mthil ltar mnyam par 'byung ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:4153: de ltar brgyad po mthong ba'ang 'byung zhing /
NK076(mu)002:4154: baca brgyad tsam bdud kyi spyod yula 'dir shugs la
NK076(mu)002:4155: cha tsam du mthong ba yanga le'u drug pa ltar
NK076(mu)002:4156: 'byung ngo // gnyis pa mngon shes la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4158: mngon sum par rtogs pa ni rtog bral yin la /
NK076(mu)002:4159: shes pa ni ma 'khrul ba ste de la rnam pa drug ni /
NK076(mu)002:4160: rtsa rgyud le'u gsum pa las bshad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4161: 'di nyid kyi tshe dbang gi skabs nas /
NK076(mu)002:4162: gzhan du lha'i rna ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4163: spyan gyi mngon par shes pa /
NK076(mu)002:4164: sngon gnas rjes su dran pa /
NK076(mu)002:4165: pha rol gyi sems shes pa /
NK076(mu)002:4167: rdzu 'phrul shes pa'am zag zad shes pa zhes so //
NK076(mu)002:4168: de rnams kyang lam gyi gnas skabs kyi zag pa gsum yod pa tshogs sbyor dang /
NK076(mu)002:4169: zag gsum med pa mthong sgom yan chad kyi mngon shes so //
NK076(mu)002:4170: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4174: dang po mngon shes kyi ming zag bcas zag med gnyis las sngon ma zag bcas mngon shes la /
NK076(mu)002:4175: de ting kun ting skabs su mdun du 'dug pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4176: mi la dmigs nas bsgoms pas de'i sems shes pa
NK076(mu)002:4178: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi skabs su mngon shes nyi
NK076(mu)002:4179: shu rtsa lnga'i grangs yongs su rdzogs para 'byung ba'i
NK076(mu)002:4181: tshogs sgrub bar chad med pa'i lam pa yin pas de'i mngon shes sa //
NK076(mu)002:4182: gnyis pa mngon shes kyi yul gyi tshad /
NK076(mu)002:4183: de ting skabs drung na 'dug pa'i mi la damgas
NK076(mu)002:4184: pa gtad nas 'ga' ste gcig gnyis gsum tsam gyi
NK076(mu)002:4186: kun ting skabs mang du 'phel ba ste bcu tsam gyi sems shes pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4187: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs dbang po lnga re res
NK076(mu)002:4188: yul lnga mthong bas mngon shes nya shu rtsa lnga
NK076(mu)002:4190: spros bcas skabs 'bring gis yul khams tshun chad mthong zhing /
NK076(mu)002:4191: rab kyis gling bzhi mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4192: bar chad med pa'i 'bring dang rab kyis gling bzhi'i
NK076(mu)002:4193: grangs gnyis gsum drug tshun chad lha'i mig gi mthong
NK076(mu)002:4194: zhing rna bas sgra thos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4195: sngon gnas shes pa sogs gcig spros dang bar chad
NK076(mu)002:4196: med pa'i lam gyi blo'i rim pas phye ba yin
NK076(mu)002:4197: no // gnyis pa zag med mngon shes la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4198: dang po rig 'dzin gsum gyi mngon shes kyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:4199: phyi ma zag med mngon shes la tshe dbang gis
NK076(mu)002:4200: stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya tshun chad mngon
NK076(mu)002:4201: shes kyi yul du gyur ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4202: sa dang po'i mngon shes stong gsum gyi stong chen
NK076(mu)002:4203: po brgya yin pa dang sagas kyi sgras sgom lam
NK076(mu)002:4204: sa dgu'i mngon shes gyi yul du 'gyur lugs yod
NK076(mu)002:4205: pa'i nang nas sogas sgras sa gnyis pa nas bdun
NK076(mu)002:4207: sa brgyad pa phyag rgya chen po ni stong gsum
NK076(mu)002:4208: gyi stong chen po brgya de gcig nas gnyis su
NK076(mu)002:4209: bgrang ba'i stong phrag bcu rdul snyed du byas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4210: grangsa med dang mnyam pa brgya de gcig nas gnyis
NK076(mu)002:4211: su bgrang ba'i stong phrag bcu'i rdul byas pa de
NK076(mu)002:4212: rnyed dang mnyam pa stong gsum mngon shes kyi yul
NK076(mu)002:4213: du gyur pa'o // lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mngon shes ni /
NK076(mu)002:4214: mnyam bzhag tu rgyal ba sangs rgyas dang mnyam pasa
NK076(mu)002:4215: 'o na mthar lam pa sangs rgyas dang khyad med
NK076(mu)002:4216: dam zhe na / bag la nyal gyi dri ma yod med kyis phya ba de bas na /
NK076(mu)002:4217: mthar lam pa dang rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gnyis la khyad par yod pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:4218: gnyis pa rgyu'i sems dpa' dang khyad par yod med phye ba /
NK076(mu)002:4219: zag med mngon shes yul de tsam yin pa de
NK076(mu)002:4220: bas na rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa yi byang chub
NK076(mu)002:4221: sems dpa' sa dang po rab tu dga' ba dang
NK076(mu)002:4222: / sngags kyi mthong lam tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang mnyam /
NK076(mu)002:4224: sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang skal ba mnyam ste /
NK076(mu)002:4225: rgyu'i sa bcu pa dang sngags kyi lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis mnyam pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:4226: mthong sgom mthar lam gsum du brjod pa'i yon tan gyi khyad yod tshul ni mi 'dra ste /
NK076(mu)002:4227: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:4228: dagngas pa yi ting 'dzin goms ma goms kyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:4229: gzhi lam cha yisa phye bas rgyu yi byang sems dang /
NK076(mu)002:4230: 'brasa bu sngags kyi rig 'dzin gsum la khyad par yod par nges so //
NK076(mu)002:4232: stong chen rnal 'byor 'di bsgom pa'i tshe rdzu 'phrul
NK076(mu)002:4233: nyi shu la sogs rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang
NK076(mu)002:4234: / 'gro ba so so'i skad du rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK076(mu)002:4235: sa g.yo ba drug byed pa chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul /
NK076(mu)002:4236: snod bcud kun gyis gsang sngags kyi sgra sgrogs pa
NK076(mu)002:4237: di ring kun brjod kyi cho 'phrul te cho 'phrul
NK076(mu)002:4238: bzhi bo yang lam lta ba cig chara la rdzogs
NK076(mu)002:4240: lam rim gyis pas de ting 'di bsgom pa'i tshe cho 'phrul bzhi 'byung ba'i rgyu tsam yin gyi /
NK076(mu)002:4241: 'o na dngos su 'byung ba med dam zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:4242: nyams lnga mathara phyin pa'i skabs su cho 'phrul bzhi yi cha gcig tsam 'byung ba yang srid do //
NK076(mu)002:4243: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la bzhi te /
NK076(mu)002:4244: dang po sgrib pa dag cing bden pa mthong ba'i rmi ltas /
NK076(mu)002:4245: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor de ting la blo gnas pa'i rmi lam la yang /
NK076(mu)002:4246: sgrib pa dag pa'i rtags lus gcer bur phyung bar rmi zhing khrus byas nas dri ma daga pa /
NK076(mu)002:4247: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas su byang chub chen po'i mchod rten mthong ba rmi'o //
NK076(mu)002:4248: gnyis pa byin gyis brlab cing lung bstan 'byung ba'i rmi ltas /
NK076(mu)002:4249: dam pa mchoga sangs rgyas dang dam pa rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' de yis /
NK076(mu)002:4250: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sras dang byang sems rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:4251: gyi spun du dgongs shing byin gyis rlob pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:4252: dang / gzhan yang rmi lam gyi mtshan mara rang
NK076(mu)002:4253: gi bla ma sdug bsngal skyob ba'i mgon po mngon
NK076(mu)002:4254: du snang basa rang la dbang bskur ba dang byin
NK076(mu)002:4255: gyis brlabs pa dang sogs sgras lung bstan pa khri
NK076(mu)002:4256: la 'jog pa zhing khams ston pa ste byang chub
NK076(mu)002:4257: kyi lam du 'dzud pa yi rtags lnga byed cinga
NK076(mu)002:4258: dang / / de la bar chad 'byung mi 'byung
NK076(mu)002:4259: dang legas pa'i yon tan dang nyes pa'i skyon 'byung
NK076(mu)002:4260: min gyi sgo nas lam la brtson 'grus gyis zhes
NK076(mu)002:4262: gsum pa de nyid bdud dang bar chad dbye ba bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4263: mtshan ltas de yang bdud bla mar sprul pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4264: lam rtags gang yin cha dbye dgos te /
NK076(mu)002:4265: bdud kyis byin gyis rlob pa dang lung ston pa
NK076(mu)002:4266: ltar snang ba nas bar chad 'byung basa nyes pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4267: bar chad byed pa'i ched du bdud 'byung ba yod
NK076(mu)002:4269: bdud kyi bar chad dang lam gyi grub rtags kyi
NK076(mu)002:4270: cha gnyis ting 'dzin dang nyams rtogs bzang ngan la
NK076(mu)002:4271: sogs brtag pa zag bcas lam gyi skabs su kun
NK076(mu)002:4272: tu gcesa so // bzhi pa de'i bar chad bsal phyir bla ma la zhu ba /
NK076(mu)002:4273: bdun kyi bar chad de dag bsal ba'i phyir rmi
NK076(mu)002:4274: lam de daga kun rang gi zhu sa bla ma
NK076(mu)002:4275: nyid las gzhan du dri zhing smra ba min no
NK076(mu)002:4276: // bcu gsum pa phan yon la drug ste /
NK076(mu)002:4277: dang po dge sdig las kyis mi gos pa'i phan yon /
NK076(mu)002:4278: chos nyid de bzhin nyid du lta bas mthong zhing ting 'dzin gyis goms na /
NK076(mu)002:4279: rgyu dge ba'i las dang mi dge ba'i las gnyis su 'dzin pa med de /
NK076(mu)002:4280: las dge sdig gi rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma rang rgyud par yong yer mi 'dzin te /
NK076(mu)002:4282: sems nyid ranga bzhin skye med du ye nas 'od gsal ba'i ngang la /
NK076(mu)002:4283: las dge sdiga gi rnam smin gyis gos pa med pas shin tu bde ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:4284: gnyis pa bde sdug gnyis su med par grol ba'i /
NK076(mu)002:4285: 'bras bu bde ba mtho ris dang mi bde ba ngan song gnyis su 'dzin pa med pas /
NK076(mu)002:4286: gnyis med rang byung gi ye shes la gnyis 'dzin gyi chags pa med cing rnam para dag pas /
NK076(mu)002:4287: bde sdug thams cad dbyer med de rang rig pa'i ye shes yin pas /
NK076(mu)002:4288: sems nyid phyogs 'dzin gyi dri mas ma gos shing
NK076(mu)002:4289: dang bas a skye ba med pa'i ngang du rnam
NK076(mu)002:4290: rtog gi zug rngu med pas rab tu bde ba'o
NK076(mu)002:4291: // gsum pa gtsang sme gnyis su med pa'i 'dod
NK076(mu)002:4292: pa'i longs spyod gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga
NK076(mu)002:4293: ldan thams cad la gatsanga ba dang dam ba'i blo
NK076(mu)002:4294: gnyis su ma 'dzin cig /de ci'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:4295: gtsang dme thams cada chos nyid spros bral du ro gciga pasa na /
NK076(mu)002:4296: spang len gnyis su 'dzin pa'i zug rngu med pasa kyang shin tu bde'o //
NK076(mu)002:4297: bzhi pa 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar grol ba'i /
NK076(mu)002:4298: shes rab che ba 2cig char dang chung 1ba rim gyis pa'i ting 'dzin gsal mi gsal gyis /
NK076(mu)002:4299: lta sgom spyod pa la sogs pa thams cad ma
NK076(mu)002:4300: nor bar rgyud lung man ngag gi gzhung nas 'byung
NK076(mu)002:4301: ba'i lugs bzhin du spyad na /
NK076(mu)002:4302: 'khor ba ma spangs chos nyid du dag pas sdug bsngal du 'dzin pa med cing /
NK076(mu)002:4303: 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs pa de'i rgyud tshim pas a rab tu bde zhes so //
NK076(mu)002:4304: lnga pa chos nyid mngon sum du mthong ba'i /
NK076(mu)002:4305: 'khor 'das chos thams cad ma lus pa sems nyid du gcig par rtogs pa'i nganga de la /
NK076(mu)002:4306: lta bar byed pa'i mkhan po dang /
NK076(mu)002:4307: blta bar bya ba'i yul gnyis ka med pa'i rang
NK076(mu)002:4308: rig pa'i ye shes kyi sgron ma rgyun chad med
NK076(mu)002:4310: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams thams cad gnyis med rang snang du mthong ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:4311: drug pa ma bgrod par sa non pa'i phan yon /
NK076(mu)002:4312: tshe 'di dang phyi ma pha rol de bzhin nyid
NK076(mu)002:4313: la gnyis su med pa'i phyir 'di nas 'gra ba
NK076(mu)002:4314: dang / pha rol du 'ong bar bya ba grub pa min te /
NK076(mu)002:4315: lus kyi yan lag bzhi stobs chen pos bgrod cing ma mchongas par /
NK076(mu)002:4316: phyogs bcu'i stong khams kyi rtog pa thams cad stong pa chen po nyid du gsal bas /
NK076(mu)002:4317: rtog pa rang ldang mi nus pas tha snyad du mnan zhes so //
NK076(mu)002:4318: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4319: dang po mtshan ma med pa'i de ting la gnas
NK076(mu)002:4320: pa 'di yi tshe dbang po drug gi skyod yul
NK076(mu)002:4322: ngu skad sogs phyi nang gi g.yeng ba'i mtshan ma
NK076(mu)002:4323: kun bsal nas rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa
NK076(mu)002:4324: nyid kyi ngang la rtse gcig tu 'dug par bya
NK076(mu)002:4325: zhing / de lta bu'i ting 'dzin de dran pasa
NK076(mu)002:4326: sngar gyi las ngan gyi bag chags kyi rgyun bcad
NK076(mu)002:4327: de phyi ma 'dod khams kyi lha dang mi'i rigs
NK076(mu)002:4328: khyad par can du skye nas gsang ba'i theg pa
NK076(mu)002:4330: gnyis pa mtshan bcas kyi man ngag ni /
NK076(mu)002:4331: mtshan med kyi 'pho ba las dgar bas yang na zhes 'dam ka ste /
NK076(mu)002:4333: snying gar rin po che'i gur phub pa lta bu
NK076(mu)002:4334: gasnga ba'i gser gyi sgrom bu'i nang snying ga'i dkyil
NK076(mu)002:4335: du kun gzhi 'od phung kha dog lnga'i ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:4336: tshona gang ba 'od dang ldan pa zhig bsam pa
NK076(mu)002:4337: dang / de'i steng du nyon yid zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du bsam /
NK076(mu)002:4338: de'i steng du yid shes h'u ring po zhig tu bsgom zhing /
NK076(mu)002:4339: de gsum brtsegs pa'i ting 'dzin la dmigs pa rtse gcig tu brtan pa thob nas /
NK076(mu)002:4340: dbugs sam rlung gi phar 'phro tshur 'dus h'u yig la thim /
NK076(mu)002:4343: mthar 'od phung de nyid phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams
NK076(mu)002:4344: cad la khyab par brdala te spyod yul thams cad
NK076(mu)002:4345: 'od phung du bsam zhing stong pa'i ngang la 'dug
NK076(mu)002:4346: go // bco lnga pa 'bras bu bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:4347: don snang stong dbyer meda stong chen gyi rnal 'byor la goms pa'i mtha' ma /
NK076(mu)002:4348: ting 'dzin de mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu dbu ma las lhag pa'i chos skur sbyor ro //
NK076(mu)002:4349: 'bras bu chos sku gsal stong dbyer med nyid la lam du byed pa'i phyir yin te /
NK076(mu)002:4350: de bzhin nyid dang chos sku gnyis rnam pa mchog
NK076(mu)002:4351: ldan gyi stong pa chen por phyogsa mthun pa yin
NK076(mu)002:4352: pas na / 'bras bu chos sku thob par brjod
NK076(mu)002:4353: kyis des na 'bras bu dngos su thob pa'i rigs
NK076(mu)002:4354: pas na / ma yina te / rgyu 'bras chos mthun sbyor btsam la dgongs pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:4355: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4356: rnam pa kun ldan gyi stong pa chen po'i don
NK076(mu)002:4357: rnal ma la rang rig pa'i blo 'byor ba'i ting
NK076(mu)002:4358: nge 'dzin bstan pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams mtshams
NK076(mu)002:4359: dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4360: don gyis na la'u zhes bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:4361: yas bgrangs gsum pa'i don du gda' 'o ////le'u bzhi
NK076(mu)002:4362: pa kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin ye shes sgyu
NK076(mu)002:4364: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:4365: don dam gsal stong chos kyi sku yi ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:4366: de la lta bas rtogs shing ting 'dzin goms pas
NK076(mu)002:4367: phyag 'tshal te / de ltar chos nyid stong pa la goms kyang /
NK076(mu)002:4368: stong zhen gyi dri ma bsal dgos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4369: gdul bya sangs rgyas la 'god phyir /
NK076(mu)002:4370: sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje /
NK076(mu)002:4371: chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje /
NK076(mu)002:4372: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje dang gsum las /
NK076(mu)002:4373: 'dir yul bral dmigs med kyi snying rje chen po
NK076(mu)002:4374: ste ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor bashada par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:4375: // gnyis pa gzhung don la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4377: de ting stong chen dang rjes su mthun pa'i kun
NK076(mu)002:4378: snang gi lus mdor bstan bco lnga po nyid kya
NK076(mu)002:4379: yan lag rgyas bshad kyi sgo nas shes par gyis
NK076(mu)002:4380: shig pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la don bco lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:4395: dang po sngon du 'gro ba la dbye ba med de /
NK076(mu)002:4396: snying rje sgyu ma'i sngon du stong pa chen po la goms pa'i rnal 'byor pasa /
NK076(mu)002:4397: khamas gsum gyi sems can thams cad thugs rjes rjes su gzung ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:4398: tshogs bsags pa yana lag brgyad pa sngon de ting bzhin byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:4399: de'i rjes la ngo bo ye shes rang gsal rnam
NK076(mu)002:4400: pa sgyu mas khyab pa'i snying rje chen po'i ting
NK076(mu)002:4402: gnyis pa dgos ched la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4404: gang zag dang chos bdag gam /
NK076(mu)002:4405: snying rje skyed byed kyi mkhan po bdag dang skye
NK076(mu)002:4406: yul gzhan gnyis su 'dzin pa'i dri ma bsal ba
NK076(mu)002:4407: dang / de ting la stong pa'i zhen pas 'ching
NK076(mu)002:4408: ba'i de'i mdud pa bshig pa yi dgos pa dang
NK076(mu)002:4410: snying rje chen po'i sgo nas gdul bya rnams thar
NK076(mu)002:4411: pa'i sa la dgod pa'i dgos ched yod pa dang
NK076(mu)002:4412: / mthar phyin pa 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig pa
NK076(mu)002:4413: thob pa'i rgyur bya zhing de'i thabs la snying rje
NK076(mu)002:4414: chen po'i rnal 'byor 'di nyid ni don du gnyer
NK076(mu)002:4416: sems nyid don dam bden pa de nyid kyi ngang
NK076(mu)002:4417: la kun rdzob 'gag med ye shes snang ba gnyis
NK076(mu)002:4418: phyogs dang ris su mi gtong ba'i dgos ched phyir
NK076(mu)002:4419: / snying rje ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor 'di
NK076(mu)002:4420: yi lam la blo rtse gcig tu gnas par byas
NK076(mu)002:4421: / te / snying rje chen po'i ting 'dzin la
NK076(mu)002:4422: 'jug pa'i thun mtshams ni de ting mthar phyin pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4423: / te / dus kyis bya'o // gsum pa bzhag thabs la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:4424: snying rje chen po'i ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i thabs dang /
NK076(mu)002:4425: 'og ma'i snying rje las khyad par spags tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:4428: snying rje bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang gis khams
NK076(mu)002:4429: gsum 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK076(mu)002:4430: thams cad / dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje chen
NK076(mu)002:4431: po sgyu ma lta bu'i ye shes su gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:4432: ngang du mig gis gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4433: rna bas sgra thos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4436: snas dri tshor ba rnams la rang snang 'gag med du sbyangs pa'i thabs la'ang gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:4437: so sora rtog pa'i shes rab kyis brtags pa'i rgyu yis thob pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:4438: snga ma de ting la goms pa'i rjes las ye shes sgyu ma gsal bas na thob pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4439: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4440: dang po blo chung ba'i lta ba'am so sor rtog pa'i rgyus sgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:4441: snying rje chen po bsgom pa'i lam pa de yis
NK076(mu)002:4442: 'khor 'das dus gsum gyis bsdus pa ma lus pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4444: rtag pa ther zug pa'i snying po rang rgyud du grub nas yod pa ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:4445: 'o na sgyu ma ltar rtogs pa ci zhe na dpe drug gi tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:4446: snang la rang rgyud bas dben pa log rtog sgyu ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:4447: snang la ngo bo med pas mig yor te rten 'brel sgyu ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:4448: cir yang ma nges par snang bas sprul pa yang dag sgyu ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:4449: snang la ma grub pas smig rgyu ste thabs sgyu ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:4450: snang lam grub pas smig rgyu ste thabs sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:4451: snang la rang bzhin med pas 'ja' tshon te ye shes sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:4452: gsal la ngo bo stong pas chu zla ste phyag rgya sgyu ma'o //
NK076(mu)002:4453: de ni dpe drug gis mtshon tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:4454: snying rje skyed byed kyi rnal 'byor pa bdag dang
NK076(mu)002:4455: skye ba'i yul 'gro ba kun ye shes sgyu mar
NK076(mu)002:4457: de ltar ma shes pa'i mtha' bsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4458: de yang rang gi blos kun tu brtags pas bdag
NK076(mu)002:4459: dang gzhan tha dada pa'i phyir gnyis su snang ngo
NK076(mu)002:4460: // don ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bo la bdag gzhan gcig pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4461: tha dad pa gnyis su med pas na /
NK076(mu)002:4462: de yang snying rje bya ba'i yul med /
NK076(mu)002:4463: rje bya rje byed kyi snang ba'i 'goga pa yang
NK076(mu)002:4464: med par rtogs pa'i lta ba mthong ba yi rjes
NK076(mu)002:4465: su bsgom pa ma shor tsam du bya ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:4466: de ltar lta ba dran pa'i rjes su snying rje bsgoms sam /
NK076(mu)002:4467: yang na sems can la dmigs pa'i rtog dpyod sngon du 'gro basa bya /
NK076(mu)002:4468: gnyis pa blo che ba dpe dang bcas nas de
NK076(mu)002:4469: ting la goms pa'i rjes su bsgom pa de la
NK076(mu)002:4470: gsum / dang po rgyu snga ma gnyis sam de
NK076(mu)002:4471: ting brtan pa'i steng nas dran pa spyi blugs sam
NK076(mu)002:4472: ye shes sgyu mar gsal ba dpe dang bcas /
NK076(mu)002:4473: de bas lta ba mthong rjes dang rtog dpyod sngon
NK076(mu)002:4474: 'gro gnyis la goms nas dran pa spyi blugs sam
NK076(mu)002:4475: / yang na rgyu de ting goms pas rjes su
NK076(mu)002:4476: dran pa ma bcos par spyi blugs su rig pa
NK076(mu)002:4477: ya shes sgyu mar gsal ba'ang /
NK076(mu)002:4478: blos sngon du lta ba dran pa'am rtog dpyod btang ba gang yang meda de /
NK076(mu)002:4479: dper na shar gyi nama mkhas nub kyi nam mkha' yul du mi byed pa ji bzhin du'o //
NK076(mu)002:4480: gnyis pa gsal dus dmigs med mkha' ltar bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:4481: rnal 'byor pa rang gi lus ngag sems dang der
NK076(mu)002:4482: ma zad 'khor 'das phyi nang gi chos thams cad
NK076(mu)002:4483: don dam par sems nyid yin pas so //
NK076(mu)002:4484: gang na'ang mi gnas yul rang rgyud du mi dmigs pas /
NK076(mu)002:4485: dpe mig gi yul du tho yor mir 'dzin kyang
NK076(mu)002:4486: mi ma grub pa'i tshul du sbyor ba yi tshul
NK076(mu)002:4487: gyis ni / sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu la
NK076(mu)002:4488: ni sgom pa'i blos rang gsal nam mkha' lta bur
NK076(mu)002:4489: gyis ni / bsgom mo // gsum pa de ma
NK076(mu)002:4490: 'gags pa thabs kyis bsgoms pa'i yon tan 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:4491: gyis ni / bsgom mo // dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:4492: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye shes sgyu mar
NK076(mu)002:4493: snang ba thabs kyi mtshan nyid yin te gzhi'i thabas
NK076(mu)002:4494: de la 'gag med du rtogsa pa'i thabs kyis ni
NK076(mu)002:4495: gnyis med du rnam par sbyor bas /
NK076(mu)002:4496: de ka bsgoms pa'i thabs chen po goms pa'i thabs
NK076(mu)002:4497: las byung ba yi 'bras bu'am yon tan gyi che
NK076(mu)002:4498: ba de na rtog pa byang ba ye shes sgyu
NK076(mu)002:4499: mar chub / skye 'jig med pas rdo rje yul
NK076(mu)002:4500: yul can du 'dzin pa las 'phags pas mchog yin
NK076(mu)002:4501: mar chub / no // gnyis pa khyad par la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4502: dang po snying rje'i ngo bo la tshad med bzhi
NK076(mu)002:4503: tshang bas mngon par gdung ba yod med kyi khyad
NK076(mu)002:4504: par shes bya phyi nang gi chos thams cad du
NK076(mu)002:4505: ni rig pa ye shes sgyu ma rang gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:4506: phyir / ye shes sgyu ma ma yin pa'i chos 'ga' tsam yang yod pa min pas /
NK076(mu)002:4507: rgyu'i theg par snying rje mas bu la gdung ba
NK076(mu)002:4508: dang 'dra bar 'gro ba ma sgral bar 'dir yul
NK076(mu)002:4509: bral gnyis med du dus gcig bsgral bas /
NK076(mu)002:4510: dgra gsoda pa lta bu ni ma yin pas chana
NK076(mu)002:4511: po gnyis su med pa'i snying rje'i rang bzhin yin
NK076(mu)002:4512: te / de la bdag gzhan gnyis su mi 'byed
NK076(mu)002:4513: pas phan pa ngang gis 'dogs pa'am rdzogs pa'i cha
NK076(mu)002:4515: gnyis med ngang la 'gyod bya'i yul med pas mi
NK076(mu)002:4516: 'gyod pa'i cha nas dga' ba'i machaga ste dga' ba
NK076(mu)002:4517: tshad med pa / bdag gzhan gnyis 'bral ba med
NK076(mu)002:4518: pa 'gro kun la snyoms pa'i cha nas btang snyoms
NK076(mu)002:4519: tshad med pa / tshad med do // 'di ni
NK076(mu)002:4520: ye shes rang gsal tshad med bzhi tshang tshul brtsis
NK076(mu)002:4521: tshad med pa / tshad med do // pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4522: de ltar tshangas par skyes pa'i rgyu tshad med bzhi
NK076(mu)002:4523: snying rje bsgom pa la tshang ste ngo bo gcig
NK076(mu)002:4524: par dus gcig la rdzogas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4525: rgyu'i theg par yul yul can gyis mangna para zhen
NK076(mu)002:4526: pa'i gdung ba gsang sngags kyi snying rje ye shes
NK076(mu)002:4527: sgyu ma bsgom pa de la meda do //
NK076(mu)002:4528: gnyis pa snying rje'i yul la dmigs dgos mi dgos kyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:4529: rgyu'i theg par ltar yul yul can gyi gdung ba med pa de yi phyir /
NK076(mu)002:4530: rgyu yi theg par 'khor ba'i rgyu ma rig pa /
NK076(mu)002:4533: dus thog ma med pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4534: rang bazhana de ma yin pa la der 'dzin pa'i 'khrul ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4535: 'khrul tshul rten 'brel bcu gnyis su dus rgyun gyis 'khor ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4536: nyes pa yang dag pa'i don las nyamsa pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4537: nga bo 'gro drug snod bcud sna tshogs su snang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4538: dpe thar dka' bas na brtson gyi ra ba lta bu ste /
NK076(mu)002:4539: 'bras bu dang ngo bo gcig tu bsdus pas brgyad
NK076(mu)002:4540: dang ldan pa'i yul sems can rnams la dmigs nas
NK076(mu)002:4541: tshad med bzhi skye ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4542: sngags kyi snying rje chen po de yis skye bya
NK076(mu)002:4543: skyed byed gcig par shes bzhin pas tshad med bzhi
NK076(mu)002:4544: snying rje chen po gcig la tshang bar 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:4545: ni / pha rol phyin pas tshad med bzhi tha dad du skye ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4546: sngags kyi tshad med bzhi ngo bo gcig cing yul
NK076(mu)002:4547: yul can gnyis su med pas de gnyis mtshungs pa'am
NK076(mu)002:4549: bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:4551: snying rje sgyu ma de dag rang gi ngo bo nyid bstan pa'ang gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:4552: don ngo bo ngos bzung ba'i rnam grangs bzhin du ming gi grangs kyang 'jug ste /
NK076(mu)002:4553: bsgom bya don gyi ngo bo dang /
NK076(mu)002:4554: sgom byed rnal 'byor ting 'dzin gyi ngo bo zhi lhag zung du 'brel ba yisa /
NK076(mu)002:4555: bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis su phye bas na zung gcig ya gnyis su 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)002:4556: zhor la sgom pa'i nges tshig dang gsum du 'byung ngo //
NK076(mu)002:4557: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4558: ngo bo dang rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4561: bsgom bya don gyi ngo bo'i rnam grangs dang /
NK076(mu)002:4562: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo'o //
NK076(mu)002:4564: sgyu ma'i ngo bo drug gi dmigs rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4565: sgyu ma dmigs med rang snang dgos ched dang bcas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4566: dang po la drug /dang po log rtog sgyu ma ni /
NK076(mu)002:4567: dang po mdor bstan pa la gsum yod pa'i ngo bo de la drug yod pa las dang po /
NK076(mu)002:4568: yul can de ma yin pa la der 'dzin gyi
NK076(mu)002:4569: log rtog snang dus ma grub pas sgyu ma de'i
NK076(mu)002:4570: ngo bo ni / chos bdag tshogs brgyad kyi pha 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:4571: gang zag badga phung lnga rags 'dzin dang phyi nang snod bcud kyi dngos po rnamas /
NK076(mu)002:4572: ngo bo med pa las ngo bo rang rgyud par
NK076(mu)002:4573: yod pa dang rtag pa bden pa la sogs bar
NK076(mu)002:4574: brtags pasa gnyis 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa bden
NK076(mu)002:4575: stong sgyu ma'i klung 'ba' zhig tu gyur pas na
NK076(mu)002:4577: rgyu rkyen las skyes pa ltar snang ba 'khrul ba'i
NK076(mu)002:4578: blo dang 'gyur nas mi bden cing baslu bas sgyu
NK076(mu)002:4581: kun rdzob tu rgyu rkyen la brten cinga 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:4582: dang 'brel bar 'byung ba yang dpe shinga rta yi
NK076(mu)002:4584: de rang rgyud du ma grub ste 'jig rten gyi
NK076(mu)002:4585: rnam par rtog pa'i rten 'brel du snang ba gzugs
NK076(mu)002:4587: dper na sgyu ma yi rta glang lta bura las nyon gyi rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa las skyes shing /
NK076(mu)002:4588: 'phral du bden pa ltar snang nas sas brten chus
NK076(mu)002:4589: sdud pa sogs kyi bya ba kun kyang don byed
NK076(mu)002:4591: 'gro ba log rtog cana rnamas la rang dang mthun par snang bar zad kyi /
NK076(mu)002:4592: don snang la rang bzhin med pas gzugs brnyan dang
NK076(mu)002:4593: 'dra ba'i phyir blo rig shes kyis brtags pas rang
NK076(mu)002:4594: rgyud par grub pa med de dben pas /
NK076(mu)002:4595: gtan tshigs de phyir phyi nang gi chos thams cad
NK076(mu)002:4596: mi bden de rdzun pa sgyu ma tsam yin te
NK076(mu)002:4597: / kun rdzob tu ming tsam du snang ba las
NK076(mu)002:4598: don dam par dngos po rang byung du med de
NK076(mu)002:4599: / / yang dag tu bden grub 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK076(mu)002:4600: gsum pa yang dag sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:4601: yang daga par bden pa nyid du gragsa so cog 'khor 'das sam /
NK076(mu)002:4602: yul shes gnyis su snang ba'i dus nyid na gang du yang ma dmigs pas grub pa med pas /
NK076(mu)002:4603: sems nyid rang snang ba'i phyir 'khor 'das kyi dngos
NK076(mu)002:4604: po cir snang yang rgyu rkyen meda par rig pa
NK076(mu)002:4605: rang shar ba yin pas 'khor 'das tha dad par
NK076(mu)002:4606: snang ba'i dus la ngo bo phyogs gcig pa gang
NK076(mu)002:4608: med bzhin rang gi blos phye bas ji ltar bltas
NK076(mu)002:4609: par snang ba dang snang bzhin du phyogs gcig par
NK076(mu)002:4610: ther zug ma yin pas rtag mtha' dang bral /
NK076(mu)002:4611: snang cha ma 'gags pas chad pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:4613: rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgyar snang ba yang rgyu rkyen gyis ma skyes par /
NK076(mu)002:4614: rang gi rig pa'i ye shes nyid lha'i sku phyag rgya sgyu mar shar nas snang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4615: khams gsum 'khor ba'ang snang tsam las rgyu rkyen las
NK076(mu)002:4616: ma skyes par ye shes sgyu mar shar ba de
NK076(mu)002:4617: bzhin yin pas chos thams cad rtsal 'gag pa med
NK076(mu)002:4618: pa'i thabs chen po rig pa ye shes sgyu ma
NK076(mu)002:4619: nyid ni 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:4620: yin no // lnga pa ye shes sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:4621: ye nas chos kun ye shes sgyu mar gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:4622: la ni rtog pa'i blo ye shes sgyu mar shar
NK076(mu)002:4623: bas rol zhing / de ltar ye shesa la ye
NK076(mu)002:4624: shes rol pa nyid kyang rang rgyud par ma grub
NK076(mu)002:4625: pas gsog ste snying po med do //
NK076(mu)002:4626: drug pa phyag rgya sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:4627: rgyal ba sprul sku mngon sum du byung zhing 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las skyob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4628: sprul sku de dag 'byung ba'i byin rlabsa kyi ston
NK076(mu)002:4629: pa longs skur snang ba'i ye shes sgyu ma ltar
NK076(mu)002:4632: byin gyis brlabs pa dang chos ston pa la'ang gong gi de bzhin te /
NK076(mu)002:4635: gnyis pa sgyu ma gnyis med rang snang du dgos ched dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:4636: de rnams rgyu rkyen gzhan la rag lus med pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:4637: ye shes sgyu ma yi ngo bor gnyis med 'jig
NK076(mu)002:4638: pa dang bral bas rdo rje ste de'i ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:4639: 'gyur ba med pas btsan po zhes /
NK076(mu)002:4640: 'dus byas las khyad par gyur pas mchoga kho na'o //
NK076(mu)002:4641: yin tshul ni don dam par 'dus ma byas kyi
NK076(mu)002:4642: sems nyid de kun rdzob tu 'dus byas su rang
NK076(mu)002:4643: snang bas 'dus byas shar nas snang ba'ang dbyer med
NK076(mu)002:4644: pas rdo rje nyid yin pa'i phyir de gnyis ngo
NK076(mu)002:4645: bosa tha dada pa min no //
NK076(mu)002:4646: 'o na snang stong res mos su bsgom pa ci yin na /
NK076(mu)002:4647: gdul bya blo damna pa ltar snang ba la snang
NK076(mu)002:4648: stong ngam bden gnyis res mos su goms par byed
NK076(mu)002:4649: pa'i thabs tsam du bstan par zad kyi /
NK076(mu)002:4650: sgyu ma'i dngos po drug don la bden pa dbyer med du ston pa la bdun /
NK076(mu)002:4651: dang po sgyu ma'i dngos po drug /log rtog sgyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:4657: de'ang 'khor ba'i ngan zhen gcod pa'i sgyu ma gsum /
NK076(mu)002:4658: 'das pa'i bzang zhen bcad pa'i sgyu ma gsum yin la /
NK076(mu)002:4659: zhes dkyus la gsal bas rim par 'dzin no //
NK076(mu)002:4660: gnyis pa sgom gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo /
NK076(mu)002:4661: 'gro ba sems can la shes pa'i sems rgyud skad cig ma gcig la /
NK076(mu)002:4662: nyon mongs dang ye shes gnyis dus gcig tu mi ldan te /
NK076(mu)002:4663: de ltar shes pa'i rgyud gciga po nyid don dam
NK076(mu)002:4664: par ma skyes la kun rdzob tu sgyu ma cing
NK076(mu)002:4667: gzung ba'i yul dang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis dang bral ba'i rang rig pa nyid /
NK076(mu)002:4668: ye shes sgyu mara ngo bo mi g.yo bas zhi gnas /
NK076(mu)002:4669: thams cad gsal bas lhag mthong yin te /
NK076(mu)002:4670: dpe chu dang zhes rnyog pa med pa dwangs bar
NK076(mu)002:4671: zla ba yi gzugs brnyan snang ba ji bzhin du
NK076(mu)002:4672: / zhi lhag tha dad min te mtshungs par gsal
NK076(mu)002:4673: ba ye shes sgyu ma ting 'dzin gyi ngo bor
NK076(mu)002:4674: / brjod do // gnyis pa nges tshig ni /
NK076(mu)002:4675: rang gi sems nyid las ma gtogs pa'i 'khor 'das kyi chosa gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:4676: bsgom bya ya shes sgyu ma yang sems las gzhan na med de /
NK076(mu)002:4677: ye shes sgyu ma yi snang ba'i sems nyid du
NK076(mu)002:4678: zhen pa chags pa dang bral ba de la tha
NK076(mu)002:4679: snyad kyi cha gsum du bsgom zhes bya ba'i nges
NK076(mu)002:4680: tshig go // lnga pa mi mthun pa'i skyon la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4682: kun snang gi ting 'dzin dang ma mthun pa'i sgrib pa'i skyon gyi dmigs gzung ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:4683: skyon skyed par byed ba'i rgyu dang /
NK076(mu)002:4684: skyon rang gi ngo bo dang skyon dbang du song ba' nyes pa bstan pa ni gsum zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:4685: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:4687: snying rje sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin la ma gomas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4688: mi dgos bzhin du brtson 'grus ched du byed pasa goms brtan gyi skyon 'byung bar byed de /
NK076(mu)002:4689: dper na rgyu me yod pa dang 'bras bu du ba'i tshul bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:4690: rgyu badga tu 'dzin pa bsgom bya sgom byed dam
NK076(mu)002:4691: gang zag dang chos bdag rnam pa gnyis kyis 'bras
NK076(mu)002:4692: bu sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin gsal du mi ster ba'i
NK076(mu)002:4693: sgrib pa yi skyon rnams rgyud la 'byung bar byed
NK076(mu)002:4694: do // gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4695: ting nge 'dzin la gnas dus kyi skyon dang /
NK076(mu)002:4698: dang po spyi'i skyon 'bring dang nyung bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4699: snying rje sgyu ma'i sngon du de ting stong pa
NK076(mu)002:4700: chen po ji bzhin pa nyid la brtan pa thob
NK076(mu)002:4701: mod kyang / rgyu ting dang 'bras bu phyag rgya
NK076(mu)002:4702: gcig spros gnyis kyi matshamas sbyor ba'i snying rja sgyu
NK076(mu)002:4703: ma'i skabs 'dir skyon g.yung ba tsam ma gtogs pa
NK076(mu)002:4705: 'on kyang de ting skabs su brjod pa'i skyon gyi
NK076(mu)002:4706: bye brag kun de ting las 'dir ngo bo 'bring
NK076(mu)002:4707: po dang / grangs bag tsam gyis nyung bar 'byung ngo //
NK076(mu)002:4708: tha mal rtog pa rags pa dang mang ba'i skyon
NK076(mu)002:4709: gyi rkyen rnams spong ba'i 'du byed brgyad kyis spangs
NK076(mu)002:4710: shing / de ting la sngar goms pas tha mal gyi rkyen rags pa sngar bas dakana no //
NK076(mu)002:4711: gnyis pa khyad par gyi skyon /
NK076(mu)002:4712: 'on kyang snying rje chen po 'di nyid bsgom dus rgod pa'i skyon sems yul la 'phro ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4713: bying bas nang du sdud pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4714: yul ma ngesa pa'i sa phyogsa su makhara khyim dang
NK076(mu)002:4715: bcas pa mthong nas sems de phyogs shor ba dang
NK076(mu)002:4716: / sa chu me rlung la sogs zad par gyi
NK076(mu)002:4717: skye mched mthong nas de'i rjes su sems 'brang ba
NK076(mu)002:4718: / dang / kha dog gcig tu ma nges pa'i mdog sna tshogs mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4722: sa bad kan te 'byung ba bzhi'i khams kyi cha 'khrul bas /
NK076(mu)002:4723: ting nge 'dzin don mi gsal ba'am /
NK076(mu)002:4725: mkhris pa ljang gu'am ser po /
NK076(mu)002:4728: bad kan smug po la sogs pa'i nad khams kyis kha dog mthong nas /
NK076(mu)002:4730: rtog pa'i skyon rnams gang yin pa blta bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:4736: khams 'khrugs pa de dag gang yin cha dbye'o //
NK076(mu)002:4737: gsum pa skyon kyi nyes pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:4738: dper na nam mkha' dwang ba la sprin gyis nyi ma sgrib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4739: ling tog gis mig sgrib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4740: mun pa yis rdzas mi gsal bar sgrib pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:4741: skyon gyi rnam pa gang yin pa de dag rgyud gzhung las gragas pa'i thun mong dang /
NK076(mu)002:4742: khyad par gyi skyon gyi bye brag phra ba dang
NK076(mu)002:4743: rags pa'i cha yisa ye shes sgyu ma'i dana blo
NK076(mu)002:4745: nyams skye ba la shin tu bul bar byed pa'i skyon yod do //
NK076(mu)002:4746: drug pa bcos thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4747: dang po nye bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:4748: sngon de ting skab sa bstan pa bzhin du rnam
NK076(mu)002:4749: par rtog pa'i nad kyi skyon bcos pa ni 'di
NK076(mu)002:4750: lta ste / gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:4751: nyams sam blo dang sbyar ba'i bcos thabs /
NK076(mu)002:4753: ting 'dzin la gnas dus kyi skyon bcos thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:4755: dang po blo rab la rang byung rang shar du grol ba /
NK076(mu)002:4756: sngon du rang gi shes bazhana gyi bya ra bas
NK076(mu)002:4757: rtog skyon so mthas choda de skyon ngos zin par
NK076(mu)002:4758: bya ste / de ltar skyon ngos zin par gyur
NK076(mu)002:4759: na rkun pa byung par tshor na bros pa'i tshul
NK076(mu)002:4760: bya ste / bzhin du / skyon ched du ma
NK076(mu)002:4761: bsal kyang skyon gyi rang bzhin chos nyid ye shes
NK076(mu)002:4762: sgyu ma'i ngang du dang bar 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)002:4763: ci'i phyir na rnam rtog gi skyon gyi mtshan ma bzang ngan phra rags ci dang ci skyes kyang /
NK076(mu)002:4764: sems nyid ye shes sgyu ma nyid du rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:4765: de ting gi bde ba la chags shing rtog pa'i skyon la zhe sdang pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4766: drod rtags 'byung du re ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4767: gol du dogsa pa'i blo mi 'byung ste /
NK076(mu)002:4769: skyon gyi bye brag thams cad ye shes sgyu ma
NK076(mu)002:4770: nyid rang snang ba las gzhan du grub pa min
NK076(mu)002:4771: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa tha mal 'khrul pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4772: lo rgyus byas te snying rje bskyed nas stong pa
NK076(mu)002:4773: dang zung 'jug tu sbyangs nas bcos pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:4774: gong gi skyon bcos thabs gnyis po de ltar gyi
NK076(mu)002:4775: don dang ma ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa blo chung
NK076(mu)002:4777: rtog pa'i skyon skye ba tshor nasa rtog pa de
NK076(mu)002:4778: dag gi lo rgyus de nyid de dang po rgyu
NK076(mu)002:4779: gang las byung / bar du ngo bo gang yin
NK076(mu)002:4780: la sogs shes rab kyis dpyad pas skyon stong nyid
NK076(mu)002:4782: gsum pa 'bring la rtog pa'i gnas yul blta ste
NK076(mu)002:4783: snying rje skye nas stong pa dang zung 'jug tu
NK076(mu)002:4784: sbyang ba / yang na gang nas skye ba'i rtog pa'i dbang po sgo lnga gnas /
NK076(mu)002:4785: yul gzugs sogs drug /gnas dang yul blta bas /
NK076(mu)002:4786: rang bzhin med par de mthong na skyon mun patsaya
NK076(mu)002:4787: lta bu rnam par dag cing sangs par 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)002:4788: // gnyis pa khams kyi bcos thabs /
NK076(mu)002:4789: rang 'dod pa min pa'i kha dog lnga mthonga ba na /
NK076(mu)002:4790: 'byung ba 'du ba bzhi ya gnyen pasa zhes /
NK076(mu)002:4791: sman dpyad kyis gzhila te nad med par byed pa lta bu'o //
NK076(mu)002:4794: sngon de ting bzhin sngara 'das kyi rjes su 'brang
NK076(mu)002:4795: ba dang phyis ma 'ongs pa yid la sngon du
NK076(mu)002:4796: byed pa dang / da lta rang bzhin gyi yul
NK076(mu)002:4797: gyi rkyen gyis dgyes shing 'phro rgod skyon byung ba
NK076(mu)002:4798: tshor na 'khor ba'i thog mtha'i nyes pa la bsam
NK076(mu)002:4799: byed pa dang / ste / 'khor ba la skya
NK076(mu)002:4800: ba bskyed la snying rje bskyed nas rgod pa'i skyon
NK076(mu)002:4801: rnams dor te ting 'dzin la dran pa'i thag pas
NK076(mu)002:4802: byed pa dang / ste / bcing ngo // gnyis
NK076(mu)002:4803: pa bying ba'i skyon ni gang zhig bsgom pa'i tshe
NK076(mu)002:4804: na sems nang du thim pas te bying rmugs su
NK076(mu)002:4805: song na khrus bya skor ba bya zhing lus bcags
NK076(mu)002:4806: byed pa dang / ste / bcing ngo // khams
NK076(mu)002:4807: bsang ngo // drod rtags la brod pas dad pa
NK076(mu)002:4808: skyed nas ting 'dzin la 'jug cing sems gzings bstod
NK076(mu)002:4809: byed pa dang / ste / bcing ngo // khams
NK076(mu)002:4810: bsang ngo // par bya'o // bdun pa nyams la
NK076(mu)002:4811: byed pa dang / ste / bcing ngo // khams
NK076(mu)002:4812: bsang ngo // par bya'o // gnyis / dang po
NK076(mu)002:4813: byed pa dang / ste / bcing ngo // khams
NK076(mu)002:4814: bsang ngo // par bya'o // gnyis / mdor bstan
NK076(mu)002:4815: / gong du bstan pa de ltar blo bzhag thabs
NK076(mu)002:4816: kyis bzhag /skyon bcos thabs kyis de dang da ltar
NK076(mu)002:4817: bcos shing brtson 'grus kyis bsgom par gyur pa'i skabs
NK076(mu)002:4818: su ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor nyid kyis nyams
NK076(mu)002:4819: gong nas gong du 'phel ba'ang lnga ste gang zhe
NK076(mu)002:4824: mthar phyin pa'i nyams kyis 'og nas gong du 'gro
NK076(mu)002:4825: ba bsgom bya'i don gyi ngo bo ye shes sgyu
NK076(mu)002:4826: ma la tha dad med kyang /
NK076(mu)002:4827: sgom byed kyi blo'i sgrib pa rab rib dag ma
NK076(mu)002:4828: dag gam tshab che chung gi chas nyams rim pa
NK076(mu)002:4829: lngar brjod do // gnyis pa rgyas pa la lnga /
NK076(mu)002:4830: dang po g.yo ba'i nyams ni /
NK076(mu)002:4831: ting 'dzin rtse gcig mi sdod par 'pho zhing yul so sor 'gyes pa'i rgod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4832: nad du thim pa yis bying ba'i skyon rnams dper
NK076(mu)002:4833: na rlung drag pos ded pa'i chu yi gnyer ma
NK076(mu)002:4834: dang 'dra bar don la blo gnas pa de /
NK076(mu)002:4835: ting 'dzin rtog pa 'dres mar cung zad yod pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:4836: nyin zhag gcig la thun drug cu rtsa bzhir phye
NK076(mu)002:4837: ba'i thun gyi tshad gcig gi sum gnyis rtog pa
NK076(mu)002:4838: nyi tshe ba rgyu ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4839: sum char rtog pa dang chos nyid 'dres mar yada pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4841: nyin zhag gcig la thun so gnyis su dgos pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4842: thun gcig gi bzhi cha'am lnga chara rtog pa de
NK076(mu)002:4843: med cing chos nyid 'ba' zhig rgyu la /
NK076(mu)002:4844: bzhi gsum mam lnga bzhi ni rtog pa dang chos
NK076(mu)002:4845: nyid 'dras mar rgyu bas na thob pa'i nyams so
NK076(mu)002:4847: nyin zhag gcig la bcu drug tu bgos pa'i cha
NK076(mu)002:4848: gcig la thun re byas pa'i thun rkyang tsam du
NK076(mu)002:4849: rtog pa med par bsgom nus shing chos nyid gsal
NK076(mu)002:4850: ba dang ldan pa rtog pa'i dbang du cung zad
NK076(mu)002:4852: dper na chu klunga dala bar 'bab pa'i chu 'gro yang 'gro bar mi mngon pa'i tshul bzhin na //
NK076(mu)002:4854: sgo gtan pa'i rdzasa rgyang 'dan bcug na rlung gis mi bsgul ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:4855: zhag gcig la brgyad du bgos pa'i thun rer /
NK076(mu)002:4856: rnam par rtog pa'i rlung gis ting 'dzin mi bsgul
NK076(mu)002:4857: bar rtse gcig tu gzhi rig pa sgyu ma la
NK076(mu)002:4859: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams /
NK076(mu)002:4861: mig gis gzugs la blta ba ltar dabnga pa'i mngon
NK076(mu)002:4862: sum du phyi nang gi snang ba gang snang thams
NK076(mu)002:4863: cad rang bzhin med pa rig pa rang gsal bar
NK076(mu)002:4864: byas pa yi don ye shes sgyu ma la bskyed
NK076(mu)002:4865: 'don zhing bogs dbyung du byar med pa'i phyir nyams
NK076(mu)002:4866: lnga'i mtha' ma mthar phyin pa'i nyams zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:4867: brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4868: sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod spyod pa'i gzhir bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4869: rjes 'jug gi lam pa rnal 'byor pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4871: dang po lam zung 'jug tu bsgom pa sa ngas rgyas kyi dgongs par shes pa /
NK076(mu)002:4872: snying rja chen po'i rnal 'byor ye shes sgyu ma sgom pa pos /
NK076(mu)002:4873: srid gsum 'khor ba'i chos thams cad don dam byang
NK076(mu)002:4874: chub sems sam ye shes sgyu ma dang 'dra bar
NK076(mu)002:4875: ni / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bla
NK076(mu)002:4876: med byang chub la mkhas pasa shesa pa ltar shes
NK076(mu)002:4877: nas kun rdzob byang chub sems kyis 'gro rnams 'khor
NK076(mu)002:4878: ba las sgrol ba'i ched du gzhan don gyi go
NK076(mu)002:4879: ni / cha bgos te / srid gsum gyi 'gro
NK076(mu)002:4880: ba sems can rnams ye shes sgyu ma dang 'dra
NK076(mu)002:4881: bar de ltar snga ma nas yin par shes pa'o
NK076(mu)002:4882: ni / cha bgos te / // gnyis pa 'bras
NK076(mu)002:4883: bu thams cad mkhyen pas gdul bya la gzigs pa
NK076(mu)002:4885: dus thams cad du 'khor 'das chos rnams rang rig kho na yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:4886: de ma yin par der 'dzin log par rtog pa
NK076(mu)002:4887: ste ye shes rang ngo ma shes lhan skyes dang
NK076(mu)002:4888: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:4889: de las log pa ni rnam par dag cing rgyud dag pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4890: 'gro rnams rang rig ye shes mnyam pa'i dbyings las mi gazhana phyir /
NK076(mu)002:4891: ma h+aa'i lugs la yul yul can gnyis su med
NK076(mu)002:4892: pa'i phyir thugs rje chen posa sangs rgyas kyi ye
NK076(mu)002:4893: shes dang / sems can gyi sems kyi chos nyid
NK076(mu)002:4894: dang 'khor 'das ngo bo gcig par 'brel bas na
NK076(mu)002:4895: shes dang / gnyis med phyir / 'gro drug gi
NK076(mu)002:4896: snang ba bden med ci lta ba bzhin dgongs pas
NK076(mu)002:4897: ci lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes /
NK076(mu)002:4898: dus snga phyi dang gansa mtho dman sogs lhag ma ma lus par snang ba kun /
NK076(mu)002:4899: rgyal ba'i ye shes kyis dgos pas /
NK076(mu)002:4900: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes kho na'o //
NK076(mu)002:4901: rgyal ba de'i rjes su 'jug pa'i snying rje chen
NK076(mu)002:4902: po'i rnal 'byor pas spyod pa'ang chos nyid de bzhin
NK076(mu)002:4903: shes par bya'o // gnyis pa rjes 'jug gi rnal 'byor pa'i spyod pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4907: dang po ye shes sgyu mar shes pa dngos /
NK076(mu)002:4908: don dam chos nyid de bzhin nyid skye ba med
NK076(mu)002:4909: pa'i dbyings nyid kun rdzob tu chos kyi bye brag
NK076(mu)002:4910: rnam pa sna tshagas pa mang po'i rnam grangs su
NK076(mu)002:4911: ma 'gags pa ni snang ba'i thabs su snang /
NK076(mu)002:4912: thabs ma 'gags par snang ba de nyid snang ba
NK076(mu)002:4913: 'gag med sgyu ma snang la ngo bo med pas
NK076(mu)002:4914: mig yor snang la bzung du med pas chu zla
NK076(mu)002:4915: gsal la stong pas gzugsa brnyan bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:4916: thabs sna tshogs su snang ba de nyid rang gi
NK076(mu)002:4917: rig pa ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor snang bas
NK076(mu)002:4918: gang la yang chags pa med cing sna tshogs kun
NK076(mu)002:4920: gnyis pa de la gnas pa'i phan yon ni /
NK076(mu)002:4921: de ltar sgyu mar snang ba'i thabs dang /
NK076(mu)002:4922: rang rgyud du mi 'dzin pa'i shes rab dang /
NK076(mu)002:4923: de gnyis dbyer med du rtogs pa'i gdangs dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:4924: pa theg pa mchog gi ting 'dzin la gnas su
NK076(mu)002:4925: gyur pas na / gzhan gyi don ji ltar spyad kyang bag chags su mi 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)002:4926: yon tan zad pa mada cing bdag gzhan gyi don
NK076(mu)002:4927: gnyis kyis tshogs gnyis 'grub ste lam la sgrib par
NK076(mu)002:4928: ma 'gyur zhes pa'am don la sgrib par mi 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:4929: ro // rang rgyud par mi 'dzin pa'i shes raba dang /
NK076(mu)002:4930: ma 'gags pa'i thabs chana de gnyis su med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4931: mchog rtogs pa'i ngang la ye nasa gnas bzhin du
NK076(mu)002:4932: 'dzin med du spyod pas rola pa yana zhes smos
NK076(mu)002:4933: pa'o // gnyis pa spyod tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:4937: tshad med bzhis gzhan don byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:4938: gong bzhin rkyen dang 'phrad na phrin las la sogs
NK076(mu)002:4939: byed cing bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa dang
NK076(mu)002:4940: / don byed yul la sogs pa 'og ma las khyad par spags tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:4942: dang po chos kun byang chub sems su gcig pa'i rtsal snying rjes kun la khyab tshul /
NK076(mu)002:4943: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang du byang chub sems su
NK076(mu)002:4944: sangs rgyas dang sems can ngo bo nyid kya rgya
NK076(mu)002:4945: gcig pas na / tshad med bzhi'i rtsa ba gnyis
NK076(mu)002:4946: su med pa'i snying rje chen po las 'byung ba'o
NK076(mu)002:4947: gcig pas na / // gnyis su med na snying rje la nges tshig med snyam pa la /
NK076(mu)002:4948: sangas rgyas dang sems cana gnyis su med par ye shes sgyu mar gciga tu rtogs na /
NK076(mu)002:4949: gnyis med du rtogs pa'i snying rje chena pa skya zhasa de la bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:4950: thams cad la khyab brdal chen por rtogs pa'i bla
NK076(mu)002:4951: ni phyogs gcig thug pa med pa'i phyir chos kun
NK076(mu)002:4952: tu shar bas na snang zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:4953: gnyis pa snying rjes phan 'dogs shing skyob pa'i byams pa /
NK076(mu)002:4954: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i thabs chen kun gyis gdul bya'i
NK076(mu)002:4955: don mdzad pa de'i ngo bo ye shes sgyu ma
NK076(mu)002:4956: yin la / de la bsgrib pa med pas 'od
NK076(mu)002:4957: gsal ba gdul bya 'dul byed gnyis su mi phyed
NK076(mu)002:4958: pas byams pa tshad med pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:4959: de ltar byams pa chen pos gdul bya thams cad
NK076(mu)002:4960: dgyes par mdzad pa de nyid 'byung khungs su gyur
NK076(mu)002:4961: pas dbyings snying rje ye shes sgyu ma bsgom pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4962: dus ma yis bu la gdung ba ltar 'gro drug
NK076(mu)002:4963: sems can lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad la
NK076(mu)002:4964: / byams pa dang snying rje chen po'i thaga pa dus rgyun ma chada par /
NK076(mu)002:4965: nyon mongas pas bcings pa 'khor ba'i lam las byams pas grol bar byed cing /
NK076(mu)002:4966: gdul bya la phan 'dogs pa'i byams pa tshad med
NK076(mu)002:4967: pa dag gisa gdul bya mnyes para gyis shig /gsum
NK076(mu)002:4968: pa 'gro ba'i don la mi skyo zhing dga' bas
NK076(mu)002:4969: dga' ba / byams pa'i don snying rje las 'byung
NK076(mu)002:4970: ba de bazhana du 'khor ba'i gnas las thar dka'
NK076(mu)002:4971: brtson ra dang 'dra bar chud pa'i sems can la
NK076(mu)002:4972: dga' ba / / snying rje chen po zhagas pa dang 'dra ba cher brkyang nas /
NK076(mu)002:4973: 'khor ba nyon mongs pa 'dam dang 'dra ba'i nang
NK076(mu)002:4974: nas thar pa'i skam sar 'dren para byed pa la
NK076(mu)002:4975: / snying rje chen pa ye shes sgyu ma'i sgo
NK076(mu)002:4976: nas 'gro don 'byung ba la skyo bar ma byed
NK076(mu)002:4977: cig /snying rje 'gro don la mi skyo ba de
NK076(mu)002:4978: bzhin du gdul bya'i skye ba phal mo che rnams
NK076(mu)002:4979: / la / lasa ngan gya sgrib pas rang rgyud
NK076(mu)002:4980: la mi gos shing skye bo sems can thams cada
NK076(mu)002:4981: ye shes sgyu mar mngon para rdzogs par sangas rgyas
NK076(mu)002:4982: para gyur nas dga' ba tshad med pa dag la
NK076(mu)002:4983: 'gyod pa ma byed cig /bzhi pa phyogs ris med
NK076(mu)002:4984: par btang snyoms pa'i btang snyoms ni /
NK076(mu)002:4985: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad gang zag gi
NK076(mu)002:4986: bdag nga dang chos kyi bdag mada pa la gnyis
NK076(mu)002:4987: med du rtogs pa'i thugs rje chen pos bdag gzhan
NK076(mu)002:4988: nam nye ring gnyis su rtog pa'i blos mi 'byed
NK076(mu)002:4989: de / sems can thams cad la bu gcig pu
NK076(mu)002:4990: la mas byams pa dang 'dra bar byams snying rje
NK076(mu)002:4991: blo nye bar bzhag par bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:4992: de yang dus thams cad du sems can la phyogs
NK076(mu)002:4993: ris kyi dra ma med par btang snyoms par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:4994: // gnyis pa ni stong chen sngon du rdzogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:4995: don bya ba'i rkyen gdul bya dang 'phrad na gzhan
NK076(mu)002:4996: don gyi spyod pa byed pa sngon de ting gi
NK076(mu)002:4997: skabs su bzhin gzhan don rdzogs par bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:4998: de dang snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor bsgoms pas
NK076(mu)002:4999: bdag nyid la gdul bya'i don du sems bskyed pa
NK076(mu)002:5000: song bas na gzhan gyi don shugs kyis rdzogs par
NK076(mu)002:5001: byed pa'o // gsum pa la'ang rgyu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhi las /
NK076(mu)002:5003: dmigs pa yul gyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:5007: phyogs gtad yod med kyi khyad par ro //
NK076(mu)002:5008: dang po dmigs pa yul gyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:5009: tshad med bzhis don bya ba'i dmigs pa'i yul du gyur pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:5010: rgyu'i theg pas sngar bshad pa ltar //
NK076(mu)002:5011: de phyir rgyu rkyen 'bras bu dang //
NK076(mu)002:5012: dus dang rang bzhin 'khrul pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:5013: tshul gyis nyams dang ngo bo dang //
NK076(mu)002:5014: btson ra lta bu brgyad la dmigs //
NK076(mu)002:5016: 'khor ba'i rgyu rkyen gnyis gcig dang /
NK076(mu)002:5017: ngo bo 'bras bu gnyis gcig ste /
NK076(mu)002:5018: de ltar bdun la dmigs nas thugs rje skye ba'i yul rgya chung la /
NK076(mu)002:5019: 'bras bu'i theg pas bdun po de'i steng du /
NK076(mu)002:5020: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi kri yog sde gsum
NK076(mu)002:5021: bsnan pas bdun gnyis bcu bzhi'i gdul bya la dmigs
NK076(mu)002:5022: pa'i yul rgya che bas 'phags pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5023: gnyis pa ngo bo'i khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)002:5024: theg pa 'og ma'i thugs rje skye bya skyed byed
NK076(mu)002:5025: kyi cha nas tshad med bzhi ngo bo tha dad
NK076(mu)002:5026: du 'dod la / 'bras bu'i theg pas yul bral
NK076(mu)002:5027: gnyis med kyi snying rje ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang
NK076(mu)002:5028: du tshad med bzhi lhun gyis grub pas spags pa'o
NK076(mu)002:5029: du 'dod la / // gsum pa byed las kyi khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)002:5030: rgyu'i theg par snying rje rtsol bcas kyi sgo nas 'gro don byed la /
NK076(mu)002:5031: ma h+aa'i snying rje chen po bdag gzhan gnyis med kyi sgo nas 'gro don byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5032: yang na rgyu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhi ni phyogs re'i don byed las mi nus la /
NK076(mu)002:5033: 'dir 'bras bu'i theg pa'i snying rje ye shes sgyu
NK076(mu)002:5034: ma gcig pu la tshad med bzhi tshang ba'i sgo
NK076(mu)002:5035: nas don byed nus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5036: bzhi pa phana yon gya khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)002:5037: rgyu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhis rang gzhan gyi don
NK076(mu)002:5038: byas pa'i 'bras bu la bcu gcig kun tu 'od
NK076(mu)002:5040: 'bras bu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhis don byas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5041: 'bras bu pad+ma spyan la sogs pa'i sku lnga grub
NK076(mu)002:5042: pas spags pa'o // lnga pa phyogs gtad yod med kyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:5043: rgyu'i theg pa'i tshad med bzhis rang man chad kyi
NK076(mu)002:5044: gdul bya la mngon par gdung ba'i phyogs gtad yod
NK076(mu)002:5045: pa yin la / 'dir ma h+aa'i ni yul bral
NK076(mu)002:5046: gnyis med kyi tshad med bzhis gdul bya la phyogs
NK076(mu)002:5047: dang ris med da kun tu don byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5048: khyad lnga po de'i phyir thun mong gi rgyu'i theg
NK076(mu)002:5049: pa chen po daga gi tshad med bzhi las sngags
NK076(mu)002:5050: kyi ma h+aa yo ga'i tshad med chen po bzhi
NK076(mu)002:5051: ni kun gyi blara gyur pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:5052: gnyis pa bdag don la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:5053: dang po spyod lam thams cad du ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang las mi 'da' ba /
NK076(mu)002:5054: snying rje ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor pa bdag
NK076(mu)002:5055: nyid kyi don bya ba'i phyir 'di ltar du phyi
NK076(mu)002:5056: nang gi spyod yul gyi snang ba thams cad kun
NK076(mu)002:5057: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang ba rtogs pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:5058: na / phyi yul dang nang sems gnyis su 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:5059: pa'i sgrib pa med par ye shes su gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:5061: ye shes sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin la blo brtan pa'i spyod pa shin tu bde ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5062: gnyis pa 'dod yon lnga sogs la spyod par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5063: 'dod pa'i longs spyod gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga dang ldan pa thams cad la /
NK076(mu)002:5064: gsang sngags phyi pa ltar dkar gsum mngar gsum la sogs pa gtsang ba 'am bzang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5065: dam rdzas lnga la sogs pa mi gtsang zhing dme
NK076(mu)002:5066: ba'i bla gnyis su ma 'dzin te 'dzin pa med
NK076(mu)002:5068: longs spyod thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes sgyu mar ro gcig cing tha dad med pas na /
NK076(mu)002:5069: bzang ngan gtsang dme gnyis su 'dzin pa med pas shin tu bde ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5070: rgyu mtshan de bas na spyad par bya ba tan
NK076(mu)002:5071: gan ma byin len pa rdzun ngag 'khyal ste lnga
NK076(mu)002:5072: dang mi spong ba nyon mongs lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:5073: dang du lena pa dam rdzas lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:5074: 'dod pa'i yon tan gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya
NK076(mu)002:5075: lnga la sagas 'khor ba'i chos nyi shu po thams
NK076(mu)002:5076: cad ye shes la ye shes sgyu mar rol bar
NK076(mu)002:5077: spyod do // dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5078: dang po sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod ngos bzung ba /
NK076(mu)002:5079: 'khor ba'i g.yul dang bdud kyi dpung bcom pas thub
NK076(mu)002:5080: pa chen po lha mi'i ston pa thub pa'i dbang
NK076(mu)002:5082: chos kun dbang thob pas ji ltar thugs la dgongs shing dmigas pa bazhana du grub /
NK076(mu)002:5083: 'o na dmigs bya dmigs byed du song ngo snyam pa la /
NK076(mu)002:5084: don dam 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams thams cad rang
NK076(mu)002:5085: rgyud med par yul yul can dmigs su med pas
NK076(mu)002:5086: / kun rdzob tu ye shes sgyu ma nyid cira
NK076(mu)002:5087: yanga 'char zhing gang du'ang grub ste sna tshogs su
NK076(mu)002:5088: / snang ba'o // gnyis pa rjes 'jug rnal 'byor pas de ltar nyams su len tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5089: dang po khyad par gyi dam tshig ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang las mi 'da' ba /
NK076(mu)002:5090: rtog pa'i chos nyid zag pa med pa thag pas zab mo'i dona ye shes sgyu mar rtogs na /
NK076(mu)002:5091: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor dag par ma gyur pa'i chos ni gang yang meda do //
NK076(mu)002:5092: ya shes sgyu ma ye nas yin pa la byed pa pos ma bcos par /
NK076(mu)002:5093: chos kun tu ye shes sgyu mar rang gsal bas
NK076(mu)002:5094: na chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye shes sgyu
NK076(mu)002:5096: thams cad ye shes sgyu ma yin pa de phyir
NK076(mu)002:5097: spyod lam bzhi po la dus thams cad kun tu
NK076(mu)002:5098: / sgyu ma'i ye shes rang gsal las 'da' bar mi bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5099: gnyis pa thun mong gi dam tshig snga ma dang mthun par 'phel ba /
NK076(mu)002:5100: rtsa ba'i dam tshig dang yan lag gi dam tshig
NK076(mu)002:5101: thams cada kun snga ma de ting bzhin du snga
NK076(mu)002:5102: ma bas 'dir nus pa'i stobs cher 'phela ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5103: bcu pa drod la dbye ba med de /
NK076(mu)002:5104: gong bstan de ltar ye shes sgyu ma yi don
NK076(mu)002:5105: lta bas rtogs shing ting 'dzin goms pas nyams su
NK076(mu)002:5106: myong ba'i drod 'khor ba'i chosa sdug bsngal gyi phung
NK076(mu)002:5107: po 'di la byams snying rje tshad mada bzhi dang
NK076(mu)002:5108: ldan pa'i byang chub sems kyis rang dbang med par
NK076(mu)002:5109: snying rje skye bas sems 'phrog par 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)002:5110: sems nyid ye shes sgyu ma ma 'khrul ba ngo
NK076(mu)002:5111: ma shes pas blo 'khrul bar snang ba la 'di
NK076(mu)002:5112: ci yin snyam du ya mtshan skya ste /
NK076(mu)002:5113: don la blta rgyu med par ting 'dzin sgom par byed pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:5114: le lor 'dug pa'ang de bzhin ya mtshan skye ste snying rje skyes so //
NK076(mu)002:5115: phyi nang gsang ba'i drod rnam pa gsum lus ngag
NK076(mu)002:5116: yid gsum la 'byung ba'ang snga ma de ting las
NK076(mu)002:5118: bcu gcig pa brtags la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5120: de ltar snying rje sgyu ma'i nyams lnga rim pa
NK076(mu)002:5121: gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i don mtha' ste tha
NK076(mu)002:5122: ma'i rtagsa ni / ting 'dzin las su rung bas
NK076(mu)002:5123: lus shing bal gyi 'dab ma lta bur shin tu
NK076(mu)002:5124: yang ba 'phur shes snyam shes pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5125: lus kyi na tsha la sogs bzod pa phra mo
NK076(mu)002:5126: thob pa de ting bas 'dir yun ring ba dang
NK076(mu)002:5127: / 'byung 'dus phung po la khams bde ba dang
NK076(mu)002:5128: mi bde ba gnyis med par bde bar snyoms pa
NK076(mu)002:5129: / dang / 'dir dus skabs phala cher rtags de
NK076(mu)002:5130: tsho yod cing 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad mgo snyoms
NK076(mu)002:5132: bas chos brgyad grangs mang ba dang ngo bo phra
NK076(mu)002:5133: rags 'bring po la ngo mnyam pa 'ong ba yin
NK076(mu)002:5135: lam 'og ma bas 'dir 'phel zhing gsal ba ni
NK076(mu)002:5137: la sogs pa'i drod rtags gzhan kun kyang lam snga
NK076(mu)002:5138: ma de ting las grangs mang du 'phel zhing rtags
NK076(mu)002:5139: kyi ngo bo yang gsal la /
NK076(mu)002:5140: dus kyang yun ring du 'byung ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5141: gsum pa mngon shes dang ting 'dzin 'di la blo brtan dgos par gdams ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:5142: rang dang lhan ciga tu drung na 'dug pa'i gang
NK076(mu)002:5143: zag pha rol po de yi sems la dmigs gtad
NK076(mu)002:5144: ting 'dzin la bzhag pa tsam gyis /
NK076(mu)002:5145: de yi sems rgyud shes pa'i mngon par shes pa
NK076(mu)002:5146: de'ang de ting bas 'dir grangs mang du 'phel ba
NK076(mu)002:5147: dang / ngo bo cung zad gsal zhing brtan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5148: de las gzhan yang sngon gnas rjes dran sogs dang /
NK076(mu)002:5150: sgra shes pa la sogs pa cung zada tsam 'byung ngo //
NK076(mu)002:5151: goms na yon tan yod pa de bas na snying
NK076(mu)002:5152: rje chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi ting 'dzin la blo
NK076(mu)002:5154: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la dbye ba med de /
NK076(mu)002:5155: ye shes sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin la gnas pa 'di
NK076(mu)002:5156: yi tshe dbang po sgo drug gi spyod yul gyi
NK076(mu)002:5157: snang ba ma lus thams cad kun dngos su sgyu
NK076(mu)002:5158: ma snang ba lta ci smos kyi /
NK076(mu)002:5159: gnyid log pa'i rmi lam du yang spyod yul thams
NK076(mu)002:5160: cad snang la rang bzhin med pa sgyu mar mthong
NK076(mu)002:5161: ba dang / sems can thams cad snying rje'i yul
NK076(mu)002:5162: gdul byas gang ba rnams rig pa ye shes sgyu
NK076(mu)002:5164: rmi lam du bla mas byin gyis barlobasa pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5165: dbang bskur ba dang legs nyes kyi lung bstan pa sogs sngar bas manga ba mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5166: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang mtshan ma lnga mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5167: de la sagas shugs snang brgyad dang gzhan yang rmi
NK076(mu)002:5168: lam bzang po byung yang ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang
NK076(mu)002:5169: blo dga' zhing chagsa par mi bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5170: bcu gsum pa phan yon la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5171: dang po yon tan tshad med par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5172: snying rje chena pa yi rnal 'byor gyi ting 'dzin la goms par byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:5173: rnal 'byor pa gsang sngags gnyis med kyi don chen
NK076(mu)002:5174: po lta ba rtogs pa yis yon tan yod pas
NK076(mu)002:5175: / dus thog ma dang mtha' ma med par ye shes sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin de ltar bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:5176: de bsgoms pa'i yon tan tshad med pa'i dpe nam
NK076(mu)002:5177: mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa ste tshad bzung med la
NK076(mu)002:5178: / rnal 'byor pa'i spyod yul ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid dang cha mthun pas gcig pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5179: gnyis pa tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing phyag rgya gcig par sbyor ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:5180: chos kun ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor ma 'gags
NK076(mu)002:5181: par spyod pas bsod namas kyi tshogs chen po dang
NK076(mu)002:5182: ldan pa / sgyu ma de yang rang rgyud pa
NK076(mu)002:5183: med pas ming tsam las de la ma chags te
NK076(mu)002:5184: rang bzhin med par shes pas ye shes kyi tshogs
NK076(mu)002:5186: de ltar snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor 'di la
NK076(mu)002:5187: goms na rnal 'byor phyi ma phyag rgya gcig pa
NK076(mu)002:5188: rtsal ba med par 'grub ste gnas skabs nye sbyor
NK076(mu)002:5189: gyi 'bras bu'o // bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la dbye ba med de /
NK076(mu)002:5190: lam mthar ma phyin de nyid bsgom 'phro la 'chi 'pho na /
NK076(mu)002:5191: sems 'pho ba'i dpe nyi ma las ma g.yos bar 'od zer 'byung ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:5192: rig pa las ma g.yos par ma 'ongs pa'i sems shar ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5193: lus 'pho ba'i dpe sa bon las ma g.yos par myu gur 'gyur ba ltar dang /
NK076(mu)002:5194: ngag 'pho ba'i dpe skyu ru ra las ma g.yos pa skyur mo'i ro 'byung ba'am /
NK076(mu)002:5195: brag las ma g.yos par brag cha'i sgra 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:5196: bzhin du ngag las ma 'phos bar ma 'ongs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5198: de ltar lus ngag yid gsum rig pa sgyu ma
NK076(mu)002:5199: las ma g.yos pas de la 'pho ba med bazhana
NK076(mu)002:5200: du lam pa'i ngo la ma 'ongs pa'i snang bar
NK076(mu)002:5201: 'pho zhing da ltar gyi snang ba 'gyur bas 'chi
NK076(mu)002:5203: sngar nas ye shes sgyu ma yul rkyen gyis mi
NK076(mu)002:5204: 'phrog par brtan par byas pa'i ngang las 'das na
NK076(mu)002:5205: kun gzhi la tshe snga ma nas las ngan la
NK076(mu)002:5206: spyod pa'i bag chags kyi rgyun thams cad gcod par
NK076(mu)002:5207: 'gyur te / lha mi'i lus rten bzang po thob
NK076(mu)002:5208: nas sbyangs ba'i las 'phros 'brela basa gsang sngags ma
NK076(mu)002:5209: h+aa'i lam 'di dang dus dang gnas skabs sogs kyis
NK076(mu)002:5210: bkol bar mi 'gyur te 'phrad nas grol bar 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:5211: 'gyur te / ro // bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5212: dang po gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:5213: blo chen phyi ma gcig spros tshogs sgrub nas thod rgal mthar chags kyis rig 'dzin thob pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:5214: blo chung na lan grangsa skye ba gzhan dag la
NK076(mu)002:5215: gong ltar thod rgal mthar chags kyis phyir mi ldog
NK076(mu)002:5216: par tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rigs su 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:5218: rnam smin rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:5219: gnyis pa gzhung bzhin bsgrubs pas mthar chag gi 'bras bu ni /
NK076(mu)002:5220: snying rje sgyu ma sgom pa'i lam 'dir gong ma'i
NK076(mu)002:5221: cha rkyen kun rdzogsa par bsgrubs pasa thun min gyi
NK076(mu)002:5222: matshana so gnyis dang dapa byad bzang po brgyad cu
NK076(mu)002:5223: kun dang ldan pa'i longs sku dabnga phyug chena pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5224: sku'i gansa 'og min nyid du brgyud nas mangna sum
NK076(mu)002:5225: du 'byung ba'i lam la tha tshama meda do //
NK076(mu)002:5226: gsum pa ma rtogs le lo byas pa'i skyon /
NK076(mu)002:5227: ye shes sgyu ma'i don ma rtogsa par ting 'dzin bsgom pa la la la dang /
NK076(mu)002:5228: spyod pa rang kha ma snyom lasa kyi le lo byas na /
NK076(mu)002:5229: tshe 'dir gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi dona gnyis
NK076(mu)002:5230: ma 'grub par phyi ma ngan song gsum du 'gro
NK076(mu)002:5231: bar 'gyur ro // des na bsgom la brtson 'grus kyis zhes shugs la gdams pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5233: yul bral gnyis med kyi snying rja chena pa ye
NK076(mu)002:5234: shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor bstan pa'i gzhung gi tshig
NK076(mu)002:5235: don rnams gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na la'u ste
NK076(mu)002:5236: yas 'grangs bzhi pa'i don bstan pa'o ////le'u lnga pa
NK076(mu)002:5237: phyag rgya gcig pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5238: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:5239: stong nyid snying rje gnyis su meda pa'i ye shes
NK076(mu)002:5240: sgyu ma'i ngang du goms pa'i ting 'dzin gyis phyag
NK076(mu)002:5241: btsal nasa / don lus snang sems gsum dbyer med la sbyangs thabs /
NK076(mu)002:5242: rtags zhi khro phyag rgya gcig pa'i lha snang stong dbyer med bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor bshad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5244: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan /
NK076(mu)002:5245: snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor pas phyag rgya gcig pa bsgom 'dod pa gang dag yin zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:5248: yid thugs rdo rje gsum ldan du bsgom pa'ang /
NK076(mu)002:5249: snga bar 'das pa'i de ting skabs /
NK076(mu)002:5250: sngon dgos thabs dang ngo bo dang /
NK076(mu)002:5251: zhes pa sogs don bco lnga ston pa'i lus kyi
NK076(mu)002:5252: sgo nas shes par gyis shig /gnyis pa yan lag
NK076(mu)002:5253: rgyas bshad la don bco lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:5268: dang po sngon du bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:5270: sbyor lam spyi yi sngon du bya ba lam mam las /
NK076(mu)002:5271: dbang thob cing lhag pa'i yo byad lnga dang ldan par bya ba la sogs bdun dang /
NK076(mu)002:5272: sngon de ting skabs bshad pa bzhin rdzogs par bya ba yis /
NK076(mu)002:5273: khyad par phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor 'ad nyid
NK076(mu)002:5274: kyi sngon du ye shes sgyu ma mthar phyin pa
NK076(mu)002:5276: dmigs rten rgyal ba'i sku gser dngul sogs kyi lugs su blugs pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:5279: 'jim pa la 'deng so byas pa la sogs yi
NK076(mu)002:5280: dam gyi lha'i mtshan ma'i sku phyag rgya rab gnas
NK076(mu)002:5281: can mdun du bzhag pa de la yan lag brgyad
NK076(mu)002:5282: pa 'bul ba sngona stong chen bzhina du bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5284: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK076(mu)002:5285: 'khor lo yongs su rdzogsa par bya ba'i lam zhi
NK076(mu)002:5286: khro'i gang rung gi phyag rgya gcig pa 'di bsgom
NK076(mu)002:5287: dgos pa dang / phyag rgya spros pa'i rgyu rgya
NK076(mu)002:5288: gcig pa 'di yis thaba par bya ba'i dgos ched
NK076(mu)002:5289: dgos pa dang / yod pa dang / rgyu stong
NK076(mu)002:5290: par zhen pa'i rtog pa'am snying rje sgyu mar zhana
NK076(mu)002:5291: pa de gnyis dag cing dbyer med du dabnga du
NK076(mu)002:5292: bya ba'i phyir rgya gcig bsgom dgos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5293: rtog pa'i yan lag phung khams skye mched la sagas lha'i dkyil 'khor du gansa 'gyur bar bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:5294: rgya gcig brtan pa thob nas gdul bya gazhana dag yongs su smin para bya ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK076(mu)002:5295: de ltar dgos ched lnga yod pa de'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:5296: lha'i sku phyag rgya' rnal 'byor bsgom pa shin tu gacasa so //
NK076(mu)002:5297: gsum pa bzhag thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5299: de yang rgya gcig la 'jug pa'i thabs la rnam pa gnyis ta /
NK076(mu)002:5300: lha bsgom pa'i sngon du rnal 'byor ba'i sems kyi rtsal yi ge la sbyangs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5301: de nas zhi khro'i lhar bskyed cing sgom pa'i thabs bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5302: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5306: dang po bsgom thabs spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5307: mdor bstan gyi snga ma yi ge la sems sbyangs
NK076(mu)002:5308: pa la blo chung ba gdams ngag gi stobs dang
NK076(mu)002:5309: / blo che ba shes rab kyi stobs kyis lha bsgom pa la 'jug pa'i gzhi bo /
NK076(mu)002:5310: rtsa ba rgyu'i yi ge aa'am h'u 'di nyid yin te /
NK076(mu)002:5314: de las dang po la shin tu gces so //
NK076(mu)002:5315: gnyis ba rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5316: dang po a la sems sbyong ba /
NK076(mu)002:5317: snying gar rig pa nyid adkar po ste /
NK076(mu)002:5318: gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan par bsgom ste /
NK076(mu)002:5319: de yang raba tu brtan par gyur pa'i tshad mi 'gyur ba bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:5322: mngon par mi 'gyur cir yang bsgyur du btub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5323: de ltar rang rig a gsal ba skyon kun bral
NK076(mu)002:5324: bas dkar ba ste gsal tshad bzhi dang ldan pa
NK076(mu)002:5329: de yang a s+pha ra na phata /
NK076(mu)002:5331: gzhi'i a de las shin tu phra ba'i a dpag
NK076(mu)002:5332: tu med pa rnams spro bas phyogs bcu thams cad
NK076(mu)002:5333: as gang bar gsal bar gyur nas sam ha ra
NK076(mu)002:5335: bsdus kyang gzhi'i a de 'phel ba dang phyogs bcu'i
NK076(mu)002:5336: a de 'grib pa med par ting 'dzin brtan pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5337: tshad gsal ba yul rkyen gyis mi 'phrog pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5338: gnyis pa h'u la sems sbyangs ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:5339: blo chen a de la sems sbyangs nas lha bskyed pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:5340: yang blo chung na a sbyangs nas thugsa ye shes
NK076(mu)002:5341: lnga mtshon pa'i ya ge h'u mthing nag gsal brtan
NK076(mu)002:5342: tshad brgyad dang ldan pa bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:5343: a la sbyangs pa de bzhin h'u la spro bsdu yang dang yang du goms 'dris byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:5344: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin snang srid phya nang snod
NK076(mu)002:5345: bacud thams cad h'u ye shes lnga ldan du gsal
NK076(mu)002:5346: bar bsdu / rang gi lus kyi yan lag lnga
NK076(mu)002:5347: dang sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad rang rig
NK076(mu)002:5348: pa'i ya shes lnga ye nas yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:5349: rtags rang snang gi yi ge h'u du gsal bar shin tu yang bsdu'o //
NK076(mu)002:5350: h'u gsal ba'i tshad ni n+ri ste mi'i snying po
NK076(mu)002:5351: de yi miga ga dbang pos mngon sum mthong ba
NK076(mu)002:5353: h'u de la 'dris shing goms nas gsal bas badga
NK076(mu)002:5354: dang gzhan gyi dona bya ba'i phyir h'u grangs med
NK076(mu)002:5355: par spro bas 'phags pa mchod cing sems can gyi
NK076(mu)002:5356: don bya ba rdzogsa nas slar gzhi po'i h'u du
NK076(mu)002:5357: bsdus te / h'u nyid kyang 'od zhu sems nyid
NK076(mu)002:5358: mi dmigs pa chos kyi dbyings su gsal bar bsgom
NK076(mu)002:5359: bsdus te / mo // de ltar 'dris shing gomsa par bya ba ste shin tu gces so //
NK076(mu)002:5360: gnyis pa lhar bskyed pa la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:5364: thun mtshams kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK076(mu)002:5367: mdor bstan phyi ma ltar bskyed pa la /
NK076(mu)002:5368: tshangs pa yi phrug gu'i cha lugs can gyi zhi ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5369: srin pa'i phrug gu'i tshul can khro bo ste /
NK076(mu)002:5370: de ltar zhi khro'i lha'i ting 'dzin rdzogsa par bya
NK076(mu)002:5371: bas zhi khro zung gcig tu ston par 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)002:5372: // gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:5376: dang po spyir gang mos su bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:5377: dang po tshangs pa'i phru gu'i cha lugs can zhi
NK076(mu)002:5378: ba'i lha yongs su rdzogs pa bsgom par bya ba'ang
NK076(mu)002:5379: / rigs lnga ganga sgrub kyang sa bon yi ge
NK076(mu)002:5380: h'u mo s+aa am h+aa lnga po sa so las
NK076(mu)002:5381: / bskyed de / 'on bzang ngan yod dam snyam na /
NK076(mu)002:5382: de yang spyir ni rigs lnga ganga bsgoms kyang /
NK076(mu)002:5383: rgyal ba gcig la bzang ngan tha dad med pas kun tu 'dra zhing mnyam la /
NK076(mu)002:5384: 'dir thugs sgrub sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skabs yin pas
NK076(mu)002:5385: rdo rje sems dpa' bsgom pa nyid du thams cad
NK076(mu)002:5386: 'adu ba ste rigs thams cad kyi gtso bo yin
NK076(mu)002:5387: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa bsgom thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5389: blo che cig char du bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5391: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:5394: dang po a la sems sbyangs shing gdan bsgom pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:5395: de nyid sgom thabs 'og nas ston pa 'di ltar
NK076(mu)002:5396: lha'i ting 'dzin de nyid la gomas par bya ba
NK076(mu)002:5397: / gzhal yas khang bskyed cing lha bsgom pa'i sngon
NK076(mu)002:5398: du de ting cir yang ma dmigs pa skye med
NK076(mu)002:5399: / dang / kun snang snying rje bsgom pa'i ngang nyid lasa /
NK076(mu)002:5400: rang rig a dakara po gsung yig 'bru dag gi phyag rgya 'od 'bar ba /
NK076(mu)002:5401: kha dog shin tu gsal zhing 'od zer 'tsher bar
NK076(mu)002:5402: ting 'dzin gsal bar bsgomsa la snod bcud thams cad
NK076(mu)002:5404: rtags ye shes a dza ni gyur par bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:5405: don da ji bzhin pa gnyis med nyid du blo goms shing 'dris par gyur nasa /
NK076(mu)002:5406: mar me gcig las gnyis chad lta bu'i /
NK076(mu)002:5407: rgyu'i ye ge a dkar po de las a s+pha
NK076(mu)002:5408: ra na phatah ces ma dmar po yi dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:5409: grangs med spro ba yis phyogs bcu thams cad a
NK076(mu)002:5410: dang ma gnyis kyis gang ba gsal bar ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:5412: sam ha ra na h'u gis bsdus te 'od du
NK076(mu)002:5413: zhu ba las nya zla nya gang ba sbrel mar
NK076(mu)002:5416: a zla ba'i dkyil 'khor brtsigs mar bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:5417: de'i 'og tu h+r+aidmar po gsal ba 'od zhus pad+ma
NK076(mu)002:5418: 'dam skyon gyis ma gos pas chags pa med pa
NK076(mu)002:5419: kha dog sna tshogs shig bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:5420: gnyis pa gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:5421: don ye shes lnga rtags b+h+r+aum las rin chena 'od
NK076(mu)002:5422: sna lnga 'abra ba'i gdan gyi 'od las zhi ba'i
NK076(mu)002:5423: gzhal yas khang sbra gur lta bur bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:5424: nya zla pad+ma rin po che'i gdan dang rin po che'i gazhala yas khang bsgom la /
NK076(mu)002:5425: zar tshags la sogs rgyan thams cad bsdus shing tshang
NK076(mu)002:5426: bas ngo bo tsha phra bar gsal bar bsgom mo
NK076(mu)002:5427: // gnyis pa brten pa lha bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:5428: rtsa ba'i lha cho ga yan lag gsum gyis bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:5429: yan lag gi lha dgu bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5431: dang po gsung yig 'bru ni gzhal yas khang gi
NK076(mu)002:5432: nang gdan de yi dkyil du gsung gi yi ga
NK076(mu)002:5434: de nyid kha dog mthinga ga 'od 'tsher la gasla
NK076(mu)002:5435: ba yi h'u de las 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro
NK076(mu)002:5437: de las 'od zer 'phra ba yis 'phags pa mchod sems can gyi don byas /
NK076(mu)002:5438: sa ha ra na h'u gis dbyings su slar bsdus nas 'od du zhu ba las /
NK076(mu)002:5440: badz+ra zhes pas shin tu rdo rje rtse lnga pa sngon po phra bar nas tsam bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:5441: rda rje las 'od zer 'phra mchod don byas te
NK076(mu)002:5442: kha dog gsal zhing 'od zer 'bar bar gyur nas
NK076(mu)002:5443: mchod don slar dbyingsa su yang ni rdo rje la
NK076(mu)002:5444: bstim para bya'o // gsum pa sku phyag rgya la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:5446: badz+ra sa t+wa zhes pas rdo rje de nyid 'od
NK076(mu)002:5447: du zhu ba las rdo rje semas dpa'i skur gyur
NK076(mu)002:5448: nasa / sku de yang shin tu cha phra zhing rgyan cha lugs tshanga zhing 'adus para bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:5449: gnyis pa yongs rdzogs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5450: dang po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK076(mu)002:5451: gong gi de bzhin sku phra mo de 'phro 'dus pas gnyis su med par gsal bar gyur nas /
NK076(mu)002:5452: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika /ces bas sku rags pa rang lus
NK076(mu)002:5453: tsam zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril
NK076(mu)002:5454: bu 'od 'bar ba bsnams pa tshul dgu dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:5455: par bsgom / gnyis pa zhal gsum phyag drug bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:5456: rdor sems bskyed pa de bzhin nyid du goms shing brtan par gyur pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5457: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5458: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags phyag drug pa nyid du bsgom ste /
NK076(mu)002:5459: de yang g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje /
NK076(mu)002:5461: g.yon tha ma ral gra 'od 'bar ba /
NK076(mu)002:5464: g.yon dang po dril bu 'od 'abra ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5465: gnyis pa yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu bsgoms lha de'i thugs kar /
NK076(mu)002:5466: shin tu cha phra ba'i 'od kyi gzhal yas khang pad+ma nyi zla'i gadna dang ldan pa der /
NK076(mu)002:5467: tsit+ta'i gnas su snying po'i lha gcig ye shes sems dpa' bsgom /
