NK076(mu)002:5468: rtsa lha'i spyi bo mgrin pa tsit+ta'i gnas gsum du
NK076(mu)002:5469: nyi zla pad+ma gsum gyi steng du +aah'u gsum las
NK076(mu)002:5470: byin rlabsa lha'i sku gsung thugs su rda rje gsum
NK076(mu)002:5471: bsgom par bya'o // rtsa ba'i lha'i dbu yi gansa spyi bo /
NK076(mu)002:5475: rna ltag g.yon dang lngar rin po che'i khang bu
NK076(mu)002:5476: lnga'i nang du h'u s+w+aa am h+aa ste yi ge
NK076(mu)002:5477: 'bru lnga bsam la shunya ta la sogs kyi sngags
NK076(mu)002:5478: brjod pas don ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i chu rgyun
NK076(mu)002:5479: gyis dbang rdzogs par bskur bas rtags rigs lngas dbu
NK076(mu)002:5481: gnyis pa cig char bsgom pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5482: dang po cig char du bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:5483: rnal 'byor ba blo ya shes rab che bas cig char dang /
NK076(mu)002:5484: chung bas rim gyis bsgom pa'i khyad par yod pa'i blos phye bas /
NK076(mu)002:5485: yang blo che na thog mar sku phyag rgya chen pa rags pa cig char du bsgom ste /
NK076(mu)002:5486: dper na chu las nya ldang ba ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:5487: snying po brjod pa tsam gyis rnal 'byor pa badga
NK076(mu)002:5488: nyid lha sku phyag rgya chen pa cig char du
NK076(mu)002:5489: bsgom sta / de yang rnam thar gsum mtshon zhal gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5490: ye shes drug ldan pa'i phyag drug pa dus rtag tu bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:5491: gnyis pa gzhal yas khang dang lhag pa'i lha snga ma dang mthun par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5492: gnas dgu 'od kyi gzhal yas khang dang pad+ma nyi
NK076(mu)002:5493: zla'i gdan bsgom pa la sogs snga ma rim gyis
NK076(mu)002:5494: pa bzhin bsgom / de'i gdan steng du yan lag
NK076(mu)002:5495: lhag pa'i lha dgu bsgom pa yang rim gyis pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5496: skabs de bzhin bsgom pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:5497: ting 'dzin de la shin tu 'dris shing gomas par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5498: gnyis pa khro bo bsgom pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5499: dang po sgom thabs rim dang cig char zhi ba dang mthun par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5500: dkyus kyi phyi ma rak+sha zhes srin po'i cha lugsa 'dzin pa khro bo rgya gcig bsgom pa'ang /
NK076(mu)002:5501: cho ga gsum gyis bskyed pa rim gyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5502: chu las nya ldang ltar cig chara gnyis las sngon zhi ba bzhin ta /
NK076(mu)002:5503: gnyis pa khyad par zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur te bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:5504: sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum gyi go cha ste
NK076(mu)002:5505: cha ga gsum dang kha dog mthing ga 'tsher ba
NK076(mu)002:5506: dang / tha dad pa'i gzhal yas khang la sogs pa yang zhi ba las bsgyur ta /
NK076(mu)002:5507: dur khrod kyi bkod pa sogs khro bo'i gzhung ltar bsgom par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5508: thugs kyi rigs badz+ra he ru ka las gzhan rigs bzhi gang rung la mos pa'ang /
NK076(mu)002:5509: rigs bzhi'i yig 'bru rnams kha dog smug ser dmar
NK076(mu)002:5510: ljang bzhi la sems sbyang te lha bskyed pa ni
NK076(mu)002:5511: / gdan dang bzhugs gnas dang rgyan sogs badz+ra he ru ka dang gcig go //
NK076(mu)002:5512: sku gsung thugs rda rje cho ga rnam pa gsum
NK076(mu)002:5513: yang rigs pa bzhi gang yin gyi rigs su bsgyur
NK076(mu)002:5514: cing / de la sku phyag rgya rags pa dang
NK076(mu)002:5515: yan lag lha dgu zhi ba ltar khro bor gnas
NK076(mu)002:5516: bsgyur ba gong gi de bzhin no //
NK076(mu)002:5517: gnyis pa phrin las kyi rim pa /
NK076(mu)002:5518: zhi khro gnyis ka blo chung ba la rim gyis bsgom pa la brtan pa thob pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:5519: blo che bas ciga char bsgom pa'i phrin las rim pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:5520: yan lag brgyad pa'i mthar mtshams bcad /
NK076(mu)002:5524: h'u zhes 'od dang gzi byin rang la thim pa las yi dam gyi lhar bskyed la /
NK076(mu)002:5525: phyi nang gi mchod pa rnams gzhung bzhin du byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK076(mu)002:5526: stong snying gnyis sngon du song nas /
NK076(mu)002:5527: rang lha'i skur rim dang cig char du bsgoms te /
NK076(mu)002:5528: yan lag lha dgu ldan par bskyed pa yan chad rdzogas nas snyan gsan dab ba /
NK076(mu)002:5532: phyi nang gsang bas mchod cing bstod pa bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5533: gsum pa bzlas pa bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:5534: gang bsgom lha'i sngags kyi yan lag ma nyams par sngags bzlas pa'ang bzlas pa'i skyon bcu spangsa te /
NK076(mu)002:5537: bar 'phro 'du ste rnam pa gsum gyis bzlas pa
NK076(mu)002:5538: yi grangs ji bzhin dam bcas pa bzhin rdzogs par
NK076(mu)002:5539: bya ba'o // 'od zer spro 1 ba dang bsdu
NK076(mu)002:5540: 3 bas bdag 4 dang gzhan 2don rdzogsa bar dmigs
NK076(mu)002:5541: bya ba'o // / phyi bsnyen pa'i dus bdag dang ye shes pa /
NK076(mu)002:5542: tha dad gsal ba'i ngang bzlas pa /
NK076(mu)002:5543: nang sgrub pa'i dus tha dad med par gsal te bzlas pa /
NK076(mu)002:5544: gsang ba sgrub pa chen po'i dus do la'i bzlas pa rnams gang mos su sbyang /
NK076(mu)002:5546: dang po grangs spyir bye ba sa ya gsungs kyang 'bru 'bum /
NK076(mu)002:5547: gnyis pa dus ci tsam dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:5548: gsum pa rtags kyi mtshan ma ma byung bar snying
NK076(mu)002:5549: po bzlas pa tshad du phyin para skyol bar bya'o
NK076(mu)002:5550: // bzhi pa thun mtshams kyi ting 'dzin /
NK076(mu)002:5551: bsgom bzlas kyis khams duba bar gyur na thabs lam
NK076(mu)002:5552: gyi dbang du lte ba la sogs pa 'khor lo
NK076(mu)002:5553: bzhi'i thig le la bltas pas bde ba 'bar ram
NK076(mu)002:5554: snying gar dbu ma'i nang dwangs ma lnga 'dus thig
NK076(mu)002:5555: le'am / ye shes snying po'i 'od kyi thig le
NK076(mu)002:5556: dkar po sran ma tsam dkar po la blta zhing
NK076(mu)002:5557: nub mo de'i ngang la nyal basa khams dub pa
NK076(mu)002:5558: le'am / sang ngo // nang bar kyang de nyid
NK076(mu)002:5559: ngang las langs nas gsung yig 'bru h'u sogs zhi
NK076(mu)002:5560: khro gang yin gyi cho ga gsum gyis bsgyur te
NK076(mu)002:5561: sku rgya gcig rdzogas par bsgoms pas /
NK076(mu)002:5562: sngon bzhin mchod bstod bzlas pa sogs brtson pas lha'i rnal 'byor la 'dris shing goms par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5563: bzhi pa ngo bo la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5564: dang po sgom byed ting 'dzin gyi ngo bo dmigs med rang snang du bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5565: rten zhi khro'i gzhal yas khang dang /
NK076(mu)002:5566: brten pa zhi khro lha ya dkyil 'khor du snang ba yang /
NK076(mu)002:5567: rang rig sems kyi cho 'phrul nyid dkyil 'khor der rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:5568: bsgom bya'i lha yang blo'i yul du dmigs nas sgom
NK076(mu)002:5569: du med de rang gi rig pa de nyid lha'i
NK076(mu)002:5570: sku gsung thugs phrin las kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi
NK076(mu)002:5571: rdzogas pa'i lha'i sku bsgom pa dee nyid rig pa
NK076(mu)002:5572: rang snang ba'o // gnyis pa bsgom bya don gyi
NK076(mu)002:5573: ngo bo yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i dpe don
NK076(mu)002:5574: rang snang ba'o // / thun mong gi rgyal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:5575: yang rgyal ba sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje sems
NK076(mu)002:5576: dpa' la sogs pa rnams kyi sku ru gsal ba
NK076(mu)002:5577: gnas skabs kun tu nor bu rin chen lta bu
NK076(mu)002:5578: rang snang ba'o // / yin te / sku lnga'i
NK076(mu)002:5579: yon tan lhun grub tu rdzogsa pas phan gdags mi
NK076(mu)002:5580: gdags kyi rnam par rtog pa'i rtsol ba med par
NK076(mu)002:5581: gdul bya 'khor lnga'i re ba yid bzhin gyis skong
NK076(mu)002:5582: ba'i dus su yon tan mi zad pa dang ma
NK076(mu)002:5584: gdul bya'i don la phar 'gro ba dang tshur 'ong
NK076(mu)002:5585: ba dang thugs rje la nye ring gi 'du shes
NK076(mu)002:5586: gang yang med par 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa bzhin
NK076(mu)002:5587: rjes 'jug gis kyang de bzhin du shes nas bsgom
NK076(mu)002:5588: mo // gsum pa sgom pa'i nges tshig /lha'i sku
NK076(mu)002:5589: phyag rgya chen po de bsgom pa'i tshe yoda pas
NK076(mu)002:5591: ma bsgoms pa tsam na meda pas skyon grol te /
NK076(mu)002:5592: grol dang ma grol ba'i 'dzin pa med pa de
NK076(mu)002:5593: thams cad rig pa bdag nyid chen po yin phyir
NK076(mu)002:5594: dgongs pa la phyogs ris med cing spyod pa lha
NK076(mu)002:5595: la blang bya dang rtog pa la dara bya med
NK076(mu)002:5596: de / lhar bsgom pa la bying ba dang rgod
NK076(mu)002:5597: pa shas che ba'i skyon med par de snyoms pa
NK076(mu)002:5598: tsam la ting 'dzin mnyam pa la bazhaga pa'am bsgom
NK076(mu)002:5599: zhes bya ba'i sgra don nam nges tshig tu brjod
NK076(mu)002:5600: de / pa'a // lnga pa mi mthun pa'i skyon la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5601: dang po thun mong gi skyon phra bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5602: ting 'dzin ngo bo dang mi mthun pa'i skyon bye brag rnams /
NK076(mu)002:5603: rgya gcig rnal 'byor la gnas pa 'di yi tshe skyon rnams dmigs ngos bzung ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:5604: dang po yi ga la sems sbyang ba nas bzung
NK076(mu)002:5605: ste sku yongs su rdzogsa pa bsgom pa'i bar dmigs
NK076(mu)002:5606: pa brjed pa dang bying rgod la sogs pa thun
NK076(mu)002:5607: mong gi skyon kun tu 'byung ba 'dir rags pa
NK076(mu)002:5608: mi 'byung ste phra ba tsam 'byung la /
NK076(mu)002:5609: tha ma skyon phra ba rgya gcig pa 'di bsgom
NK076(mu)002:5610: pa'i skabs las 'byung ba de shes bzhin bya ra
NK076(mu)002:5611: ba'i so mtha' bcud pa gces so //
NK076(mu)002:5612: gnyis pa khyad par gyi skyon bcu gcig bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:5613: phyag rgya gcig pa 'di nyid kyi khyad par gyi skyon la gnyis las /
NK076(mu)002:5614: dang po yi ge la sems sbyang ba'i skyon gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5615: smig rgyu ltar blo yul du a h'u rab rib tsam las mi srung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5616: yi ge snang yang du ba'i gsob kyi rdzas ltar mi gsal ba mag mog tu 'dug pa /
NK076(mu)002:5617: yi ge gsal ba 'grings nas 'gro ba grib ma lta bu'i nag nog gis chod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5618: gnyis pa lha bsgom pa'i dus su 'gyur ba'i skyon brgyad ni /
NK076(mu)002:5619: lha rang gi lus gang gi tshad du dmigas gnas
NK076(mu)002:5620: bsgom pa la che chung gi tshad 'gyur 1ba dang
NK076(mu)002:5623: bzhengs bzhugs kyi tshul 'gyur 2 ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5625: zhi khro'i cha lugsa rin po che'i rgyan dang /
NK076(mu)002:5627: sku mdog dkar po la sogs 'gyur 5 ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5630: kha dog ste sku mdog 'ba' zhiga las mi snang ste sku'i dbyibs med pa 7 dang /
NK076(mu)002:5631: dbu'i gtsug tor nas rima par nub cing mi gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5632: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5633: dang po skyon bcos thabs spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:5634: de ltar skyon dbang du gyur pa shes bzhin bya ra bas tshora bar byas ta /
NK076(mu)002:5635: mtshan ma'i 'adu byed kyi rnam rtog gi rlung gisa
NK076(mu)002:5636: skyon byung bsams nas ting 'dzin bskyod par ma bya'o
NK076(mu)002:5637: // gnyis pa bye brag tu khyad par gyi skyon bcos thabs /
NK076(mu)002:5638: gong bstan de ltar skyon ngos zina pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK076(mu)002:5639: skyon de daga kun gyi bcos thabs ni 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:5640: 'dir khyad par gyi skyon la'ang rab rib mag mog
NK076(mu)002:5641: grib ma gsum la'ang snying rje 'gyu ba sgyu ma
NK076(mu)002:5642: dang stong pa la ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang la
NK076(mu)002:5644: de goms pa'i rjesa las phra ba'i yi ge bsgom
NK076(mu)002:5645: pa thob pa yin te yun mi ring bar thun
NK076(mu)002:5646: tshod ma sun tsam du 'dug cing bsgom par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:5647: // skyon brgyad kyi snga ma drug la sku ri bo ltar che zhing gdos bcas /
NK076(mu)002:5650: rang rgyud du bsgom par bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:5651: bdun pa la kha dog gsal kyang dbyibs med pa la /
NK076(mu)002:5652: kha dog la brten nas sku'i dbyibs dang gnyis bsra ste bsgom para bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5653: brgyad pa rim par nub pa'i skyon la spyi yi
NK076(mu)002:5654: rnam pa gsal ba min kyang bya braga zhal phyag
NK076(mu)002:5655: phyag sor sogs gang gsal la blo gnas par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:5656: // gsum pa spyod lam gyi skyon bcos thabs ni /
NK076(mu)002:5657: sgo gsum gyi bya bar 'os pa min pa ting 'dzin dang mi mthun pa'i las /
NK076(mu)002:5658: yi ge bri mchod sogs kun dora bar byas ta /
NK076(mu)002:5659: 'gro nyal 'dug sdod spyod lam bzhi rnal du ma
NK076(mu)002:5660: 'byor ba'i skyon rnams dor zhing gtang bar bya ba'o
NK076(mu)002:5662: dang po nyams snga ma bzhin 'phel ba /
NK076(mu)002:5663: sngon de ting kun ting gnyis la nyams lnga zhugs
NK076(mu)002:5664: nas brtan mod kyang phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:5665: la / gomas pas nyams rim lnga gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i tshul bstan ba'ang lam snga ma /
NK076(mu)002:5666: de kun gnyis su bstan pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5667: gnyis pa nyams lnga mtshan ma dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK076(mu)002:5668: g.yo nyams dus su smig rgyu de chu min kyang yod snang ltar /
NK076(mu)002:5669: yi ge dang lha mi snang yang yid yul du yod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5670: thob pa'i dus me stag chung ngu yis lci ba
NK076(mu)002:5671: skam po la mched de du bsngo lang gis byu
NK076(mu)002:5672: nga ba de ma thag med pa bzhin yi ge
NK076(mu)002:5673: dang lha gsal ma thag med pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5674: goms pa'i dus srin bu ma khyer mtshan mo 'od
NK076(mu)002:5675: yod pa shing sogs 'phags su mi snang bzhin snga
NK076(mu)002:5676: ma bas lha gsal ba rgyun ring nas yang mi
NK076(mu)002:5677: gsal lo / brtan pa'i dus mar me rlung gis ma bskyod ltar /
NK076(mu)002:5678: thun bar du lha gsal la rtog pa med pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5679: mthar phyin dus nam mkha' dwangs pa la nyi ma shar ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:5680: dus thun nam nyin mtshan phyed par rig pa lhar gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5681: de ltar nyams lnga mtshan ma'i tshul de dag dang sbyar te shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5682: gsum pa rtsol ba che chung rang gi nyams dang sbyar ba /
NK076(mu)002:5683: rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang snyoms /
NK076(mu)002:5684: rtsol ba med pa'i nyams pa mchan /
NK076(mu)002:5685: dus phyang ba'i btang snyoms dang gsum gyi rim pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5686: sems spro bas sgo gsum gyis rtsol ba byed pa
NK076(mu)002:5687: ste mdor na de dag skabsa kyis blang dor nyams
NK076(mu)002:5689: brgyad pa spyod pa la gsum /bdag don gyi spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:5690: gzhan don ting 'dzin brtan pa'i yon tan no //
NK076(mu)002:5692: dang po spyod lam bzhi la zhi khro gang yin gyi skabs dang sbyar ba /
NK076(mu)002:5693: rang gi spyi mgrin snying lte bzhir yig 'bru h'u
NK076(mu)002:5694: bzhis khro bo bzhir bskyed la dus rtag tu matshamas
NK076(mu)002:5696: chos kun rang byung ye shes la rig pa bdag
NK076(mu)002:5697: nyid chen po'i longs spyod tshogs kyi machada pa bya
NK076(mu)002:5698: ba ni / nang gi sbyin sreg kyang za tshogs gtong lung ltar dang du blang bar bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:5699: gzugs sgra dri ro reg chos sogs yul drug spros
NK076(mu)002:5700: pa med pa'i thiga la'am 'dod yon lha ma drug
NK076(mu)002:5701: tu gsal bas lha la lha thim par rol zhing
NK076(mu)002:5702: / dbang po rnam shes sems dpa' brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:5703: yul dang dus phyi nang gi sems ma ste yab yum du sbyor bar shes par bya /
NK076(mu)002:5704: de yang yi dam gyi lha zha khra rgya gcig
NK076(mu)002:5705: pa gang yina pa'i skabs kyis sems dpa' sems ma
NK076(mu)002:5706: / koo ri dang sid+ha la sogs par bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5707: gnyis pa bdag nyid chen po'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:5708: gong bstan bzhin chos thams cad rig pa bdag nyid
NK076(mu)002:5709: chen po'i ngang du sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis
NK076(mu)002:5710: su med par shes pas rang la mchod pa 'bul
NK076(mu)002:5711: ba yis / sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus
NK076(mu)002:5712: pa rang rig ye shes dang tha dad med pas
NK076(mu)002:5713: ba yis / mnyes shing / rto ga tshogs rang
NK076(mu)002:5714: rig gsal bas srid pa khams gsum gyi sems cana
NK076(mu)002:5715: rigs drug dang de dag bskyed pa'i sa bon a
NK076(mu)002:5716: n+ri su tri pre duthams cad la byang chub sems
NK076(mu)002:5717: kyi bde ba'i ro dga' ba chen pos khyab nas
NK076(mu)002:5719: gsum pa dus dang gnas skabs thams cad du bsgom pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:5720: rnal 'byor ba phan tshun du 'gro ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5723: zas la longs spyod pa'i tshe dang /
NK076(mu)002:5724: nyon mongs chags sdang la sogs dang lus kyi na tsha /
NK076(mu)002:5725: sems kyi sdug bsngal 'byung ba'i tsha na yang /
NK076(mu)002:5726: gsang ba'i theg pa chen po gsang sngags yi dam
NK076(mu)002:5727: gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya bsgom pa'i ting 'dzin mi
NK076(mu)002:5729: dus kun lha'i nga rgyal dang ma bral ba sngon
NK076(mu)002:5730: bzhin dbang po yul dus thams cad lha yab yum
NK076(mu)002:5731: du sbyor bas myur du 'bras bu lha'i dngos grub
NK076(mu)002:5733: bzhi pa bya ba spang bas phyogs gcig pa'i spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:5734: rgyu de ting dang 'bras bu rgya gcig pa de
NK076(mu)002:5735: gnyis matshamas sbyor bas kun snang dang gsum gyi bar
NK076(mu)002:5736: skabs kun tu bsgom pa kho na min pa chos
NK076(mu)002:5737: spyod dgu yi spros pa dor te /
NK076(mu)002:5738: gtan du dor ba min pas rgyud la ldan yang
NK076(mu)002:5739: sgom pa'i skabs dang du blang bar bya ba min
NK076(mu)002:5741: g.yeng ba drug las mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:5742: lnga pa spyod pa dag cing brtson pa dang ldan pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:5743: lus ngag yid lha'i sku gsung thugs rdoo rje gsum
NK076(mu)002:5744: du bsgom pas rang las dman la phyag dang skor
NK076(mu)002:5745: ba mi bya / zhi khro'i phyag rgya'i lha yi
NK076(mu)002:5746: rnal 'byor ting 'dzin spyod cing nyams su len pa
NK076(mu)002:5747: ba mi bya / la / lta ba'i don dang
NK076(mu)002:5748: ldan cing sngags dang phyag rgya ma nyams par spyod
NK076(mu)002:5750: bsgom bzlas la brtson 'grus shin tu cher bskyed de
NK076(mu)002:5751: bsgrub na dus myur bar yi dam lha 'grub par
NK076(mu)002:5752: 'gyur ro // drug pa tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:5753: spyod lam thams cad lha yin pa la lha gsal
NK076(mu)002:5754: ba'i rol ba ma 'gags par bsod namas kyi tshogs
NK076(mu)002:5755: te / de la spyod bzhin la rang bzhin med
NK076(mu)002:5756: par shes pas ma chags pas ye shes tshogs dang
NK076(mu)002:5757: gnyis su meda par rdzogs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5758: gnyis pa gzhan don gyi spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:5759: gdul bya gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir bzlas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5760: 'od zer gyi 'phra 'du'i rim pasa bdag gzhan gyi
NK076(mu)002:5762: phyag rgya spros bcas kyis don bya ba'i yul gyi rkyen dang 'phrad pasa de'ang mi 'dor te /
NK076(mu)002:5763: rgya gcig skabs spros pa bsgom pa'i dus min yang
NK076(mu)002:5764: gdul bya gzhan gyi don du dbang bskur ba la
NK076(mu)002:5765: sogs pa bya ba'i phyir phyag rgya spros pa'i ting
NK076(mu)002:5766: 'dzin de'ang 'di nyams su len par byed cing bsgom
NK076(mu)002:5767: par ston / de'i phyir gdul bya gang dang 'dul
NK076(mu)002:5768: thabs 'tshams par bstan pas gzhan gyi don rdzogs par
NK076(mu)002:5769: par ston / byed do // gsum pa ting 'dzin brtan pa'i yon tan ni /
NK076(mu)002:5770: de yang rnal 'byor pa badga nyid kyi don sgrub pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:5771: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa rnamas /
NK076(mu)002:5772: rgya gcig pa 'di la brtan pa thob na dangsa
NK076(mu)002:5773: grub la sbyor basa gang yang the tshom med par
NK076(mu)002:5775: dgu pa dam tshig rgya gcig 'di la gnas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5776: tsha lam gyi gzhii 'dzin pas gzhi dang 'dra ba'i
NK076(mu)002:5777: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig kun dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:5778: mod kyang / khyad par du gsung gi dam tshig
NK076(mu)002:5779: gi gzhi la sngags phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa
NK076(mu)002:5781: yi dam lha'i sku'i phyag rgya chen po'i rnal 'byor du gsal ba'i ngang las spyod yul kun tu /
NK076(mu)002:5782: yang lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las mi 'da' bar bsdam par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5786: gsang ba sems kyi drod gsum po yang /
NK076(mu)002:5788: lam snga ma gnyis su drod g.yo ba dang thob pa'i tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:5789: 'dir snga ma pas goms pa dang brtan pa'i char 'phel bar 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)002:5791: phyi'i drod 'dod pa'i longs spyod la zhen pa med pa sngar bas chung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5792: dbang po yul dus snang ba kun lha'i ting 'dzin la goms pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5793: nang gi drod dbugs phyi nang du rgyu ba chad
NK076(mu)002:5794: pa dang gsang ba'i drod ting 'dzin gyi thun mtshams
NK076(mu)002:5795: dang bral te / gong du bstan pa'i phyi nang
NK076(mu)002:5796: gsang ba'i drod kyi bye brag ma lus pa kun
NK076(mu)002:5797: dang gsal brtan du ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:5798: bcu gcig pa rtags la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:5800: rgya gcig rtags chen po ni ting 'dzin goms shing /
NK076(mu)002:5801: mthar phyin pa'i tshe smig rgyu /
NK076(mu)002:5805: nyi ma lta bu'i matshana ma lnga po de dngos su mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5807: du ba lta bu'i lang long dang /
NK076(mu)002:5808: smig rgyu lta bu gya gyu /
NK076(mu)002:5809: srin me lta bu dmar 'phro dang /
NK076(mu)002:5810: mar me lta bu dmar skam gsal /
NK076(mu)002:5811: mkha' la nyi shar lta bur snang /
NK076(mu)002:5813: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum gyi gsung yig 'bru /
NK076(mu)002:5815: sku yongs rdzogs kyi skya mched dngos su mthong ba rnams /
NK076(mu)002:5816: lha grub pa'am rtags sam mtshan ma yin ta /
NK076(mu)002:5817: 'bras bu grub pa yi rtags kyi thog ma yin pas dang po'i rtags zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5819: de ting kun ting gnyis pas dmigs pa rgya che ba'i rgya gcig pa'i mngon shes kyang /
NK076(mu)002:5820: ting 'dzin snga ma gnyis las 'dir grangs nyer lnga sogs mang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5821: yul rgya che ba dang gnyis kyis bla na med /
NK076(mu)002:5822: gzhan yang sgo lnga'i dbang shes nyi shu rtsa lnga'i mngon shes kyang /
NK076(mu)002:5823: rgya gcig skabs 'dir g.yo thob tsam du 'byung bar the tshom med do //
NK076(mu)002:5825: lus kyi rtags rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul /
NK076(mu)002:5826: ngag gi rtags kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul /
NK076(mu)002:5827: sems kyi rtags rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul /
NK076(mu)002:5828: sems gyi mthu'i rtags byin rlabs rnams kyang /
NK076(mu)002:5829: cha 'phrul bzhi yi tshul de rnams kyang g.yo thoba tsam du 'byung bar byed do //
NK076(mu)002:5830: bzhi pa brtags sngar bas gsal zhing brtan par 'byung tshul /
NK076(mu)002:5831: drod rtags de dag las gzhan yang phyi nang gi rtags dang /
NK076(mu)002:5833: bdun kyi spyod yul la sogs pa kun sngon du
NK076(mu)002:5834: song ba de ting snying rje gnyis pas rgya gcig
NK076(mu)002:5835: pa'i skabs 'dir ngo bo gsal zhing brtan pa thob
NK076(mu)002:5836: pa 'byung ste / ting 'dzin gong ma gnyis kha
NK076(mu)002:5837: phral te bsgom pa yin la 'dir rgya gcig pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5838: rnal 'byor bden pa dbyer med bsgom pa de ni
NK076(mu)002:5839: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin goms pa'i stobs kyis thob pa
NK076(mu)002:5840: pa 'byung ste / yin no // bcu gnyis pa mtshan ma rmi lam la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:5841: dang po legs nyes gsal brtan du 'byung ba /
NK076(mu)002:5842: spyod lam bzhi las nyal ba gnyid kyi rmi lam
NK076(mu)002:5843: du lam sgrub pa legas pa'i yon tan dang nyes
NK076(mu)002:5844: pa'i skyon 'byung ba'i bye brag kun /
NK076(mu)002:5845: lam snga ma gnyis pas 'dir gsal bar 'byung zhing sngar bas kyang shin tu brtan pa 'byung ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5846: gnyis pa grub pa'i rtags kyi rmi ltas bcu bzhi 'byung ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:5847: zhi khro gang yin gyi lha'i bsam gtan ting 'dzin sngags la 'bad pas bzlas pa byas pa yis /
NK076(mu)002:5848: sgrub pa pos ni grub pa'i rmi ltas bcu bzhi po 'di dag ni rtags su mthong ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:5850: dang po ni bdag nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi mthu dang mtshungs shing mnyam par mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5851: gnyis pa ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas longas spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dpes brgyan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5852: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid dang tha dad med par na dus myur du thob par mthong ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5854: byang chub sems dpa' chen pa rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:5855: brgya byin la sogs khams gsum na gnas pasa //
NK076(mu)002:5856: rnal 'byor bdag la mchod pa byed par rnal 'byor pa des rang gi rmi lam na mthong ngo //
NK076(mu)002:5858: gnyis med kyi ye shes chen po 'od dang 'dra'
NK076(mu)002:5859: gzugs skur snang ba'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub semas
NK076(mu)002:5860: dpa' yis gzugs la sogs pa 'doda pa'i yon tan
NK076(mu)002:5861: lnga po rnams kyis dus rtag tu bdag la mchod
NK076(mu)002:5864: rdo rdo sems dpa'i gzugs chen po dang /
NK076(mu)002:5865: gragsa chena phyag na rda rje'i gzugs mchog dag tu /
NK076(mu)002:5866: gnyid log pa'i rmi lam dag na rnal 'byor pa rang gi gzugs lha de dag tu mthong ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:5868: grags chen phyag na rdo rje gsang ba'i dbang po dang /
NK076(mu)002:5869: byang chub sems dpa' 'khor lo bsnam pa cana sgrib
NK076(mu)002:5870: bsal dang sangs rgyas chen po rnam par snang mdzad
NK076(mu)002:5871: la sogs kyis bdag la phyag 'tshal ba'i /
NK076(mu)002:5872: rmi lam 'di dag sgrub pa pos mthong bar gyur pa de lus lha'i sku /
NK076(mu)002:5874: sems thugs kyi ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i mthu las skyes pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:5876: rin po che dang dar gyi rgyan bcu gsum pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5877: rgyan rnams thams cad kyis yongs su rdzogs par brgyan
NK076(mu)002:5878: pa'i lha yi bu mo yid du 'ong ba dang
NK076(mu)002:5879: / mi'i khya'u dang bu ma yid 'ong dag gisa
NK076(mu)002:5880: bdag la 'dod yon lnga'i mchod pa byed pa mthong
NK076(mu)002:5881: / na / rtags de ni dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur ba'i ltas yin no //
NK076(mu)002:5883: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad rnams ni /
NK076(mu)002:5884: rang rang gi zhing na gnas pa dag bdag gis nges par mthong ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:5885: rgyal ba des bdag la thugs na dgyes par gyur nas kyang /
NK076(mu)002:5886: chos kyi mdzod po ti glegs bam la sogs yid
NK076(mu)002:5887: du 'ong ba yi gtam la sogs bdag la snang
NK076(mu)002:5889: chosa kyi 'khor lo sgyur ba'i mthu dang sprul sku
NK076(mu)002:5890: thub pa lta bu la 'khor sems can kun gyis
NK076(mu)002:5891: yongs su bskor nas chos ston pa mthong ba ni
NK076(mu)002:5892: rnal 'byor pa lha'i bsam gtan lus ngag yid gsum
NK076(mu)002:5893: rdo rja gsum la dbyer mi phyed par gnas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5894: / dama tshiga las mi 'da' ba'i sbyor bas mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:5896: nyams dga' ba'i sa phyogs sna tshogs pa kun dga'
NK076(mu)002:5897: ba'i skyed mos tshala la lha yi bu mo la
NK076(mu)002:5899: bdag nyid la sangs rgyas kun gyis byin gyis brlabs par mthong ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:5900: yi dam lha'i bsam gtan gyi ting 'dzin las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshiga can gyis mthong pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5902: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub semsa dpa' mang po yis /
NK076(mu)002:5903: bdag lha sgom pa de la ni mngon sum para dbang bskur ba mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5905: riga 'dzin gyi rgyal po chen po mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin pa de yis /
NK076(mu)002:5906: bdag nyid la mchod pa byed par rnal 'byor pa des mthong ngo //
NK076(mu)002:5907: lus ngag yid lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum
NK076(mu)002:5908: du bsgom pa las byung ba'i yon tan sna tshogs
NK076(mu)002:5909: pa'i rmi lam gsal bas skyon gyi dri ma med
NK076(mu)002:5910: pa yang daga de mthong na /
NK076(mu)002:5911: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi rda rja gsum
NK076(mu)002:5912: bsgoms pa las skyes pa'i 'bras bu bla na med
NK076(mu)002:5913: pa yi rgyal ba nyid 'grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:5915: rigs ngan pa gdol pa dang khya ya sbyor ba byed pa la sogs pa'i khong nas /
NK076(mu)002:5916: phag dang stag sogs gcan gzan gzhan gyi sbyor ba
NK076(mu)002:5917: byed pa rnal 'byor pa rdo rje 'dzin pas mthong
NK076(mu)002:5919: rigs ngan pa bltar mthong yang blang dor med par
NK076(mu)002:5920: rtogs pa'i blo dang ldan pa rdo rje semas dpa'
NK076(mu)002:5921: yi ngo bor / rang gi sems kyi ngo bo
NK076(mu)002:5922: ye nas gnas pa de na 'bras bu'i rdo rje
NK076(mu)002:5925: gsung yi ge dang thugs dang sku'i phyag rgya rnam
NK076(mu)002:5926: gnyis kyi skye mcheda gsum mthonga bar 'byung ba'ang sems
NK076(mu)002:5927: kyi gnas lugs gong bzhin 'grub pa de bzhin no
NK076(mu)002:5928: // bcu gsum pa phan yon la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5929: lha bsgoms pa'i phan yon dang /
NK076(mu)002:5930: ma bsgoms pa'i skyon gyi ngos nas brtson 'grus gyis shig gdams pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5931: zhal mthong bas mos shing bsgrubs pa'i phan yon no //
NK076(mu)002:5933: dang po tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:5934: rnal 'byor pas yi dam lha yi sku ni gsal la ma 'gags par bsgoms na /
NK076(mu)002:5935: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs chena po rdzogs te gzugs sku thob par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:5936: lha de nyid chu zla'i tshul du snang la rang bzhin med par shes par gyur na /
NK076(mu)002:5937: 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogas chena po rdzogs te chos sku thob para 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:5938: gnyis pa yon tan chung yang bsgrubs na 'grub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5939: yon tan rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyi sgo gsum
NK076(mu)002:5940: yi dam lha yi sku gsung thugs dang tha dad
NK076(mu)002:5941: med par mnyam par sbyor basa na /
NK076(mu)002:5942: de las gzhan pa'i rig pa'i gnas lnga la sogs
NK076(mu)002:5943: pa'i mkhas pa'i yona tan chung yanga 'bras bu yi
NK076(mu)002:5944: dam lha ni 'grub par 'gyur ba la the tshom
NK076(mu)002:5945: med do // de yang ya gdod ma nas lha
NK076(mu)002:5946: dang bdag gnyis ngo bo dbyer med pas mnyam pa
NK076(mu)002:5948: yi dam gyi lha nyid yin pa nyid du ni dus rtag tu bsgom pa bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:5949: gsum pa lha gcig bsgoms pas 'bras bu kun thob pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:5950: rgyal rnams gcig tha dad las grol phyir /
NK076(mu)002:5951: bde gshegs kun dang mnyam par sbyor bar gyur pasa /
NK076(mu)002:5952: de'i phyir rgyal ba'i dkyil 'akhara kun dang mnyam para sbyor ba'i 'bras bu thob par 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)002:5953: de nas bdag nyid rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun dang
NK076(mu)002:5954: mnyam par sbyor ba'i phyir mthar thug rgyal ba'i sku
NK076(mu)002:5955: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga dang ye shes
NK076(mu)002:5956: lnga yongs su rdzogsa shing grub par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:5957: gnyis pa ma bsgoms pa'i skyon gyi ngos nas brtson 'grus gyis shig pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:5958: dang po lha ma bsgom pa'i skyon /
NK076(mu)002:5959: yi dam lha yi mtshan nyid ni gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:5960: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK076(mu)002:5961: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag po yin pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:5962: yi dam gyi lha spangs nas gzhan dge ba ci
NK076(mu)002:5963: spyad kyang 'dod pa'i don 'bras bu med par 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:5964: te / dper na sman pas bor pa 'i nad pa bzhin no //
NK076(mu)002:5965: gnyis pa brtson 'grus gyis shig gdams pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:5966: dang po brtson 'grus gyis shig gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:5967: rtsa ba dang yan lag dam tshig bzhin du bsrung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:5968: skyon bcu spangs te sngags bzlas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:5969: yi dam gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya rgyun mi bacada pa /
NK076(mu)002:5970: dam tshig las chos sku phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:5971: bsgom pa rnams la sgo gsum gyis brtson 'grus che
NK076(mu)002:5972: bar bya zhing blo brtan para byas la gzung ngo
NK076(mu)002:5973: // gal te rnal 'byor pa lha'i bsgom bzlas la
NK076(mu)002:5974: brtson 'grus chung bar gyur na skyon ci yod ce
NK076(mu)002:5976: slar rdo rje dmyal ba la sogs par ltung bas
NK076(mu)002:5977: nyen shin tu yang che bar gsungs ste /
NK076(mu)002:5978: gnyis pa gal te nan tan ma byas pa'i skyon gyi dpe don ni /
NK076(mu)002:5980: ral kha 'gyid pa'i tshe rala gri'i so la bag zon gyis nan tan du /
NK076(mu)002:5981: yu ba nas legs par ma bzung na skyon ni
NK076(mu)002:5982: rang gi lag pa gcod par 'gyur ba de bzhin
NK076(mu)002:5983: du lha bsgom sngags bzla ba la nana tan meda
NK076(mu)002:5984: pa'i gsang sngags pa rnams tshe 'dir phung ba'am yang
NK076(mu)002:5985: na phyi mar bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu bla med byang
NK076(mu)002:5987: gsum pa brtson 'grus med pa'i skyon /
NK076(mu)002:5988: skyon 'dug pa de bas lha'i bsgom bzlas la bar
NK076(mu)002:5989: chad cing brtson 'grus meda par gyur na dper na
NK076(mu)002:5990: sa bon mes tshig pa btab pa las /
NK076(mu)002:5991: 'bras bu myu gu 'byung bar 'doda pa dang 'dra ste /
NK076(mu)002:5992: tshe 'di ched du gnyer nas bsgrubs par byas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:5993: 'bras bu mchog thun dngos grub gang yang med par
NK076(mu)002:5994: 'agyur zhing / phyi mar mi khom pa'i gnas brgyad
NK076(mu)002:5995: la sogs pa 'khor bar kha brgyud para 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)002:5996: 'agyur zhing / // gsum pa zhal mthong bas mos shing bsgrubs pa'i phan yon /
NK076(mu)002:5997: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i rnal 'byor pa gang
NK076(mu)002:5998: zhiga yi dam lha'i zhal mathanga zhing mos pa byas
NK076(mu)002:5999: pa yis / de la bsnyen cing bkur ba dang mchod pa byas pa'i bsod nams kyis /
NK076(mu)002:6000: mi dge ba bcu dang mtshams med lnga ste bco lnga /
NK076(mu)002:6003: log pa brgyad la sogas pa las ngan gyi sgrib
NK076(mu)002:6004: pa thams cad sbyangs ta rnam smin nam tshe dbang
NK076(mu)002:6005: rig 'dzin gyi sa la sbyor bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:6006: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma ni /
NK076(mu)002:6007: rgya gcig gang zag gis mi rtag ste tshe 'pho ba'i dus mthong na yang /
NK076(mu)002:6008: yi dam lha'i sku'i phyag rgya dang ma nyams par ting 'dzin gsal bar yid la bzung sta /
NK076(mu)002:6009: sngar mi dge ba'i las bsags pa'i las kyis ngan
NK076(mu)002:6010: song la sogs pa'i 'khor bar mi 'akhara bar rang
NK076(mu)002:6011: nyid kyis gang 'dod pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khyad
NK076(mu)002:6012: par can du / a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:6013: gyi steng du rang yi dam gyi skur bsam la
NK076(mu)002:6014: par can du / / 'og nas yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyi stobs kyis bteg la //
NK076(mu)002:6015: a yam sam ti dzah a s+pha ra na phatah ces brjod de /
NK076(mu)002:6017: nub bde ba can sogs gang mos kyi gnas su bskul bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6018: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6019: dang po gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin la sbyor ba /
NK076(mu)002:6020: mthar phyin cing blo chen thod rgal gyi dbang du
NK076(mu)002:6021: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa la the
NK076(mu)002:6022: tshoma med do // nyams mthar ma phyin cing blo
NK076(mu)002:6023: chung bas 'on te rnam smin du tshe 'dir ma
NK076(mu)002:6024: tshoma med do // gyur na yang / nyams mtho dman dang /
NK076(mu)002:6025: blo rtsal dang brtson pa che chung gi rim pa yis /
NK076(mu)002:6026: rnam smin rig 'dzin de nyid bar do'am phyi ma'am
NK076(mu)002:6027: skye ba lan grangsa gzhan bdun tshun chad la thob
NK076(mu)002:6028: par 'gyur ro // nyams mthar phyin cing blo rtsal
NK076(mu)002:6029: dang brtson pa rab yin na tshe la yang dbang
NK076(mu)002:6030: ba'i rig 'dzin 'di la ma thob kyang phyi ma'am
NK076(mu)002:6031: par 'gyur ro // / spros pa dang tshogs sgrub nas thob ba'am /
NK076(mu)002:6032: gzhan skye ba lan grangs bdun tshun chad la tshe dbang thob par nges so //
NK076(mu)002:6033: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:6034: rnal 'byor pa ting 'dzin las su rung ba rnams kyis /
NK076(mu)002:6035: yi dam lha sku phyag rgya chen pa rang rig
NK076(mu)002:6036: pas mngon sum du gsal bar rdzogs par 'gyur zhing
NK076(mu)002:6037: / sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba'i tshad
NK076(mu)002:6038: yul gyis mi 'phrog pa la brtan pa thob nas
NK076(mu)002:6039: yid gnyis dang the tshom med par bsgrub pa byas
NK076(mu)002:6040: / na / mthar thug rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs
NK076(mu)002:6041: kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dngos grub chen po 'abra ba
NK076(mu)002:6042: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa nyid 'grub
NK076(mu)002:6043: / na / par 'gyur ro // gsum pa ma
NK076(mu)002:6044: thob kyang ngan song dang theg dman du ltung bar
NK076(mu)002:6046: / phyag rgya gcig pa 'di ltar bsgoms shing bsgrubs
NK076(mu)002:6048: / par byas na / 'bras bu tshe 'dir dang
NK076(mu)002:6049: bar dor mngon du ma byung yang /
NK076(mu)002:6050: tshe rabs sam skye ba brgyud pa thams cada du
NK076(mu)002:6051: lha dang ma yi lus rnam dag dbang po tshang
NK076(mu)002:6052: zhing gsal ba ste matshana yongs su rdzogs pa thob
NK076(mu)002:6053: nas gzhan gyi sdug bsngal sela ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6054: bde gshegs sprul pa'i sku 'jig rten du 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6055: gnas dang dus kyis mi bkol zhing 'phrad pa dang
NK076(mu)002:6056: 'phrad nas kyang mtshan nyid kyi thega pa dman para
NK076(mu)002:6058: theg mchog gsang sngags bla med kyi byang chub las
NK076(mu)002:6059: phyir mi ldog pa'i gzungs la zhugs pa yin no
NK076(mu)002:6060: // de lta bu'i yon tan yod pa de bas
NK076(mu)002:6061: na rgya gcig pa'i lam 'adi nyid dang dus skabs
NK076(mu)002:6063: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan don ba den pa dbyer med
NK076(mu)002:6064: rtags yi dam lha'i sku phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting
NK076(mu)002:6065: nge 'dzin gyi bsgom bston par byed pa'i gzhung gi
NK076(mu)002:6066: tshig don rnams mtshams dang ris su gcod cing mtshams
NK076(mu)002:6067: 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na la'u ste /
NK076(mu)002:6068: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK076(mu)002:6069: yas bgrangs pa'i lnga pa'i don du gda' 'o ////le'u
NK076(mu)002:6070: drug pa spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor la gsum ste
NK076(mu)002:6071: / dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:6072: rang ga yi dam gyi lha zhi khro rgya gcig
NK076(mu)002:6073: pa la lta ba dang ting 'dzin gyi phyag dbyer
NK076(mu)002:6075: lha gcig du mar spros pa'i tshul du bsgom pa'i
NK076(mu)002:6076: rnal 'byor ting 'dzin gyi rim pas bshad par bya
NK076(mu)002:6077: ba ni / gnyis pa gzhung don la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6078: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:6079: phyag rgya spros bcas bsgom pa'i gzhi'o lus mdor bstan
NK076(mu)002:6080: yang sngar de ting gi skabs su don bco lnga
NK076(mu)002:6082: 'dir yang don bco lnga bzhag pa yis de rnam
NK076(mu)002:6083: par dgrol pa'i phyir yan lag rgyas par bshad par
NK076(mu)002:6084: bya'o // gnyis pa yan lag rgyas bshad la bco lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:6099: dang po sngon du bya ba la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6100: dang po lam snga ma la goms pas rten bzhengs shing rab gnas bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:6101: de kun rgya gcig gi rnal 'byor dang rnam pa
NK076(mu)002:6102: gsum phyag rgya spros pa'i sngon du rdzogs par byas
NK076(mu)002:6103: nas / sa dang gser dngul rwa shing la sogas pa rnams la lha'i sku'i phyag rgya byas te /
NK076(mu)002:6107: thang la rdul tshon te ra ma'i rgyu bzhi 'am /
NK076(mu)002:6108: rwa shir rus pa la 'bur du bskos pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:6109: rin po che las lugsa su blugs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6110: 'jim pa las 'der so byas pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK076(mu)002:6111: de ltar las dang bya ba'i lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan
NK076(mu)002:6112: gyi dkyil 'khor ni sgrub pa'i khang bu dngos su
NK076(mu)002:6113: bya zhing / de la rab gnas byas pas ye
NK076(mu)002:6114: shes pa'i byin rlabs dang ldan pa nye bar brten
NK076(mu)002:6115: bya zhing / par bya'o // gnyis pa mchod rdzas bshams shing cha rkyen bsdu ba /
NK076(mu)002:6116: ma h+aa ba linga rta gtor ma chen po dang /
NK076(mu)002:6117: a mri ta bdud rtsi dang /
NK076(mu)002:6119: phyi yi mchod pa rnam lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:6120: nang gi mchod pa gsum po rnams dgram /
NK076(mu)002:6121: rol mo'i mchoda pa la sogs mchod pa'i cha rkyen rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:6122: gzhan yang mchod pa'i yo byad ci ltar bsdu bar 'os pa rnams gzhung bzhin bsdu bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6123: gsum pa sngon 'gro'i las kyi rim pa bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:6124: dang po srung 'khor khro bo bcus phyogs mtshams bcingas /
NK076(mu)002:6125: de nas yan lag brgyad pa nas bzung ste /
NK076(mu)002:6127: byin dbab yan chad kyi rim pa rdzogsa par byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:6128: bdag nyid las kyi lha bdud rtsi 'akhyil pa'am yi
NK076(mu)002:6129: dam gang yin gyi rnal 'byor dang ldan pa'i ting
NK076(mu)002:6130: 'dzin gyis phyi nang gi mchod rdzas rnams tshul bzhin
NK076(mu)002:6131: du byin gyis brlab para bya /
NK076(mu)002:6132: de yang thog mar bdud rtsi'i chus bsangs /
NK076(mu)002:6133: badz+ra yak+shasa bgegs bskrad de mchod pa rnams byin gyis brlabs la stan la 'dug go //
NK076(mu)002:6134: gnyis pa dgos ched la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:6135: dang po bdag don gyi dgos ched bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6136: lha'i sku du mar gsal bar byas pas bsod namsa kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogsa par bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:6137: phyi nang gi spyod yul phung khams skye mched rnams
NK076(mu)002:6138: lha yi dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlab pa'i dgos
NK076(mu)002:6140: 'bras bu yi ge 'khora lo tshogs chen gyi sa brgyud nas mthar dbyung bar bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6141: tshom bu tshogs sgrub la spros pa mthar phyin pa'i dus kyis bsgrub dgos pa'i phyir bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6142: gnyis pa gzhan gyi dgos ched brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:6143: dbang gi las dgra bgegs dang gzungs ma la sogs dgug pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6144: drag po'i las dgra bgegs gling khams gzhan du btang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6145: dbang gi las 'byung po'i kha bcingas ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6146: gzhan gyis byad du bcug pa dgrol ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6147: rgyas pa'i las sri'u lo tog nad pa sogs gso ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6148: drag po'i las dgra bgegs bsad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6149: gzhan gyi phyogs phama par bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6150: rgyas pa'i las bdag gi phyogs rgyal bar bya ba
NK076(mu)002:6151: rnams phyag rgya spros pa'i ting 'dzin 'dis 'grub par
NK076(mu)002:6153: lam pa ganga daga spros pa'i gdul bya ji snyed pa thams cad kyang /
NK076(mu)002:6154: phyag rgya spros pa bsgom pa'i phrin las kyis yang dag pa'i sa la gdon pa'i phyir ra //
NK076(mu)002:6155: gsum pa sgom thabs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6156: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK076(mu)002:6157: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstim pa /
NK076(mu)002:6158: de la mchod cing phrin las kyi rim pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6161: rgya gciga rnal 'byor la brtan pa thob nas /
NK076(mu)002:6162: rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa'ang zhi khro rnam pa gnyis yod pa sta /
NK076(mu)002:6164: rgya gcig dang rjes su mthun par zha ba sproos bcas dang /
NK076(mu)002:6165: khra bo spros bcas gnyis ston te /
NK076(mu)002:6166: zhi khro de gnyis gang rung ra re yanga rim dang cig char gyi tshul gnyis kyis /
NK076(mu)002:6167: gdul bya'i blo che chung gi rim pa dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:6168: par rim cig char gang 'tshams su bsgom par ston
NK076(mu)002:6169: pa yin no // gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6174: mdor bstan gyi snga ma zhi la spros pa rang la'ang rim gyis dang cig chara ba gnyis so //
NK076(mu)002:6175: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6177: mdor bstan la gnyis su phye bas phyi ma cig
NK076(mu)002:6178: char rgya gcig pa bzhin du spros pa la cig
NK076(mu)002:6180: nam mkha'i nyi zla dang gza' skar thams cad dus
NK076(mu)002:6181: gcig tu chu dkyil rnyogs ma dwang bar ma 'dres
NK076(mu)002:6182: par gsal zhing 'char ba bzhina du /
NK076(mu)002:6183: rgya spros lha'i sku gsal ba skad cig ma gcig la 'oda du 'abra bar bsgom pa'ang /
NK076(mu)002:6184: snying pa h'u badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs pa brjod pas
NK076(mu)002:6185: zhi ba'i 'khor lo lha'i dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus
NK076(mu)002:6186: gsum yongs rdzogs gsal bar shar ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6187: gnyis pa rim gyis pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6188: dang po ngo bo spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:6189: rim gyis pa de mdor bstan gyi sngon du bstan
NK076(mu)002:6190: pa ni rgya gcig pa'i rim gyis pa bzhin du
NK076(mu)002:6191: 'dir spros bcas la rim gyis 'jug pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:6192: snang ba lha yi dkyil 'khor du lta bas mthong
NK076(mu)002:6193: ba dang lam snga ma'i rgya gcig rnal 'byor la
NK076(mu)002:6194: goms pa'i stobs kyis rgya spros ting 'dzin thob pas
NK076(mu)002:6195: dper na shes bya gcig shes kyang du ma la
NK076(mu)002:6197: rgya spros lha'i dkyil 'khor du ma shar ba dang
NK076(mu)002:6198: rnal 'byor pa gcig gis rim par gsal bar byed
NK076(mu)002:6199: pa'ang / gnyis pa dbye bas bye brag tu bshad pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6201: khro bor ma bsgyur bar ma bcos rnal ma'i zhi
NK076(mu)002:6202: ba'i dkyil 'khor la dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo spros
NK076(mu)002:6203: pa dang / tshom bu spros pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6205: zhal phyag spros pa la bslab pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6206: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6207: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6208: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6209: bsdus pa la lha rigs lnga yab yum bcu sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:6210: 'bring po la bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6211: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khora la pho brang gi lha lnga bcu /
NK076(mu)002:6212: sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug /kun bzang yab yum gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6213: thub pa drug sgo pa yab yum brgyad de brgyad cu rtsa gnyis rnams la rim par bslab bo //
NK076(mu)002:6214: gnyis pa tshom bu spros pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6215: dang po tshom bu gcig pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6216: mdor bstan gyi gnyis pa tshom bu spros pa la gsum las /
NK076(mu)002:6217: dang po gcig pa la bslab pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:6218: rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gtso bo mi bskyod pa
NK076(mu)002:6219: yaba yum gnyis su bsal bar gnas pa'i gzhal yas
NK076(mu)002:6220: khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba mu khyud gru
NK076(mu)002:6221: chad sgo gtod du gsal bar bsgom par byas te
NK076(mu)002:6222: gdan lnga brtsegs dang ldan pa'i dbus kyi lte ba
NK076(mu)002:6223: na rigs kyi bdag pa rdo rje sems dpa' yab
NK076(mu)002:6224: yum gnas la / de la rdo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' ni /
NK076(mu)002:6225: shar du rdo rje sem dpa' dang /
NK076(mu)002:6227: lhor rdo rje rin chen dang rdo rje 'bar ma /
NK076(mu)002:6228: nub tu rdo rje chos dang /
NK076(mu)002:6230: byang du rdo rje las dang /
NK076(mu)002:6232: de ltar yab yum brgyad dang /
NK076(mu)002:6233: phyogs bzhi'i khro bo yab yum brgyad kyis bskor bas na lha bco brgyad do //
NK076(mu)002:6234: gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa /
NK076(mu)002:6235: tshom bu gcig pa la blo brtan pa thob nas /
NK076(mu)002:6236: mdun du sku'i rnam par snang mdzad yab yum la /
NK076(mu)002:6241: nub tu rdo rje chags pa /
NK076(mu)002:6243: byang du rdo rje legs pa /
NK076(mu)002:6244: rdo rje phreng ba ma ste bcu /
NK076(mu)002:6245: rgyab tu gsung gi rigs snang ba mtha' yas yab yum la /
NK076(mu)002:6246: shar du rdo rje chos dang /
NK076(mu)002:6252: byang du rdo rje smra ba /
NK076(mu)002:6253: rdo rje gsal bkra ste bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:6254: dbus su thugsa rdor sems yab yum bcu ste 'khor lo'i pho brang du lha sum cu /
NK076(mu)002:6255: phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo yab yum bcu drug ste
NK076(mu)002:6256: lha zhe drug rdzogsa para bsgoms pa la yi ge
NK076(mu)002:6257: +aahmh'u 'abru gsum sku gsung thugs kyi lha bskyed pa'i
NK076(mu)002:6258: brda'a 'o // lha grangs nyung ting 'dzin blo stobs chung ba'am /
NK076(mu)002:6259: mi yi lus ngag yid gsum yod pa'i dbang du
NK076(mu)002:6260: tshom bu gsum pa'i lha zhe drug gi ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:6261: la shin tu gomas shing 'dris par bya ba gces
NK076(mu)002:6262: pa yin no // gsum pa tshom bu lnga pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6263: de ltar tshom bu gsum pa la blo brtan pa thob nas /
NK076(mu)002:6264: gtso bo'i zhal shar du gzigs pa'i g.yas lha brtsibs
NK076(mu)002:6265: steng du yon tan rigs rin 'byung yab yum la
NK076(mu)002:6266: / shar du rdo rje rin chen dang /
NK076(mu)002:6269: rdo rje me tog /nub tu rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK076(mu)002:6271: byang du rdo rje gzhad pa /
NK076(mu)002:6274: g.yon byang gi rtsibs nyid du phrin las kyi rigs don grub yab yum la /
NK076(mu)002:6275: shar du rdo rje las dang /
NK076(mu)002:6279: nub tu rdo rje gnod sbyin /
NK076(mu)002:6281: byang du rdo rje khu tshur /
NK076(mu)002:6282: rdo rje 'bebs ma lte yab yum bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:6283: de ltar yon tan phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor dang
NK076(mu)002:6284: gnyis bazhaga pas pho brang gi lha lnga bcu dang
NK076(mu)002:6285: / phyogs mtshams steng 'og gi khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste lha bdun cu'o //
NK076(mu)002:6286: de ltar sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i
NK076(mu)002:6287: don rnal ma la blo 'byor ba'i lha'i dbang du
NK076(mu)002:6289: de la shin tu 'dris shing goms nas mthar phyin pa'i dus na tshogs sgrub la sbyor ro //
NK076(mu)002:6290: gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:6291: dang po rtsa ba'i rnam grangs spros pa /
NK076(mu)002:6292: mdor bstan gyi gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:6293: rtsa ba'i rnam grangs lha gtso bo thugs rdo rje
NK076(mu)002:6294: sems dpa' yab yum gyi sku nyid du gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:6295: ting 'dzin la brtan pa thob nas /
NK076(mu)002:6296: sku rnam snang gsung snang mtha' gatsa bora byas pa'i ting 'dzin gsal ba /
NK076(mu)002:6297: de ltar gsum po'i ting 'dzin 'tshora ba med par brtan pa thob pa nasa /
NK076(mu)002:6300: rigs lnga char rdzogas par bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:6301: de yang yab yum zung du 'brel bar bsgom pa la blo brtan pa thob par byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:6302: rigs lnga bo'i don rang rang gi rigs su spros
NK076(mu)002:6303: pas sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su byed pa
NK076(mu)002:6304: pos ma bcos par rang bzhin ngang gisa gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:6305: la / de ltar rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi lhag pa'i dkyil 'akhara bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:6306: gnyis pa yan lag la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:6307: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6308: nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6309: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6312: yan lag thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rtsa
NK076(mu)002:6313: ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:6314: yin / de yang rtsa lha mi bskyod pa yab yum la /
NK076(mu)002:6315: yan lag lha nyer bzhi yab la bkod de /
NK076(mu)002:6325: mig rtsa'i phyi ru byams pa /
NK076(mu)002:6333: brang gi rgya mdud lding khang kun tu bzang po /
NK076(mu)002:6335: sta zur g.yas lha min thub pa /
NK076(mu)002:6337: lte bar byol song thub pa /
NK076(mu)002:6338: mgrin par yi dwags thub pa /
NK076(mu)002:6339: gsang gnas dmyal ba'i thub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6340: de ltar rtsa ba'i lha yab la yab nyi shu rtsa bzhi bkod /
NK076(mu)002:6341: rtsa ba'i lha yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma la /
NK076(mu)002:6342: yum bco brgyad bkod tshul ni yab dang mtshungs so //
NK076(mu)002:6343: rtsa lha mi bskyod pa yab yum gsal bas der
NK076(mu)002:6344: yab yum gnyis ma bgrangs bas gzhan lha bzhi bcu
NK076(mu)002:6345: po de nyid kyi snying gar phra ba shes rab
NK076(mu)002:6346: kyi lha tshon gang re re dang /
NK076(mu)002:6347: 'og gi sku gsung thugs kyi lha rnams la yan
NK076(mu)002:6348: lag spros pa'i bdag po rigs lngas dbu brgya pa
NK076(mu)002:6349: ste / de yang thabs lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK076(mu)002:6350: la sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gsum 'phror zhes
NK076(mu)002:6352: mdor na thabs dang shes rab lha brgyad cu /
NK076(mu)002:6353: sku gsung thugs kyi lha brgya nyi shu /
NK076(mu)002:6354: dbu rgyan ye shes kyi lha stong ste sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6355: 'o na stong dang nyis brgya yod ce na /
NK076(mu)002:6356: spar khab tu rtsa lha nyis brgya mi bgrang dbu rgyan ye shes lha stong kho nar bzhed do //
NK076(mu)002:6357: gnyis pa de ji ltar ldan tshul /
NK076(mu)002:6358: de ltar rtsa lha stangs te yab rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK076(mu)002:6359: dpyal te yum dbyings phyug ma gnyis kyi sku phyag rgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:6360: de la bkod pa'i sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor yang /
NK076(mu)002:6361: sku ri rab tsam la bzhugs gnas kyi rtsa'i snod til 'bru'i nang du shong ba'i tshul bzhin tu /
NK076(mu)002:6362: rtsa lha mi che yan lag lha mi chung bar thun mong dang /
NK076(mu)002:6363: khyad par gyi dpe byad brgyad cu dang mtshan bzang so gnyis kya rgyan spras par bzhugs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6364: gnyis pa nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6365: de ltar gtso mchoga rdor sems yab yum la lha stong dang ldan par byas nasa /
NK076(mu)002:6366: chos bya ba mo dang yid byed pa po kun bzang yab yum la stong /
NK076(mu)002:6367: rgyal ba ragas bzhi yab yum la'ang stong tsho re re bsgom par bya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:6368: sems dpa' yab yum zung brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:6369: sgo ba yab yum zung bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:6370: de ltar yab yum zung bcu gnyis la stong tsho bcu gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:6371: gong gi drug bsnan pas stong tsho bco brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:6372: thub pa drug gi lha'i gnas mal du lha yab
NK076(mu)002:6373: yum 'khril sbyor du bkod pas stong tsho drug go
NK076(mu)002:6374: // kun tu bzang mo ma gtogs so //
NK076(mu)002:6375: de ltar stong tsho nyi shu rtsa bzhi po rnams
NK076(mu)002:6376: kyang 'oda zer 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar bar bsgom
NK076(mu)002:6377: pa ni / sangs rgyas nyi khri bzhi stong gi dkyil 'khor dus gciga tu gasla ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6378: gsum pa bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6379: phyi snod phyogs bcu 'jig rten gyi khams ma lus
NK076(mu)002:6380: pa thams cad lha'i gzhal yasa khang du bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:6381: la / nyi zla dang gza' skar thams cad gdan dang rgyun du gsal /
NK076(mu)002:6382: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad bade bar gshegsa pa dkyil 'khora ma lus par bsgom pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:6383: bsam yasa lhun gyis grub pa'i ting 'dzin nyid la slob pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6384: bzhi pa zhal phyag spros pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6385: mdor bstan gyi bzhi pa zhal phyag spros bcas ni /
NK076(mu)002:6386: dang po tshom bu gciga pa la zhal gsum phyag drug tu bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:6387: de la ting 'dzin brtan pa thob nasa tshom bu
NK076(mu)002:6388: gsum pa la'nga zhal gsum phyag drug bsgom pa de
NK076(mu)002:6389: bzhin ta / de la brtan pa thob nas tshom
NK076(mu)002:6390: bu lnga pa yang zhal gsum phyag drug snga ma
NK076(mu)002:6391: ltar rjes su mthun par goms nasa /
NK076(mu)002:6392: de ltar dkyil 'khor dang rnam grangs spros pa'i skabs
NK076(mu)002:6393: su lha kun la zhal gsum dang phyag drug rdzogs
NK076(mu)002:6395: gnyis pa khro bo la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:6397: gdul bya'i dbang gis zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur ba'i 'khor la'ang /
NK076(mu)002:6401: zhal phyag spros pa dang bzhi yod pa zhi ba'i skabs de bzhin du yin te /
NK076(mu)002:6402: gnyis pa rgyas pa la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6403: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6404: dang po dkyil 'khor spros pa la gsum las /
NK076(mu)002:6405: bsdus pa la lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad de /
NK076(mu)002:6409: sgo ma bzhi ste nyi shu /
NK076(mu)002:6410: dbang mo nyer brgyad dang lnga bcu nga brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:6411: de bsgom zhing goms par gyur nas /
NK076(mu)002:6412: 'bring po de'i steng khro bcu bsnan pas drug cu rtsa brgyad la goms nas /
NK076(mu)002:6413: rgyas pa zhi ba'i skabs de bzhin lha brgya rtsa
NK076(mu)002:6414: brgyad yod pa yin te 'og gi rnam grangs spros
NK076(mu)002:6415: bcas kyi skabs su gsal lo //
NK076(mu)002:6416: gnyis pa tshom bu la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6417: dang po gcig pa dang gsum pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6418: dang po tshom bu la gsum las /
NK076(mu)002:6419: gcig pa ni dbus kyi lte ba la thugs badz+ra
NK076(mu)002:6420: ha ru ka yab yum gzhi po gnyis kyis gtso
NK076(mu)002:6421: byas pa la 'khor thugs kyi rigs chung gi khro
NK076(mu)002:6422: bo yab yum brgyad bsgom pa la brten nas /
NK076(mu)002:6423: gsum pa ni mdun shar gyi rtsibs steng du sku bud+d+ha khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK076(mu)002:6424: rgyab nub kyi rtsibs steng du gsung pad+ma khrag 'thung
NK076(mu)002:6425: yab yum gyi khra ba mdun rgyab tu gasla bar
NK076(mu)002:6426: bsgom pa da la brtan pa thob nas 'khor sku
NK076(mu)002:6427: gsung gi rigs chung khro bo yab yum brgyad dang
NK076(mu)002:6428: bacasa par bsgom / gnyis pa lnga pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6429: de ltar sku gsung thugsa kyi khrag 'thung yab yum la shin tu brtan par byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:6430: g.yas lho'i rtsibs steng du yon tan rat+na khrag 'thung dang /
NK076(mu)002:6431: g.yon byang gi rtsibs steng du /
NK076(mu)002:6432: phrin las karma khrag 'thung ste khro bo yaba yum
NK076(mu)002:6433: rnams ting 'dzin gyi gsal bar bsgoms nasa 'khor rigs
NK076(mu)002:6434: chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad dang bcas pa
NK076(mu)002:6435: tshom bu 'khor bo'i lha tshogs rnams rdzogs par bsgom
NK076(mu)002:6436: pa nyams rim pa bzhin tu /
NK076(mu)002:6437: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga'i lha gang bsgom gsal bar
NK076(mu)002:6438: byas pa la ting 'dzin ma sun par je gsal
NK076(mu)002:6439: du gyen du 'aphara bar bstan par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6440: gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6441: dang po rtsa ba'i rnam grangs spros pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6442: gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la zhi ba dang
NK076(mu)002:6443: rjes su mthun par 'jigs byed khro bo'i rnam grangs
NK076(mu)002:6445: gcig ni rdo rje'i rigs badz+ra he ru ka dang /
NK076(mu)002:6446: gnyis pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs bud+d+ha dang /
NK076(mu)002:6448: bzhi pa rin po che'i rigs dang /
NK076(mu)002:6449: lnga pa las kyi rigs karma he ru ka ste
NK076(mu)002:6450: gtso bo rigs lnga yab yum bcu ka'i ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:6452: de ltar re re la'ang 'khor lo'i lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi'i chas phye bas /
NK076(mu)002:6453: rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad brgyad kyis
NK076(mu)002:6454: bskor ba'i pho brang gi lha lnga bcu'i tshoma bu
NK076(mu)002:6455: la gnas ma ma mo brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:6456: yul ma phra men brgyad dang /
NK076(mu)002:6458: slas ma dbang mo nyer brgyad dang /
NK076(mu)002:6459: h'u chena khro bo bcu ste brgya rtsa brgyad kyi lha gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6460: gnyis pa yan lag gi rnam grangs /
NK076(mu)002:6461: gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gnyis la yan lag gi lha bkod pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:6462: rtsa lha yab kyi lag g.yas badz+ra khrag 'thung /
NK076(mu)002:6466: dbu na bud+d+ha khrag 'thung bkod la /
NK076(mu)002:6469: lce'i 'doms rtsi'i nang du nang gi ma mo bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6470: phyi la phyi'i ma mo bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6471: mthil bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6472: sgal tshigs la dbang mo nyer brgyad bkod do //
NK076(mu)002:6473: yum gyi yan lag lnga la yum lnga /
NK076(mu)002:6476: lce dang bzhi'i 'doms rtsa'i nang du phyogs kyi phra men bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6477: phyi la mtshams kyi phra men bzhi bkod pa'i thabs
NK076(mu)002:6478: kyi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad po de la shes
NK076(mu)002:6479: rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' re re /
NK076(mu)002:6480: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gsum ste nga brgyad
NK076(mu)002:6481: pa cha lnga'i grangs na nyis brgya dang dagu bcu'i
NK076(mu)002:6482: lha rnams kyi yan lag tu ldan pa de rnams
NK076(mu)002:6483: la dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga ste stong dang
NK076(mu)002:6485: de ltar lus la bkod pa'i lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la brtsis pas /
NK076(mu)002:6486: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu yod do //
NK076(mu)002:6487: bzhi pa zhal phyag la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6488: dang po zhal phyag spros pa la bslab pa /
NK076(mu)002:6489: dang po khro bo zhal gciga phyag gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6490: de la brtan pa thob nas zhal gsum phyag drug dang /
NK076(mu)002:6491: de la brtan pa thob nas dbu dgu dang phyag
NK076(mu)002:6492: bco brgyad lha kun dang ldan par bsgom pa dang
NK076(mu)002:6493: / de nas dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6494: dbu dgu bargya phyag stong brgyad bargya nas zhabs phyag grangsa med pa'i bar du slob par byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6495: gnyis pa de lam pa gang gi spyod yul yin pa /
NK076(mu)002:6496: zhal phyag gi rnam grangs de dag gang zag rim
NK076(mu)002:6497: gyis pas slob pa'i thabs su brjod kya dngos su
NK076(mu)002:6498: spyod yul ni / tshogs lam rgya gcig spros la
NK076(mu)002:6499: zhal gsum phyag drug /sbyor lam du dbu dgu phyag
NK076(mu)002:6500: spyod yul ni / bco brgyad / mthong lam du dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag zhe gnyis dang /
NK076(mu)002:6501: sgom lam du dbu dgu bargya phyag stong brgyad brgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:6502: zhal phyag grangsa med par bsgom pa de mthar lam
NK076(mu)002:6503: lhun grub kyi spyod yul yin pa ltar rim para
NK076(mu)002:6504: ldan pa'o // gnyis pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstim pa /
NK076(mu)002:6505: gong bstan bzhin de ltar rim cig char gyi sgom thabs gnyis dang ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK076(mu)002:6506: dang po la zhugs par du slob tha ma mthar
NK076(mu)002:6507: phyin gyi bar du skabs su dam tshig gi dkyil
NK076(mu)002:6509: ye shes rang bzhin gyi yul 'og min nas snyan
NK076(mu)002:6510: gsan dbab spyan drangs par byas ta phyag rgya bzhis
NK076(mu)002:6511: gnyis su med par gzhug cing sku gsung thugs brtan
NK076(mu)002:6512: par bzhugs pa la sogs pa'i cho ga dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:6513: par byas la / gsum pa phrin las kyi rim pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6514: dang po phrin las gzhung gi rim pa /
NK076(mu)002:6515: de nas phyag 'tshal ba la sogs mchod rdzas dang
NK076(mu)002:6516: tshig sngags phyag rgya ting 'dzin rnams kyis rim pa
NK076(mu)002:6518: bstod pa bya zhing smon lam gdab pa dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:6519: nas bsnyen pa dzapra dang tshogs rnams gzhung bzhin bya'o
NK076(mu)002:6520: // gnyis pa lhag ma mjug gi rim pa /
NK076(mu)002:6521: nang nub thun mtshams kyi bar skabs su zhi khro
NK076(mu)002:6522: gang yin gyi lhag ma'i gnas la dbang rnams kyi
NK076(mu)002:6524: rang gis sngon dam bcas pa'i dam tshig bsgrags la phrin las bcol zhing /
NK076(mu)002:6525: ya hi gats+tshasa zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las la dgya brtan ma bskyong ngo //
NK076(mu)002:6526: de nas 'khor lo ste dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing lus
NK076(mu)002:6527: bsrung go bgo spyod lam rgyun gyi ting 'dzin la
NK076(mu)002:6528: gnas pa kun zhi khro gang yin gyi man ngaga
NK076(mu)002:6529: gi bsgom khog gzhung bazhana du bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6530: bzhi pa ngo bo la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6531: dang po ngo bo rang snang yul med zhi gnas lhag mthong zung 'brel du /
NK076(mu)002:6532: phung po khams skye mched la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs
NK076(mu)002:6533: thams cad zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gyi lhar snang ba
NK076(mu)002:6534: yang / dpe rgya mtsho'i nang du gzugs brnyan snang ba ci bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:6535: snod bcud phung khams skye mched kyi chos kun gyi
NK076(mu)002:6536: dngos po yang rang rig pa zhi khro'i lhar gsal
NK076(mu)002:6537: ba rnams gcig dang du ma yongas gyi mtha' dang
NK076(mu)002:6539: rig pa lhar gasla ba la yul yul can gang du'ang zhen pa med pas lhag mthong /
NK076(mu)002:6540: de'i ngang las mi g.yo basa zhi gnas /
NK076(mu)002:6541: zung 'brel bsgom bya'i rnal 'byor ting 'dzin gyi ngo bora rgyal bas bka' rgyud kun nas gsungs so //
NK076(mu)002:6542: gnyis pa rnam grangs spros pa /
NK076(mu)002:6543: rtog tshogs rang bzhin gyis lhar gnas pa spros pas
NK076(mu)002:6544: nyams su len pa'i rnal 'byor ting 'dzin yang lha
NK076(mu)002:6545: du mar spros / lha de yang gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i ngo la khro bo dang /
NK076(mu)002:6546: zhi ba gnyis su spros so //
NK076(mu)002:6547: de re re la'ang 'khor lo dkyil 'khor spros pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6548: phyag rgya rnam grangsa spros pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6551: de ltar gzhi lam tshul kun nas spros pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:6552: na mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu'ang yi ge 'khor
NK076(mu)002:6553: lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa ste de'ang sku
NK076(mu)002:6554: dang ye shes du mar spros pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6555: gsum pa nges tshig bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:6556: de ltar spros pas nyams su myong zhing gsal ba
NK076(mu)002:6557: ni rgya spros rnal 'byor sgra don nam nges tshig
NK076(mu)002:6558: 'grub pa'o // lnga pa skyon la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:6559: dang po le lo la zhugs pa dang mtshan ma la zhen pa'i skyon /
NK076(mu)002:6560: spros pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas pa 'di yi tsha snyom las su le lo dang /
NK076(mu)002:6561: mi dge ba'i las bya ba ngan zhen gyi le lo rnam pa gnyis kyi skyon dang /
NK076(mu)002:6566: nyi ma sogs matshana ma lnga po dngos su 'byung
NK076(mu)002:6567: ba mthong zhing de la yang dag tu 'dzin na
NK076(mu)002:6569: gnyis pa bdud kyi spyod yul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6570: dang po nye bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:6571: rgya spros rnal 'byor pas grub rtags kyi spyod yul
NK076(mu)002:6572: la dam par bzung ste zhen na bdud kyi spyod
NK076(mu)002:6573: yul bco brgyad du mthong ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6575: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6576: dang po bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dngos /
NK076(mu)002:6577: dang po snang ba gzugs kyi bdud ni /
NK076(mu)002:6578: sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa grangs med 'jig rten du
NK076(mu)002:6579: 'gyed pa mthong ba dang gcig /gnyis pa 'du 'dzi
NK076(mu)002:6580: g.yeng ba'i bdud / bdag gzhan gyi nang nas dam par 'dug pa mthong ba'am /
NK076(mu)002:6581: yang na sangs rgyas byang sems kyis dam par 'dun cing dam par mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6582: gsum pa grags pa sgra yi bdud sangs rgyas byang
NK076(mu)002:6583: sems kyis bdag la skyes bu dam para smra ba
NK076(mu)002:6584: dang / bzhi pa bar chad g.yeng ba'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6585: rgyal bas gsungsa pa'i bstan pa mdo sngags kun gasla
NK076(mu)002:6586: bar mthonga zhing thos pa med par 'chad nus pa
NK076(mu)002:6587: dang / lnga pa mngon shes log pa'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6588: skad cig gcig la dus gsum gyi chos thams cad gsal bar shes shing mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6589: drug pa skye gnas la zhen pa'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6590: rgyud drug gi lam dang gnas kun mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6591: bdun pa snying rje sprul pa'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6592: sems can da dag la snying rje'i sems rang dbang med pa shugs kyis 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6593: brgyad pa snang ba 'od kyi bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6594: phyi nang gi snod bcud kun kyang nyin mtshan med par gsal bar mthonga ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6595: dgu pa rdzu 'phrul ston pa spyod pa'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6596: ri brag la sogs ci la'ang bdag gi lus thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6597: bcu pa nga rgyal dregs pa'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6598: nam mkha' la sa la byed pa bzhin du 'phur nas 'gro zhing 'adug nus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6599: bcu gcig pa byin gyis brlab pa'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6600: rgyal bas phyag brkyangs nas bdag gi mgo lus byugs te sangs rgyas par lung ston pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6601: bcu gnyis pa bslu ba rdzun gyi bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6602: lha klu la sogs 'gro ba kun gya so so'i
NK076(mu)002:6603: skad du bdag gis chos smra zhing ston nus pa
NK076(mu)002:6605: bcu gsum pa mtshan mas g.yeng ba'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6606: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad kyis bdag la bkur sti dang rim gro'i gansa su mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6607: bcu bzhi pa re dogs the tshom bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6608: ting nge 'dzin gyi shugs la stong gsum thams cad
NK076(mu)002:6609: mtho dman med par lag mthil ltar mnyam par bkod
NK076(mu)002:6610: pa dang / bco lnga pa chags ba gegs byas kyi bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6611: stong gsum de nyid kyi rang bazhana skyu ru ra
NK076(mu)002:6612: lag mthil du bzhag pa ltar gsal bar snang ba
NK076(mu)002:6613: dang / bcu drug pa don du mi 'gyur bar gol ba'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6614: sems ting 'dzin lasa su rung basa bdag gzhan gyi
NK076(mu)002:6615: don spyod pa ci la'ang thogsa pa med par spyod
NK076(mu)002:6617: bcu bdun pa che ba'i nga rgyal snyam pa'i bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6618: dam pa'i chos ston pa'i don la rtogs pa dang
NK076(mu)002:6619: mos par gyis shig ces sangs rgyas byang sems kyis
NK076(mu)002:6620: bdag la bka' bsgo ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6621: bco brgyad pa bkur sti bar chad kyi bdud /
NK076(mu)002:6622: 'jig rten pa'i gtso bo lha chen po rnams kyis
NK076(mu)002:6623: bdag la mchod pa 'byung ba dang bco brgyad po
NK076(mu)002:6625: 'di yan chad nas thod rgal 'ong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6626: blo rab 'bring tha ma la nges pa med pas /
NK076(mu)002:6629: tha ma rmi lam du 'ong ngo //
NK076(mu)002:6630: gnyis pa de rang bzhin med par shes na grub rtags /
NK076(mu)002:6631: rnal 'byor pa gang gis spyod yul bco brgyad po de dag mthong ba'i dus na /
NK076(mu)002:6632: de dag la rang bzhin med par rang snang gnyis med du rtogs na /
NK076(mu)002:6633: lam ma nor bar dam pa grub pa' rtags yin no //
NK076(mu)002:6634: gsum pa mi shes dga' brod byed na bdud du gyur tshul bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:6635: de ltar sems kyi chos nyid rang snang du ma
NK076(mu)002:6636: shesa par grub rtags dam par bzung nas dga' brod
NK076(mu)002:6637: rloms sems byed pa rnams badud kyi bar chad kyi
NK076(mu)002:6638: las su gyur pas na bdud kyi spyod yul yin
NK076(mu)002:6639: te / de ci'i phyir zhe na 'jig rten gyi
NK076(mu)002:6640: khe dang snyan grags thob par 'dod pas sems rang
NK076(mu)002:6642: gzhan gyis bdag la skyes bu dam par basngagasa pa
NK076(mu)002:6643: bstod pa'i che ba thoba nasa 'du 'dzi dang longs
NK076(mu)002:6644: spyod kyi mtshan mas g.yeng ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6645: 'bras bu thob tu re ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6646: ma thob kyi gol du dogs pa cung zada yod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6647: rtags byung bang tsam du'am nga zhes pas sems kheng
NK076(mu)002:6648: sa che bas nga rgyal 'phel nas g.yeng shor ba'o
NK076(mu)002:6649: // gsum pa thun mong gi skyon phra ba byung tshul /
NK076(mu)002:6650: thun mong gi skyon tha mal pa yang sngar bas
NK076(mu)002:6651: 'dir grangs nyung bar 'byung la ngo bo shin tu
NK076(mu)002:6653: dbugs kyi rgyu ba'i skad cig gi nang du ting
NK076(mu)002:6654: 'dzin gzung 'dzin gyi dbang du song ma song bye
NK076(mu)002:6656: drug pa skyon bcos thabs la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:6657: dang po le lo'i skyon bcos thabs /
NK076(mu)002:6658: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba dang rkyen 'jug pa'i ting 'dzin gnyis dbang 'byor bas /
NK076(mu)002:6659: 'ag nyams thob cing lta sgom zung du 'brel bas
NK076(mu)002:6660: nyams len la bskyed rim byer med pa'am tshogs lam
NK076(mu)002:6662: snang stong dbyer med 'bras bu lha'i dkyil 'khor lam
NK076(mu)002:6663: du shes shing ting 'dzin la blo brtan par gyur
NK076(mu)002:6664: pa yis / le lo gnyis po'i dbang du mi
NK076(mu)002:6665: gtang bar 'bras bu thob pa'i rtsol ba'i bya ba
NK076(mu)002:6666: pa yis / med cing / don yal bar dor
NK076(mu)002:6667: ba mada pa'i brtson 'grus dang du blang bar bya'o
NK076(mu)002:6668: pa yis / med cing / // gnyis pa matshana
NK076(mu)002:6669: ma'i skyon bcos thabs dpe dang bcas smig rgyu la
NK076(mu)002:6670: sogs lnga mtshan ma ci byung rang rig pa'i cha
NK076(mu)002:6672: de dag sems nyid yin par shes pa'i phyir mtshan
NK076(mu)002:6673: ma de dag mthong ba la 'bras bu thob tu
NK076(mu)002:6674: re ba dang / ma thob pa'i dogs pa med
NK076(mu)002:6675: par shes par gyis shig /dper na nam mkha'i ranga
NK076(mu)002:6676: bzhin de la nyi zla gza' skar dang glog 'agyu
NK076(mu)002:6677: re ba dang / ba dang / 'aja'a tshon shar
NK076(mu)002:6678: ba sprin mang po phan tshun du 'khrugs par 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:6679: yang nam mkha'i rang bzhin nam dbyings de la gzhan
NK076(mu)002:6680: du 'gyur zhing nyams pa med pa'i dpe bzhin no
NK076(mu)002:6681: re ba dang / ba dang / // don sems
NK076(mu)002:6682: nyid mi dmigs pa chosa kyi dbyis nyid gdul bya'i
NK076(mu)002:6683: blo la bsam yas para 'das pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK076(mu)002:6684: yon tan phrin las rmad du byung ba ngo mtshar
NK076(mu)002:6686: nyams kyi mtshan ma bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad
NK076(mu)002:6687: la sogs sna tshogas pa rnam 'byor pa'i nyams la
NK076(mu)002:6689: chos nyid de bzhina nyid la nyams shing 'gyur ba med par shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6690: gsum pa bdud kyi spyod yul gyi skyon bcos thabs /
NK076(mu)002:6691: spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa ting 'dzin gyi stobs dang
NK076(mu)002:6692: yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogsa par 'gyur yang
NK076(mu)002:6693: / gang zag dang chos kyi bdag gnyis med para shes pas nga rgyal dang rloms sems med de /
NK076(mu)002:6694: bdud kyi spyod yul du rtags dang mtshan ma yi bye brag gang mthonga ba de yang /
NK076(mu)002:6695: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes su rang snang
NK076(mu)002:6696: ba nyid du lta bas shes shing ting 'dzin gyis
NK076(mu)002:6697: rgyud la sbyar bas re dogs mi bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6700: rtog pa'i snang ba lha'i snang bar 'byed pa phyag
NK076(mu)002:6701: rgya spros pa'ang nyams gong nas gong du 'phel bar
NK076(mu)002:6703: gong bstan ltar bslab pa'i rim pa snga ma goms
NK076(mu)002:6704: nas phyi ma slob pa ji bzhina nyams 'phel te
NK076(mu)002:6705: / rgya gcig nyams lnga sngon du brtan cing mthar
NK076(mu)002:6706: phyin mod kyang rgya spros pa 'adi la da gzod
NK076(mu)002:6708: sngar snang 'byed spros pa la ma goms pa'i dbang gisa nyams rnam pa lnga 'byung ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6709: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la nyams lnga rim pa skye tshul /
NK076(mu)002:6710: rigs sam tshom bu gsum pa dang lnga pa'i lha
NK076(mu)002:6711: gsal ba'i tshe rtog pa'i dbang du cung zad g.yo
NK076(mu)002:6712: bas / ting 'dzin la rtog pa'i bar chad 'byung
NK076(mu)002:6713: ba de nyams lnga'i dang pa g.yo ba'i nyams yin
NK076(mu)002:6714: pa' //lha da gsal ba'i tshad la nyin zhag phrugs
NK076(mu)002:6715: gcig la thun gcig gi bazhir bgos pa'i cha gcig
NK076(mu)002:6716: tsam skyon dbang 'gyur zhing cha gsum tsam du lha
NK076(mu)002:6717: gsal la rtog pas mi g.yo ba de ni gnyis
NK076(mu)002:6718: pa thob pa'i nyams yin ta /
NK076(mu)002:6719: rkyen med na rtog pa med par thun rkyang gcig
NK076(mu)002:6720: bsgom nus pa ni gsum pa goms pa'i nyams yin
NK076(mu)002:6721: pa'o // thun rkyang gcig bsgom nus pa de nyid
NK076(mu)002:6722: rtog pa'i rkyen dbang du mi 'agro zhing lhar gsal
NK076(mu)002:6723: ba de ni bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams yin pa'o
NK076(mu)002:6724: pa'o // // de nas nyin zhag gam dus phyed par ting 'dzin la gang gnas pa de la /
NK076(mu)002:6725: shin tu yang rtog pa'i rkyen gyis mi 'phrog pa
NK076(mu)002:6726: ni nyams lnga pa ste mthar phyin pa'i nyams so
NK076(mu)002:6727: // gsum pa rnam grangs spros pa la sbyar bas brtsad pa'i skyon spang ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:6728: stong dang nyi khri la sogs pa rnam grangs spros
NK076(mu)002:6729: pa la nyams lnga po de dag sbyar na zag
NK076(mu)002:6730: med mthong bsgom mthar lam gsum gyi rig 'dzin du
NK076(mu)002:6731: thal bar 'gyur ba'i skyon yod pa /
NK076(mu)002:6732: de bas na rtsa ba'i rnam grangs dang zhi khro'i
NK076(mu)002:6733: tshom bu dang dkyil 'khor la nyamsa lnga sbyar ba'i
NK076(mu)002:6735: brgyad pa spyod pa la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:6736: lta dgongs chos nyid kyi spyod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6737: rmad byung thabs kyi spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:6738: khyad par chogs kyi spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6740: dang po lta dgongs nyam nga med par spyod pa dpe dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:6741: rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor chen po'i lta ba las mi 'da' ba'i spyod pa'i tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:6742: 'dod yon la ca ltar spyad kyang lta bas ranga bzhin meda par shes pas /
NK076(mu)002:6743: dper na nam mkha' la bya chena khyung ldinga ba bzhin du g.yang mi za /
NK076(mu)002:6744: chu la rkyal chena 'phyo ba nya mo bzhin nyam nga med /
NK076(mu)002:6745: nam mkha' la rlung chen 'phyo ba la thogs chags med pa bzhin tu /
NK076(mu)002:6746: rgya spros rnal 'byor pas lta ba yang dpe gsum po de bzhin ltar /
NK076(mu)002:6749: thogs pa med par blta zhing spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6750: gnyis pa lta ba'i don las mi 'da' pas ci spyod tshogs gnyis rdzogs par sbyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:6751: rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor chena po'i sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:6752: lta bas zin pa'i chos spyad bya'i yul thams cada
NK076(mu)002:6753: kun la spyad bya spyod byed dbyer mada par spyod
NK076(mu)002:6754: pas / snang ba ma 'gags pa bade ba'i ro mchog chen po myong bar 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)002:6755: de la rnal 'byor pa su zhiga zhen pa dang chags par mi byed do //
NK076(mu)002:6756: spyad bya'i yul ma 'gags par spyod bzhin du de
NK076(mu)002:6757: la ma chagas shing mi 'dzin pas ye shes kyi
NK076(mu)002:6759: spyad pas bde ba yi ra mchog myong ba nyid
NK076(mu)002:6760: ma 'gags pa bsod nams kyi tshogas su 'gyur ba'o
NK076(mu)002:6761: // de ltar tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa de lta bu
NK076(mu)002:6762: yi ngang 'ba' zhig tu spyad bya'i yul thams cad
NK076(mu)002:6763: // la spyod pas / 'di ni tshogs gnyis cig
NK076(mu)002:6764: char du rdzogs pa'i spyod pa rlabs chen yana no
NK076(mu)002:6765: // la spyod pas / // gsum pa lta spyod 'brel bar gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:6766: lta ba spyod pa ya chara ma gyur te lta spyod 'brel bar /
NK076(mu)002:6767: sngags 'achanga lam pa rnams kyis dus rtag tu spyod par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6768: gnyis pa rmad byung thabs kyi spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:6772: 'dod yon lnga ste lnga tshan bzhi po ni theg pa 'og mas spang bar bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6773: smad par bya ba'i spyod pa ma lus ba kun /
NK076(mu)002:6774: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi don rang gzhan gyi don
NK076(mu)002:6775: phyir bkag pa med par 'jola nyog tu sbyad de
NK076(mu)002:6776: / lnga bzhi la sogs ganga yanga ma 'gags par
NK076(mu)002:6777: spyod par byas la 'dzin chags med pas ma thogas
NK076(mu)002:6778: / shing / dbyer med du spyod pas tshogs gnyis su 'gyur ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:6779: pad+ma 'dam nas skyes kyang 'dam skyon gyis ma gos
NK076(mu)002:6780: bzhin du gong gi spyod pa nyes pas ma gos
NK076(mu)002:6781: par thabs la mkhas pas spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6782: gsum pa khyad par tshogs kyi spyod pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6783: spyod yul lha'i dkyil 'khor du spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:6784: 'dod yon snang ba lhar bsgom nas spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:6785: stong khams srid tshad kyi shes rab yum dang 'dod
NK076(mu)002:6786: yon rnams la rab 'bring tha mar spyod tshul lo
NK076(mu)002:6791: dang po spyod byed ye shes sam yab tu bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:6792: yan lag lnga dang dbang pa lnga dang rnam shes
NK076(mu)002:6793: tshogs brgyad po kun rang rig rang snang bar shes
NK076(mu)002:6794: pas / de dag rnam pa rang ga ma min te /
NK076(mu)002:6795: mtshan med ltar na gyis mtshon nas ye shes lnga'i don du lta bas shes par bya /
NK076(mu)002:6796: mtshan bcas ltar na zhi ba rjogs pa'i yab kyi dkyil 'khora nyid du bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:6797: zhi ba la dgar bas yang na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:6798: gnyis pa spyad bya dbyings sam yum du bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:6803: rega bya la sogs pa yul gyi rtogs pa kun /
NK076(mu)002:6804: rnam pa rang ga ma mina te mtshan med ltar
NK076(mu)002:6805: na yi ge m+aum du mtshon pa mnyam pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:6806: kyi dbyings su shesa par bya /
NK076(mu)002:6807: 'dir mtshan bcas lta ngan zhi ba yuma gyi dkyil
NK076(mu)002:6808: 'khor nyid du bsgom zhi ba la dgar bas yang
NK076(mu)002:6809: na khro mo yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgama
NK076(mu)002:6811: mdor na spyod lam gyi yul 'di ltar du snang
NK076(mu)002:6812: ba thams cad lha dang lha mor gsal bas lha
NK076(mu)002:6814: chos nyid la chos nyid rol ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6815: gnyis pa 'dod yon la spyod thabs la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:6816: dang po 'dod yon snang ba lhar shes nas bsgom pa dngos /
NK076(mu)002:6817: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya la sogs pa'i 'dod yon lnga po thams cad dang /
NK076(mu)002:6818: gzhan yang rdzogs pa sna tshogs su snang ba thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:6819: 'bras bu de bzhin gshegsa pa'i rang bzhin rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK076(mu)002:6820: gzugs mdzes pa'i lha mo la sogs 'dod yon gyi lha dang lha mor brtag go //
NK076(mu)002:6821: gnyis pa 'dod yon la spyod pa'i rtog pa lhar
NK076(mu)002:6822: dag pa'i spyod yul thams cad kun tu bzang por
NK076(mu)002:6823: dag pa / rtog pa thams cad spyod yul lhar
NK076(mu)002:6824: dag pa kun tu bzang po yi rang bzhin du
NK076(mu)002:6825: dag pa / zhes pas / 'dod pa'i yona tan
NK076(mu)002:6826: lnga po rnams thams cad la thogsa pa dang 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:6827: chags med par ma 'gags par spyod par byas te
NK076(mu)002:6828: dag pa / zhes pas / / de kho nas
NK076(mu)002:6829: bsod nams kyi tshogs chena po yan par brtag go
NK076(mu)002:6830: dag pa / zhes pas / / // yang na
NK076(mu)002:6831: der ma zad 'dod yon lnga po de bzhina gshegs
NK076(mu)002:6832: pa rigs lngara yang brtag cing shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6833: gsum pa stong khams srid tshad kyi shes rab yum dang 'dod yon la spyod tshul /
NK076(mu)002:6834: spyod yul 'di las gzhan pa yang stong gsum gyi
NK076(mu)002:6835: khams thams cad na gnas pa'i shesa rab dbyings ma
NK076(mu)002:6836: yum dang 'dod yana lnga po thams cad rnams la
NK076(mu)002:6837: / bzang ngan rab 'bring tha ma thams cad kun la blang dor med par spyad do //
NK076(mu)002:6838: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6840: zag ldog yod pa'i phyir ma bsrungs pa'i skyon no //
NK076(mu)002:6843: gzhan don du gang 'tshams ltar bsrung ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6845: rim dang cig char ba'i da ma tshig go //
NK076(mu)002:6847: dang po mi spang zhing dang du blang ba'i dam
NK076(mu)002:6848: tshig dang du blang ba dam rdzas lnga dang mi
NK076(mu)002:6849: spang ba nyon mongs lnga po kun kyang /
NK076(mu)002:6850: spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa yis dus rtag tu spyad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6851: spyad pa de la chags shing zhen pa med para gyur pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6852: yon tan gang 'byung na mchog thun dngos grub ngo mtshar ba ya mtshan chen pa 'byung ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:6853: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga mdo tsam du bashada pa rgyas pa'i nga gsum pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:6854: le lag gi nyer bdun pa'i nang nas 'byung ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6855: gnyis pa spyod lam kun la spros pa'i rnal 'byor las mi 'da' bar bsrung ba /
