NK076(mu)002:6856: dbang po'i spyod yul du mthong thosa thams cad kun dang /
NK076(mu)002:6857: 'agro ba dang 'dug pa dang nyal ba la sogs pa'i tshe na /
NK076(mu)002:6858: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis bsgom pa spros bcas kyi
NK076(mu)002:6859: rnal 'byor las ma nyamsa par ting 'dzin de ya
NK076(mu)002:6860: dbyings na gnas par lam pa'i shes rab kyi dbang
NK076(mu)002:6861: bo mchog dang ldan pa dag gis dus rtag tu
NK076(mu)002:6862: spyod par bya'o // gnyis pa cig char ba'i dam
NK076(mu)002:6863: tshig /rim gyis dam tshig las yang na cig char
NK076(mu)002:6864: ba'i dam tshiga 'og nas 'byung ba 'di lta bu
NK076(mu)002:6865: spyod par bya'o // rtogs na / thams cad dbyer
NK076(mu)002:6866: med spyod pa sgo gsum gyis ji ltar spyad kyang
NK076(mu)002:6867: rig 'dzin sngags kyi sdom pa las mi 'da' ba
NK076(mu)002:6868: spyod par bya'o // rtogs na / yin no // ji ltar mi 'da' zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:6869: chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus par lha'i dkyil
NK076(mu)002:6870: 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas par rtogs pa la
NK076(mu)002:6871: / 'bras bu bsgrub cing dam tshig bsrung bar bya ba med de /
NK076(mu)002:6872: de bsrungs pa las dge ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6873: ma bsrungs pas mi dge ba'i rnam smin gnyis ka
NK076(mu)002:6874: dbye ru med pa rmi lam ltar rtogs tsa na
NK076(mu)002:6875: / ye nas dbyer med du sangs rgyas pa de
NK076(mu)002:6876: la dam tshig bsrung rgyu rdul phra mo tsam yang
NK076(mu)002:6877: / meda do // gnyis pa gzhan don gang ltar 'tshams pa cig char ba'i bsrung ba /
NK076(mu)002:6878: gzhan don bya ba'i phyir rgyud las grags pa'i rtsa
NK076(mu)002:6879: ba yan lag gi bsrung bya yi dam tshig kun
NK076(mu)002:6880: / gdul bya ganga la mos pa ltar blo dang
NK076(mu)002:6881: 'tshams par 'da' bar mi byed par srungs shig gnyis
NK076(mu)002:6882: pa zag ldog yod pa'i phyir ma bsrungs pa'i skyon
NK076(mu)002:6883: / / ston pa rda rja sems dpa'i bkas bshad
NK076(mu)002:6884: pa'i sdom pa'i rtsa ba lnga dang yan lag gi
NK076(mu)002:6885: dam tshig thams cad kun gzhung nas bshad pa'i lta
NK076(mu)002:6886: spyod dbyer med kyi de bzhin nyid du ni ma
NK076(mu)002:6887: bsrungs na skyon ji ltar 'byung zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:6888: dbang dus dam chu de yak+sha khro bo rdo rje
NK076(mu)002:6889: gnod spyin tsha ba me yi dbal lta bu lcags
NK076(mu)002:6890: kyi sdig pa can gyis khyod kyi snying la gnas
NK076(mu)002:6891: bcas nas snying rtsad nas drangs te khrag 'thung nasa
NK076(mu)002:6892: dus min tshe thung phyi ma ngana songa gsum du
NK076(mu)002:6894: de yi sdug bsngal tsha grang bkres skom glen lkugs
NK076(mu)002:6895: sogs bzod pa'i glags ni tshad bzung du med do
NK076(mu)002:6896: // dam tshig nyams na ngan song ltung ba da yi phyir /
NK076(mu)002:6897: de kun gcig spros kyi tshogs lam bzhir 'khor bar
NK076(mu)002:6898: ldog cing ngan song du ltung ba'i zag pa gsum
NK076(mu)002:6901: phyi'i drod lus shing bal gyi 'dab ma lta bur shin tu yang /
NK076(mu)002:6902: nang gi drod dbugs phyi nang gnyis kyi rgyu ba yun ring du bral ba dang //
NK076(mu)002:6903: gsang ba sems kyi drod rnal 'byor pa'i ting 'dzin mkha' la gza' skar shar ba bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:6904: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor ma 'dres par gsal ba lhag mthong yin la /
NK076(mu)002:6905: rtogs pa'i mthar mi g.yo ba zhi gnas /
NK076(mu)002:6906: bsgom bya sgom byed kyi spyod yul du zhen pa med par zhi lhag zung 'jug gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6907: drod gsum de'i zhara las 'byung ba'i drod kun kyang tshogs lam chen po 'dir rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:6908: 'di tsam zhes grangsa kyis bgrang ba'i cha lasa 'adsa te mang bar 'byung ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6909: bcu gcig pa rtags la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6911: spros pa'i ting 'dzin lasa su rung ba'i rtagsa rnams kyang /
NK076(mu)002:6912: sngon rgya gcig la byung bar bstan pa rnams 'dir
NK076(mu)002:6913: de rnams las stobs su gyur pas 'aphala ba dang
NK076(mu)002:6914: / lus khams bde mi bde snyomsa shing ranga gi
NK076(mu)002:6915: lus bad basa gang ba shin tu rgyas pa dang
NK076(mu)002:6916: / / nang 'adu ba rnam bazha dang bral bas na tsha la bzod pa thoba pa /
NK076(mu)002:6917: sngar bas tshab cha ba 'byung ngo //
NK076(mu)002:6919: sngon gnas dran pa sogs mngon par shes pa drug dang /
NK076(mu)002:6920: dbang shes kyang sgo re res kyang yul lnga lnga gcod pas rtsa lnga'i grangs kyi mngon shes rdzogs /
NK076(mu)002:6921: spros pa'i blo'i mngon shes rab 'bring gi cha yis
NK076(mu)002:6922: phye bas yul khams tshun chad dang gling gciga tsam
NK076(mu)002:6923: tshun chad kyi yul gsal bar mthong zhing de nyid
NK076(mu)002:6924: kyi gdul bya 'dul bar byed do //
NK076(mu)002:6925: de rgyu ci las byung zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:6926: 'jug pa'i rnam shes tshogs drug rang rgyud tha dad
NK076(mu)002:6927: du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dag cing dwangs pa'i stobs
NK076(mu)002:6930: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyi bya ba
NK076(mu)002:6931: nyi shu po yang rab 'bring gi cha yis g.yo
NK076(mu)002:6932: ba dang thob pa tsam 'byung ba rung ngo //
NK076(mu)002:6933: de yang mdo'i le'u bcu drug pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:6935: las kyi chos 'phrul gnyis las 'di ni dang po'o //
NK076(mu)002:6936: lha klu gnod sbyin sogs 'gro ba thams cada la
NK076(mu)002:6937: rang rang gi skad du mthun par chos ston nus
NK076(mu)002:6938: pa rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul /
NK076(mu)002:6939: mngon shes kyi yul tshun chad sa gayasa 'byung ba
NK076(mu)002:6940: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul ston par byed pa dang
NK076(mu)002:6941: / bdag gis sngags brjod pa kun ya ge yi
NK076(mu)002:6942: sgrar snang nas gsang sngags brjod par byed pa kun
NK076(mu)002:6944: bzhi pa mthong snang la re dogs mi bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:6945: de ltar cho 'phrul bzhi 'di dag mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:6946: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang /
NK076(mu)002:6947: glang chen zhon dang grur zhugs sogs shugsa la snang
NK076(mu)002:6948: ba brgyad mthong ba'ang re ba dang dogs pa'i rtog
NK076(mu)002:6950: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:6951: dang po rmi lam snga ma dang mthun cing rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:6952: spros pa'i skabs 'dir rmi lam mtshan ma rgya gcig
NK076(mu)002:6953: pa dang chos mthun pa ste ngo bo gcig par
NK076(mu)002:6954: rmi ltas bcu bzhi 'byung ba yin no //
NK076(mu)002:6955: 'o na khyad med dam zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:6957: gtan par gyur pas khyad phye ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:6958: rgyud kun las mtshan ma bzang po'i ltas su rgyal bas lung bstan pa kun /
NK076(mu)002:6959: tshogs lam chen po spros pa'i skabs 'dir thams cad rdzogs par 'byung ba yina no //
NK076(mu)002:6960: gnyis pa rmis ltas kun 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:6961: de dag rdzogs pa'i rgyu mtshan ni tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:6962: 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa'i rmi ltas spros pa'i
NK076(mu)002:6964: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid rig 'dzin rnams
NK076(mu)002:6965: kyi dngos sam brgyud pa'i rigs kyi rgyu yin pa'i
NK076(mu)002:6966: phyir ro // mthar phyin rig 'dzin rnams kyi mtshan
NK076(mu)002:6967: ma rmi ltas bzang po thams cad 'byung ba'i sa
NK076(mu)002:6969: der ma zad bar chad med par tshogsa sgrub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:6970: skabs su'ang mtshan ma rmi ltas 'di kho na 'byung
NK076(mu)002:6971: ba gsal brtan gyi khyad par yod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:6972: bcu gsum pa phan yon bstan pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:6973: dang po rtog tshogs lhar gsal ba /
NK076(mu)002:6974: gzugs sogs phung po lnga nyid de bzhina gshegs pa rigs lnga /
NK076(mu)002:6975: sa sogs 'byung ba lnga po nyid ni rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:6976: mig sogs dbang po bzhi dang rnam shes bzhi ni phyi nang gi byang chub semas dpa' brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:6977: mig gi yul gzugs sogs bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)002:6978: 'das pa sogs dus bzhi ni byang chub sems ma chen mo brgyad yin no //
NK076(mu)002:6979: bdag tu rtog pa rags pa las skyes pa'i lus
NK076(mu)002:6980: kyi chos rnam pa bzhi po khro bo bzhi yin
NK076(mu)002:6981: / rtag chad bdag mtshan mu bzhi khra ma bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:6982: shu gas la yid chos kun bzang yab yum /
NK076(mu)002:6983: nyon drug thub drug yin pa' //gnyis pa lha sems nyid rang snang du rtogs nas bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:6984: rtog tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba de yang sems
NK076(mu)002:6985: rang gi rig pa nyid lha dang lha mo'i dkyil
NK076(mu)002:6986: 'khor du snang ba yin ces bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:6987: da bzhin du rtog pa lhar mnyam par rdzogas pa
NK076(mu)002:6988: la 'bras bu kun lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags de
NK076(mu)002:6989: bzhin gshegas pa lnga dang don ye shes lnga nyid
NK076(mu)002:6990: rgyu rkyen med par rang byung chena po'i ngang la
NK076(mu)002:6991: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar bsgom
NK076(mu)002:6992: pa'o // gsum pa bsgoms pa'i yon tan spyod yul dag cing cir yang 'grub par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:6993: bzang ngan nam gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa gnyid dang
NK076(mu)002:6994: bral ba'i spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa thabs mkhas pa
NK076(mu)002:6995: nyid kyis / rtog tshogs thams cad zhi khro'i lha
NK076(mu)002:6996: ru gsal bas lha de yang dngos po rang rgyud
NK076(mu)002:6999: rna bas sgra thos pa la sogs rang rgyud pa med pa'i tshul gyis /
NK076(mu)002:7000: rang gi rig pa'i ye shes lhar gsal bar bsgom pa'i dus na /
NK076(mu)002:7001: don dam lha'i rang bzhin cir yang grub pa med
NK076(mu)002:7002: par gsal ba las kun rdzob ji ltar bsam par
NK076(mu)002:7003: snang bas cir yang 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7004: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la gnyis //
NK076(mu)002:7005: dang po 'da' tshul yon tan dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:7006: spros pa'i rnal 'byor gang zhig 'chi ba'i rkyen gyis
NK076(mu)002:7007: spyod yul 'gyur zhing tshe 'pho ba'i dus byung na
NK076(mu)002:7008: / rgya spros zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor tshom bu bsgom
NK076(mu)002:7009: pa gang yin dran pas bzung nas bsgoms pa yis
NK076(mu)002:7010: / / rang rgyud kyi las ngana pa ngan 'gro'i lam gyi zhena pa'i blo rgyun bcad nas /
NK076(mu)002:7011: srid pa bar ma do' ma tshe phyi mar blo chung rnam smin dang /
NK076(mu)002:7012: che na tshe dbang gnyis la sbyor te mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin thob pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7013: gnyis pa nus pa zhan cing bsgom pa'i skabs med
NK076(mu)002:7014: kyang gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu 'byung bar bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:7015: / rnal 'byor pa blo chung ba gang zhig ting
NK076(mu)002:7016: 'dzin brtson 'grus kyi nus pa zhan pas 'da' ka
NK076(mu)002:7017: ma'i ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i skabs meda par tshe 'pho
NK076(mu)002:7019: sngar gyi ting 'dzin gyis 'phen pa'i 'brel ba spros
NK076(mu)002:7020: bcas bsgom pa'i sa bon rgyud la yod pa'i rkyen
NK076(mu)002:7021: gyis / tsha rabas skye ba phyi mar kun tu
NK076(mu)002:7022: bde 'gro lha mi'i go 'phang khyad par can thob
NK076(mu)002:7023: nas dkon mchog gsum 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7024: dus dang gnas kyis mi bkola bar gsang sngags kyi
NK076(mu)002:7025: lam la spyod pas 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa'o
NK076(mu)002:7026: // bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7027: dang po gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:7028: rnal 'byor pa gang gis snyom las kyi le lo med par brtson 'grus cher byas na /
NK076(mu)002:7029: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam gyi rig
NK076(mu)002:7030: 'dzin gnyis gang rung zhig thob par gyur pa yang
NK076(mu)002:7031: / gang gi stobs kyis thob ce na chos nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7032: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams par bsrung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7033: rkyen smon lam rnam dag btab pa'i mthu dang /
NK076(mu)002:7034: sgrub pa'i cha rkyen gyi yan lag cho ga lnga /
NK076(mu)002:7036: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pasa bsgrubs na mthong lam rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7037: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:7038: zhi khro phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i ting
NK076(mu)002:7039: 'dzin yang nas yang du rgyun chags par bsgom pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7040: bsoda nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7041: longs spyod kyis / mun pa ma spangs par snang
NK076(mu)002:7042: ba dang dug ma spangs sman du 'gyur pa'i tshul
NK076(mu)002:7043: longs spyod kyis / ji bzhin du / rtog tshogs
NK076(mu)002:7044: ma spangs bar 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su
NK076(mu)002:7045: gsal bas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa
NK076(mu)002:7046: mchog brnyes pa ste thob pa ni phyogs mthun gyi
NK076(mu)002:7047: longs spyod kyis / ji bzhin du / 'bras bu'o // nye sbyor ni /
NK076(mu)002:7049: blo chung na tshogs sgrub thob pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7050: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:7051: zhi khro'i lha sku phyag rgya du mar spros nas /
NK076(mu)002:7052: bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor ting 'dzin la bslab pa'i thabs ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams /
NK076(mu)002:7053: mtshams dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u zhes bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:7054: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK076(mu)002:7055: 'dir yas bsgrangs drug pa'i don du gda' 'o ////spyi
NK076(mu)002:7056: don gnyis pa bar chad med par tshogs sgrub pa
NK076(mu)002:7057: la gsum ste / dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:7058: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor spros bcas gnyis la rtogs shing goms pas phyag btsal nas /
NK076(mu)002:7059: lam zag bcas zag med la sbyor ba'i gang gis
NK076(mu)002:7060: kyang bar chad med para zag med mthong lam rig
NK076(mu)002:7061: 'dzin la sbyor bar byed pa yi /
NK076(mu)002:7062: tshogs sgrub pa spros mthar phyin pa'i dus kyi rjes
NK076(mu)002:7063: thog tu sbyor lam tshom bu tshagas sgrub pa bashada
NK076(mu)002:7064: par bya / gnyis pa gzhung don la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7065: dang po spyir bsnyen sgrub bzhi tshogs sgrub kyi skabs 'dir shes par gdams pa /
NK076(mu)002:7066: de la sbyor lam bar chad mada pa'i lam du zhi khro'i tshogs sgrub par byed pa'ang /
NK076(mu)002:7067: bsnyen pa dang ni nya ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7068: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK076(mu)002:7069: bsnyen sgrub bzhi po'i don rdzogs par tshogs sgrub pa'i skabas 'dir shes para bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7070: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhi bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK076(mu)002:7073: bsnyen sgrub bzhi po 'di yang lam dus kyi bsnyen sgrub dang /
NK076(mu)002:7075: de'i cha rkyen sbyor ba yi bsnyen sgrub bzhi'o //
NK076(mu)002:7076: gnyis pa rgyas pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:7077: lam rim mjug gi bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)002:7078: sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi 'og mchod pa'i skabs su kha 'phang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7079: sgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi gtso bor bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7082: de ltar bsnyen sgrub bzhi cha gsum yod pa yi /
NK076(mu)002:7083: dang po lam gyi rim pa'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi'o //
NK076(mu)002:7084: de la bzhi yod pa'i dang po bsnyen pa na /
NK076(mu)002:7085: byang ba don dam dang chub pa kun rdzob sems
NK076(mu)002:7086: dbyer med kyi don rtogs shing ting 'dzin la brtson
NK076(mu)002:7088: grangs dus rtags kyi bsnyen pa gsum yod pa'i nang nas dam pa las chud mi za ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7089: 'grub sla ba yin pa'i phyir byang chub kyi sems
NK076(mu)002:7090: rtogs shing ting 'dzin chas phye bas de ting byang
NK076(mu)002:7091: ba kun ting snying rje chub pa gnyis goms pa
NK076(mu)002:7092: man chad bsnyen par brjod do //
NK076(mu)002:7094: de la brten nas lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po
NK076(mu)002:7095: du mar gsal ba ste bsgom pa ni 'og ma
NK076(mu)002:7096: bas 'bras bu la nye ba'i phyir nye ba'i bsnyen
NK076(mu)002:7097: pa yin pas na gtan tshigs de yi phyir zung
NK076(mu)002:7098: 'jug rgya gcig pa dang snang byed rgya spros gnyis
NK076(mu)002:7101: sgrub pa nyid ni sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam du tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7102: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po /
NK076(mu)002:7104: zhag sum cu phrag drug la sogs kyi dus kyi
NK076(mu)002:7105: tshogs sgrub pa'i mthas mtshan ma rtags kyi bsnyen pa
NK076(mu)002:7106: rdzogs nas sgrub pa chen po ni nub tha ma
NK076(mu)002:7108: des 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid mthong lam
NK076(mu)002:7109: du rnam smin tshe dbang gang thob kyi 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:7110: grub pa'o // gnyis pa sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi kha 'phang ba /
NK076(mu)002:7111: mdor bstan gyi gsum pa sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi
NK076(mu)002:7112: ni 'og khro bo'i gsang ba'i mchod pa'i skabs su
NK076(mu)002:7114: gsum pa sgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:7119: dang po sgrub thabs spyir bstan pa'i ngos nas mdor bstan /
NK076(mu)002:7120: mdor bstan gyi gnyis pa sgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi
NK076(mu)002:7121: gtso bor tshogs sgrub kyi skabs 'dir rgyas par bstan
NK076(mu)002:7122: pa ni / sgrub pa'i gzhi dang gzhung dag gis tshogs sgrub pa'i thabs rdzogsa para 'gyur te /
NK076(mu)002:7127: sgrub thabs phun sum tshogsa pa lnga yis sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung la /
NK076(mu)002:7128: bsnyen pa dang nye bsnyen sgrub pa dang sgrub chen bazha yis sgrub pa'i gzhung bsrang bar bya ba'ang /
NK076(mu)002:7129: rnal 'byor pa gang daga gcig spros kyi skabs zhi khro gang la mos pa ca bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:7130: 'dir yang zhi ba dang khra bos tshogs bsgrub par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7131: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7132: zhi ba dang khro bo'i tshogs sgrub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7135: spyiir zhi khro gnyis yod pa de la yang snga
NK076(mu)002:7136: ma zhi ba'i sgo nas tshogs sgrub la gansa phun
NK076(mu)002:7137: sum tshogs pa dang gcig /dus phun sum tshogs pa
NK076(mu)002:7138: dang gnyis / yo byad phun sum tshogs pa dang gsum /
NK076(mu)002:7139: ston 'khor sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa dang bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:7140: sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa dang lnga yis /
NK076(mu)002:7141: bsnyen grub yan lag bzhi dang sbyar bas zhi ba'i tshogs sgrub kyi gzhung rdzogsa par shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7142: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7143: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung /
NK076(mu)002:7144: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:7151: dang po sgrub pa po spyi'i mtshan nyid /
NK076(mu)002:7152: phun tshogs lnga ldan pas bsgrub dgos pa da la
NK076(mu)002:7153: sgrub pa po zhi ba rgya spros pa'i ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:7157: yig 'bru ste cha ga lnga ni rdzogsa par byas shing /
NK076(mu)002:7159: glu tshig rgyan dang bgo ba /
NK076(mu)002:7161: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byada dang lnga na tshogs sgrub sngon du rdzogs par ldan /
NK076(mu)002:7162: sngags yid skyob pa dang byin rlabs spar khab las gsungs /
NK076(mu)002:7165: de yang thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' dang gcig /sku gsung thugs kyi lha dang bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:7166: dbu rgyan lha ste lnga sngags kya yana lag lnga rdzogs pa'i ting 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:7167: rnal 'byor pa tshom bu lnga pa la pho mo lnga bcu /
NK076(mu)002:7168: gsum pa la zhe drug /gcig pa la pho mo bco brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:7169: 'tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis tshogs bsgrub na /
NK076(mu)002:7170: the tshom med pas na nges par 'grub ste gang
NK076(mu)002:7171: 'grub na sgro skur med bar legs pa'i dgos pa
NK076(mu)002:7172: yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas mthong lam rnam smin
NK076(mu)002:7173: tshe dbang gnyis dang mthar thug sku lnga lhun gyis
NK076(mu)002:7175: sgyu 'phrul rtsa bshad kyi don ston pa yi bla ma ni /
NK076(mu)002:7178: spyod pa'i mdzod ma h+aa gsum ldan dang /
NK076(mu)002:7179: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na'i dbang bzhi'i chu bo bzhi rdzogsa pa dang bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:7180: phyi bar chad kyi dgra bgegs bzlog pa /
NK076(mu)002:7181: nang nyon mongs lam du slong ba /
NK076(mu)002:7182: gsang ba bde sdug ro snyoms pa /
NK076(mu)002:7183: snying rje phan sems kyis slob ma rjes 'dzin gyi gnyer bzhi dang ldan pa lnga /
NK076(mu)002:7184: rgyud sde la mkhas shing lung don khrol ba dang
NK076(mu)002:7185: drug /phrin las kyi cho ga khrigs la makhasa pa
NK076(mu)002:7186: dang bdun / bla ma'i man ngaga zab mo'i nyams
NK076(mu)002:7187: myong drod 'achanga ba dang brgyad rgyud la 'chang ba
NK076(mu)002:7188: dang bdun / yi / rnal 'byor pa zag bcas
NK076(mu)002:7189: spros pa mthar phyin pa dang ldan nas zag med
NK076(mu)002:7190: la sbyor nus pa'i ston pa shin tu bsten par
NK076(mu)002:7191: dang bdun / yi / bya'o // gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:7192: ston pa rdo rje slob dpon la sgo gsum gyis
NK076(mu)002:7193: mnyes pa gsum gyis mchod cing dbang rdzogs pa thob
NK076(mu)002:7194: nas brtson 'grus kyis rgyud spyangs rtogs pa'i lta ba
NK076(mu)002:7195: de ting sogs gsal ba rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK076(mu)002:7196: gi dama tshiga ma nyams pa /
NK076(mu)002:7197: rtsa ba rkyen dang las kyi sngagas gsum dang phyag
NK076(mu)002:7198: rgya la sogs bzhi rnams ma nyams par shes shinga
NK076(mu)002:7199: / bza' btung sogs kyi yo byad lnga dang ldan pa'i 'khora gya tshogs kyis 'grub bar 'gyur la /
NK076(mu)002:7200: de rnams dang mi ldana na bsgrubs kyang don med cing brlag par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7202: dang po gnas btsal zhing brtags nas sa chog bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:7203: dgra bgegs kyi sde dpung gi bar chad chen pos mi tshugsa pa'i gnas btsal bar byas shing /
NK076(mu)002:7204: rdo rje las rim las 'byung ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:7205: sa gzhi dang bar snang gi mtshan nyid sogs bkra shis pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7206: mi chos kyi gtsug lag dang /
NK076(mu)002:7207: lha chos kyi lo rgyus rnam pa gnyis ka bkra shis par ldan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7208: rang gi yid du 'ong ba'i sa phyogs batsala te
NK076(mu)002:7209: las rim nas bshad ltar sa yi cho ga rgyas
NK076(mu)002:7210: par bya ba'o // gnyis pa de rang gnas brtsigs shing phyug bsrung dang brgyan pa /
NK076(mu)002:7211: gnas rnyed nas tshom bu gcig gsum lnga gang bsgrub lha'i grangsa mang nyung bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:7212: gnas khang che chung tshad rkyen sgrub pa po mang nyung bzhin du 'tshams par bya //
NK076(mu)002:7213: de'i 'khor khang phyi mar g.yos byed /
NK076(mu)002:7215: bar mar gsang spyod bya ste rim pa gsum dang
NK076(mu)002:7216: ldan pa'i khang par rin chena gser dngul sogs dang
NK076(mu)002:7217: / tsan+dana gla rtsi la sogs byug pas bgegs bsrung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7218: rin chena sna tshogs kyi rgyan mdzes par spras pa'i sgrub gnas gzhal yas khang dang /
NK076(mu)002:7219: rang nyams dga' zhing yid du 'ong bar bya ba shin tu gces so //
NK076(mu)002:7224: sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus kyi tshes grangsa ni
NK076(mu)002:7225: zla ba yar gyi ngo tshes brgyad la lha'i tshogs
NK076(mu)002:7226: 'dus pa'i dus yin pas brtsam par bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:7227: shin tu yang tshes grangs de dang skar ma rgyal
NK076(mu)002:7228: dang gza' phur bu rnams 'jom pa'i dus la 'jug
NK076(mu)002:7229: na bla med byang chub sgrub pa'i spyod pa rlabs
NK076(mu)002:7230: po che chera spyod pa 'di ni rang bzhin gyi
NK076(mu)002:7232: gasnga sngags mchog gi dngos grub myur du thob pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7233: phyir tshes grangs gza' dang skar ma bkra shisa pa
NK076(mu)002:7234: ste bzang po rnams blang bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7235: gnyis pa sgrub pa 'grub pa'i dus /
NK076(mu)002:7236: lha bsgom dam tshig ldan pas zhag ni sum cu
NK076(mu)002:7237: phrag drug gam ste zla ba drug /rab 'og gis
NK076(mu)002:7238: zla ba bcu gnyis te lo gcig 'bring gis zla
NK076(mu)002:7239: ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis
NK076(mu)002:7240: / tha mas zla ba bcu drug lo gcig dang
NK076(mu)002:7241: zla ba bzhi dag gis tshe la dbang sgyur pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7242: raga 'dzin rnams kyi nang nas lam mchog tshe dbang
NK076(mu)002:7243: / 'grub pa'i phyir / sbyor lam gyi rnal 'byor
NK076(mu)002:7244: ba'i shes rab dang brtson 'grus che chung gi chas
NK076(mu)002:7245: phye bas dus nye ring rim pa bzhin du bsgrub
NK076(mu)002:7246: / 'grub pa'i phyir / bo // bzhi pa yo byad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7247: spyir yo byad tshogs par bsog pa /
NK076(mu)002:7248: gos rgyan dang bza' ba dang btung ba dang gsang ba +aa li k+aa li dang /
NK076(mu)002:7249: bro gar glu sogs sgrub pa byed pa'i dus kyi ya byad lnga rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:7250: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan gyi yo byad steng 'og log
NK076(mu)002:7251: gi rgyan rnams dang phyi nang gsang ba'i machada pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7252: rdzas dang / dngos grub rten yo byad thod sku mar me sogs dang /
NK076(mu)002:7253: dgra bgegs dang nad kyi bar chad rkyen zlog gi yo byad go mtshon /
NK076(mu)002:7256: sman dang sman pa bcas rnams bsdus so //
NK076(mu)002:7257: gnyis pa bye brag tu yo byad dag par bsdu zhing 'tsho ba'i yo byad byin gyis brlab pa /
NK076(mu)002:7258: yo byad de rnams dam nyams /
NK076(mu)002:7260: sme sha can sogs kyi lag nas ma byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7261: phud ma nyams par rnam par dag par bsdus par byas ta /
NK076(mu)002:7262: de la tsha gsum du bcad la byin gyis brlab ste /
NK076(mu)002:7263: dang po tram las rin po che'i mchod sdong 'od
NK076(mu)002:7264: 'bar ba'i rtse mo +aah'u gsum las phyi nang gi
NK076(mu)002:7266: gnyis par nyi zla'i steng dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i 'phro
NK076(mu)002:7267: 'dus 'dod yon gyi lhar brlabs rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK076(mu)002:7268: kyis rol / tha mar sa las nam mkha' mdzod
NK076(mu)002:7269: kyi sngags rgyas spel te lhag mgron mchod pa bya'o
NK076(mu)002:7270: kyis rol / // lnga ba sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:7271: sgrub pa'i thabs bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang sbyar ba yis sgrub gzhung bsrang /
NK076(mu)002:7272: bar chad med pa'i gnas shin tu dben pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7273: dgos pa'i longs spyod bza' btung sogs bsogs shing ci
NK076(mu)002:7274: bde bar yo byad lnga 'jol nyog tu spyod rgyu
NK076(mu)002:7275: dang / dam tshig ma nyamsa lta sgom bla dang
NK076(mu)002:7276: ni rab tu ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo'i tshogs
NK076(mu)002:7277: dang / pasa / tshogs sgrub 'jug pa'i dang pa
NK076(mu)002:7278: la tshom bu'i lha grangs gang dus ci tsam bsgrub
NK076(mu)002:7279: par khas blangs shing dam mnos pa bzhin tu mthar
NK076(mu)002:7280: dang / pasa / phyin par bya'o // de ltar
NK076(mu)002:7281: ma grub par dam bca' dang ldan pas rnal 'byor
NK076(mu)002:7282: pho mo 'dus ta bsgrub par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7283: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7285: grogs yo byad la spyad thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:7291: zhor la zhag grangs rgyud bzhin shes nas sgrub par bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7293: dang po lhag ting gi dkyil 'khor gsal lam gzugs
NK076(mu)002:7294: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bri zhing rgyan dang rdzas dgod
NK076(mu)002:7295: pa / bsgrub gzhi song nas yang na zhes rgyud kyi tshig shugs so //
NK076(mu)002:7296: sgrub pa'i dal dpag tshad dang rgyang gragsa su gsal bas sam /
NK076(mu)002:7297: tshom bu gsum po so sa rang rang gi blo dang 'atshamas pa'i lhag pa gzugsa brnyan dal /
NK076(mu)002:7303: dkyil 'khor rgyan dang phyi nang gi mchod pa sogs dal gyi mtha' 'khor ba dgram pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7304: gnyis pa phyi mchod bya zhing mtshams bcad pa /
NK076(mu)002:7305: de nas gnas kyi phyi rol du cha gsum gyi
NK076(mu)002:7306: gtor mas mchod pa'i las rnams rdzogs par byas te
NK076(mu)002:7307: / rgyal chen phyogs skyong gi tho btsug nas phyi mtshams bcad cing bsrung /
NK076(mu)002:7309: sga byang gdags shing mtshams rim pa bzhin du bcad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7310: gsum pa sngon du bya ba'i las rnams rdzogs par bya dgos pa /
NK076(mu)002:7311: grangs rtags dus bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa bzhi
NK076(mu)002:7312: las 'di bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa bya ba'i
NK076(mu)002:7313: dona du sngon du 'gro bar bya ba gong gi
NK076(mu)002:7314: de rnams rdzogs pa'i lasa rnams thon zin par bya
NK076(mu)002:7316: gnyis pa nye bsnyen la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7318: de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams nang du 'dus pas tshul phyag bya /
NK076(mu)002:7319: khro bcus phyogs bcings shing mtshams bcad /
NK076(mu)002:7323: phyi nang gi mchod rdzas rnams byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK076(mu)002:7324: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:7325: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK076(mu)002:7326: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing mchod bstod
NK076(mu)002:7327: smon lam tshogs mchod lhag ma dzapa bsnyen gyi las
NK076(mu)002:7328: rim / nye bsnyen gyi tshad dang byed las bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7331: yan lag dbang bskur byin rlabs kyi lha bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7334: rnal 'byor pa gcig gis lha kun spyir bsgom pa'am
NK076(mu)002:7335: yang na rnal 'byor pa yab yum re re dang
NK076(mu)002:7336: lha yab yum brang sprad nas bsgom zhing tshom bu'i
NK076(mu)002:7337: 'khor lo gcig gsum lnga rim pa bzhin du bsgom
NK076(mu)002:7338: par bya ba'o // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7339: dang po tshom bu gcig gsum lnga mi grangs lha grangs sprad nas bsgom lugs /
NK076(mu)002:7340: rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes rab yum gyis /
NK076(mu)002:7341: yab rnams kyis de bzhin gshegsa pa rigs kyi yab
NK076(mu)002:7342: lnga dang yum rnams kyis rigs kyi yum du bsgoma
NK076(mu)002:7343: / 'khor pho mo yab rnams kyis rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:7344: yum rnams rang rang gi rigs chung gi semas ma rnams yum nyid du bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:7345: lha so so'i rigas gang yin pa dang phyag rgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:7346: ting 'dzina rnams ma 'dres par yang dag par so sora gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:7347: gnyis pa gcig gis kun bsgom byed lugs de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:7348: dang po tshom bu gcig pa /
NK076(mu)002:7349: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs thams cad kyi 'dus tshul
NK076(mu)002:7350: ni rigs lngar 'dus pa yin te de yang bsdu
NK076(mu)002:7351: na thugs sgrub sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lugs kyi rigas
NK076(mu)002:7352: kya gtso bo rdo rje rigs su 'dus pa yin
NK076(mu)002:7354: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes brjod kyis mi langs kyang /
NK076(mu)002:7355: bsdu na thugsa ye shes lngar 'dus te /
NK076(mu)002:7356: ye shes lnga yang thugsa kya machaga stong nyid ye shes kho nar 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:7357: rdor sems yab yum rigs chung sems dpa' yab yum
NK076(mu)002:7358: dang bcas zung lnga ya bcu khro bo'i tshagas sgo
NK076(mu)002:7359: ba yab yum dang ldan pa yi tshoma bu gciga
NK076(mu)002:7360: pa'i lha yab yum bco brgyad kyi tshogs rnams bsgom
NK076(mu)002:7361: mo // gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa /
NK076(mu)002:7362: gcig pa'i lho byang gnyis bzhag pas /
NK076(mu)002:7363: mdun nam shar phyogs su de bzhin rigas kyi tshom bu yab yum bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:7364: dbus su rda rje'i rigas tshom bu bcu /
NK076(mu)002:7365: rgyab bam nub tu pad+ma'i rigs tshom bu bcu ste
NK076(mu)002:7366: de ltar sku gsung thugsa kyi tshom bu cha gsum
NK076(mu)002:7367: gyi mthar / phyogs mtshams brgyad du khra ba yab
NK076(mu)002:7368: yum bcu drug zhal sbyor ba'i tshogas dang ldan pa
NK076(mu)002:7369: gyi mthar / yi / tshoma bu gsum pa'i lha zhe drug gi tshogs rnams bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:7370: gsum pa tshom bu lnga bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:7371: gtso bo yab lnga dang gtso mo yum lnga yi
NK076(mu)002:7372: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par zhal sbyor
NK076(mu)002:7373: ba can du bzhugs pa yi tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:7374: 'og gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa lnga po re re la yang /
NK076(mu)002:7375: rtsibs chung bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa re re ste pho brang cha lnga /
NK076(mu)002:7376: dbus kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba la rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7377: rtsibs bzhir rdo rje'i rigs kyi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad rnams kyis bskor ba /
NK076(mu)002:7378: rdo rje rigs kyi tshom bu ltar gsal ba'i rnal 'byor pa yab yum bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:7379: de bzhin tu shar lho nub byang bzhir rnam snang /
NK076(mu)002:7382: don grub yab yum gyis gtsor byas pa rnams la /
NK076(mu)002:7386: las kyi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad brgyad kyis bskor ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:7387: rigs bzhi'i tshom bu la lha bzhi bcu /
NK076(mu)002:7388: gong gi dbus kyi tshom bu'i lnga bcu ste /
NK076(mu)002:7389: de ltar tshom bu lnga yi tshom bu'i lha lnga
NK076(mu)002:7390: bcu rnal 'byor pho mo lnga bcur gsal bar bsgom
NK076(mu)002:7391: pa bkod la / tshom bu cha lnga po de'i mthar phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:7394: rnal 'byor yab yum cha bcu la /
NK076(mu)002:7395: khro bo yab bcu dang khro mo bcu ste /
NK076(mu)002:7396: lha nyi shu gsal bar bkod pas lha bdun cu
NK076(mu)002:7397: de dag dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam
NK076(mu)002:7399: gnyis pa yan lag dbang bskur byin rlabs kyi lha bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:7400: de dag la sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7401: lha gsum ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba'i rtags rigs
NK076(mu)002:7402: lnga dang thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' ldana par
NK076(mu)002:7403: byas nas / gnyis pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:7404: spyan drangs shing mchod bstod smon lam tshogs mchod lhag
NK076(mu)002:7405: ma dza pra bsnyen gyi las rim /
NK076(mu)002:7406: ranga bazhana lhun grub 'og min gansa nasa snyan gsan dbab par byas ta /
NK076(mu)002:7407: spyan drangs gnyis su med par gzhug cing bstan par
NK076(mu)002:7408: bzhugs gsol byas la phyag 'tshal phyi nang gsang ba'i
NK076(mu)002:7409: mchod pa rnams rima par mchoda pa rdzogsa nasa glu
NK076(mu)002:7410: ye shes kyis bstod da smon lam btab la dza
NK076(mu)002:7412: de tshar nas mchod bstod bshags pa rig me dor
NK076(mu)002:7413: dngos grub bskul zin nasa dza pra khang bsdus ta
NK076(mu)002:7414: / de nas skal ldan rnal 'byor pa mi'i tshogsa
NK076(mu)002:7415: kyis dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs la 'byor ldan yo byad
NK076(mu)002:7416: kyi tshogs tshul bzhin du mchoda pa'i phrin las gzhung
NK076(mu)002:7417: / ltar du bya / de ltar bsgrubs pas nang
NK076(mu)002:7418: nub kyi bar skabs su mkha' 'gro so gnyis sogs
NK076(mu)002:7419: lhag mgron la lhag ma sbyin cing phrin las bcol
NK076(mu)002:7420: / ltar du bya / / sgrub la bar chad
NK076(mu)002:7421: byed pa'i nyul le ma yang dus su bzlog cinga
NK076(mu)002:7422: / ltar du bya / / bsnyen pa bya'o // gsum pa nye bsnyen gyi tshad dang byed las /
NK076(mu)002:7423: de yang zla ba phyed kyi phyed zhag bdun du nya ba'i bsnyen pa bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:7424: bdag mdun lha gasla ba'i bar du bzlas pa'i 'od
NK076(mu)002:7425: zer dkar po 'phro bas bde bar gshegs pa mchod
NK076(mu)002:7426: la / tshur 'dus bdag gi sgrib pa sbyangs nas dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7428: de nas zhag bco lnga yi nub tha ma zhag
NK076(mu)002:7429: gcig ma gtogs pa mar phyed zhag bdun du sgrub
NK076(mu)002:7430: pa bya ste / bzlas pa'i 'od zer dmar po
NK076(mu)002:7431: phar 'phros pas dngos grub bstsol cig par bskul tshur
NK076(mu)002:7432: 'dus pas dngos grub thob par bsgom te /
NK076(mu)002:7433: de gnyis bsnol mas don gnyis bsgrub para bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7434: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po dang zhor la zhag
NK076(mu)002:7435: grangs rgyud bzhin shes nas sgrub dgos par bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:7436: / de ltar sgrub pa'i zhag grangsa zla ba drug
NK076(mu)002:7437: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gang dang gang yin
NK076(mu)002:7438: / par / bzlas grangs tshad nas grub pa'i rtags 'od la sogs pa rnams byung na /
NK076(mu)002:7439: nub tha ma la ye shes lha'i sku gsung thugs
NK076(mu)002:7440: kyi dngosa grub bzlas pa'i 'od zer kha dog mthing
NK076(mu)002:7441: ga tshur bdag la 'dus nas blang ba ni sgrub
NK076(mu)002:7442: pa chana po'o // dngos grub yum gyi mkha' las
NK076(mu)002:7443: blang pa ni sgrub pa chen po +aa li nyams
NK076(mu)002:7444: pa chana po'o // su len pa'o // gong gi
NK076(mu)002:7445: dus zla phyed la sogs pa de bzhin du brtsis
NK076(mu)002:7446: pas chog gam zhe na mi chog ste /
NK076(mu)002:7447: bsnyen sgrub kyi yun le'u dgu pa /
NK076(mu)002:7449: rgyud kya nang nas gsungs pa'i zhag grangsa sum cu
NK076(mu)002:7450: phrag drug la sogs pa bshad pa bzhina du cha
NK076(mu)002:7451: bgo la bsgom bzlas la bar chad mada para tshom
NK076(mu)002:7453: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i grogs yo byad la spyod thabs la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:7454: dang po yo byad lnga spyad thabs mdor bstan /
NK076(mu)002:7455: tshogs sgrub pa'i dus su spyir spyod lam du yo byad lnga la longs spyod cing rol la /
NK076(mu)002:7456: gnyis pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa /
NK076(mu)002:7457: dngos su spyod lugs khro bo'i skabs su bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7458: bye brag sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa rnam pa gnyis
NK076(mu)002:7459: po tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su gal che bas gtso
NK076(mu)002:7460: ru dgos pa gang ltar yin pa yi tshul rgyas
NK076(mu)002:7461: bshad ni / dkyus kyi phyi ma gdug pa 'dul
NK076(mu)002:7462: bar byed pa khro bo'i skabs su shes par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:7463: bshad ni / // gsum pa yo byad lnga la
NK076(mu)002:7464: sbyang thabs yon tan dang bcas pa rgyas par bshad
NK076(mu)002:7465: bshad ni / // pa la gnyis / dang po
NK076(mu)002:7466: mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi rang nas chos
NK076(mu)002:7467: nyid la chos nyid ye shes la ye shes rol
NK076(mu)002:7468: pa'i tshul gyis spyad thabs zhi khro gnyis thun mong
NK076(mu)002:7469: bshad ni / // pa la gnyis / ni /
NK076(mu)002:7470: gong du bstan pa'i snga ma yo byad lnga la
NK076(mu)002:7471: spyad thabs rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bstan par
NK076(mu)002:7473: gos dang rgyan gyi yo byad bza' ba dang btung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7476: rang rig ye shes yi ge h'u gis mtshon nas
NK076(mu)002:7477: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du shes pas yo byad
NK076(mu)002:7478: rnams la ma chags pa'i tshul gyis rab tu spyad
NK076(mu)002:7479: na / ngo matshara ba 'bras bu'i tshogs chen gnyis
NK076(mu)002:7480: 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khora thams cad bdag nyid chen po'i
NK076(mu)002:7481: mchod pas mnyes pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:7482: gsang ba +aa li k+aa li sogs pa'i yo byad
NK076(mu)002:7483: bza' btung gos rgyan bro gar glu tshig ste lnga
NK076(mu)002:7484: pa rnams / rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid yin
NK076(mu)002:7485: pa'i phyir don dam ma skyes pa'i chos nyid rang
NK076(mu)002:7486: rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bor gsal bas mi
NK076(mu)002:7487: rtog pa chos nyid la chos nyid thim pas kun
NK076(mu)002:7488: rdzob tu ma 'gags pa'i ya shes gnyis med kyi
NK076(mu)002:7490: zhi ba las gciga shasa khro bo'i tshogs bsgrub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7491: yo byad la spyod pa'i tshe na'ang mtshan ma med
NK076(mu)002:7492: pa'i spyod thabs ting nge 'dzin de bzhin no //
NK076(mu)002:7493: gnyis pa mtshan bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang nas spyad thabs de la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:7494: lha bye brag tu gsal ba'i ngang nas yo byad
NK076(mu)002:7495: lnga la spyad thabs bye brag tu bshad pa dang
NK076(mu)002:7496: / spyir sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i ting 'dzin gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:7497: ngang nas yo byad la longs spyod pa'i yon tan
NK076(mu)002:7498: / bstan pa'o // dang po la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7499: yo byad bzhi la spyad thabs dang /
NK076(mu)002:7500: de'i rjes su gsang ba'i yo byad la spyad thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:7502: bsam yas lhun grub kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:7503: ngang nas lus bsgul yan lag bsigs pa'i yon tan
NK076(mu)002:7504: dang / gtso bo lha rang rang gi lus la
NK076(mu)002:7505: lus kyi yan lag dang rtog pa'i yan lag gis
NK076(mu)002:7506: lha gsal ba'i ngang nas bro glu gos rgyan la
NK076(mu)002:7508: tshom bu rang rang gi lha gsal ba'i ngang nas
NK076(mu)002:7509: bro glu dang bza' btung la spyod pa'i yon tan
NK076(mu)002:7512: phyogs bcu mtha'a yas dus bzhis bsdus pa yi snod
NK076(mu)002:7513: bcud 'jig rten gyi khams thams cada rang rig pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7514: ngang du dbyer meda pa'i man+da la ste dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:7515: gsal / thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i phyir nyi
NK076(mu)002:7516: zla shar ba'i gdan dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas khang
NK076(mu)002:7517: de la pad+ma ltar chagas pa med pa'i gdan bting
NK076(mu)002:7518: gsal / nas / rgyu ye shes rin chen yon
NK076(mu)002:7519: tan zada pa mada par 'byung ba'i pho brang gi
NK076(mu)002:7520: lha'i gzhal yas khang dbus kyi lte ba sogs sa
NK076(mu)002:7521: gsal / nas / / de yang rgya che chung
NK076(mu)002:7522: gi tshad blos dpag tu meda pa yi phyir ro
NK076(mu)002:7523: gsal / nas / / // lha'i ngo bor rang
NK076(mu)002:7524: rig byang chub bde ba chen po dang ldan pa
NK076(mu)002:7525: bzhugs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi dkyil 'khor la yang
NK076(mu)002:7527: med bde ba chen po dang ldan pa'i byang chub
NK076(mu)002:7528: kyi sems lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK076(mu)002:7529: tshom bu gang yin gyi lha ting 'dzin gyis rab
NK076(mu)002:7530: tu bkod nasa 'dod pa ci byed na yo byad
NK076(mu)002:7532: snod bcud kyi rtog pa ma lus pa thams cad
NK076(mu)002:7533: lha'i dkyil 'khor mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su bsdus
NK076(mu)002:7534: par bsgoms nasa / gnyis pa spyod lugs kyi yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:7535: lus bskyod pa dang yan lag bsgul cing bsigs na /
NK076(mu)002:7536: mig sogs dbang pa lnga yi spyod yul lha rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba kun kyang /
NK076(mu)002:7537: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen pa nyid du ye nas yin para bshad do //
NK076(mu)002:7538: gnyis pa lus dang yan lag gi lha gsal ba'i ngang nas spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7542: dang po gzhal yas khang dang lha bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:7543: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzina gyi dkyil 'khor spros pa
NK076(mu)002:7544: bsgom pa'i skabs na mi res lha re bsgom pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7545: lus la lus kyi yan lag gi lha bkod nas
NK076(mu)002:7547: gcig gis kun bsgom na bro sogs byed pa'i tshe
NK076(mu)002:7548: na rang lhar gsal lus la yan lag lha bsgom
NK076(mu)002:7549: pa yanga / b+h+au las gzhal yas khang dang 'og gzhi tsakra'i dkyil 'khora rtsibs bzhi ba'i steng du /
NK076(mu)002:7550: gdan nya zla gnyis zung du 'phrugs pa'i zhes brtsegs pa'i sa gzhi la /
NK076(mu)002:7551: pad+ma chagas meda kyi gdan bting nasa /
NK076(mu)002:7552: gong gi gdan de'i steng du rnal 'byor ba thams
NK076(mu)002:7553: lha yab dang shesa raba lha yum gnyis gcig la
NK076(mu)002:7554: gcig chags pa med pa'i tshul du bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:7555: gnyis pa yan lag gi lha bsgom pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7557: lus kyi yan lag bzhi mgo dang dbang pa lnga bo thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:7558: rang rgyud pa'i rnam pa min pa'i rang bzhin ngang
NK076(mu)002:7559: 'am yongs kyi lha rigs lnga rnam par dag pa
NK076(mu)002:7560: yin pa dang / ting 'dzin kyang de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga yi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7561: gnyis pa rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7563: ye nasa rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa la sus
NK076(mu)002:7564: kyang ma bcos par yongs kyis grub pa la de
NK076(mu)002:7565: rang rgyung du grub pa med de /
NK076(mu)002:7566: de ltar gzhi yin pa bsgom pa lhag pa'i ting
NK076(mu)002:7567: 'dzina gyi rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyis lha ji ltar
NK076(mu)002:7568: bsgom na / tshom bu'i lha gsal ba'i dbu la
NK076(mu)002:7569: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi gtso bo la 'khor
NK076(mu)002:7570: bsgom na / lha bcu bsgom / yan lag bzhi
NK076(mu)002:7571: la rigs bzhi'i gtso 'khor lha bcu bcu ste bzhi
NK076(mu)002:7572: bsgom na / lha bcu bsgom / bcu bsgom pa'o
NK076(mu)002:7573: // de yang lag g.yas rdo rje rigs kyi lha
NK076(mu)002:7574: bsgom na / lha bcu bsgom / bcu bsgom pa'o // bcu / g.yon rin chen rigs /
NK076(mu)002:7577: lha de dag kha dog dang dbyibs dang phyag rgya phyag mtshan rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:7578: thabs yab dang shes raba yum ste tshom bu lnga bcu gsal bar bsgoms te /
NK076(mu)002:7579: gnyis pa 'phro 'du byas pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:7580: lha de dag las 'od zer phyogsa bcur spro zhing
NK076(mu)002:7581: don gnyis byas khyad par ngan song gsum gyi sgrib
NK076(mu)002:7582: pa sbyangs la / slar rang lhar gsal ba'i yan
NK076(mu)002:7583: lag gi gnas su bsdu zhing dkyil 'khora rang la
NK076(mu)002:7584: pa sbyangs la / bstim mo // 'das pa theg
NK076(mu)002:7585: 'og dang ma 'das pa 'khor ba'i sems can thams
NK076(mu)002:7586: pa sbyangs la / bstim mo // cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:7587: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhing khams khyad par can du
NK076(mu)002:7588: gsal bar rnam para sbyangs de sbyor ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:7589: gnyis pa spyod thabs kyi yan lag la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:7590: bskyod pa'i yon tan dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:7593: bro gar glu tshig thun mong spyad thabs dang /
NK076(mu)002:7594: mngon shes kyi spyad thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:7597: de ltar du rnal 'byor pas lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK076(mu)002:7598: gsal ba'i yan lag chen pa mgo bo la sogs
NK076(mu)002:7599: lnga bskyod na / gnyis pa yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:7600: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thugs rjes gzhan
NK076(mu)002:7601: don la g.yo nas don ci mdzad na 'gro ba
NK076(mu)002:7602: lnga yi sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7603: byang chub kyi lam du 'dzud par mdzad cing /
NK076(mu)002:7608: nyon mongs pa'i snyigs ma lnga yang sems bde ba'i ngang du rnam par daga go //
NK076(mu)002:7609: gnyis pa bgo ba gos la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7611: rgyu bzang la kha dog mdzes shing bzo legs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7612: dar gyi chas gosa lnga bgos na ting 'dzin ye
NK076(mu)002:7613: shes lnga'i 'od zer sna tshogas 'phro bar bsgom na
NK076(mu)002:7614: yon tan ni 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro bar 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:7616: de nas dus mthar thug pa med pa'i bar du /
NK076(mu)002:7617: sems ya shes lnga rtogs pa yis rang la brgyan para 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7620: rin po che'i rgyan brgyad la sogs pa'i rgyan mchog
NK076(mu)002:7621: mdzes pas rnal 'byor pa'i lus brgyan nas lha'i ting
NK076(mu)002:7622: 'dzin gyi tshom bu'i lha tshogs 'od 'abra zhing gsal
NK076(mu)002:7623: bar bsgom sta / de la phyogs bcu gang bar lha'i dkyil 'khor spra zhing /
NK076(mu)002:7624: spros dus rig pa bdag nyid chen pa'i lha yi dkyil 'khor du gsal la /
NK076(mu)002:7626: gsal dus sems nyid mi dmigs pa skye ba med pa'i dbyings kyi ngang nas dkyil 'khor mchoda na /
NK076(mu)002:7627: 'dod yon lnga ru gsal ba ma 'gags pa thabs
NK076(mu)002:7628: dang rang bzhin med pa'i shes raba kyi tshul du
NK076(mu)002:7630: bde ba mchog gi ro yang myong zhing bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs par byed do //
NK076(mu)002:7631: bde ba de la ma chagas shing 'dzin pa med
NK076(mu)002:7632: pa'i ye shes kyi tshogs dang tshogs chen po gnyis
NK076(mu)002:7634: bzhi pa bro gar glu tshigs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7635: thun mong du spyod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7636: gar bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:7639: rkang pa'i bra stabs lag pa'i gar thabs kya phyag rgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:7640: ngag gis snyan pa'i glu dbyangs len pa'i tshig dang
NK076(mu)002:7641: ting 'dzin dang ldan pa dag gis sgra bsgragsa na
NK076(mu)002:7643: phyogs bcu' 'gro drug gi skye gansa bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can ma lus pa kun /
NK076(mu)002:7644: sku lnga lhun grub drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen po'i sku ru mthong par 'gyur zhanga /
NK076(mu)002:7645: gsung lnga lhun grub dam pa chos kyi dung chen po'i sgra yang thos par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7646: nyon shes kyi sgrib pa gnyis byang nasa bla med byang chub 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7647: bro'i sgo nas bden pa mthong ba dang glu'i sgo
NK076(mu)002:7648: nas snyan pa dang gragsa pa thob cing bsod nams
NK076(mu)002:7649: kyi tshogs chen po 'grub la de la yang ma
NK076(mu)002:7650: chags par mi 'dzin pas ye shes kyi tshogs chen
NK076(mu)002:7651: po gnyis dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7652: gnyis pa gar bye brag bshad pa /
NK076(mu)002:7653: rnal 'byor pho mo lhar gsal ba'i thabs yab dang
NK076(mu)002:7654: shes rab yum thams cad kun langs la gar bya
NK076(mu)002:7655: ba ni / mi gcig gis kun bsgom na gar byed dus 'khor bsdus la rang gtso bor gsal /
NK076(mu)002:7656: dbus nas shar phyogs su kha bltas te /
NK076(mu)002:7657: rtog pa zil gyis gnon pa seng ge'i stabsa chen pos mchong bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7658: lnga pa mngon shes la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7663: lus kyi dbang po ste snying ga'am lte ba lnga la rigs lnga'i yi ge lnga bsgom tshul /
NK076(mu)002:7667: lce la h+r+aih lus la +aahste de rnams gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:7668: yi ge las 'od zer 'phros 'phags pa mchod sems
NK076(mu)002:7670: tshur 'dus bdag gi la sogs pa la thim pas
NK076(mu)002:7671: mig gis gzugs nye ring med par mthong ba la
NK076(mu)002:7672: sogs pa'i mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogsa so
NK076(mu)002:7673: // gnyis pa spyod pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:7674: des 'dod pa'i yon tan gzugs sogs yul lnga la 'dzin chags med par rol pas /
NK076(mu)002:7675: yon tan des rnal 'byor ba bdag gi don dang
NK076(mu)002:7676: sems can gzhan gyi don rnams yongs su rdzogsa par
NK076(mu)002:7677: byed pa'o // gsum pa tshom bu rang rang gi lhar gsal ba'i ngang nas spyod thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7679: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga gang rung gi lhar gsal
NK076(mu)002:7680: ba'i rnal 'byor pa yab yum rnams kyis phyogs bcu'i
NK076(mu)002:7681: rgyal ba'i yon tan rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:7682: phan tshun gcig la gcig 'od zer phar 'phro zhing tshur bdag la bstim par byas te /
NK076(mu)002:7683: de ltar ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor tshom bu gang
NK076(mu)002:7684: rung gi lha 'od 'bar bar ting 'dzin gsal bar
NK076(mu)002:7685: gyur nas rnal 'byor pas bdag cag lhar gsal ba
NK076(mu)002:7686: dang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad gnyis su med
NK076(mu)002:7687: par bsgom mo // gnyis pa spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7688: dang po bro gar glu la spyod pa'i thabs yon tan dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:7689: shar lho nub byang phyogsa te rang rang gi phyogs su rim pa bzhin du kha bltas te /
NK076(mu)002:7691: sku de bzhin gshegs pa gsung pad+ma yon tan rat+na las kyi don grub kyi glu dang /
NK076(mu)002:7692: bro yi tshig rgyas ba rgyud nas 'byung ba ltar brjod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7693: de'ang ye shes lnga'i rgyan du bro glu bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:7694: ragas lnga'i spya yi glu tshig brjod pa dad bro bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:7695: seng ge glang chen rta mchog rma bya shang shang
NK076(mu)002:7696: dang rnam pa lnga stobsa lnga dang glu lnga dang
NK076(mu)002:7698: rang rang gi ting 'dzin gyi srog dang ldana pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7699: rigs lnga'i bro glus bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis yongs
NK076(mu)002:7701: gnyis pa bza' btung la spyad thabs de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7703: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang mura ba btung ba'i bye brag rnams /
NK076(mu)002:7704: snang ba ma 'gags thabs dang rang bzhin med pa
NK076(mu)002:7705: shes rab de nyid gnyis su med pa'i ngang la
NK076(mu)002:7706: gnas shing mchod bya mchod byed tha dad med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7707: bdag nyid chen pa'i gnas su stob pa mchod pa
NK076(mu)002:7708: phul ba yis / gnyis pa spyod pa'i yon tan la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7709: dang po mchog gi dngos grub du gyur pa /
NK076(mu)002:7710: bdag dang sangs rgyas gnyis med dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad la mnyes pas khyab cing /
NK076(mu)002:7711: bdag dang srid gsum gyi semas can ma lus pa
NK076(mu)002:7712: thams cad la dga' ba dang bde ba chen pos
NK076(mu)002:7714: gnyis pa zas bdud rtsi mchog tu bsgyur zhing thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:7715: zas dug can la yi ge +aahbakoda de 'ju 'dul
NK076(mu)002:7716: byed pa tsam gyis bdud rtsir 'gyur zhing de'i yon
NK076(mu)002:7718: yon tan zas de zos pas rlung mkhris bad kan
NK076(mu)002:7719: 'du ba bzhi po re re yang brgya rtsa gcig
NK076(mu)002:7720: ste bazha brgya rtsa bzhi'i nada sel zhing bdud rtsi'i
NK076(mu)002:7721: 'od zer las longs spyod phun tshogs 'byung zhing ngan
NK076(mu)002:7722: song gi sa bon tri bre duhrnamasa sbyong ba dang
NK076(mu)002:7723: / de las ci yang gzhan bye ma las gser
NK076(mu)002:7724: du 'gyur ba la sogs dngos po phan tshun mi
NK076(mu)002:7726: gnyis pa gsang ba +aa li sbyor ba'i yo byad la spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7727: dang po yab yum gyi mkha' gsang brlabs nas bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i spyad thabs /
NK076(mu)002:7728: de ltar yo byad bzhi dang ldana pa'i rnal 'byor
NK076(mu)002:7729: pa yis thabs yab dang shes rab yum du ldan
NK076(mu)002:7730: par gyur nas / phung khams skye mched lha dang
NK076(mu)002:7731: mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara byin gyis brlab cing
NK076(mu)002:7732: 'dod pa'i sgyu rtsal gyis bde ba rgyas pa'i cha
NK076(mu)002:7733: rnams kyang rdzogs para bya ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:7737: sgrub pa chen po gsang ba bzhi yi rim pas /
NK076(mu)002:7738: rtogs pa thams cad bde stong gnyis su med pa'i yum gyi mkha' dbyingsa su sbyor ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:7739: gnyis pa yon tan de la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:7740: dang po zab mo'i dbang gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:7741: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su meda pa'i gsang ba'i
NK076(mu)002:7742: mkha' dbyings nasa nyi zla byang chub kyi sems bde
NK076(mu)002:7744: 'od zer lus la 'phro zhing bde ba 'bar bas
NK076(mu)002:7745: lus kyi phyogs bcura rtsa khams kyi rang bzhin bde
NK076(mu)002:7746: ba'i ye shes su gsal zhing /
NK076(mu)002:7747: zag med kyi bde basa lus la khyab pas na
NK076(mu)002:7748: thabs chen po snying rje bas lhag pas na thabs
NK076(mu)002:7749: kyi mchog shesa rab ye shes kyi dbang dang bde
NK076(mu)002:7750: ba'i mchog shin tu brtan pa dang ldan pas dbang
NK076(mu)002:7751: yang rdzogsa pa'o // gnyis pa gsang ba'i lha mo
NK076(mu)002:7752: bcu gnyis rdzogs par rol ba'i dus su lha'i dkyil
NK076(mu)002:7753: 'khor 'char ba'i yon tan yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo
NK076(mu)002:7754: rje dang yum gyi mkha' dril bu gnyis sbyor ba
NK076(mu)002:7755: las byung ba'i yang dag pa'i bde ba dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:7756: yang rdzogsa pa'o // pa la / phyag rgya bzhi ni g.yas kyis bzung ba lcags kyu ma /
NK076(mu)002:7757: g.yon gyi 'khyud pa zhags pa ma /
NK076(mu)002:7758: stod smad bsdom pa lcags sgrog ma /
NK076(mu)002:7759: bde ba bskyod pa dril bu ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:7760: lha mo brgyad yab yum chas kyis sgeg pa'am nyi zla dkar dmar gyis mdzes pa l+aa s+ye ma /
NK076(mu)002:7761: bde ba rgyun mi 'chad pa m+aa le ma /
NK076(mu)002:7762: rtsa nas ha si'i sgra sgrogs pa girti ma /
NK076(mu)002:7763: rtsa mdud grol ba'am bskyod pa nirti ma /
NK076(mu)002:7764: bde ba'i ngos tshim pa d+hup+pe ma /
NK076(mu)002:7766: bde stong gi don gsal ba +aa lo ke /
NK076(mu)002:7767: bde bas bsil zhing ros gang ba gan+d+he ma'o //
NK076(mu)002:7768: de ltar gsang ba'i lha mo bcu gnyis rdzogsa par
NK076(mu)002:7769: yab yum rol bas nyi zla byang chub sems gnyis
NK076(mu)002:7770: dus gcig tu mkha' la ldan nas /
NK076(mu)002:7771: yab yum thabs shes gnyis med du nyi zla zung du 'brel bar gyur nas /
NK076(mu)002:7772: rtog tshogs thams cad bde bar gshegsa pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:7773: du gsal bas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK076(mu)002:7774: 'byung zhes bya'o // gsum pa thun mong gi dngos grub grub pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:7775: de'i dus su yab yum gyi thig le nyi zla
NK076(mu)002:7776: slar bzlog nas rlung dang 'dres pas skye 'jig med
NK076(mu)002:7777: pa rdo rje'i gzugs su chagas pas thabs las gyur
NK076(mu)002:7779: de ltar sbyor ba'i mchod pa chen po des thun
NK076(mu)002:7780: mong gi dngos grub tshe ring dang mkha' la bya
NK076(mu)002:7781: bzhin 'gro ba dang kha dog gsal zhing 'od zer
NK076(mu)002:7783: bzhi pa mchog gi dngos grub 'bras bu 'grub pa'i yon tan de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7784: dang po yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis mthong ba /
NK076(mu)002:7785: sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum 'phrul pa mtshon pa
NK076(mu)002:7786: lha yab ste phung lnga sogs rtog pa thams cad
NK076(mu)002:7787: lha'i dkyil 'akhara bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ste
NK076(mu)002:7788: / yab yum 'brel bas d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi
NK076(mu)002:7789: bcu rtsa gnyis rang rig pa'i mangna sum du gsal
NK076(mu)002:7791: phyogsa bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i chos
NK076(mu)002:7792: thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du mngon sum du rdzogs
NK076(mu)002:7794: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK076(mu)002:7795: 'khor lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad 'grub par
NK076(mu)002:7796: 'gyur ro // gnyis pa ye shes bla ma'i sa mthong ba /
NK076(mu)002:7797: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK076(mu)002:7798: la brtan pa thob pa'i tshad gsal ba yul rkyen
NK076(mu)002:7799: gyis mi 'phrog pa'i rnal 'byor ba yis 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:7800: ci ltar thob na phyogs bcu dang dus bzhira yang
NK076(mu)002:7801: dag pa'i sa'am 'gro ba'i don la gshegas pa yi
NK076(mu)002:7802: sangas rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7803: khamas gsum 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi khams dang
NK076(mu)002:7804: bsam pa thams cad rang rig pa'i mangna sum du
NK076(mu)002:7805: gnyis med gsal bar 'gyur ba ni ye shes bla
NK076(mu)002:7806: ma'i sa thob pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:7807: gnyis pa spyir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i ting 'dzin gsal
NK076(mu)002:7808: ba'i ngang nas yo byad la spyod pa'i yon tan
NK076(mu)002:7809: bstan pa / tshom bu'i lha zung 'brel sgyu 'phyul
NK076(mu)002:7810: d+r+wa bas zhes rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rdzogsa
NK076(mu)002:7811: pa'i dkyil 'khor dang rnam grangs spros pa la brtan
NK076(mu)002:7812: pa thob pa'i snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge
NK076(mu)002:7813: 'dzina dang ldan pas des yo byad lnga de yang
NK076(mu)002:7814: rkang pa'i bro stabs dang lag pa'i gar stabs sna
NK076(mu)002:7815: tshogs kyi glu tshig dang bcas pa blang ba'i dus
NK076(mu)002:7816: bstan pa / na / sprul pa'i 'adu 'phro dang
NK076(mu)002:7817: bcas pa'i dus lha'i sku gsung thugs las mi 'da'
NK076(mu)002:7819: yon tan sa la thogs med 'dzul zhing klu'i bu mo dbang du 'dus nas longs spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:7820: lam nam mkha' la bya bzhin 'gro zhing lha dang
NK076(mu)002:7821: gnod sbyin bu mo rnams la longs spyod cing dbang
NK076(mu)002:7823: ngag gi sgo nas glu tshiga dang sgra yi spyod
NK076(mu)002:7824: pa'i dus lha'i sku gsung thugs dbyer med phyag rgya
NK076(mu)002:7825: yis de'i ngang nas lce steng yi ge h+r+aihbakoda de
NK076(mu)002:7827: mar gdul bya la chosa kyi 'khor lo ston pa'i dngos grub thob para 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7828: zhi ba rin po che'i rgyan /
NK076(mu)002:7829: khro bo la rus rgyan dang /
NK076(mu)002:7830: zhi drag gi dar dang glang ko sogs bgo ba'i
NK076(mu)002:7831: yo byad la spyod dus lha'i phyag rgya yi ngang
NK076(mu)002:7832: nas spyod pas / 'bras bu ni lus la gzi
NK076(mu)002:7833: byin 'od 'bar ba'i rgyal pa gzhan gyis zil gyis
NK076(mu)002:7834: gnon thub pa med pa seng ge lta bur 'grub
NK076(mu)002:7835: nas spyod pas / par 'gyur / dam rdzas lnga
NK076(mu)002:7836: sogs bza' ba dang btung ba'i longs spyod rnams lha'i
NK076(mu)002:7837: phyag rgya yis mchod pa'i 'bras bu /
NK076(mu)002:7838: yid bzhin nor bu'i 'od lta bu sku gzi mdangs
NK076(mu)002:7839: ldan pa dang zas thams cad bdud rtsi'i bcud 'gro
NK076(mu)002:7841: brda tshig tu bstan pa'i +aa la sbyor ba'i yo byad dang /
NK076(mu)002:7842: k+aa li sgrol pa'i yo byad dam yang na k+aa li yab /
NK076(mu)002:7843: +aa li yum gnyis kyi phung khams lha'i sku gsung
NK076(mu)002:7844: thugs kyi phyag rgya gsal ba'i ngang snyoms par zhugs
NK076(mu)002:7846: phrin las bzhi po thamsa cad dang /
NK076(mu)002:7847: mchog thun dngos grub thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:7848: spyi don gnyis pa khro bo'i tshogs sgrub pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7849: phun sum tshogs pa lngasa sgrub pa'i gzhi gzung ba /
NK076(mu)002:7850: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:7853: gdul bya gdug pa'i tshogas rnams 'dul ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub par bya ba la /
NK076(mu)002:7858: sgrub thabs phun tshogs rnams na /
NK076(mu)002:7859: khro bo tshogs sgrub kyi mchog tu dmigas pasa bsgrub gzhi bazhaga pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:7860: gnyis pa rgyas pa la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:7862: dur khrod dam rtsi shing nags tshal chen pa yod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7863: grong las dpag tshad rgyang grags las ring ba dgra
NK076(mu)002:7864: bgegs nad gsum gyi bar chad kyis dben pa'i sa
NK076(mu)002:7866: rdo rje las rim la sogs pa'i gzhung nas bshad pa dang mthun pa yi gnas rnyed nas ni /
NK076(mu)002:7867: sa chog bya ba sa phyogs de yi gnod pa sbyin pa'am gdon bgegs la glud gtor sbyin /
NK076(mu)002:7868: khro bo'i phur bas bskrad cing sa la gter mnan /
NK076(mu)002:7869: sa gzhi ye shes kyi rang mdangs dur khrod kyi
NK076(mu)002:7870: gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlab pa la sogs
NK076(mu)002:7871: sa gzhi mnyam pa ste cho ga rdo rje las
NK076(mu)002:7873: gnyis pa sgrub pa po la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7874: dang po spyir ting 'dzin mthu ma nyams pas bsgrub pa /
NK076(mu)002:7875: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste khro bo yab yum zung
NK076(mu)002:7876: du 'brel bas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas dpal
NK076(mu)002:7877: khrag 'thung khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha lnga bcu
NK076(mu)002:7878: rtsa brgyad bsgom pa spros pa'i skabs su brtan pa
NK076(mu)002:7879: thob pa'i stobs kyis cha ga lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:7880: sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:7881: yo byad lnga bcas bco lnga tshad shing rdzogs pa'i khro bo mthar phyin pa yi /
NK076(mu)002:7887: brgya dang bco brgyad sogs skal ba mnyam pa 'dus
NK076(mu)002:7888: pas tshogs bsgrub na mthong lam gyi dngos grub nges
NK076(mu)002:7890: gnyis pa bye brag tu ston 'khor mtshan nyid dang ldan pas bsgrub pa /
NK076(mu)002:7891: de yang ston pa rdo rje rgyal po mdzod ba
NK076(mu)002:7892: rgyad dang ldan pa dbang gi chu bo rdzogs pa
NK076(mu)002:7893: can dang / rdo rje rgyal tshab rdo rje rgyal
NK076(mu)002:7894: pa dang lta sgom gyi yon tan mnyam par mtshungs
NK076(mu)002:7895: can dang / pa dang / karma las mkhan skad
NK076(mu)002:7896: kyi gdangs cha zhing snyan pa phrin las kyi 'grigs
NK076(mu)002:7897: kyi rim pa ma nor ba'i 'phreng bar ldan pa
NK076(mu)002:7898: can dang / pa dang / sogs dang / las
NK076(mu)002:7899: bzhi'i zhi ba'i yum shing ljon pa ltar skyed bya
NK076(mu)002:7900: bzang zhing rgyud zhi zhing 'jam pa /
NK076(mu)002:7901: rgyas pa shing lcug phran lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:7902: dbang gi sdong gcig /drag po'i me reg ste de ltar mtshan nyid rdzogsa pa'i gzungs ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:7903: rnal 'byor de dag chags sdang med par ming po
NK076(mu)002:7904: dang sring mo'i tshul lta bu'i brtsa gdung che bar
NK076(mu)002:7905: ldan pa / tshom bu lnga ba man chad gcig gis kun bsgom pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:7906: yang na mi grangs lha grangs sprad nas pho mo zung 'brel dag gis bsgrub par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7907: gsum pa yo byad la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:7908: yo byad rnams 'tshogs par bsogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:7912: dang po sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad /
NK076(mu)002:7913: dkar rtsa yab kyi byang sems /
NK076(mu)002:7914: dmar rtsi ste yum gyi rak+ta /
NK076(mu)002:7918: rdo rje dung chen te thod pa rak+ta dmar gyis bkang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7919: mi rkang gi dung dang srog shing ste mi'i sgal tshigs gsar rnying dang /
NK076(mu)002:7920: lha'i rten khro bo'i gzugs bris sku dang /
NK076(mu)002:7921: lugsa chen te lugs sku dang /
NK076(mu)002:7922: dung mchog ste thod sku dang /
NK076(mu)002:7923: dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad dang /
NK076(mu)002:7924: dpal gyi chas brgyad de bcu drug tshang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7925: sgrub pa po rnams 'tsho ba'i ya byad kha zas rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:7926: sgrub pa rdzas kyi ya byad rdo rje dril bu /
NK076(mu)002:7927: mar me sogs mchod rdzas thams cad dang /
NK076(mu)002:7928: zhing du gyur pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7929: bkra shis dag pa'i zhing skye ba bdun pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7930: 'dir thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing bcu te /
NK076(mu)002:7931: mchog las gyur pa bdun dang /
NK076(mu)002:7932: mchog phran ngan song gsum dang /
NK076(mu)002:7934: bar chad rkyen zlog gi yo byad la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:7936: phur ba dang lce baga ste gu gul nag po /
NK076(mu)002:7937: nang zlog sman dang sman par bcas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7938: dgra zlog rdo rje go cha mtshon cha mda' mdung ral gri dang bacasa pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7939: tshogs sgrub la dgos pa ji snyed pa yi rdzas rnams kun /
NK076(mu)002:7940: gnyis pa de ji ltar spyad na /
NK076(mu)002:7941: rnal 'byor pa rang nyid 'jigs byed dpal chen po'i
NK076(mu)002:7942: skur gsal ba'i ting 'dzin dang ldan pas thams cad
NK076(mu)002:7944: nyams nga ba dang bag tsha ba'i 'jigs pa med pa'i semas kyis spyad par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7946: yo byad de rnams bsdus te yo byad tshogs su bya zhing bsgrub pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:7947: rang gis dngos grub ci 'dod pa'i yo byad gang
NK076(mu)002:7948: dagsa par snang ba thams cad badga gisa tshang bar
NK076(mu)002:7949: dgonga bar bya'o // bzhi pa dus la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7951: sgrub pa'i zhag grangs ni blo tha mas sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gama /
NK076(mu)002:7952: rab kyis zhag drug cu ste zla ba gnyis dang /
NK076(mu)002:7953: 'bring gis zhag dagu bcu rtsa drug ste zla ba gsum dang zhag drug gi bar du /
NK076(mu)002:7954: 'jigs byed chen po'i khro tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bsgoma par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7955: gnyis pa dus la re dogas med par bsgrub pa /
NK076(mu)002:7956: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i lha yab yum zung du 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK076(mu)002:7957: lta sgom gyi gdengs dang bacasa pa'i bsam pa yisa
NK076(mu)002:7958: 'bras bu thob tu re ba dang ma thob pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7959: dogs pa med par rab tu brtson 'grus bskyed la
NK076(mu)002:7960: bsgrub bo // lnga pa sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:7961: rgyas pa'i le'u don brgyad pa ltar tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:7962: ngag glu tshig sgra dang lus bro gara 'du 'phro
NK076(mu)002:7964: shes raba thabsa su sbyor shesa pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7965: thabs shes gnyis su med par rol ba'i nyi zla
NK076(mu)002:7966: byanga chub semas kyi bde bas bdag gzhan la mchoda
NK076(mu)002:7967: pa dang / sgrub pa'i dus kyi lus ngag gi
NK076(mu)002:7968: brda la sogas pa'i yon tan ni ji ltar zhe
NK076(mu)002:7969: pa dang / na / 'grub thag nye ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:7971: gzhan zil gyis gnon pa phal pa'i yid tshod du
NK076(mu)002:7972: mi 'gyur ba sogs kyi dgos ched du ma yod
NK076(mu)002:7973: do // rgyas par kun 'dus kyi brda'i le'u las shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7974: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang btung ba rnams ro zhim pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7975: bgo ba reg bya 'jam pa la sogs 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga dang ldan pa rnams /
NK076(mu)002:7976: rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin mthun pa thams cad
NK076(mu)002:7977: kyis mdor na khro bo tshogas sgrub kyi tshom bu
NK076(mu)002:7978: gcig gsum lnga po rnams mngon sum du bsgrub par
NK076(mu)002:7979: bya'o // gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7981: lam spyi yi bsnyen sgrub sngon zhi ba'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:7982: gnyis pa sgrub ba'i bsnyen sgrub la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:7983: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba dngos dang /
NK076(mu)002:7984: sgrub pa'i grogs yo byad la spyad thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:7987: khro bo tshogs sgrub pa'i thabs kyi bsnyen pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:7990: grub pa chen po bzhi ni gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:7991: gnyis pa brgyad bshad la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:7997: dang po ting 'dzin nam dal brtsig cing bri ba /
NK076(mu)002:7998: dang pa bsnyen pa'i dus kyi tshe na gong du
NK076(mu)002:7999: bshad pa'i gnas chena po dben pa'i sa phyogs der
NK076(mu)002:8001: slob dpon mthar nye ba'i lam pas rgyang grags dang
NK076(mu)002:8002: dpag tshad la sagas pa mchog gi dkyil 'khor bya
NK076(mu)002:8003: ba dang / blo chung ba rnams kyis lhag pa
NK076(mu)002:8004: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor tshom bu gcig pa lus
NK076(mu)002:8005: ba dang / gang ngam / gsum pa la lus da'am /
NK076(mu)002:8006: lnga pa la lus gsum gya tshad /
NK076(mu)002:8007: dpon slob gnyis ka blo chen lhag pa'i ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:8008: gyi gzugs brnyan rang gi rig pas dpag tshad rgyang
NK076(mu)002:8009: grags su bsgom ci nus par lha'i dkyil 'khor gsal
NK076(mu)002:8011: blo chung na gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la phyag rgya ste thugs phyag mtshan /
NK076(mu)002:8012: gzugs te sku tsaka li dang /
NK076(mu)002:8013: snying po ste gsung yig 'bru dang bcas pa rnams
NK076(mu)002:8014: kha dog lnga yi tshona gyis dkyil 'khor bri bar
NK076(mu)002:8015: bya'o // gnyis pa yo byad byin gyis brlab pa /
NK076(mu)002:8016: de nas yo byad rnams sngon zhi ba'i skabs bzhin du tsho gsum bcad la byin gyis brlabs nasa /
NK076(mu)002:8017: gsum pa phyi mchod bya zhing phyi mtshams bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:8018: phyi mchod bya ba ni rang nyid rdo rje sems
NK076(mu)002:8019: dpa' la lha mo bcu gnyis kyis bskor bar bsgoms
NK076(mu)002:8020: la / 'phags pa rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs
NK076(mu)002:8021: rnams spyan drangs shing mchod cing phya rol ba'i chos
NK076(mu)002:8022: la / skyong ni / phyogs skyong bcu dang rgyal
NK076(mu)002:8023: chen bzhi la gtor ma dang pos mnyes par bya
NK076(mu)002:8024: la / skyong ni / ba dang / snying rje dang lan chags kyi mgron gnyis pa yang /
NK076(mu)002:8026: tha ma sbyin pasa shes pa'i rgyud tshima par byas la /
NK076(mu)002:8027: phyogs skyong rgyal chen la bstan pa bsrung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8028: rigs drug 'byung po la rang gnas su dengs shig dang /
NK076(mu)002:8029: bgegs la bar chad ma byed ces bka' bsgo bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:8030: bzhi pa srung 'khor gyis mtshams bcad pa /
NK076(mu)002:8031: de nas phur mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:8032: 'jigs byed zhe sdang rdo rje'i ting 'dzin gyi dbang
NK076(mu)002:8033: du badga rnal 'byor bzhugs nasa h'u k+aa ra dang
NK076(mu)002:8034: / ta ki ra tsa la sogs pa rim par bskul nas /
NK076(mu)002:8035: snying po brjod pa tsam gyis khro bo bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:8036: khro mo bcu 'khor du bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:8037: rang rang las ta ki ra tsa spros te rang
NK076(mu)002:8038: rang gis bskul nas khro bcu'i gdan pad+ma nyi zla'i
NK076(mu)002:8039: steng du phyogs skyong bcu bkug la gzir zhanga phur
NK076(mu)002:8040: pa sku stod khro bo smad phur bur bsgoms nas
NK076(mu)002:8041: / bdud rtsi 'khyil bas phur pa rnams rim par gadba par bsgom la /
NK076(mu)002:8042: de la ye shes khro bo yab yum rnams rang
NK076(mu)002:8043: bzhina gyi gnas 'og min nas snyan gsan dbab spyan
NK076(mu)002:8044: drangs bstim la mchoda pa dang bstod de /
NK076(mu)002:8045: sgrub la bar chada byed pa'i bgegs thams cad khro bo bcu'i ting 'dzin mchog gisa bzlog par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:8046: de ltar bsnyen sgrub kun gyi thun monga du mtshon
NK076(mu)002:8047: cha lnga yi bsrung ba'i 'khor la bsgom par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:8048: // gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8050: bsnyen pa song ba de na sa gnyis pa nye bsnyen la /
NK076(mu)002:8051: dal gyi rgyan zhing gi bla re dang /
NK076(mu)002:8052: rgyu ma'i lda ldi la sogs steng logs kyi rgyan rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:8053: rdor dril thod sku sogs sgrub pa'i rdzas gang yin dang /
NK076(mu)002:8054: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi mchod pa rnams dgram pa rdzogsa nas /
NK076(mu)002:8055: phyi mtshams ni bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i ting 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:8056: mtshan nyid sde gsum la bka' bsgo log pa'i bgegs bsrung /
NK076(mu)002:8057: nang mtshams rnam par rgyal ba'i spyi bo nas mi
NK076(mu)002:8058: g.yo ba bskyed pa'i ting 'dzin gyis phyi rgyud sde
NK076(mu)002:8059: gsum la bka' bsgo log pa'i bgegs bsrung /
NK076(mu)002:8060: gsang mtshams khro bo bcus bsrung bas bskyed rdzogs gsum
NK076(mu)002:8061: la bka' bsgo log pa'i bgegs bsrung bar bya ste
NK076(mu)002:8062: / sngon dpal chen pos las kyi srin pa'i rgyal
NK076(mu)002:8063: po ma tam ka ru tra mnan pa'i tshul bzhina
NK076(mu)002:8065: sgrub pa po ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir rtagsa gsum dang ldan ces /
NK076(mu)002:8066: skra mtshams zhag gi zo ris /
NK076(mu)002:8067: dpral mtshams thal chen tshom bu /
NK076(mu)002:8068: smin mtshams rak+ta'i thig le gsum gdab par bya /
NK076(mu)002:8069: brjod med kyi bshags pas sgrib pa sbyangs dam bca' ye shes lha'i byin dbab par bya /
NK076(mu)002:8070: de nas rang lhar gsal bas phyi nang gsang ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8071: mchod rdzas rnams gzhung bzhin byin gyis brlab par bya'o
NK076(mu)002:8072: // gnyis pa gzhung bzhin bya ba de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:8074: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing phrin las kyi rim pa /
NK076(mu)002:8078: rgyan dang cha lugs rdzogs par bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:8079: yan lag gi lhas dbang bskur byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8082: sngon 'gro rdzogs pa da nas khro bo'i lha'i 'khor la ste tshom bu gcig pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:8083: tshom bu gsum pa dang tshom bu lnga ru bsgom par bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8084: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8085: dang po gzhal yas khang du lha bsgom tshul spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:8086: gnas gzhal yas khang ni tshom bu gcig pa la
NK076(mu)002:8087: 'og gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar 'khor lo
NK076(mu)002:8088: rtsibs bzhi dang / gsum pa la lte ba dang shar nub kyi rtsibs la rtsibs bzhi pa gsum /
NK076(mu)002:8089: lnga ba la lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi bcas la 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:8090: bar khyams sga gnyis rim rnams su lha ji ltar
NK076(mu)002:8091: bsgom na dpal 'jigs byed chen po khro bo'i 'akhara
NK076(mu)002:8092: la rtsibs bzhi dang ldan pa'i dbus kyi lte ba
NK076(mu)002:8093: la rigs kyi gtso bo btsun mo'i tshogs dang rigs
NK076(mu)002:8094: chung gi khro bo'i tshogas dang ldan par bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:8095: ni / gnyis pa tshom bu'i lha sgom thabs bye brag tu bshad pa de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:8096: dang po tshom bu gcig pa /
NK076(mu)002:8097: de yang zhi ba shar dang drag pa byang dbang
NK076(mu)002:8098: nub dang rgyas pa lho'i rtsibs chung bzhi po der
NK076(mu)002:8099: gdul bya 'jigs par byed pa'i tshogs chen bud+ta dang
NK076(mu)002:8102: rat+na te ru ka bzhi po de bzhugs pa'i sa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:8103: de yi dbus su rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid zhi
NK076(mu)002:8104: ba las draga por bcosa pa badz+ra he ru ka'i
NK076(mu)002:8105: tshul du / rang gi sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung
NK076(mu)002:8106: thugsa kyi dkyil gtso bo yab yum dang 'khor rigs
NK076(mu)002:8107: bzhi yab yum du gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:8108: de ltar rdo rje rigs kyi de bzhin rigs dang /
NK076(mu)002:8112: ral gri las kyi rigs kyi tshom bu pho brang gi lha yab yum bcu bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:8113: gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa /
NK076(mu)002:8114: tshom bu gcig pa las gzhan pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK076(mu)002:8115: rdo rje'i tshom bu gsum pa la mos pa yin
NK076(mu)002:8116: na / mdun du sku b+hud+d+ha'i tshom bu /
NK076(mu)002:8117: rgyab tu gsung pad+ma'i tshom bu /
NK076(mu)002:8118: dbus su thugs rdo rje rigs kyi 'jigs byed khro
NK076(mu)002:8119: bo tshom bu de dag re re la lha bcu
NK076(mu)002:8120: bcu ste pho brang gi lha sum cu bskyed do
NK076(mu)002:8121: // gsum pa tshom bu lnga pa'i lha bskyed cing bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:8122: 'jigs byed khro bo'i tshom bu lnga po de nyid
NK076(mu)002:8123: la yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni
NK076(mu)002:8124: / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad rigs lngar 'dus
NK076(mu)002:8125: pa'i phyir na tshom bu cha lnga yi rigs lnga
NK076(mu)002:8126: re re la'ang rigs chung bcas pa'i yab yum zung
NK076(mu)002:8127: nya shu rtsa lnga ste 'khor lo cha lnga la
NK076(mu)002:8128: / bkod pa ni / mdun sku yi rigs bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum la /
NK076(mu)002:8130: byams pa'i snying po yab yum /
NK076(mu)002:8131: thugs rje'i snying po yab yum /
NK076(mu)002:8132: lo ka'i snying po yab yum /
NK076(mu)002:8133: btang snyoms yab yum ste bcu /
NK076(mu)002:8134: rgyab gsung gi rigs pad+ma he ru ka yab yum gyi 'khor /
NK076(mu)002:8138: 'byung bar byed pa yab yum ste tshom bu bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:8139: dbus thugs kyi rigs badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi 'khor /
NK076(mu)002:8143: karma snying po yab yum ste bcu /
NK076(mu)002:8144: g.yas yon tan gyi rigs rat+na he ru ka yab yum gyi 'khor /
NK076(mu)002:8148: sna tshogs rdo rje yab yum ste bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:8149: g.yon phrin lasa kyi rigs karma he ru ka yab yum gyi 'khor /
NK076(mu)002:8152: nyams myong yab yum dang bcu ste pho brang lha lnga bcu yongs su rdzogs par bsgom mo //
NK076(mu)002:8156: khro bo yab yum nyi shu bcas /
NK076(mu)002:8158: brgya dang bco brgyad yod do //
NK076(mu)002:8159: gnyis pa rgyan cha lugs rdzogs par bsgom pa /
NK076(mu)002:8160: de dag kyang dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:8162: 'bar ba'i gar dgu'i cha lugsa la sogs pa gdul
NK076(mu)002:8163: bya gdug pa can 'jigs pa'i khro bo'i tshogas na
NK076(mu)002:8164: rang bzhin 'og min na 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i
NK076(mu)002:8166: sgrub pa po yab yum zung gcig gis lha yab yum spyir bsgom pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:8167: yang na rnal 'byor pa ra re lha re re ru bsgom pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:8168: de dag kyang tshama rngam chen po'i rol ba khro bo'i cha lugsa su gsal bar bsgom pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8169: gsum pa yan lag gi lhas dbang bskur byin gyis brlab pa /
NK076(mu)002:8170: de nas lha thams cad la yan lag lhag pa'i dkyil 'akhara dbu rgyan lnga /
NK076(mu)002:8172: ye shes sems dpa' dang dgu dgura lha re re ldana pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:8173: de ltar sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i lha gsum dang /
NK076(mu)002:8174: ye shes lngas dbang bskur thob pa'i rtags su dbu rgyan rigs kyi lha lnga /
NK076(mu)002:8175: thugs ye shes sems dpa' ste lha dgu dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:8176: pa'i bdag nyid dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa
NK076(mu)002:8177: la / gnyis pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs pa la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:8178: dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i las rim bstan pa dngos /
NK076(mu)002:8179: rang bzhin ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor snyan gsan dbab /
NK076(mu)002:8180: spyan drangs la lcags kyus phyag rgyas dgug /zhags pas
NK076(mu)002:8181: gzhug /lcags sgrog gis bcing brtan par bzhugs su gsol
NK076(mu)002:8182: / dril bus dgyes pa bskyed nas /
NK076(mu)002:8183: phyag 'tshal nas sman mchod yan chad kyis rim pa
NK076(mu)002:8184: bzhin mchod par bya' //gnyis pa bdud rtsi dngos grub
NK076(mu)002:8185: blang ba'i sngags / lce ston gyi 'grel bar /
NK076(mu)002:8188: khong la yod pas kha bskangs ba'i dgongs pa ltar bshad na /
NK076(mu)002:8190: sku'i snying po su ra to bde ba /
NK076(mu)002:8197: ka phrin las sam yang na khrag 'thung /
NK076(mu)002:8203: sku'i sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK076(mu)002:8207: am a am gsung gi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK076(mu)002:8211: h'u h'u h'u thugs kyi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK076(mu)002:8212: lung gra chad la nyal ba zur la bslang ba s+w+aa dang h+aa gnyis yin te /
NK076(mu)002:8213: s+w+aa yon tan gyi snying po /
NK076(mu)002:8216: s+w+aam s+w+aa s+w+aam yon tan gyi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK076(mu)002:8217: h+aa phrin las kyi snying po /
NK076(mu)002:8220: h+aa h+aam h+aa phrin las kyi sku gsung thugs gsum mo //
NK076(mu)002:8221: badz+ra rdo rje ma h+aa chen po ka pa la
NK076(mu)002:8222: thod pa kharga snying po d+ha na sbyin pa dz+wa
NK076(mu)002:8223: la 'bar ba sad+d+hi dngos grub ste bde ba bdud
NK076(mu)002:8224: rtsi chen po lnga dpal 'bar ba khrag 'thung chen
NK076(mu)002:8225: po sngags kyi dkyil 'khor rigs lnga'i sku gsung thugs
NK076(mu)002:8226: yon tan phrin las kyi dngos grub stsol cig pa'o
NK076(mu)002:8227: // de ni bdud rtsi 'bul zhing dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:8228: gsum pa rnam lnga'i mchod pa ma h+aa chen po
NK076(mu)002:8229: sh+r+ai dpal he ru ka khrag 'thung a me me
NK076(mu)002:8230: tog d+hu me bdug /spos sid+d+ho grub pa b+ha wa
NK076(mu)002:8231: tu gyur cig /sam ha ra na sdud cig /h'u
NK076(mu)002:8233: dpal khrag 'thung chen po la me tog bdug spos
NK076(mu)002:8234: kyi mchod pas don gnyis grub par gyur cig /de
NK076(mu)002:8235: nas lha mo rang la bsdu bas thugs badz+ra khrag
NK076(mu)002:8236: 'thung gi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par
NK076(mu)002:8237: bsam / de ni gtor ma'i steng gi 'dod yon gyi lha mos mchod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8242: sa ma ya dam tshig /ru lu ru lu hub gsum btung ba /
NK076(mu)002:8245: de ni rnal 'byor chen po nang gi dam tshig las mi 'da' ba'i phyir dam blang ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8246: gtor ma hub gsum btung bas sku gsung thugs kyi
NK076(mu)002:8247: dam tshig las mi 'da' bas dngos grub ngo mtshar
NK076(mu)002:8249: lnga pa gtor ma 'bul zhing mchod stod bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:8263: kh+aa hi gsol cig /a la la ho mnyes pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:8264: gtor ma bdud rtsi bde ba'i phreng ba rgyun chad med par 'bul bas /
NK076(mu)002:8265: mnyes pa chen po'i phreng ba rgyun chad med pa
NK076(mu)002:8266: 'byung ba'i gnas yi dam 'bar ba khrag 'thung tshogs
NK076(mu)002:8267: kyi gtso bo la mchod cing 'khor rnal 'byor ma
NK076(mu)002:8268: la sbyin pa gsol cig mnyes par gyis shig pa'o
NK076(mu)002:8269: // de nas sbyor sgrol la sogs pas mchod nas bstod pa smon lam yan chad rdzogs nasa /
NK076(mu)002:8270: gsum pa bsnyen pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:8273: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' gsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8274: lha ye shes sems dpa'i dza bra khang mdun du
NK076(mu)002:8275: ltags pa ste mda' gang tsam gyi nam mkha' la
NK076(mu)002:8276: gsal zhing / bzlas pa'i 'phro 'du gsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8278: lha dang bdag 'phro 'du gsum ldan gyi sga nas bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8280: ni ye shes lnga ldan sngags kyi mgo 'dren /
NK076(mu)002:8281: badz+ra rdo rje ma h+aa chen po kro d+ha khro bo sh+r+aa dpal he ru ka khrag 'thung /
NK076(mu)002:8282: badz+ra rdo rje kro d+h+ai khro mo shwa ri dbyings
NK076(mu)002:8283: phyug ma sarba thams cad dush+ta na sngang ba h'u
NK076(mu)002:8284: sdud cig phata sgrol cig pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:8285: ming nas bos pa'i sngags so //
NK076(mu)002:8286: ru lu ma h+aa sa ma ya h'u ni thugs dam gnad nas dbab pa'i sngags so //
NK076(mu)002:8287: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u ni bsnyen sngags
NK076(mu)002:8288: sam che yon gyi sgo nas bstod pa'i sngags so
NK076(mu)002:8289: // lce ston gyis bsnyen pa'i dus su badz+ra /
