NK076(mu)002:8290: rtsa ba ru lu gnyis snang /
NK076(mu)002:8292: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK076(mu)002:8294: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /ru lu ru lu ma h+aa sa ma ya h'u phata /
NK076(mu)002:8296: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /badz+ra kro t+ai
NK076(mu)002:8297: shwa ri sarba dush+tam h'u phatah sgrub pa chen po'i
NK076(mu)002:8298: dus thams cad dril te bzla gsungs /
NK076(mu)002:8299: gsum pa rigs gzhan la'ang bsnyen dus kyi dmigs pa de ltar du bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:8300: de ltar badz+ra he kur ka la bzlas bsnyen skyol
NK076(mu)002:8301: nas sogs khong na rigs lnga gzhan bzlas te khro
NK076(mu)002:8302: bcu'i sngags bcas bsnyen pa bya ba ni 'od zer
NK076(mu)002:8303: 'phro 'adu yasa / zhag bdun gyi bar sgrib pa
NK076(mu)002:8304: sbyong bar ye shes pa'i rgyud bskul dang dngos grub
NK076(mu)002:8305: kyi snod du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8308: de yang ye shes kyi lha mdun gyi bar snang du bzhugs pa la /
NK076(mu)002:8309: dam tshig sems dpa'i thugs ka nas 'od zer byung nas /
NK076(mu)002:8310: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar 'phros thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK076(mu)002:8311: tshur 'dus sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangsa nas dngos
NK076(mu)002:8312: grub kyi snod du rung bar byed par bsam zhing
NK076(mu)002:8313: / 'phro 'du bsnol mar byed pa ni bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogsa pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8316: lha bskyed pa dang sngags bzlas pa nye bsnyen de
NK076(mu)002:8317: bzhin du sgrub pa bya ba'i dus su yang 'od
NK076(mu)002:8318: zer dmar po phar 'phros tshur 'dus kyis dngos grub
NK076(mu)002:8319: stsol cig par thugs rgyud bskul ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8320: tshur 'dus pas bdag la dngos grub sdud par bsam zhing /
NK076(mu)002:8321: sngags bzlas pa'i skyon bcu rgya gcig skabs ltar spangsa te bsgrub par bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8322: de ltar sgrub pa byed pa'i dus su dgos par shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:8323: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:8324: dang po sgrub pa bya ba dngos /
NK076(mu)002:8325: de yang nub tha ma'i zhag gcig de la sgrub
NK076(mu)002:8326: pa'i dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams shin tu bstar zhing
NK076(mu)002:8327: sngags bzlas pa'i 'od zer mthing ga phar mi 'phro
NK076(mu)002:8328: bar tshur bsdu ba'i dgongs pa 'ba' zhig bya ba
NK076(mu)002:8329: ni sgrub pa chen pa'i dngos grub len pa yin
NK076(mu)002:8331: gnyis pa spyir dzapa dgongs kyi ting 'dzin bya thabs /
NK076(mu)002:8332: nye bsnyen dus sdig sgrib sbyang zhing nyes skyon dag
NK076(mu)002:8333: pa'i phyir 'od zer dang yig 'bru shel gyi bung
NK076(mu)002:8334: ba lta bu kha dog dkar po bya zhes pa
NK076(mu)002:8335: dang / sgrub pa'i dus dngos grub la chags shing dbang du sdud phyir /
NK076(mu)002:8336: 'od zer yig 'bru rnams bya ru'i bung ba ltar kha dog dmar po bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8337: sgrub pa chen po'i dus dngos grub gzhan gyi dbang
NK076(mu)002:8338: du mi 'gyur ba'i rtags su 'od zer mthing ga'i
NK076(mu)002:8339: bung ba mang po dag ltar dmigs /
NK076(mu)002:8340: bsnyen sgrub kyi rim pa bzhin du nye bsnyen dang /
NK076(mu)002:8341: sgrub pa'i dus bunga ba me tog la phar 'gro tshur 'ong byed pa ltar dang /
NK076(mu)002:8342: sgrub pa chen po'i dus matsha la sera ba chena
NK076(mu)002:8343: po 'bab pa bzhin 'od zer tshur bstim pa yin
NK076(mu)002:8344: no // gsum pa rtags byung na bar chad brtag cing dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8345: ngan rtags 'od dkar po srog bdag /sngon po klu /
NK076(mu)002:8347: nag po dam log gi rtags /
NK076(mu)002:8352: dra yang ngan pa gla rtsi gzhob dri /
NK076(mu)002:8353: bzang po dri zhim pa nyams dga' ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8354: sgra mi snyan pa yun thung ba ngan rtags /
NK076(mu)002:8355: snyan nas yun ring ba lha'i rtags dang /
NK076(mu)002:8356: gzugs yid du mi 'ong ba srin po lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)002:8357: lha'i gzugs gsal zhing nyams dga' ba bzang rtags so //
NK076(mu)002:8358: phyag mtshan dang sgrub rdzas rnams nam mkhar 'khor ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8359: mar me cher 'bar ba dang bza' btung sman raka gtor ma rnams 'khola ba sogs rtags byung na /
NK076(mu)002:8360: bdud kyi bar chad dang lha'i 'grub rtags kyi cha
NK076(mu)002:8361: rnamas gang yin dpal he ru ka'i sngags dang phyag
NK076(mu)002:8362: rgya'am / thod pa tshar gsum gyi phyag rgya sngags rang gi nyams kyis brtag par byas te /
NK076(mu)002:8365: gal te bar chad yin na rdo rje drag po'i
NK076(mu)002:8366: sngags dang phyag rgya ting 'dzin rdzas sogs kyis bskrad
NK076(mu)002:8367: de bdag nyid lhar gsal go bgo lus bsrungsa byas
NK076(mu)002:8368: la / sgrub pa'i zhag grangs tshang zhing dngos grub kyi rtags byung na /
NK076(mu)002:8369: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gyi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos
NK076(mu)002:8370: grub rang gi lus ngag yid gsum gyi rtog pa'i
NK076(mu)002:8371: gnas su mthun pa nyid du sbyar zhing /
NK076(mu)002:8374: rdzu 'phul rkang pa la bstim pa sogs rtog tshogs
NK076(mu)002:8375: kyi gnas su dngos grub bstim zhing k+aa ya w+aak+ka
NK076(mu)002:8376: tsit+ta ma h+aa tish+tha badz+ra dang /
NK076(mu)002:8377: sems can gyi don gyi phyir dngos grub brtan para bya'o /
NK076(mu)002:8378: rtags ldan nas dngos grub blang pa des na sngon zhi ba tshogs sgrub skabs bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:8381: yo byad la spyad pas so so'i yo tan dang rnam pa gsum thoba pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:8382: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub gsum thob par 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)002:8383: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i grogs yo byad la spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8384: sbyor sgrol gnyis la spyod thabs dang /
NK076(mu)002:8385: yo byad bzhi la spyod thabs so //
NK076(mu)002:8387: dang po bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:8388: las gzhu nga rdzogs nas zhi bar khas blangs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:8389: gsang ba sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa rgyas para bshad
NK076(mu)002:8391: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8396: bsgral bas mi gos pa'i gtan tshigs /
NK076(mu)002:8397: sgrol ba'i nges tshig /sbyor sgrol don la tha dad med par bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8399: dang po mngon du phyung ba'i sgrol ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8400: de yang zhing du gyur pa la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:8401: bkra shis dag pa skye ba bdun pa /
NK076(mu)002:8402: thugs rjes bzung ba la bdun mchog dang /
NK076(mu)002:8403: mchog phran ngan song gsum ste bcu po de rnams /
NK076(mu)002:8404: dkyil 'khor lhor gru gsum bri ste e ram gyis drag po'i dal bskyed la /
NK076(mu)002:8406: ma las byung ba'i nya zla'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK076(mu)002:8407: bsgral ba'i thabs la mkhas pas gan rkyal gyis snying gar rdo rjes mnan bzhag go //
NK076(mu)002:8408: lha'i nga rgyal bdag dpal chen po'i nga rgyal /
NK076(mu)002:8409: sgrol ging ta ki ra tsa /
NK076(mu)002:8412: bsgral bya ru tra rang rgyal dang lnga /
NK076(mu)002:8414: lngas lag gi 'adu byed kyis bsgral lo //
NK076(mu)002:8415: ting 'dzin bsgom pa bsgral bya'i rnam shes h'u dkar po drug tu gyur pas /
NK076(mu)002:8416: 'khor bar skye ba'i sa bon drug bag chags bcas
NK076(mu)002:8417: rnam par dag /h'u de sna bug g.yon nas zhugs
NK076(mu)002:8418: sku'i dbyibs brgyud yum gyi mkha' dbyings su thim par
NK076(mu)002:8419: bsgom / de nas yum mkhar yig 'bru de thugs
NK076(mu)002:8420: phyag rgyar rdo rje 'od 'abra ba gcig tu gyur
NK076(mu)002:8421: bsgom / / rdo rje de rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK076(mu)002:8422: skur gyur te 'od zera sna lnga 'phro bas rab
NK076(mu)002:8423: tu brjid pa dang ldan pa /
NK076(mu)002:8424: rdor sems spyi gtsug tu 'khor ba las rnam para
NK076(mu)002:8425: rgyal ba mi bskyod pa tshon gang ba rigs bdag
NK076(mu)002:8426: bcas bsgom / de ltar bsgral ba'i shes pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:8427: de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje sems dpar byin gyis
NK076(mu)002:8429: a las zla dkyil du bzhag pa /
NK076(mu)002:8430: yam las rlung gis bteg nas a yam s+pha ra na phatah ces pas 'og min du 'phangs te /
NK076(mu)002:8431: 'og min gyi rgyal ba rdo rje sems dpa' yab
NK076(mu)002:8432: yum gyi mkha' gsang du song nas rdo rje' rigs
NK076(mu)002:8434: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dbang yang bskur /
NK076(mu)002:8435: h'u badz+ra ng+h+rikra mum d+aa du shwa r+ai /
NK076(mu)002:8436: zhes brjod pas rdor sems yab yum gyi skur gyur /
NK076(mu)002:8437: phata dzahs phyir brton pas mtshan dpe rdzogs pa'i skur gyur par bsgom /
NK076(mu)002:8438: gnyis pa thabs chen pos bsgral ba /
NK076(mu)002:8439: de yang sngon byung dus su sku gsung thugs shin
NK076(mu)002:8440: tu khros pa'i khro bo dpal chen po rdo rje
NK076(mu)002:8441: srin po yisa thugs rje dang bsgral ba'i thabs kyi
NK076(mu)002:8442: sgo nas lha chen ru tra 'khor dang bcas pa
NK076(mu)002:8443: bsgral ba ltar / rjes 'jug gi rnal 'byor pas
NK076(mu)002:8444: chos nyid mngon sum du lta bas rtogsa pa'i gdeng
NK076(mu)002:8445: ldan gyi ting 'dzin gyis goms nas /
NK076(mu)002:8446: sbyor lam mthar phyin pa'i dus su bsgral bya sgrol
NK076(mu)002:8447: byed gnyis su med para thabs kyi sgo nas bsgral
NK076(mu)002:8448: zhing rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bya'o
NK076(mu)002:8449: // gsum pa dbang po yul dus kyi /
NK076(mu)002:8451: sbyor lam pa'i thugs rje chana po'i sgo nas dgongs pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK076(mu)002:8452: gang bsgral na a n+ri su tri pre du dza
NK076(mu)002:8453: zhes lam rgyud lnga'i semas cana ma lus pa'i rnam
NK076(mu)002:8456: sems can thams cad kyi bdag 'dzin ma lus pa
NK076(mu)002:8457: chos nyid gnyis su med pa'i ngang du bsgral bar
NK076(mu)002:8458: bya'o // bzhi pa rang bzhin gyi /
NK076(mu)002:8459: bsgral zhing ni phyi nang snod bcud kyi 'jig rten
NK076(mu)002:8460: ji snyed na gnas pa'i 'gro drug gi sems can
NK076(mu)002:8461: phra rags ma lus pa kun /
NK076(mu)002:8462: sgrol mkhan bdag nyid dag mnyam chena pa lta bas rtogs pa sbyor lam pa yi /
NK076(mu)002:8464: rang bzhin mnyam nyid kyi dbyings su yang ni rtogs pas bsgral bar bya ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:8465: lnga pa ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol ba /
NK076(mu)002:8466: phyi ltar dbus kyi ra rab chena po'i phyogs bzhi'i
NK076(mu)002:8467: gling bzhi gling phran brgyad la gnas pa'i semas can
NK076(mu)002:8468: bsgral bya ma lus pa kun /
NK076(mu)002:8469: sgrol ba'i mkhan po thugs rja chen pa'i stong nyid
NK076(mu)002:8470: snying rje dang ldan pa'i sbyor lam rnal 'byor pa
NK076(mu)002:8471: ting 'dzin dang ldan pa'i byin rlabsa kyis /
NK076(mu)002:8472: bsgral thabs ting 'dzin rang rig ram du gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8473: ye shes kyi me chana po 'bar bar bsgom par
NK076(mu)002:8474: byas te / ye shes kyi me des sems can
NK076(mu)002:8475: thams cad kyi rgyud la gnas pa'i rnam rtog bag
NK076(mu)002:8476: chags ma lus pa bsreg para bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:8477: sems can kun gyi sems gnyis med chos kyi dbyingsa
NK076(mu)002:8478: su yanga ni rang grol du bstim pa ste rtogs
NK076(mu)002:8480: sa steng ste srid pa khams gsum mam /
NK076(mu)002:8481: nang lus ngag yid gsum gyi mtshan la thams cad bsreg pa'i me yin no //
NK076(mu)002:8482: me rang rgyud pas bsregs pa ltar ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:8483: rnal 'byor pa'i yida kyi rnam par shes pa lta
NK076(mu)002:8484: dgongs las su rung bas ye shes kyi me ru
NK076(mu)002:8485: rab tu 'bar te bsregs pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:8486: ye shes kyi me bskyed pa'i sa bon ni /
NK076(mu)002:8488: gnyis pa bsgral bas mi gos pa'i gtan tshigs la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:8489: dang po bden pa gnyis kyi tshul du rtogs pas
NK076(mu)002:8490: sbyor sgrol gyis mi gos pa na des bdag la
NK076(mu)002:8491: mi sgrib / gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyed pas
NK076(mu)002:8492: ngo mtshar zhing las ngan spyad pas gnas ngan par
NK076(mu)002:8493: 'agro ba'i rgyu zhing bcu thams cad sdug bsngal las
NK076(mu)002:8494: thar bar byed pa'i thabas 'di las lhag pa med
NK076(mu)002:8495: mi sgrib / do // gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang
NK076(mu)002:8496: ba ye gdod ma nas skye ba med pa'i rgyu
NK076(mu)002:8497: shes pa'i lta bas de bzhina nyid rtogs /
NK076(mu)002:8498: rkyen 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams su blangs pas /
NK076(mu)002:8499: lus sgyu mar snang ba 'di yang thol mir 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:8500: pa lta ra mig yor gyi tshul du shes nas
NK076(mu)002:8501: / dngos grub gnyis sgrub pa'i don du sbyor ba dang sgrol ba'i bya ba kun byas kyang /
NK076(mu)002:8502: rang mtshan ltar byas pa'i dri ma rdul phra rab
NK076(mu)002:8503: kyi cha shas tsam yanga byas pa mada pas na
NK076(mu)002:8504: / skyon gyis mi gos bar bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8505: gnyis pa phung po la rnam par dbye ba'i gtan tshigs kyis sgrol bas mi gos pa /
NK076(mu)002:8506: tshul de ltar rtogs na kun rdzob tu sems can bsgral ba yi bya ba kun byas kyang /
NK076(mu)002:8507: don dam ltar na bsgral ba'i dngos pa de dag
NK076(mu)002:8508: ma grub pas rang rgyud pa gang yang med do
NK076(mu)002:8509: // spyir log rtog ngo bor snang ba'i phung po
NK076(mu)002:8510: lnga pa 'di rig pas brtags te rang bzhin med
NK076(mu)002:8511: par phra rab tu gzhig para bya /
NK076(mu)002:8512: bye brag gzugs phung sogs bshigs na sha rus la sogs 'byung ba khams lnga'i bag la zhala /
NK076(mu)002:8513: 'o na bkag pa'i stong pa'o zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:8514: rig pas ma bshigs tsam na yanga sha rus la
NK076(mu)002:8515: sogs 'byung ba lnga yi ngo bo yin pas bsgral
NK076(mu)002:8516: rgyu med do // gsum pa rnam shes la dmigs su med pas sgrol bas mi gos pa /
NK076(mu)002:8517: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad rang rgyud gzugs su grub pa med pasa basda par byas na /
NK076(mu)002:8518: dper na rmi lam du srog gacada par snang yang don la ma grub pa'i tshul ci bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:8519: 'khrul ngor srog gcad bya gcod byed du gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:8520: nyid na yang dag pa'i don la dngos pa rang
NK076(mu)002:8522: bzhi pa sems kyi rang bzhin la sgrol du med pa /
NK076(mu)002:8523: kun gzhi byang chub sems kya rang bzhin spros dang bral ba'i chos nyid de la ni /
NK076(mu)002:8524: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad dgrar langs kyang /
NK076(mu)002:8525: sangs rgyas la sogs sus kyang zin cing sod pa med pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8526: gsum pa sgrol ba'i nges tshig /
NK076(mu)002:8527: 'o na bsgral rgyu med na ci bsgral ce na /
NK076(mu)002:8528: rnal 'byor ba'i thugs rjes gdul bya gang bsgral na /
NK076(mu)002:8529: bdag 'dzin la sogs rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan mar zhen pa thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:8530: log rtog phyin ci log tu 'dzin pa las bzlog par byas ta /
NK076(mu)002:8531: bsgral ba'i lta dgongs ting 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:8532: sngagsa dang phyag rgya rnams la blo shin tu goms
NK076(mu)002:8533: shing brtan par gyur pasa bsgral bya'i shes pa la
NK076(mu)002:8534: dbang bskur te / 'bras bu bla med byang chub kyi zhing la dgod par bya /
NK076(mu)002:8535: log rtog rgyun bcad byang chub la bkod pa de
NK076(mu)002:8536: ka tsam la ni 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i don
NK076(mu)002:8537: gyis bsgral ba zhes bya bar tha snyad du gdags
NK076(mu)002:8538: so // bzhi pa sbyor sgrol tha dad med par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:8539: de yang gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa bsgral ba yi
NK076(mu)002:8540: dus nyid na chos nyid gnyis med du sbyor ba
NK076(mu)002:8543: bsgral bya'i rgyu nyon mongs dang /
NK076(mu)002:8544: 'bras bu sdug bsngal ma lus kun rtsad nas bcad nas /
NK076(mu)002:8545: 'bras bu bla med byang chub kyi gnas su bsgral bas na /
NK076(mu)002:8546: bsgral bya sgrol byed gnyis su med pa chos nyid
NK076(mu)002:8547: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su sbyor ba yin no
NK076(mu)002:8548: // gnyis pa ga na sbyor ba la lnga /
NK076(mu)002:8549: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor ba /
NK076(mu)002:8553: thabs chen po'i sbyor ba'i phan yon gyi ngos nas 'jug bsdu ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:8555: dang po gang la sbyor ba'i yum /
NK076(mu)002:8556: de yang phyi ltar na lha mo dngos dang /
NK076(mu)002:8560: dang po lo grangs kyi dbye ba /
NK076(mu)002:8561: lo bcu gnyis la lha mo /
NK076(mu)002:8563: nyi shu ma rigs ngan mo'o //
NK076(mu)002:8564: gnyis pa rtsa yi sgo nas dbye ba /
NK076(mu)002:8568: gsum pa byang sems sgo nas dbye ba /
NK076(mu)002:8569: nyi zla gnyis 'dzag pa lha mo /
NK076(mu)002:8571: gnyis ka mi 'dzag pa rigs ngan ma'o //
NK076(mu)002:8572: bzhi pa sbyor thabs kyi sgo nas dbye ba /
NK076(mu)002:8573: bdag gzhan gnyis kyi bde ba bskyed pa lha mo /
NK076(mu)002:8575: bdag bde ba tsam rigs ngan ma'o //
NK076(mu)002:8576: de lhar bzang ngan dbye nas rigs bzang brten cing
NK076(mu)002:8577: rigs ngan mi brten pa'am yang rnal 'byor pa nus
NK076(mu)002:8578: pa che na bzang ngan mi dbye bar bya ste
NK076(mu)002:8579: / dngos su lha klu'i bu mo bkug pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:8580: gnyis pa ci ltar sbyor ba'i thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8582: dang po yum la khrus gsum bya /
NK076(mu)002:8584: chos gsum bshad nas sta gon du byas pa ni bsnyen pa'i yan lag /mkha' gsang brlabs /
NK076(mu)002:8587: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos drug cu rtsa bzhis ni /
NK076(mu)002:8588: bde ba rgyas bar byed pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8589: phyag rgya bzhis rol pa ni sgrub pa dang ni /
NK076(mu)002:8590: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blang ba ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK076(mu)002:8591: nub tha ma la mthong lam gyi ye shes chen po rgyud la skye bar byed pa /
NK076(mu)002:8592: dngos grub chen po yum gyi mkha' las blang ba'i dbang du'o //
NK076(mu)002:8593: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:8595: shes rab bam dbyings kyi cha 'dzin pa'i yum gzungs ma mtshan nyid ldan pa la /
NK076(mu)002:8598: dri bzang gi khrus gsum bcas byas la /
NK076(mu)002:8599: dar dang rin po che rus pa'i rgyan gsum gyi chas su zhugs /
NK076(mu)002:8600: gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa /
NK076(mu)002:8601: de nas yum gyi lus la bde gshegas yum gyi
NK076(mu)002:8602: dkyil 'khor kun bkod de phung khams lhar byin brlabs
NK076(mu)002:8603: / mkhang gsang gzhal yas khang du tshom bu'i lha bkod /
NK076(mu)002:8604: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid rig pa rdo rje sems dpa'i lhar bsgomsa nas /
NK076(mu)002:8605: gsum pa sgrub pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:8607: phyag rgya bzhis rol ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8608: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su med par zung 'brel du ldan par bya /
NK076(mu)002:8610: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje dang /
NK076(mu)002:8611: yum gyi dril bu gnyis su med cing las su rung ba dang ldan pa byas par gyur nas /
NK076(mu)002:8612: yum gyi mkha' gsang pad+ma'i rnam pa 'dab ma brgyad
NK076(mu)002:8613: pa'i dkyil 'khora gzhal yas khang du bskyed pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:8614: du / yab kyi gu h+ya badz+ra gzhug la /
NK076(mu)002:8616: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro /
NK076(mu)002:8619: yab kyi byang chub sems thig le nyid yum gyi
NK076(mu)002:8620: pad+ma' gnas su son pas bde ba chen po'i thugsa
NK076(mu)002:8621: kyi dkyil 'khor du spro bar bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8622: g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems /
NK076(mu)002:8625: mthar phyin pa'i sems dang lnga'i rim pa byung ba'i de bzung ba'i thabs kyis ngos zin pa yasa /
NK076(mu)002:8626: lus dang mkhang gsang du bkod pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK076(mu)002:8627: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa la byang chub kyi sems
NK076(mu)002:8628: dgyes pa chen po bde ba'i mchod pa phul bas
NK076(mu)002:8629: / bdag dang sangs rgyas sems can thams cad rang rig pa'i ngo bor mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:8630: bde bas bdag mchod rgyal ba mnyes pa ni mchog ga ma zhen pa'i sbyin pa yin pas na /
NK076(mu)002:8631: gnyis med bde chen du bstim mo //
NK076(mu)002:8632: gsum pa sbyor ba'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:8633: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsum mnyes pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:8634: rnal 'byor pa'i rig pa dang 'gro drug gi sems
NK076(mu)002:8635: can dbyer med pas 'gro ba sems can mang pos
NK076(mu)002:8636: kyang dgyes pa'i bde ba mnyam du thob nasa /
NK076(mu)002:8637: slar yang yab yum bde stong gnyis su med pa'i mkha' dbyings su sgrol bas na thim zhes pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8638: de ltar thim par gyur nas yum gyi mkha' dbyings
NK076(mu)002:8639: nasa lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po 'abra bar bsam
NK076(mu)002:8640: mo // de yang bde bar gshegs pa thabs yab
NK076(mu)002:8641: dang shes raba yum gnyis med du rdzogs shing rigs
NK076(mu)002:8642: lnga lhun grub kyi phyag rgya drug pa kun tu
NK076(mu)002:8643: mo // bzang dang / thub pa drug kyang yang dag par rdzogs /
NK076(mu)002:8644: de ltar snang ba ma 'gags pa bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK076(mu)002:8645: de la ma chags pa ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK076(mu)002:8646: tshogs chen po gnyis kyang rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:8647: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8648: dang po dngos grub chen po yum gyi mkha' las blang ba /
NK076(mu)002:8649: de ltar bde chen ye shes sgrub pa'i thabs yan lag bzhi'i sgrub chen mthar /
NK076(mu)002:8650: dngos grub blang bar bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:8651: gang blang na yab yum gnyis su med par rol
NK076(mu)002:8652: ba las byung ba'i thig le nya zla gnyis 'dres
NK076(mu)002:8653: pa'i yon tan thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i sting
NK076(mu)002:8654: po de / dkyil 'khora thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NK076(mu)002:8655: ye shes lngar gsal bar phyed pa'i rten yin pas
NK076(mu)002:8657: sus blang na bar chad med lam pas /
NK076(mu)002:8659: tshogs sgrub nub tha ma'i tho rangs dus /
NK076(mu)002:8663: thig le 'dren zlog la mkhas pa'i yab kyi rda rje lce yis blang ste /
NK076(mu)002:8664: gsang ba rdo rje nyid do //
NK076(mu)002:8665: yang na lce rdo rje rtse lnga bsgom de yis blang ngam /
NK076(mu)002:8666: tshul ji ltar blang na bung bas me tog 'jib pa'i tshul du blang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:8667: dgos ched ci'i phyir blang na /
NK076(mu)002:8668: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag tu thob par bya phyir blang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:8669: gnyis pa dngos grub blangs pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:8670: dngos grub gnyis te gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:8671: mkha' la bya bzhin 'gro zhing lha'i bu mo la longs spyod /
NK076(mu)002:8674: tsha ring ba la sogs pa'i khong nas sa la
NK076(mu)002:8675: byi ba bzhin 'dzul nas klu'i bu mo la spyod
NK076(mu)002:8676: pa / gzhan yang mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul du ma thob bo //
NK076(mu)002:8677: mchog gi dngos grub ni yid bzhin nor bu rin
NK076(mu)002:8678: po che las ma g.yos bzhin du dgos 'dod char
NK076(mu)002:8679: bzhin 'byung bas na sprin gya tshogs /
NK076(mu)002:8680: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po rgyal ba drug pa yang thob par 'gyur /
NK076(mu)002:8681: gsum pa de ltar sbyor ba'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:8682: 'gro drug gi dus dang gnas nas tha mal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8683: bde ba la sbyor ba'i yon tan de dag snang
NK076(mu)002:8684: zhing yod pa yin kyang ngo ma shes thabs kyis
NK076(mu)002:8686: sbyor ba'i mchod pa thabs kyis zin pa'i ye shes
NK076(mu)002:8687: bde ba chen pa yab yum mnyam par sbyor zhing
NK076(mu)002:8688: / rtog pa thams cada bde stong dbyer med kyi dbyings su sbyor bas na /
NK076(mu)002:8689: de'i yon tan gyis ngan 'gror mi ltung zhing yang
NK076(mu)002:8690: dag pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)002:8691: // bzhi pa sbyor sgrol gnyis don la tha dad med par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:8692: sbyor bas bde chen lhan skyes ye shes kyi don
NK076(mu)002:8693: rtogs pa 'di ni gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa rnams
NK076(mu)002:8694: bsgral ba chen pa'am ngan song las bsgral ba yang
NK076(mu)002:8695: yin la / chags rtog bsgral ba nyid na chos nyid byang chub la sbyor ba yang yin pas /
NK076(mu)002:8696: de ltar sbyor ba'i dus nyid na rtog pa rang
NK076(mu)002:8697: kha ma ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir sbyor sgrol gnyis
NK076(mu)002:8699: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi sbyor ba /
NK076(mu)002:8700: gzhi ye'am gdod ma nasa rtog pa ragas pa thams cad lha yab dang /
NK076(mu)002:8701: phra ba thams cad yum lha mo yi dkyil 'khora
NK076(mu)002:8702: du gsal bar gnas pa yang dag pa'i sa la
NK076(mu)002:8703: sbyor ba dang / gsum pa dbang po yul dus /
NK076(mu)002:8704: dbang pa rnam shes brgyad lha sems dpa' yab brgyad dang /
NK076(mu)002:8705: yul dus brgyad lha sems ma brgyad du gsal ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:8706: de gnyis 'phrad pa ni lha yab yum gnyis med
NK076(mu)002:8707: du sbyor ba ste dbang po yul dus kyi sbyor
NK076(mu)002:8708: ba'o // bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi /
NK076(mu)002:8709: phung po lnga po nyid rigs lnga'i de bzhin gshegas
NK076(mu)002:8710: pa dang sa la sogs pa'i 'byung ba lnga nyid
NK076(mu)002:8711: rigs kyi yum lnga nyid du sbyor ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8712: dbang po bzhi rnam shes bzhi sems dpa' brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:8713: yul bzhi dus bzhi lha ma sems ma brgyad nyid du sbyor ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8714: bdag rtog rnam bzhi khro bo bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)002:8715: rtag chad mu bzhi khra mo bzhi sbyor ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8716: yid chos gnyis kunabazanga yab yum /
NK076(mu)002:8717: nyon drug thub drug /de las gzhan pa khro mo'i
NK076(mu)002:8718: dkyil 'khor la sogs rtog tshogs thams cad ma lus
NK076(mu)002:8720: chos nyid mnyam pa'i dbyings dang de rtogs pa'i rang
NK076(mu)002:8721: rig pa'i ye shes su lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gyis
NK076(mu)002:8722: dkyil 'khor du mnyam par sbyor ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:8723: lnga ba thabs chen po sbyor ba'i phan yon gyis mjug bsdu pa /
NK076(mu)002:8724: sngon byung dus dpal chen pos ma chags thabs kyi sbyor bas srin mo skem ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:8725: dbang mo rnams la rol kyang nyes pas ma gos pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:8726: rjes 'jug rnal 'byor pas yab yum gnyis su med
NK076(mu)002:8727: par sbyor ba yi dus nyid na thabs mkhas bde
NK076(mu)002:8728: ba'i ro la chags pa rang ga ma med pa'o
NK076(mu)002:8729: // de ltar bde ba'i ro la ma chags pa
NK076(mu)002:8730: ye shes su shar ba la pho mo gnyis su
NK076(mu)002:8731: snang nas chags par rang ga ma dang tshul mthun
NK076(mu)002:8732: par chags pa spyod pa'i dus nyid na chags pa'i
NK076(mu)002:8733: ro nyid ye shes su gsal bas chags pa zina
NK076(mu)002:8734: pa dang chagas pa'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa'i
NK076(mu)002:8735: don 'di ni tshangas par spyod pa'i mchog bde ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8736: ye shes la dbang sgyur bas rgyal pa yin te
NK076(mu)002:8737: // / de ni shin tu yang dag pa'i chags
NK076(mu)002:8738: pa chen po spang gnyen ro gcig tu gyur pas
NK076(mu)002:8739: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid yin
NK076(mu)002:8740: // / no // gsum pa rang ga mar spyod pa'i skyon /
NK076(mu)002:8742: don dam chos nyid kyi lta ba ma rtogs pa yi rnal 'byor pas /
NK076(mu)002:8743: kha 'byams tshig gi lta ba sgra'i rjes su 'brangs nas sbyor sgrol rang gar spyad par gyur na /
NK076(mu)002:8744: sbyor ba'i rnam smin 'bras bus yi dwags dang /
NK076(mu)002:8745: ro myags 'dam gyi dmyal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8746: rgyu mthun 'bras bu mngal gyi srin bur skye bar bshad /
NK076(mu)002:8747: sgrol ba'i rnam smin 'bras bu yang sos dmyal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8748: rgyu mthun 'bras bu las kyi srin po'i gnas su skye bar bshad do //
NK076(mu)002:8749: gnyis pa yo byad bzhi la spyod thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8753: dang po spyad thabs kun spyir zhi ba dang mthun par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:8754: sbyor lam rnal 'byor pas tshogs sgrub pa'i mchod pa byed pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:8755: 'gro nyal 'dug sdod la sogs spyod lam bzhi po thams cad du /
NK076(mu)002:8756: dur khrod chas brgyad kyi rgyan rnams bgos shing gdags par byas te /
NK076(mu)002:8757: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad rnams zhi ba tshogs
NK076(mu)002:8758: sgrub kyi rjes su mthun par mtshan med ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:8760: rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gar ngag gi glu
NK076(mu)002:8761: tshiga rnams kyang mtshan med kyi ting 'dzin gsal ba
NK076(mu)002:8763: gnyis pa bro gar spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8764: dang po lta ba'i phyag rgya lha gsal ba'i ngang las mi 'da' ba /
NK076(mu)002:8765: dbang po dang yul dang dus dang rig pa rnam shes te rtog tshogs de rnams /
NK076(mu)002:8766: dbang po dang rnam shes ni thabs yab dang /
NK076(mu)002:8767: yul dus ni shes raba yum du gsal ba gnyis su med par ldan par 'gyur zhing /
NK076(mu)002:8768: thabs shes gnyis med mnyam pa'i ngang nyid du gnas
NK076(mu)002:8769: pa de lta bas rtogs nas ting 'dzin gasla bar
NK076(mu)002:8770: gyur na / rtog tshogs thams cad lha yab yum
NK076(mu)002:8771: zung 'brel las mi 'da' ba'i gnyis med bde ba
NK076(mu)002:8772: chen po'i mchog gi phyag rgya yin no //
NK076(mu)002:8773: gnyis pa bro gar gyi dus su lha bsgom pa'i
NK076(mu)002:8774: ting 'dzin yon tan dang bcas pa de la bzhi
NK076(mu)002:8775: / dang po yan lag lnga la rigs lnga'i lha
NK076(mu)002:8776: bsgom zhing bsgul bskyod byas pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang
NK076(mu)002:8778: yab yum rnams kyi bskyod chen de yan lag bzhi
NK076(mu)002:8779: mgo bo dang lnga la b+h+r+aum las 'khor lo'i gzhal
NK076(mu)002:8780: yas khang rtsibs bzhi re re bsgoms pa rnams su
NK076(mu)002:8781: / mgo bor bud+d+ha sogs rigs chung dang khro bo yab ste nyer lnga /
NK076(mu)002:8782: khro mo yul nyer lnga ste lnga bcu po thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:8783: ting 'dzin gsal zhing de dag la 'od zer mang po 'phro bar bsgoms na /
NK076(mu)002:8784: lus bsgul ba dang yan lag bskyod pa thams cad
NK076(mu)002:8785: lha las mi 'da' bas lha sku phyag rgya chen
NK076(mu)002:8786: po yin te / gnyis pa goms pa 'dor dus ting 'dzin dang ldan pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:8787: de ltar lhar gsal ba'i rkang g.yas thabs yab dang /
NK076(mu)002:8788: rkang g.yon shes rab yum du ldan pa'i zhabs gnyis
NK076(mu)002:8789: dus rtag tu rdo rja rtse lnga pa 'od 'bar
NK076(mu)002:8791: thabs chen gom pa re ra sa la bskyod cing dor bar byas na yanga /
NK076(mu)002:8792: don chags pa med pa'i rtags su rkang rjes la
NK076(mu)002:8793: me tog pad+ma chags pa med pa'i rtags re re
NK076(mu)002:8794: 'byung bar bsgom / rkang pa'i rdo rje dang sa
NK076(mu)002:8795: gzhi'i pad+ma de gnyis ting 'dzin gsal bar 'byor na
NK076(mu)002:8796: 'byung bar bsgom / / de bar du gang song
NK076(mu)002:8797: ba'i sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i byang
NK076(mu)002:8798: chub kyi zhing du skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:8799: gsum pa yan lag so sor lha bsgoms nas bskyod pa'i ting 'dzin ldan pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:8800: yan lag lnga rigs lnga ye nas yin pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor zhi ba'i lha rnams kyang /
NK076(mu)002:8801: de res 'dir khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha lnga
NK076(mu)002:8802: bcu yan lag bzhi mgo bo dang lnga la bsgom
NK076(mu)002:8803: par bya ste / dbu yi gnas su de bzhin
NK076(mu)002:8804: rigs b+hu d+d+ha he ru ka rigs chung dang bcas
NK076(mu)002:8805: pa'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba de nyid bsgul zhing bskyod
NK076(mu)002:8806: par bya ste / na / sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK076(mu)002:8807: 'khor te zhing khams thams cada thugs rje 'gro ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8808: don la g.yo bar nus pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8809: lag g.yas rdo rje'i rigs badz+ra he ru ka /g.yon
NK076(mu)002:8810: rin po che'i rigs rat+na he ru ka rigs chung
NK076(mu)002:8811: bcas gsal ba'i lag gi 'adu byed bskyod par byas
NK076(mu)002:8812: na / rig 'dzin gyi zhing khams thams cad ting
NK076(mu)002:8813: 'dzin gyi nus mthu skyes nas rang don du sa
NK076(mu)002:8815: gzhan don thugs rje 'gro ba'i don la g.yo bar nus so //
NK076(mu)002:8816: rkang pa g.yas las kyi rigs karma he ru ka
NK076(mu)002:8817: /g.yon pad+ma he ru ka rigs chung bcas gsal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8818: rkang pa'i stabsa chen mnan zhing machangas na /
NK076(mu)002:8819: g.yon gyis sems can gyi sdug bsngal mi bazada pa
NK076(mu)002:8820: dmyal ba la sogs thams cad las grol ba dang
NK076(mu)002:8821: / g.yas kyis bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang log par 'dren pa thams cad gnon par nus pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8822: bzhi pa yan lag kun bskyod cing ting 'dzin dang ldan pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:8823: spyir lus kyi yan lag thams cad dus gcig bsgul zhing bsigas na /
NK076(mu)002:8824: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi ba spu'i bu ga re re nasa /
NK076(mu)002:8825: khro ba sna tshogs rdul phra rab snyed grangs med par spro ba /
NK076(mu)002:8826: de yi yang sprul pa grangs med rnams kyis /
NK076(mu)002:8827: don bya ba'i gnas phyogs bcu'i zhing stong gsum gyi
NK076(mu)002:8828: stong chen po'i 'jig rten khamas dag dang ma dag
NK076(mu)002:8829: par ma rnams la rdul phra rab kyi grangs snyed
NK076(mu)002:8830: du don byed mkhan khro bo'i gdul bya 'dul ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8831: phrin las kyi sgo nas don 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK076(mu)002:8832: pa rnams rdul phran gyi grangs snyed du snang nas
NK076(mu)002:8834: de dag gi thugs rjes gdul bya rnams 'dul zhing
NK076(mu)002:8835: slar rang gi ba spu'i bu ga'am chos nyid dbyings
NK076(mu)002:8836: su bstim mo // gsum pa spyad thabs kun zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur te spyad thabs /
NK076(mu)002:8837: khro bo la khyu mchog ma he la sogs pa'i bro stabs dang /
NK076(mu)002:8838: yang na rkang pa'i bro lag gi gar ngag gi glu tshig dang mig gi lta stangs dang /
NK076(mu)002:8839: ting 'dzin gyis yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i thabs
NK076(mu)002:8840: thams cad kun sngar gyi zhi ba'i tshogs sgrub kyi
NK076(mu)002:8841: dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bstan pa lasa /
NK076(mu)002:8842: 'dir bro gara rtsed 'jo la sogs khro bor bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:8843: bzhi pa lhag ma la sogs mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:8845: de nas dpal chen po'i 'khor gyi phra men dbang mo rnams lhag mas tshim par byas te /
NK076(mu)002:8846: rta gdong gi phyag rgyas dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8847: so sor mchod pa dang las la bka' bsgo ba
NK076(mu)002:8848: la sogs pa rnams las gzhung ltar rgyas par byasa
NK076(mu)002:8849: nas las la bkye la brtan ma skyong dal bsdu
NK076(mu)002:8850: sta spyod lam bzhir lha'i ting 'dzin dang mi 'bral
NK076(mu)002:8851: bar spyad do // tshul de ltar bsgrubsa pas 'bras
NK076(mu)002:8852: bu mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin 'grub ba na the
NK076(mu)002:8853: bar spyad do // tshoma med do // gnyis pa sbyong ba'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:8854: tshogs sgrub rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes raba
NK076(mu)002:8855: yum thams cada kyis gong gi ting 'dzin gyi tshul
NK076(mu)002:8856: de lta bu yis yo byad lnga la longs spyod
NK076(mu)002:8857: na / sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa rnams kyang mnyes pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:8858: srid pa khams gsum gyi 'gro ba sems can thams
NK076(mu)002:8859: cad la 'dod yon gyi 'od zer 'phros pas bde
NK076(mu)002:8860: ba'i ro dga' ba chen posa khyab pasa sbyin par
NK076(mu)002:8861: 'gyur ba'o // spyi don gnyis pa tshogs sgrub pa'i yon tan la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:8862: dang po rtags 'phel ba la brten pa /
NK076(mu)002:8863: drod rtags chena rnams sngon spros pa'i skabs su bstan
NK076(mu)002:8864: pa bzhina du 'byung zhing gong las grangs mang du
NK076(mu)002:8865: 'phel zhing ngo bo gsal la yun ring brtan pa
NK076(mu)002:8866: 'byung ngo // gnyis pa mngon shes brtan pa /
NK076(mu)002:8867: mngon shes kyi yul la gling grangs 'phel ba gling bzhi drug tshun chad kyang mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:8868: mngon shes drug kyang gsal brtan 'byung ngo //
NK076(mu)002:8869: gsum pa rmis ltas lung bstan thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:8870: rna bas sgra snyan du thos pa /
NK076(mu)002:8871: gnyid kyi rmi lam dag tu yang bde ba can
NK076(mu)002:8872: la sogs pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams na gnas pa
NK076(mu)002:8873: rnams su skye bar lung bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:8874: lha ma'i skye ba khyad par can gang dag 'dzin par lung bstan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:8875: rig 'adzana gyi sa thob pa lung ston 'byung ba rnams yang dag rtags sam /
NK076(mu)002:8876: bdud kyi bar chad yin brtag par bya ba gces so //
NK076(mu)002:8877: spyi don gsum pa tshogs sgrub pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8878: blo che bas lhag bcas tshe dbang thob tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:8879: blo chung bas lhag med rnam smin thob tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:8881: sgrub pa mthar phyin tshe 'di la tshe dbang thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:8882: mthar ma phyin kyang phyi ma la thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:8883: lan grangs gzhan la tshe dbang thob pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:8885: dang po tshe dbang thob nas sangs rgyas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:8886: tshogs sgrub pa'i zhag grangsa sum cu phrag drug gam /
NK076(mu)002:8890: nang du 'byung ba'i lus nyid ma spangsa para skye
NK076(mu)002:8891: 'chi med pa tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi
NK076(mu)002:8892: sa non te / dus der rang don du lo
NK076(mu)002:8893: stong drug brgya la sogs yun ring por zag med
NK076(mu)002:8894: mthong lam pa'i chosa nyid kya bde ba la longs
NK076(mu)002:8895: sa non te / spyad nas / lam mthar chags
NK076(mu)002:8896: sam thod rgal gang rung gi sgo nas bla med
NK076(mu)002:8897: rdo rje semas dpa'i mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK076(mu)002:8899: thun mong dang thun min gyi dpe byad brgyad cu dang /
NK076(mu)002:8900: mtshan bzang so gnyis kyis rnam par brgyan cing zag
NK076(mu)002:8901: pa med pa'i mngon par shes pa drug dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:8902: la ci lta ba dang ji snyed pa thams cad
NK076(mu)002:8903: mkhyen pa'i ye shes mnga' ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:8904: bsod nams ye shes kyi tshogs chen po gnyis kyang
NK076(mu)002:8905: mngon sum du rdzogs par rol ba'i bdag nyid yang
NK076(mu)002:8906: dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas longs sku'i zhing khams kyi
NK076(mu)002:8907: gdul bya la rang dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK076(mu)002:8908: spyod yul ma lus pa kun tu sku dang ye
NK076(mu)002:8909: shes kyi man+dala gsal bas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs
NK076(mu)002:8910: chen gyi sa thob pa yin pas na /
NK076(mu)002:8911: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang bas ji ltar dmigs shing
NK076(mu)002:8912: dgongs pa bzhin du lhun gyis grub par 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)002:8913: // gnyis pa de yang las dang dus la rag lus med par tshe gcig la sangs rgya ba /
NK076(mu)002:8914: gong gi de bas na mtshan nyid pa ltar sngar bsags pa'i las 'phro dang /
NK076(mu)002:8915: dus grangs med la sogs pa rag lus med pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:8916: las dus la rag lus pa'i sems zhum pa de
NK076(mu)002:8917: dora bar byas nas sgo gsum gyis brtson 'grus chen
NK076(mu)002:8918: pa yi sgo nas zag pa med pa'i don mthong
NK076(mu)002:8919: lam la sbyor nas mthong ba'i chos tshe 'di la
NK076(mu)002:8921: gnyis pa tshe phyi mar tshe dbang thob pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:8923: mjug bsdus te the tshom med par thob tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:8925: dang po phyi ma lha mi khyad par can thob cing theg mchog mi brjed par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:8926: tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor ting 'dzin bzhi las su
NK076(mu)002:8927: rung ba'i lam pa rnams kyis sbyor lam tshogs sgrub
NK076(mu)002:8928: pa 'di lta bu yi lasa la 'bad par byas
NK076(mu)002:8929: na / blo dang brtson 'grus zhan pas 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:8930: mthong lam tshe 'di la mngon du ma byung yanga
NK076(mu)002:8931: na / / tshe 'di la rang gi lus ngag
NK076(mu)002:8932: yida gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs bsgom pa la rang
NK076(mu)002:8933: na / / dbang thob nasa / sangs rgyas sprul
NK076(mu)002:8934: pa'i sku 'jig rten gyi khams su gang du 'byung
NK076(mu)002:8935: bar shes nas de dang skal ba mnyam par lha
NK076(mu)002:8936: mi'i skye ba can blangs nas 'jal bar 'gyur ro
NK076(mu)002:8937: na / / dbang thob nasa / // de yang
NK076(mu)002:8938: gsang sngags la sbyangs pa'i las 'phro de dang 'brel
NK076(mu)002:8940: gsang sngags 'di nyid dang 'phrad cing theg pa dman
NK076(mu)002:8941: pa nyan rang la sogs pa la 'jug cing spyod
NK076(mu)002:8942: pa'i sar yang mi skye ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:8943: yo byad lnga la spyod pa'i bsod namas dang /
NK076(mu)002:8944: thams cad chos nyid du shes bas ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis dang ldan pa'i dpung tshogsa kyis /
NK076(mu)002:8945: skye ba snga ma phan chad kyi rgyu las ngan
NK076(mu)002:8946: gyi sgrib pa ma rig pa'i mun pa rnams sbyangs
NK076(mu)002:8947: pa'i phyir / 'bras bu ngan song gsum gyi yul du yongas su mi ltung zhing /
NK076(mu)002:8948: mtho ris su skye na yang gnas ngan pa dang
NK076(mu)002:8949: longs spyod chung ba dang mi bde zhing sdug bsngal
NK076(mu)002:8950: ba'i gnas ngan sanga gsum sogs mi khom brgyad du
NK076(mu)002:8952: mi brjed pa'i gzungs mchog dam pa lta ba rtogs shing ting 'dzin goms pa dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:8953: skye bas bar chad kyang gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg
NK076(mu)002:8954: pa mchog gi brjod bya rjod byed gang yin brjed
NK076(mu)002:8956: de la 'jug cing nyams su len nus pa'i dran pa phun sum tshogs pa thob bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:8957: de yang tsha ringa zhing nad med pa dang bde zhing 'byor ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan /
NK076(mu)002:8958: gnyis pa mtshan dang ldan zhing yon tan rdzogs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:8959: lha dang mi'i skye gnas kyi mchog stong rigs thob pa'i sa'am gnas skabas der yang /
NK076(mu)002:8960: lus dang byad bzhin bzang zhing mdzes la yan lag lhag chad med par rdzogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:8961: dbang pa lnga tshang zhing nying lag la chada lhag
NK076(mu)002:8962: med pa ste gzugs phun sum tshogs pa thob par
NK076(mu)002:8963: 'gyur ro // skad kyi gdangs bzang la snyan cing
NK076(mu)002:8964: phun sum tshogs pa tshangs dbyangs lta bu ldan pas
NK076(mu)002:8965: 'gro ba'i dona byed nus pa dang bdag gi 'byor
NK076(mu)002:8966: ba'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kun
NK076(mu)002:8967: 'gyur ro // / log 'tsho'i sgo nas sems can
NK076(mu)002:8968: gzhan la gnod pa med para yang dag pa'i 'tsho
NK076(mu)002:8969: ba rtsol med du 'grub pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:8970: gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i tshan po che yi mthu
NK076(mu)002:8971: stobs dang ldan pa phyag na rdo rje lta bur
NK076(mu)002:8972: 'gyur zhing de yang 'gra ba'i don du 'gyur ba'i
NK076(mu)002:8973: mthu stobs phun tshogs pa yang dag pa 'grub par
NK076(mu)002:8974: 'gyur ro // de ltar stobs dang ldan yang sems
NK076(mu)002:8975: can gzhan la gnod pa yanga mi byed pa'i thog
NK076(mu)002:8976: nas sems can la snying rje che zhanga gsang sngags
NK076(mu)002:8977: kyi don rtogs nus pa'i shes rab dang ldan par
NK076(mu)002:8978: 'gyur ro // 'gyur / tshogs sgrub pa'i mthu stobs
NK076(mu)002:8979: che zhing yo byad la spyod pa'i thabs la mkhas
NK076(mu)002:8980: pa dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas bdag dang gdul
NK076(mu)002:8981: bya gzhan gyi don rdzogsa par byed nus pa'i phrin
NK076(mu)002:8982: las phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:8983: gsum pa der tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob tshul /
NK076(mu)002:8984: dbang rab lus rten der zag bcas kyi lam rnams
NK076(mu)002:8985: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu skye sha med pa'i tshe
NK076(mu)002:8986: la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin sa thob /
NK076(mu)002:8987: sangs rgyas sprul sku'i che ba'i yon tan dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i nor bu rin po che lta bu /
NK076(mu)002:8988: bgoda pa'i zhing khams tshad gazhala ba las yas pa'i khang thams cad la /
NK076(mu)002:8989: dper na 'dod lha rigs drug yod pa'i drug pa
NK076(mu)002:8990: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyis rang las sprul nas longs
NK076(mu)002:8992: yo byad lnga la dbang basgyur zhing longs spyod pa'i
NK076(mu)002:8993: 'bras bu mthong lam gyi dngos grub dam pa thob
NK076(mu)002:8994: par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa mjug bsdus te the tshom med par thob tshul /
NK076(mu)002:8995: 'bring gis tshe phyi ma la tshe dbang du gyur pa de yi phyir /
NK076(mu)002:8996: tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin tshe phya ma'i
NK076(mu)002:8997: dus de nyid du sbyor ba la lta smos kyang
NK076(mu)002:8998: ci dgos te nges par gdon mi za bar 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:8999: ro // gsum pa lan grangs gzhan la tshe dbang thob pa /
NK076(mu)002:9000: gong du bstan pa'i tshul de ltar sbyor lam tshogs
NK076(mu)002:9001: sgrub ba la sgo gsum brtson 'grus rab dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:9002: pas ni / dbang po brtson 'grus rab kyi mthong lam tshe 'di nyid la thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9003: 'bring gis tshe phyi mar tshe dbang thob par ma gyur na yang /
NK076(mu)002:9004: tha mas skye ba brgyud pa'i lan grangs de las
NK076(mu)002:9005: gzhan du'ang tshe dbang thob ste skye ba bdun nyid
NK076(mu)002:9006: las mi 'da' bar mthong lam mam tshe dbang rang
NK076(mu)002:9007: la bzhi yod pa'i nang nas rig 'dzin rigs kyi
NK076(mu)002:9009: gnyis pa rnam smin thob tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9010: dang po sgrub pa mthar phyin pas tshe dbang ma
NK076(mu)002:9011: thob kyang tshe 'di la rnam smin thob pa'i dpe
NK076(mu)002:9012: don / de yang cha ga lnga dang sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:9013: yo byad lnga po dag ste lnga gsum bco lnga
NK076(mu)002:9014: po de dag sbyor lam gyis mngon sum rdzogs par
NK076(mu)002:9015: byas nas dam tshig ma nyamsa pa dang ldan pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9016: rnal 'byor pa rnams ngasa par 'tshogs te tshogas bsgrub
NK076(mu)002:9017: cing yo byad lnga la spyad na /
NK076(mu)002:9018: 'bras bu tshe dbang tshe 'di la mngon du ma byung yanga /
NK076(mu)002:9019: blo chung bas rnam smin thob ste /
NK076(mu)002:9020: dper na rgyal po zhig gis bran mo ngana pa
NK076(mu)002:9021: dang bshos pa ste sbyor bas kyang rgyal po'i sras
NK076(mu)002:9022: 'byung ba'i sa bon nur nur po bran mo'i mngal
NK076(mu)002:9023: du chags pa'i bu de yang rgyal po'i rigs 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9024: te / de skye ba mthong ma thag nas rgyal
NK076(mu)002:9025: bu de dmangs thams cad kyis blar te bkur ba'i
NK076(mu)002:9027: rgyal sar bton pa'i tshe 'khor 'bangs kun la dabnga bsgyur ba'i stobs dang ldan pa de la /
NK076(mu)002:9028: 'jig rten pa'i lha rnams kyis kyang gsol mchod la sogs re ba'i mthu'am bsam pa skyes pas /
NK076(mu)002:9029: rgyal bu de la bsrung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9031: mchod pa byed pa yi dpe de ltar du /
NK076(mu)002:9032: tshogs sgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa lta ba dang ting
NK076(mu)002:9033: 'dzin gyi stobs dang ldan pa rnam smin rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9035: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i dam can ma mo
NK076(mu)002:9036: mkha' 'gro la sogs chos skyong srung ma mang ma
NK076(mu)002:9037: lus snang po kun gyis sems lhar smin pa de
NK076(mu)002:9038: yi dbang gisa spyi gtsug tu khur cing srung bar
NK076(mu)002:9039: byed la / rnam smin gyi lus kyi spyod yul
NK076(mu)002:9040: dor nas shi 'phos ma thag yi dam lha'i skur
NK076(mu)002:9041: smin pa de dngos su gsal ba phyag rgya zhes
NK076(mu)002:9042: rgya chen rig 'dzin du nges par rdzogas par 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:9043: byed la / ro // gnyis pa mthar ma phyin
NK076(mu)002:9044: kyang phyi ma la thob par gdams pa dang bcas
NK076(mu)002:9045: byed la / ro // pa / dbang po tha
NK076(mu)002:9046: ma'i nang nas blo che ba'i gang zag la la
NK076(mu)002:9047: gong du bstan pa de ltar tshe 'dir rnam smin
NK076(mu)002:9048: de nyid thob ngesa na yang /
NK076(mu)002:9049: blo chung ba la la dag de ltar ma gyur
NK076(mu)002:9050: pas phyi ma la bsod namas bsags pa'i sa la
NK076(mu)002:9052: de yang tshe rabs skye ba thams cada kyi bar
NK076(mu)002:9053: du bral ba'i 'bras bu las ngan par gyur pa
NK076(mu)002:9054: mtshams med pa lnga mi dge ba bcu lci ba
NK076(mu)002:9055: bzhi log pa brgyad la spyod pa'i sa dang gnas
NK076(mu)002:9056: kun tu tshogs sgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa de skye
NK076(mu)002:9058: lha mi'i theg pa la sogs pa nges 'byung gi
NK076(mu)002:9059: theg pa bzhi la'ang 'jug cing spyod par mi 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:9060: / thob pa'i 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg
NK076(mu)002:9061: pa'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa'i bshes gnyen dag tu 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:9062: ta skye ba phyi ma lan grangs gzhan la rnam
NK076(mu)002:9063: smin rig 'dzin thob par byas nasa sngon gong du
NK076(mu)002:9064: spyod yul dor nas phyag rgya chen po thob par
NK076(mu)002:9066: phyi mar rnam smin thob nas rgya chen la sbyor
NK076(mu)002:9067: ba 'di la the tshoma dang som nyi ldan pa
NK076(mu)002:9068: min pas / las 'phro skal ba dang ldan pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9069: rnal 'byor pa kun gyis dus rtag tu tshogs sgrub
NK076(mu)002:9070: la brtson 'grus chen po bskyed par byos shig /gsum
NK076(mu)002:9071: min pas / pa le'u'i mtshan / ngan song du ldog pa'i bar chad med pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:9072: lam gzhan gyi bar chad med pa'i sbyor lam du
NK076(mu)002:9073: tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas
NK076(mu)002:9074: mthong lam bsgrub pa'i thabs ston par byed pa'i gzhung
NK076(mu)002:9075: gi tshig don rnams gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na
NK076(mu)002:9076: la'u ste / yas bgrangs bdun pa'i don du gda'
NK076(mu)002:9077: 'o ////spyi don gsum pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:9078: zag med kyi lam la gsum ste /
NK076(mu)002:9079: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:9080: thun mong gi dngos grub las khyad par du gyur
NK076(mu)002:9081: pa lhag pa'i ste mchog gi dngos grub rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9083: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yis bsgrubs pa'i sgo nas mos par byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:9084: sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu med pas bde ba chen
NK076(mu)002:9085: po rig 'dzin gyi sa la gdul bya dgod para
NK076(mu)002:9086: bya ba' phyir / zag bcas tshogs sbyor gnyis kyi
NK076(mu)002:9087: lam mthar phyin pa'i gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu'i mtshan
NK076(mu)002:9088: nyid zag med mthong sgom mthar gsum gyi rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9089: bzhi po bshad par bya ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:9090: gnyis pa gzhung don la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9096: rgya spros mthar phyin nas zla ba bcu drug sogs
NK076(mu)002:9097: rab 'bring tha ma'i dus kyi zhi khro'i tshom bu
NK076(mu)002:9098: tshogs sgrub pa'i sbyor lam bar chad meda pa'i lam
NK076(mu)002:9099: pa nasa / zag bcas phung po 'di yi lhag
NK076(mu)002:9100: ma yi lus 'bras bu'i sa la med pa rnam
NK076(mu)002:9101: smin dang yod pa tshe la dbang ba yi /
NK076(mu)002:9102: mya ngan las 'da' basa zag bcas mthar phyin nas zag med la sbyor ba yang /
NK076(mu)002:9103: thun mong theg pa nyan thos la lhag bcas lhag
NK076(mu)002:9104: med gnyis yod pa lta bur rig 'dzin gyi skabs
NK076(mu)002:9105: 'dir yang lhag bcas lhag med gnyis zung gcig tu
NK076(mu)002:9107: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9108: lhag med rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:9109: lhag bcas tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin no //
NK076(mu)002:9117: lam gong ma la sbyor tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:9120: dang po thod rgal ba gcig spros /
NK076(mu)002:9121: de ltar gnyis yod pa de la thog ma lhag
NK076(mu)002:9122: med du sbyor ba rnam smin rig 'dzin bshad pa
NK076(mu)002:9124: thod rgal dbang btsan du rab rgya gcig pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9125: 'bring rgya spros lha du ma'i rnal 'byor ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9126: la nyams brtan zhing mthar phyin byas pa nyid kyi
NK076(mu)002:9127: sa nas rnam smin thob pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:9128: gnyis pa mthar chags tshogs sgrub nas /
NK076(mu)002:9129: mthar chags dbang du rgya spros ba'i rnal 'byor de mathara phyin pa thob nas /
NK076(mu)002:9130: sbyor lam du blo rab 'bring tha ma'i chas zla drug gam /
NK076(mu)002:9133: bcu drug gi bar du bsnyen sgrub bzhis tshogs sgrub pa'i tsha rnam smin rig 'dzin thob pa yin /
NK076(mu)002:9134: tshe dbang lta bur skye shi med pa rdo rje'i lus su smin cing grub par ma gyur par /
NK076(mu)002:9135: lta ba ting 'dzin goms pa'i stobs chung ba dang
NK076(mu)002:9136: rkyen brtson 'grus dang smon lam gyi mthu zhan pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9137: phyir na / sngar nas las kyi lus la bdag
NK076(mu)002:9138: tu rtog pa'i bag chags las grub pa rnam par
NK076(mu)002:9140: 'byung bzhi 'dus pa las grub pa 'byung ba'i lus dang /
NK076(mu)002:9141: 'byung ba rags pa snyigs ma'i cha las grub pa lhag ma'i lus dang /
NK076(mu)002:9142: sngar las kyis 'phen pa las grub pa'i las kyi
NK076(mu)002:9143: lus de bzhag nas 'bras bu rdo rje 'chang chen
NK076(mu)002:9145: rgya chen lhun grub brgyud nas rig pas 'gro bas na /
NK076(mu)002:9146: lhag med mya ngan las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:9147: gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9148: dang po rnam smin thob pa'i ngo bo dpe don /
NK076(mu)002:9149: yid yi dam lha yi sku rgya chen rnal 'byor ting 'dzin gsal zhing rdzogs par smin kyang /
NK076(mu)002:9150: lhag ma'i lus kyi rnam pa 'ching ba'i d+r+wa bas bsgribsa par gyur pas /
NK076(mu)002:9151: dper na ka la pang+ka ste bya khyung phrug sgong rgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:9152: mi 'jigs seng phrug mngal rgya dang bral ma thag rtsal ma dang mnyam pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:9153: tha mal ba'i lus rgya 'di dang bral nas yid yi dam lha'i sku /
NK076(mu)002:9154: ngo bo rgya chen rig 'dzin nyid du snang bar
NK076(mu)002:9155: byed pa de la rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9156: zhes brjod do // gnyis pa rnam smin gyi nges
NK076(mu)002:9157: tshig rnal 'byor pa'i yid kyis yi dam lha sku
NK076(mu)002:9158: yi gzugsa gsal bar bzung zhing /
NK076(mu)002:9159: tha mal ba'i lus kyi rgya mdud kyis bsdams pa de ni grol bar gyur ba dang de nas /
NK076(mu)002:9160: 'bras bu phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin lha'i sku nyid mngon
NK076(mu)002:9161: sum du gsal bar gyur pa'i chos dang ldan na
NK076(mu)002:9162: / rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin zhes de la brjod do //
NK076(mu)002:9164: rgya mig rkos phor nang du rgya sa 'dam pa
NK076(mu)002:9165: btab pas nang du gzugs dod kyang rgya mig dang
NK076(mu)002:9166: ma bral bar du mi gsal ba'i dpe ji lta
NK076(mu)002:9167: bura / yi dam lhar smin pa de lus rgya
NK076(mu)002:9168: dang bral ma thag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9169: thob la ma rag pa'i cha dang ldan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9170: yid lha'i sku gzugsa su rtsal rdzogsa par smin pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9171: ting 'dzin stobs chen du gyur pa de kho na
NK076(mu)002:9172: rnam smin rig 'dzin ngo bo yin pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9173: bzhi pa ming gi rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9174: dang po thob pa'i ming grangs gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9175: dang po rnam smin da yang lta dgongas bzang ngan
NK076(mu)002:9176: dang spyod pa zab mi zab pa'i khyad para gnyis
NK076(mu)002:9177: yod de / de yang rgya gcig spros nas thob pa'i rnam smin de dgongs spyod dma' zhing /
NK076(mu)002:9178: tshogs sgrub nas thob pa'i rnam smin dgongs spyod bzang par 'dod /
NK076(mu)002:9179: rgyu mtshan des gcig spros nas thob pa de dgongs
NK076(mu)002:9180: spyod rgya mtsho snga ma gcig spros dang rgyud mthun
NK076(mu)002:9181: la / tshogs sgrub nas thob pa phyi ma tshogs
NK076(mu)002:9182: sgrub dang rgyud mthun pas de ltar dgongs spyod rnams
NK076(mu)002:9183: stobs che chung gi chas rnam smin du ming grags
NK076(mu)002:9184: la / pa yin no // gnyis pa thob ba'i ngo bo'i ming grangs gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9185: lhag ma'i lus med 'byung ba'i lus med lasa kyi
NK076(mu)002:9186: lus med par dgongs pa mya ngan las 'das pa
NK076(mu)002:9187: 'bras bu rgya chen rig 'dzin du'ang smin pa'i chas
NK076(mu)002:9188: brjod pa'o // lnga pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9190: rang don du ci spyad zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor du
NK076(mu)002:9191: gsal zhing lha la lha rola pa'i tshul du spyod
NK076(mu)002:9192: pas ma 'gags pa bsod nams dang /
NK076(mu)002:9193: ma dmigs pa ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis zung 'jug
NK076(mu)002:9194: tu rdzogs par byed pa de ni rnam smin gyi
NK076(mu)002:9195: bdag gi don du spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9197: yid yi dam lha'i skur smin pas phrin lasa zhi
NK076(mu)002:9198: rgyas dbang drag bzhis gzhan don yongs su rdzogs par
NK076(mu)002:9199: byed pasa / gdul bya yal bar ma 'dora bar
NK076(mu)002:9200: yang dag ba'i lam don la dgongas pa ni gzhan
NK076(mu)002:9203: phyag rgya gcig spros nas rnam smin thob pa de dang /
NK076(mu)002:9204: tshogs sgrub nas thob pa de'ang rab kyis tshe 'di la thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9205: 'bring gis bar do dang phyi ma nas thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9206: tha mas kyang lan grangsa brgyud pa gzhan bdun tshun
NK076(mu)002:9207: chod du blo dang brtson pa rab 'bring tha ma'i
NK076(mu)002:9208: tshul dag gis rnam smin thob par 'gyur gyis /
NK076(mu)002:9209: de nas phyag chen la sbyor nas mthar thug gi
NK076(mu)002:9210: 'bras bu thob pa la mtshan nyid pa ltar bskal
NK076(mu)002:9211: pa grangs med par mi 'gyang ste ci'i phyir zhe
NK076(mu)002:9212: na dgongs pa mtho ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9213: tshogs kyi spyod pa'i brtul zhugs ldan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9214: sgo gsum brtson 'grus bskyed pa rnams gtso bor byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:9215: bdun pa lam gong ma la sbyor tshul la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:9217: gang rnam smin rig 'dzin de lus rgya dang bral ma thag pa ru /
NK076(mu)002:9218: bar do med pa'i ngang du yi dam lha'i sku
NK076(mu)002:9219: phyag rgya chen po la sogs ba bzhi rdzogs pa
NK076(mu)002:9220: rnam smin sku bdag nyid mngon du gyur pas /
NK076(mu)002:9225: las kyi rigs dang lnga la sogs pa'i rigs gang yin pa de rig pas 'dzin pa la /
NK076(mu)002:9226: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste rnam
NK076(mu)002:9227: smin gyi gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu yin pas so
NK076(mu)002:9228: // gnyis pa lam gyi dbye sa dang 'du sa gcig par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9229: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu phyag rgya chen po yin
NK076(mu)002:9230: pas de yi phyir phyag rgya chena po thob pa
NK076(mu)002:9231: / rgya gcig spros dang sbyor lam bar chad med
NK076(mu)002:9232: pa'i thog nas lam mchog rnam smin la dbye sa
NK076(mu)002:9233: gsum yod kyang 'du sa rgya chen du gcig pa
NK076(mu)002:9234: ste dper na wa rgyun gyi dkyil chu lta bu
NK076(mu)002:9235: / yin no // yang na de phyir rgya chena dang /
NK076(mu)002:9236: sbyor lam bar chad med pa gnyis lam mchoga tshe
NK076(mu)002:9237: rnam gnyis kyi rigs dbye sa dang 'du sa gciga
NK076(mu)002:9238: yina no // brgyad pa mngon shes /
NK076(mu)002:9239: sbyor lam bar chad med pa'am phyag rgya gcig spros kyi thog nas rnam smin thob pa ya /
NK076(mu)002:9241: de nyid kya ming can mngon shes yul grangs mi
NK076(mu)002:9242: 'gyur kyang 'dir zag med thob pa'i nus pas yul
NK076(mu)002:9243: gsal ba nges pa nyid du khyad yod par gyur
NK076(mu)002:9244: pa'ang yin te / rgya gcig nas thob pa'i rnam smin gyis dpag tshad dang /
NK076(mu)002:9245: spros pa nas gling bzhi gcig dang /
NK076(mu)002:9246: tshogs sgrub nas gling khams grangs gnyis nas drug gi bar du mngon shes kyi yul la sbyor ro //
NK076(mu)002:9247: gnyis pa lhag bcas tshe dbang la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:9248: dang po tshe dbang gi khyad par spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9249: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma lhag bcas tshe dbang ni
NK076(mu)002:9250: rgya spros ting 'dzin mthar phyin pa'i dus kya tshom
NK076(mu)002:9251: bu tshogs sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor basa /
NK076(mu)002:9252: lta dgongas ting 'dzin gsal ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9253: tshogs kyi spyod pa sbyor sgrol dang /
NK076(mu)002:9254: sgrub pa la brtson 'grus bskyed pa chen po dang
NK076(mu)002:9255: ldan pa'i stobs kyis sbyangs pa lam mchog yongs su
NK076(mu)002:9257: gsang ba'i yo byad +aa li sbyor ba thabs lam
NK076(mu)002:9258: sbyangs ba las byung ba thabs kya tshe dbang dang
NK076(mu)002:9259: / steng 'og gi rlung stobs lasa skyes pa'i tshe dbang /
NK076(mu)002:9260: gzhan pa'i sman dang dza gad 'brang rgyas la sogs
NK076(mu)002:9261: yo byad kyis grub pa'i rtags dang ldan pa dang
NK076(mu)002:9262: / dngos grub la rol cing longs spyod pa'i nus
NK076(mu)002:9263: mthu las byung ba bdud rtsi sman las byung pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9264: / tshe dbang dang / de dag rang rang gis
NK076(mu)002:9265: thob par byed pa'i thabs ni sman za ba'i thabs
NK076(mu)002:9266: / tshe dbang dang / dang / thig le bzung ba'i /
NK076(mu)002:9269: rgyu zhes ra mo shag la sogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9271: rlung tshogs sgrub shes rab bzhi yis phye bas tshe dbang bzhi sa sor tha dad byung na yang /
NK076(mu)002:9272: 'dir tshogs sbyor gyi lam sbyangs pa'i stobs las skyes
NK076(mu)002:9273: pa yi tshe dbang ni gzhan gsum po las mchog
NK076(mu)002:9275: zag pa med pa'i rig 'dzin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:9276: gnyis pa lam mchog gi tshe dbang bye brag tu bshad pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9285: lam gong ma la sbyor ba'i tshul ste bzhi gnyis
NK076(mu)002:9286: brgyad kyis tshe dbang gi lus rnam bzhag mdor bstan
NK076(mu)002:9287: gyi rnam grangs rgyas par rdzogs par bshad pa ni
NK076(mu)002:9288: 'di lta ste / gnyis pa rgyas pa de la brgyad de /
NK076(mu)002:9289: dang po tshe dbang thob ba'i rgyu la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9290: dang po drang don gyi rgyu ni /
NK076(mu)002:9291: lam pa gang dag 'bras bu 'thob par byed pa'i thabas dang /
NK076(mu)002:9292: 'bras bu la mos pa dranga pa yi don tsam
NK076(mu)002:9293: du tshe dbang thob pa'i rgyur bya ba ni drang
NK076(mu)002:9294: don gyi rgyu'o // gnyis pa nges don gyi rgyu de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9296: nges pa'i don du zag bcas kyi thos bsam sgom
NK076(mu)002:9297: gsum gyi shes rab rnam pa gsum la rim gcig
NK076(mu)002:9298: tu goms par byasa nas tshe dbang thob pa la
NK076(mu)002:9299: / gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9301: bden pa gnyis med kyi ting 'dzin gyi lta bas
NK076(mu)002:9302: chos nyid mnyam pa'i don ma nor bar rtogs te
NK076(mu)002:9303: dgag sgrub dang bral ba dus dang gnas skabs kun
NK076(mu)002:9304: tu chos nyid mtha' bral yangs pa chen pa cig
NK076(mu)002:9305: char du bsgom pa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:9307: lam rim gyis pa'i dbang du rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9309: de kun rgya spros tshogs grub ste /
NK076(mu)002:9310: lam tshogs sbyor gyi rnal 'byor rnam pa lnga po /
NK076(mu)002:9311: lta ba'i skabs thos bsam shes rab kyis rtogs blo
NK076(mu)002:9312: de goms pas cho gas 'grub pa'i rnal 'byor ba
NK076(mu)002:9313: ni / sbyor lam du zla ba zhag gi grangs rtsa rgyud gsang snying le'u dgu pa nas /
NK076(mu)002:9314: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam /
NK076(mu)002:9315: la sogs gsungs bzhin du tshogs sgrub par byed pas
NK076(mu)002:9316: 'bras bu skye shi med pa rdo rje lta bu'i
NK076(mu)002:9317: lus su tshe dbang 'grub par the tshom med de
NK076(mu)002:9322: lhag ma'i lus nyid ma spangs par skye shi med
NK076(mu)002:9323: pa rdo rje'i lus su gyur tshul de ni de
NK076(mu)002:9326: dang po tshe dbang thob pa'i dus /
NK076(mu)002:9327: bsgrub cing 'grub pa'i zhag grangs ni rab kyis zhag sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam /
NK076(mu)002:9328: 'bring gis zla ba bcu gnyis te lo gcig /zla
NK076(mu)002:9329: ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis
NK076(mu)002:9330: sam / tha ma zla ba bcu drug ste lo gcig dang zla ba bzhi po dag gis /
NK076(mu)002:9331: blo dang brtson 'grus rab 'bring tha ma gzhung nas
NK076(mu)002:9332: ji ltar bshad ba bzhin du nyams su blangs nas
NK076(mu)002:9333: bsgrubs na nges par mi bslu bar tshe la rang
NK076(mu)002:9334: dbang sgyur zhing lus mi 'dor ba sprul sku'i rig
NK076(mu)002:9335: 'dzin gyi dam pa lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9337: gnyis pa lam gong ma la sbyor te sangs rgyas pa'i dus /
NK076(mu)002:9339: 'brasa bu lha'i sangs rgyas gnyis gzhi la gdod nas
NK076(mu)002:9340: dbyer med pa dus gcig tu rdzogs pa yi don
NK076(mu)002:9341: de nyid rang rig byang chub kyi sems nyid la
NK076(mu)002:9342: rang dbang thob sta rtogs nas mngon du gyur cing
NK076(mu)002:9343: / de'i rang don gyi tshe tshad 'di lo brgya pa'i dbang du lo brgya phrag bcu dang /
NK076(mu)002:9344: drug ste lo stong drug brgya gnas pa yi bar
NK076(mu)002:9345: lo brgya re brgya ra nas je gzhon la byis
NK076(mu)002:9346: pa gzhon nu lo brgyad pa lon pa dag tu
NK076(mu)002:9347: snur zhing 'jig rten du gnas nas /
NK076(mu)002:9348: mthar da ltar gyi lus 'di ma bor bar yang
NK076(mu)002:9349: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa la khyer
NK076(mu)002:9350: nas 'gro ba'i don nus pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9351: gsum pa ngo bo la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9357: sprul pa'i lus kyi cha byad do //
NK076(mu)002:9360: gzhi bden pa dbyer med kyi don rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta bas mthong /
NK076(mu)002:9361: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting 'dzin tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi mthar phyir pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK076(mu)002:9362: sbyor lam du zhi khro'i tshogs kyi longs spyod yo byad lnga /
NK076(mu)002:9363: khyad par +aa li spyod cing tshogs sgrub pa'i dngos grub khyad par can blangs pa'i stobs kyis /
NK076(mu)002:9365: de yang lus kyi zag pa lus rang dbang med par rgas rgud dang 'dor len gyi sdug bsngal /
NK076(mu)002:9366: khams kyi zag pa gshang gci dang 'du ba bzhis khams mi bde ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9367: skye gnas kyi zag pa skye gnas bzang ngan la
NK076(mu)002:9368: rang dbang med par 'jug pa sogs te zag gsum
NK076(mu)002:9370: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i lus su grub par
NK076(mu)002:9371: gyur pas tshe la dbang sgyur ba yi rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9373: de yang mthong ba'i chosa tshe 'di la mya ngan las 'da' ba thob pas /
NK076(mu)002:9374: lhag ma'i lus 'di nyid ma bor bar 'di dang
NK076(mu)002:9375: bcas bzhin du mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa la
NK076(mu)002:9376: 'gro nus pa'o // bzhi pa yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:9377: 'khor ba'i 'jigs pa brgyad dang nyon mongs pa lnga
NK076(mu)002:9378: po kun dang bral zhing 'og nas ston pa'i cho
NK076(mu)002:9380: gnyis pa sprul pa'i lus kyi cha byad /
NK076(mu)002:9381: tshe dbang rig 'dzin de'i cha byad ni /
NK076(mu)002:9382: lha dang mi'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin te /
NK076(mu)002:9383: 'dod lha drug gi rgyal po dang /
NK076(mu)002:9384: mi'i rgyal po 'khor los sgyur ba la sogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9385: gzugs khams kyi lha tshangas pa yi cha lugs su gnas pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:9386: de rnams kyi skye ba rnam par dag pa rang
NK076(mu)002:9387: dbang can dang dbang po dang yan lag lhag chad
NK076(mu)002:9389: 'on kyang lha mi rnams dang khyad par yod dam med ce na khyad yod la /
NK076(mu)002:9390: de dag gi khyad par ni zag med kyi sa
NK076(mu)002:9391: la gnas pa dang mi gnas par gyur pa'i khyad
NK076(mu)002:9392: par yod pa yin bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:9393: lha mi'i rgyal po'i cha byad de nyid kyis gdul
NK076(mu)002:9394: bya de'i rigs can la bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi chos
NK076(mu)002:9395: ston ste sprul pa'i sku'i rgyal tshab byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9396: gnyis pa yon tan la lnga /
NK076(mu)002:9397: dang po bral ba'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:9398: dper na 'gro ba gang dag dug sbrul gyis mi
NK076(mu)002:9399: 'jigs pa la rtsi ma ki t+aa 'chang ba ltar
NK076(mu)002:9400: du / tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin de yang 'jigas pa bral te /
NK076(mu)002:9405: 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa lnga dang bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:9406: sogs khong du 'jigs pa brgyad dang 'khor ba'i nyes skyon thams cad dang bral ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:9407: gnyis pa thob pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:9409: cho 'phrul bzhi po dag gi yan lag nyer lnga
NK076(mu)002:9410: dang nyi shu la sogs pa kun gyi rtsal dang
NK076(mu)002:9412: gsum pa skye ba'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:9413: tshe'am rig pa dang skye ba la rang dbang sgyur
NK076(mu)002:9414: ba'i stobs kyis lha mi'i rgyal po'i skye ba rnam
NK076(mu)002:9415: dag khyad par can blang ba yis /
NK076(mu)002:9416: bzhi pa 'dul zhing gi yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:9417: gzhan don du stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig
NK076(mu)002:9418: rten gyi khams brgya tshun chad kyi gdul bya 'dul
NK076(mu)002:9419: bar byed do // lnga pa rgyu'i sa dang po dang skal ba mnyam pa'i yon tan /
NK076(mu)002:9420: rgyu ya theg pa chen po'i sa dang po rab
NK076(mu)002:9421: tu dga' ba dang tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang skal
NK076(mu)002:9422: ba mnyam mo // gnyis pa phyag chen brgyad pa /
NK076(mu)002:9423: gsum pa lhun grub bcu pa dang mnyam pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9424: gsum pa sku tshe'i tshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9425: dang po bdag don tshe tshad /
NK076(mu)002:9426: bdag gi don gyi phyir thos bsam la sogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9427: lam don du gnyer ba 'bras bu thob pa'i dus
NK076(mu)002:9428: ni / lo brgya phrag bcu drug ste lo stong
NK076(mu)002:9429: drug brgya'i tshe yis rang don rdzogs nas 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:9430: ni / la sbyor ba'o // gnyis pa gzhan don gyi tshe tshad /
NK076(mu)002:9431: gdul bya gzhan gyi don du tshe la rang dbang thob pa yin pa'i phyir tshad bzung med de /
NK076(mu)002:9432: bzhugs par bzhed na bskal pa grangs med pa'i bar
NK076(mu)002:9433: du 'jig rten gyi khams su gnas par 'gyur yang
NK076(mu)002:9434: / bgres rgud mi mnga' ba'i sku ni shin tu gzhon pa lo brgyad pa'i tshul du snang ste /
NK076(mu)002:9435: gdul bya rtag 'dzin dang le lo can 'dul ba'i dus kyi sprul pa'i lus 'chi 'pho ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9436: mi 'dul na 'dug par yang byed do //
NK076(mu)002:9437: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9439: de la dngos su lung ston cing dbang bskur 'byung ba lung bltan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9440: gnas dang skye ba dang cha byad kyang gzhan don gyi skabs kyis ma nges pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9442: ngo bo'i dang ming gi rnam grangs so //
NK076(mu)002:9444: dang po tshe dbang rig 'dzin spyir bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:9445: ngo bo nges bzung ba bzhin du rnam grangs kyang rnam par 'jug ste /
NK076(mu)002:9447: ra mo shag dang rtag tu phyi nang gi bdud
NK076(mu)002:9448: rtsi lnga yi sman gyis bcud len pa'i tshe dbang
NK076(mu)002:9449: dang / 'og sgo sbyor ba'i thabs las gyur pa'i tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:9450: rnal 'byor rlung bzung ba tshe ring bar gyur pa
NK076(mu)002:9451: sgrol ma rlung las gyur pa'i tshe dbang rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9452: dang / ma h+aa yo ga'i tshogs sbyor gyi lam
NK076(mu)002:9453: mchoga lta sgom spyod gsum gyi rtsal yongs su rdzogsa
NK076(mu)002:9454: pa'i tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:9455: de ltar tshe dbang la rim pa bzhi po de'i /
NK076(mu)002:9458: skye ba la yo byad la mos pa la rdzu
NK076(mu)002:9459: 'phrul la chos la ye shes la sems la las
NK076(mu)002:9460: la smon lam la dbang ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:9461: dbang bcu yod pa'i dang pa tshe la dbang ba tsam du 'dra mod kyanga /
NK076(mu)002:9462: de dag la khyad yod de /
NK076(mu)002:9463: gnyis pa lam mchog rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang khyad par du bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9464: tshe dbang bzhi po de dag nyid la khyad par drug las /
NK076(mu)002:9465: dang po mthu dang byin rlabs la che chung gi khyad par yod de /
NK076(mu)002:9466: gsum po bdag don kun 'gro spang mi nus shing /
NK076(mu)002:9467: rdzu 'phrul nyi shu sogs 'byin mi nus la /
NK076(mu)002:9469: gnyis pa zag pa yod med khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:9470: gsum po la zag pa yod la /
NK076(mu)002:9471: 'di la snga ma bzhin mi zag ste zag med kyi mthong lam ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK076(mu)002:9472: gsum pa bskyed pa rgyu'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:9473: gsum po'i rgyu ni sman la sogs pa yin la
NK076(mu)002:9474: 'di'i rgyu ni tshogs sgrub kyi shes rab gsum yin
NK076(mu)002:9475: pa dang / bzhi pa ngo bo'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:9476: gsum po 'jig rten pa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:9477: 'di'i ngo bo ni lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pas 'das pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9478: de ltar 'khor 'das dang zag bcas zag med rnam pa gnyis su 'gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9479: lnga ba lta dgongs kyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:9480: gong du bshad pa'i khyad yod pa da bas na /
NK076(mu)002:9481: gsum por zag med kyi dgongs pa med la /
NK076(mu)002:9482: 'di ni zag med kyi chos nyid rang mtshan gyi dgongs pa la mnga' brnyes pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9483: drug pa spyod pa'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:9484: gsum pos bdag gzhan gyi don rgya chen po spyod mi nus la /
NK076(mu)002:9485: 'dis ni bdag gzhan gyi don rlabs po cher spyod nus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9486: sangs rgyas sprul sku'i rgyal tshab byed nus pa /
NK076(mu)002:9487: des na dgongs pa spyod pa la khyad par yod pa smos ci dgos te /
NK076(mu)002:9488: lam mchog 'di las gzhan pa sman dang /
NK076(mu)002:9490: rlung las grub pas tshe dbang thob pa de gsum yang tshe dbang tsam po ba yin pas /
NK076(mu)002:9491: lam mchog yongs rdzogs kyi tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang 'dra ba min no //
NK076(mu)002:9492: gnyis pa ming gi rnam grangs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9494: lam mchog gi tshe dbang rang la'ang yon tan gyis
NK076(mu)002:9495: mtshan gyi rnam grangs mi 'dra ba'i chas brjod pa
NK076(mu)002:9497: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:9498: dang po ming bzhi'i lus dang bcas nas mya ngan la 'da' bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9499: lhag ma'i lus te gzugs kyi phung po dang /
NK076(mu)002:9500: ming bzhi'i phung pora bcas pa yis bskal pa grangs
NK076(mu)002:9501: med la sogs ci tsam gnas par 'dod pa la
NK076(mu)002:9502: rang dbang thob pa'i tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9503: grub pa'i phyir / lhag ma'i lus dang /
NK076(mu)002:9506: lus kyi lus dang bcas ma spangs mya ngan las 'das pas lhag bcas kyi mya 'das zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:9507: gnyis pa zag ldog med par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9508: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum po kun
NK076(mu)002:9509: zad pa'i tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin chen po
NK076(mu)002:9511: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ji ltar spyad kyang 'khor
NK076(mu)002:9512: ba la ldog pa meda pa'i lam pa zhes bya'o
NK076(mu)002:9513: // gsum pa dbugs dbyung nas bden pa mthong bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9514: rig pa la ranga dbang thob pas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi 'jigs pa las dbugs dbyung ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:9515: ngal bso ba'i phyir dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor zhes bya /
NK076(mu)002:9516: tshe dbang gi skabs 'dir zag bcas zag med sangs
NK076(mu)002:9517: rgyas kyi sa'i bden pa gsum las 'dir bdena pa
NK076(mu)002:9518: bar ma zag med rang gi mtshan nyid mthong bas
NK076(mu)002:9519: zag med mthong lam pa bya /
NK076(mu)002:9520: bzhi pa rig pa 'dzin par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9521: chos rang dang spyi'i don rnams la mkhas pa'i lta
NK076(mu)002:9522: ba rtogs shing ting 'dzin goms pas spyod pa rig
NK076(mu)002:9523: pa ye shes dang mi 'bral bar 'dzin pas na
NK076(mu)002:9525: rig 'dzin de'i cha lugs kyang lha dang mi la sogs pa'i cha lugs yin la /
NK076(mu)002:9526: ting 'dzin zhi khro gang yin pa'i rdo rja yi rigs la sogs pa'i rgyud 'dzin par byed cing /
NK076(mu)002:9527: mi gtong ba'i gzungs dang ldan pa las rig 'dzin gyi ming thob pasa rig 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:9528: gsum pa don bsdus te bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9529: de la sogs pa mthong lam pa'i yon tan gyi
NK076(mu)002:9530: rnam grangs kyis btags na mtshan gyi rnam grangs bsam
NK076(mu)002:9531: gyis ma khyab cing brjod kyis mi lang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:9532: gnyis pa de la dngos su lung ston cing dbang bskur 'byung bar lung bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9533: tshe dbang 'di la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis dngos
NK076(mu)002:9534: su sa khams te zhing khams 'di dang 'dir rgyug
NK076(mu)002:9535: la sgro 'dogs chod cig ces pa'i lung ston pa
NK076(mu)002:9536: dang / gsang mtshan rdo rje ch+gee mo zhes rda
NK076(mu)002:9537: rje'i ming nas bos ming gi dbang bskur bar 'byung
NK076(mu)002:9538: dang / ngo // gsum pa gnas dang skye ba
NK076(mu)002:9539: cha byad kyang gzhan don gyi skabs kyis ma nges
NK076(mu)002:9540: dang / ngo // pa / lta bas mthong zhing
NK076(mu)002:9541: ting 'dzin gomas pa'i nus mathu dang ldan pas spyod
NK076(mu)002:9542: yul thams cad rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK076(mu)002:9543: nyid du rang snang ba ma gtogs gzhan med pas
NK076(mu)002:9544: tshe la dbang ba'i rig pa 'adzana pa'i gnas de
NK076(mu)002:9545: dang / ngo // pa / yin te / de
NK076(mu)002:9546: ltar thams cad rig pa rang snang bas gnas su
NK076(mu)002:9547: ma gyur pa med pas brten pa'i gnas la phyogs
NK076(mu)002:9549: skye ba dang cha byad kyang gdul byi'i don bya ba'i skabs kyisa 'gyur zhing ma nges so //
NK076(mu)002:9550: lnga pa dgongs pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9551: mi dmigs pa chos nyid kyi dgongs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9552: ma 'gags pa phyag rgya'i dgongs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9553: dgongs pas gnas nas mthar 'bras bu la sbyor tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:9555: dang po dgongs pa mthong bya mthong byed med par
NK076(mu)002:9556: chos nyid mngon sum du mthong ba la sogs sgo
NK076(mu)002:9557: lnga yul med rang gsal ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:9558: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams rig pa bdag nyid chen
NK076(mu)002:9559: por rang snang du rtogs pa'i phyir yul du dmigs
NK076(mu)002:9560: su med do // gtan tshigs de'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:9561: chos can kun kyang yul yul can du mi mthong ngo //
NK076(mu)002:9562: 'o na de'i chosa nyid mthong ngam zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:9563: chos nyid kyang yul yul can du mi mthong bas
NK076(mu)002:9564: des na sangsa rgyas kyi thugs kyang yul yul can
NK076(mu)002:9566: 'o na 'khor ba mthong ngam zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:9568: nang bcud 'gro drug gi sems can kyang rang gi
NK076(mu)002:9569: sems nyid rang snang ba las gzhan du mi mthong
NK076(mu)002:9570: ngo // des na yul med rang gsal gnyis med du gang mthong ba /
NK076(mu)002:9571: des ni mtha' bral lhun grub yul yul can phyogs
NK076(mu)002:9572: re'i nyes skyon med pas yang dag pa zag med
NK076(mu)002:9573: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong zhes bya ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:9574: gtan tshigs de bas rna ba'i sgra yul yul can
NK076(mu)002:9575: gang du thos pa med par sgra grags stong zung
NK076(mu)002:9576: 'jug rang snang du thos pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9580: yid kyis yul rig pa sogs yul med rang snang
NK076(mu)002:9581: gnyis med du mthong bas na mthong ba'i lam mo
NK076(mu)002:9582: // gnyis pa de'i rgyu lta sgom gyi stobs las byung ngas zag bcas las khyad par gyur pa /
NK076(mu)002:9583: de ltar bden pa mthong ba'i rgyu gang las byung zhe na rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9584: rkyen 'jug pa ting 'dzin bzhi dang bar chad med pa tshogs sgrub pa las skyes pas /
NK076(mu)002:9585: de yi phyir bden pa dbyer med rang rig mngon sum du rtogs pa'i mchog tshe dbang ni /
NK076(mu)002:9586: bden pa dbyer med kyi rig pa ranga dbang thob
NK076(mu)002:9587: nasa sngon ngo bo'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin yin
NK076(mu)002:9588: te / lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum
NK076(mu)002:9589: gyis 'khor bar zag pa ni tshe dbang rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9591: gnyis pa ma 'gags pa phyag rgya'i dgongs pa /
NK076(mu)002:9592: sngon chad tshogs sbyor gnyis kyi lam gyi spangs bya'i
NK076(mu)002:9593: rtsol ba dang gnyen po'i rtsol ba'i 'adu byed rnams
NK076(mu)002:9594: kyang zag med kyi tshe dbang 'di la med de
NK076(mu)002:9595: / de'i rgyu mtshan ni 'dir mnyam rjes 'dres shis
NK076(mu)002:9596: nyon mongs mngon gyur dag pas 'bras bu thob tu
NK076(mu)002:9597: / re ba dang / ma thob pa'i dogs pa'i 'dzin chags dang bral bas /
NK076(mu)002:9598: blo che chung gi dbang gis blo chung na lha
NK076(mu)002:9599: stong nas nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs rim par
NK076(mu)002:9600: bsgom pa'am / blo chen rima pa med par cig char du rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis /
NK076(mu)002:9601: stong nas nyi khri bzhi stong la sagas bsam yas
NK076(mu)002:9602: grangs mang lha'i 'khora la rang rig par gsal bar
NK076(mu)002:9603: rdzogsa pa'i rnal 'byor ting 'dzin la gnas nas zhi
NK076(mu)002:9604: khro'i dkyil 'khor rnam pa gnyis kyis rang gzhan gyi
NK076(mu)002:9605: don thams cad sgrub par mdzad do //
NK076(mu)002:9606: gsum pa dgongs pa la gnas nas mthar thug 'bras bu la sbyor tshul /
NK076(mu)002:9607: dgongs pa de yi ming ni tshe la dbang sgyur
NK076(mu)002:9608: ba'i rnal 'byor gyi ting 'dzin zhes bya ba yin
NK076(mu)002:9609: te / rang don du lo brgya phrag bcu drug gi cha ma rdzogs kyi dus kyi bar du /
NK076(mu)002:9610: rang gi shes rab gsum gyis lam goms par byas nas mthar chags pa phyag rgya chen po /
NK076(mu)002:9611: thod rgal ba lhun grub gnyis thob pa'i tha ma
NK076(mu)002:9612: skad cig ma gcig gi cha yis rdo rje lta
NK076(mu)002:9613: bu'i ting 'dzin gyis shes sgrib 'joms pas dpa' bo
NK076(mu)002:9614: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sbyor ba'o
NK076(mu)002:9615: // drug pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9616: dang po bdag don gyi spyod pa /
NK076(mu)002:9617: tshe dbang rang dang rigs mthun yang blo che zhing
NK076(mu)002:9618: dgongs pa mchog tu gyur pa'i tshe dbang rgan po
NK076(mu)002:9619: rnams phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)002:9621: gsang sngags zag med kyi don la thos pa'i shes rab kyi thob pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9622: bsam pa'i shes rab kyis don rig par byas shing rtogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9623: bsgom pa'i shes rab kyis don rang gi rgyud la sbyor bas /
NK076(mu)002:9624: dper na dkyus sar phyin pa'i rta cang shesa te thogs med du 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:9625: lta ba de kun gyi sngon du 'gro ba yin
NK076(mu)002:9626: pas lta de'i dang shes rab gsum rtsal 'don pa
NK076(mu)002:9627: ni bdag po'i dona gyi spyod pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9628: gnyis pa gzhan don yon tan dang bcas pa de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9633: kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul te bzhi po de dag dang /
NK076(mu)002:9634: mngon par shes pa drug kyang mngon par shes pas /
NK076(mu)002:9635: tshe la dbang sgyur ba de nyid kyi ming dang ldan pa yis /
NK076(mu)002:9636: tshe la dbang bsgyur bas rtsa ba'i lus skye 'jig
NK076(mu)002:9637: med pas rdo rje'i sku' ngang las ma g.yos bzhin
NK076(mu)002:9638: gzhan don phrin las kyis bya ba byed cing 'gro
NK076(mu)002:9639: don thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ba yin
NK076(mu)002:9640: no // gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9641: cho 'phrul bzhis gzhan don bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9642: gzhan don mdzad nas 'bras bu la sbyor tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:9643: rmad du byung ba'i spyod pas gdul bya 'dul bar bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9645: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9648: kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyis gzhan don mdzad pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9650: dang po rdzu 'phrul nyi shu bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9651: cho 'phrul bzhi yi thaga mar sprul pa rdzu 'phrul
NK076(mu)002:9652: gyi cho 'phrul gyis gdul bya gzhan gyi don spyod
NK076(mu)002:9654: lam lta sgom gyi nus pa'i mthu can du gyur
NK076(mu)002:9655: pa'i skye ba rang dbang can tshe dbang rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9656: des / rdzu 'phrul nyi shu la spyod pa'i tshul /
NK076(mu)002:9657: ci lta bu nus she na /
NK076(mu)002:9658: lus shing bal ltar yang bas nam mkha' la bya bzhin 'phyo ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9659: rig 'dzin gyi gnas thams cad bgrod /
NK076(mu)002:9660: ngag gi bden pa 'grub pas chu bo'i rgyun gyen la ldog pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9661: rlung zhi bar gyur cig brjod pas mi 'gul ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9662: ri dang brag la sogs par thogs pa med par 'dzul nus pa chu la mi bying ba dang /
