NK076(mu)002:9664: dug dang mtshon gyis 'jigs par mi 'gyur te mi tshugs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9665: lus 'di mngon sum du mi snang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9666: lus gcig la manga por sprul pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9667: de dag las gzhan pa yang rang nyid kyi yod
NK076(mu)002:9668: la ji ltar 'doda pa bzhin du 'grub ste gang
NK076(mu)002:9669: zhe na / 'jig rten gyi lha ma srin sde brgyad rnams la bdag gis dbang bsgyur ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9670: rang gzhan gyi tshe dang dus la bsring bar 'dod
NK076(mu)002:9671: na bsring bar nus la bstung 'dod na bstung nus
NK076(mu)002:9672: pa dang / stong gsum gyi khams thams cad yungsa 'brur shong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9673: yungs 'brus stong gsum gyi stong chen pos gang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9674: ba spu nyag gcig gis stong gsum dgang ba stong
NK076(mu)002:9675: khams ba spu'i bu gar bsdu ba'ang yungs 'bru'i dpe
NK076(mu)002:9676: de bzhin no // srid pa bsreg pa'i bskal pa yi me yang gzhil bar nus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9677: rang gi lus la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'bum dus gcig la dgye nus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9678: sa phyogs skam po'i sar chu dbyung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9679: bye ma la gsera du 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9680: sol ba la ljon shinga du 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9681: gnyis pa 'byung ba lnga stobs chen du bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:9682: nam mkha'a la rdo rje'i skas pa sgoms pas rdo rje'i brag ltar sra ba'i skas 'byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9683: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bar bsgoms nas
NK076(mu)002:9684: tha mal gyi me yanga 'tshig par 'gyur ba dang
NK076(mu)002:9685: / kham las ye shes kyi chu rgyun 'bab pa'ang /
NK076(mu)002:9686: dpe gong gi de bzhin du tha mal gyi chu yang dag pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:9687: yam las ye shes kyi rlung gis 'jig rten gyi
NK076(mu)002:9688: khams 'thor bar bsgoms pas gtong ba rlung gis byed
NK076(mu)002:9689: pa dang / e las thams cad stong par bsgoms
NK076(mu)002:9690: pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad stong zhing steng
NK076(mu)002:9692: 'og nas steng du 'phen par bya ba'ang 'grub bo //
NK076(mu)002:9693: gsum pa las kha tshar brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:9694: ting 'dzin gyis dgra bgegs dgug pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9695: gling khams gzhan du gtang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9696: dgra bgegs kyi kha bcing ba /
NK076(mu)002:9697: gzhan gyis byad du bcug pa dgrol ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9698: sri'u dang lo tog nad pa gso ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9700: gzhan gyi g.yul 'pham par bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9701: bdag gi g.yul rgyal bar byed pa la sogs pa
NK076(mu)002:9702: rnams rang gis ji ltar dmigs shing bas pa bzhin
NK076(mu)002:9703: du 'grub ste / de yang ting 'dzin las su rung bas so //
NK076(mu)002:9704: bzhi pa gdug pa can dbang du bsdu ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9705: dang po dud 'gro gdug pa can dbang du bsdu na /
NK076(mu)002:9707: stag dom la sogs pa'i gcan gzan gdug pa can rnams kyang /
NK076(mu)002:9708: khyi la zan byin pa bzhin du bdag nyid phyi nasa rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
NK076(mu)002:9709: gnyis pa bar chad gdug pa can dbang du bsdu ba /
NK076(mu)002:9710: gzhan yang bar du gcod pa'i bdud gnod sbyin dang /
NK076(mu)002:9711: lha srin lus sems gdug pa can la sogs pas /
NK076(mu)002:9712: bdag la bar chad kyis tshugs par mi 'gyur /
NK076(mu)002:9713: slar bran g.yog bzhin du bdag gi bka' nyan pas
NK076(mu)002:9714: phrin las cing bcol thogs med sgrub par byed par
NK076(mu)002:9715: 'gyur ro // gnyis pa rjes su byed pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:9716: lha mi'i lus 'di ma bor bar tshe da bang rig 'dzin gyii sara gnas nas /
NK076(mu)002:9717: de'i thugs rje sprul pa'i byin rlabs kyis sprul sku'i rgyal tshab mdzad nas /
NK076(mu)002:9718: lha klu la sogs 'gro ba so so'i skad dang
NK076(mu)002:9719: mthun pa yis 'gro ba so so thar pa'i lam
NK076(mu)002:9722: ngan song gsum po'i gnas stongs shing mtho ris kyi dge ba'i las la bskul ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9723: gdul bya de nyid lam stegs kyi theg pa chung ngu nyan rang la dgod cing /
NK076(mu)002:9724: nyan rang de dag nyid thega pa chen po byang
NK076(mu)002:9725: chub sems dpa'i lam la dgod cing de nas gsang
NK076(mu)002:9726: sngags kyi lam la bkod par mdzad do //
NK076(mu)002:9727: so so'i skye bo rnams thar par bskul zhing nyan
NK076(mu)002:9728: rang rnams zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i mtha' la zhen
NK076(mu)002:9729: pa slong bar byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9730: rab dga' la sogs pa sa bcu' byang chub sems
NK076(mu)002:9731: dpa' rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i shes bya yi
NK076(mu)002:9732: sgrib pa rnams rim par sbyong bar byed cing /
NK076(mu)002:9733: bde bar gshegs pa longs sku dang sprul sku'i 'khor
NK076(mu)002:9734: sa la gnas pa dang mos pas spyod pa rnams
NK076(mu)002:9735: la'ang chos ston par mdzad do //
NK076(mu)002:9737: stong gsum gyi stong chen po brgya brgyad cu'i zhing
NK076(mu)002:9738: tshun chad kyang mngon shes kyi yul yin pas 'jig
NK076(mu)002:9739: rten de rnams / phyogs cha drug tu g.yo ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9740: tshab che bas rab tu g.yo ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9741: kun tu khyab cing tshabs che bas shin tu g.yo ba sogs chos snang ba'i mdzad pa snang basa /
NK076(mu)002:9742: de'i yon tan ni zhing ngam de na gnas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9743: sems can rnams mi rtag pa rgyud la skye zhing
NK076(mu)002:9744: lam la zhugs pa rnams kyi phyi ltar sa g.yos
NK076(mu)002:9745: pas / nang ltar ting 'dzin gyi nyams g.yos nas
NK076(mu)002:9746: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa sa yi rim
NK076(mu)002:9747: pa gong nas gong du sbyor bar byed /
NK076(mu)002:9748: bzhi pa kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyis gzhan don mdzad pa /
NK076(mu)002:9749: mthong lam tshe la dbang ba de nyid kyis gsang
NK076(mu)002:9750: ba sngags kya rang sgra bsgrags pas sgra skad kun
NK076(mu)002:9751: kyang yon tan rmad du byung ba gsang sngags kyi
NK076(mu)002:9752: sgra ti ri rir grags pasa de'i yon tan ni
NK076(mu)002:9753: phyi nang gi bdud bzhi la sogs dang bgegs rnams
NK076(mu)002:9754: 'dul zhing / sems can rnams kyi rgyud la ngan
NK076(mu)002:9755: song gsum gyi las dang nyon mongs pa rnams spyod
NK076(mu)002:9756: 'dul zhing / la / 'gro ba drug gi sems
NK076(mu)002:9757: can ma lus pa'i don yang blo dang 'tshams pa
NK076(mu)002:9759: gnyis pa gzhan don mdzad nas 'bras bu la sbyor tshul /
NK076(mu)002:9760: zhi rgyas dbang drag sogs phrin lasa rnam pa bzhi po thams cad kun byas nas /
NK076(mu)002:9761: mthar thug gi 'bras bu skye shi dang 'pho 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:9762: med pa'i g.yung drung chos kyi sku brgyud nas thob
NK076(mu)002:9763: la / gdul bya'i ngor mtshan so gnyis dang /
NK076(mu)002:9764: dpe byad brgyad cu po kun gyis brgyan pa'i gzugs skur snang nas /
NK076(mu)002:9765: lam mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu lam gyi rtsol ba bya ba med para pad+ma can dang /
NK076(mu)002:9766: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis mngon sum 'grub bo //
NK076(mu)002:9767: gsum pa rmad du byung ba'i spyod pas gdul bya 'dul bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9768: rgyas pa la sogs kyi rgyud las gsungs pa mi spang ba lnga /
NK076(mu)002:9771: 'dod yon lnga ste tshan bzhi yi spyod pa la
NK076(mu)002:9772: bye brag bcu tshan gnyis te 'khor ba'i chos nyi
NK076(mu)002:9773: shu la spyod pa dang phrin las zhi rgyas dbang
NK076(mu)002:9774: drag bzhi po rnams kyi gzhan don phyed pa ni
NK076(mu)002:9775: / tshe la dbang sgyur ba yi skabs 'di nyid du thogs pa med para 'byung bas /
NK076(mu)002:9776: sngon cho 'phrul gyi skabs su bstan pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:9777: stong gsum stong chen po brgya yi yul khyon de
NK076(mu)002:9778: dag gi gdul bya ma lus pa 'dul bar byed
NK076(mu)002:9779: / bdun pa mngon shes la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:9780: dang po mngon shes 'byung ba'i rgyu mig la sogs
NK076(mu)002:9781: pa'i skye mched bcu gnyis po yang ngo bo rang
NK076(mu)002:9782: byung gi ye shes rang yin pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:9783: skye mched bcu gnyis po de nyid cir yang 'char bas gcig gi mtha' dang /
NK076(mu)002:9784: rang byung ye shes las ma g.yos pas du ma'i
NK076(mu)002:9785: mtha' gnyis su med para rang rig pa'i mngon sum
NK076(mu)002:9786: du lta bas rtogs shing ting 'dzin gyis goms pas
NK076(mu)002:9787: / skye mched yul dbang gnyis med du mthong nasa
NK076(mu)002:9788: tshogs drug gi yul shes tha dad 'dzin pa'i dri
NK076(mu)002:9789: ma drug sbyangs pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:9790: gnyis pa mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9791: gong bstan ltar stong khams brgya'i yul de nyid tshun
NK076(mu)002:9792: chad kyi gzugs dang sgra dri ro reg bya rnams
NK076(mu)002:9793: dbang po lnga re re nas yul lnga gcod pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9794: mngon par shes pa'i bye braga nyi shu rtsa lngar
NK076(mu)002:9795: shar bas sgo lnga gcig gis yul lnga gcod par
NK076(mu)002:9796: byed pasa / dbang po lnga tshang ba dang ma tshang ba'i 'jigs pa'i dogs pa med do //
NK076(mu)002:9797: gsum pa drug rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9798: mngon shes nyer lnga de las gzhan du ste lha
NK076(mu)002:9799: yi rna ba yi mngon shes kyis stong khams brgya
NK076(mu)002:9800: tshun chad kyi sgra che chung nye ring med par
NK076(mu)002:9801: thos pa dang / lha'i spyan gyi mngon para shes
NK076(mu)002:9802: pa yis gzugs che chung nye ring med bar mthong
NK076(mu)002:9803: thos pa dang / ba dang / rang gzhan gyi
NK076(mu)002:9804: sngon tshe rabs kyi skye ba'i gnas dang skye ba
NK076(mu)002:9805: ci blangs rjes su dran pa yi mngon shes dang
NK076(mu)002:9806: thos pa dang / ba dang / / sems can
NK076(mu)002:9807: pha rol po rnams kyi sems kyi rtog pa ci
NK076(mu)002:9808: rgyu ba shes pa'i mngon shes dang /
NK076(mu)002:9809: 'gro ba gzhan 'di tsam nas 'chi 'apha ba dang
NK076(mu)002:9810: skya ba gang du len pa rnams mkhyen pa yi
NK076(mu)002:9811: mngon shes dang / rdzu 'phrul gyi bya ba shes
NK076(mu)002:9812: pa ste mi mthun pa brgyad la sogs ston pa'am
NK076(mu)002:9813: mngon shes dang / / gong gi spyod yul de
NK076(mu)002:9814: rnams la 'dzin pa med pas na zag pa zad
NK076(mu)002:9815: pa'i mngon shes dang drug go //
NK076(mu)002:9816: bzhi pa mngon shes kyi yul dang ming gi rnam grangs /
NK076(mu)002:9817: stong gsum brgya de snyed tshun chad kyi yul dang
NK076(mu)002:9818: gdul bya'i bye brag rnams mngon sum du shes pas
NK076(mu)002:9819: / gdul bya mos pa tha dad pa gang dang
NK076(mu)002:9820: ganga yang rung ba rnamas la 'dul thabs gang la
NK076(mu)002:9822: mngon shes de yi ming gi rnams grangs ni /
NK076(mu)002:9823: 'khor bar mi ldog pa'i mngon shes zhes kyang bya
NK076(mu)002:9824: zag pa med pa'i mngon shes kyang bya ba dang
NK076(mu)002:9825: / tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rigas kyi mngon shes zhes kyang bya /
NK076(mu)002:9826: de ltar mngon shes kyi mtshan gyi rnam grangs ni
NK076(mu)002:9827: yon tan gyi cha las mngon shes kyi ming yang
NK076(mu)002:9828: brjod pa'o // brgyad pa lam gong ma la sbyor tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9830: bdag gama gzhan don bya ba'i phyir tshe la rang dbang cana gyi rig 'dzin des /
NK076(mu)002:9831: rang don du sku tshe'i tshad lo stong drug brgya nyid dam /
NK076(mu)002:9832: gzhan don du skal pa grangs med ci snyed para 'jig rten du bzhugs pa'i mthar /
NK076(mu)002:9833: ranga gi sgrub pa'i 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:9834: sngon zag bcas rgya gcig spros skabs su blo che
NK076(mu)002:9835: chung yod pa bzhin 'dir 'bras bu la sbyor ba
NK076(mu)002:9836: la mthar chags rim gyis sbyor ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9837: thod rgal cig char du sbyor lugs gnyis 'byung ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:9838: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:9839: dang po rim gyis bgrod pa mthar chags pa /
NK076(mu)002:9840: de yang mdor bstan gyi snga ma mthar chags rim gyis sbyor tshul /
NK076(mu)002:9841: zag med mthong ba'i lam tshe dbang 'di nyid du /
NK076(mu)002:9842: tshe dbang rang ga zag med kyi thos bsam sgom
NK076(mu)002:9843: pa'i shes rab gsum la blo gomas par byas pas
NK076(mu)002:9844: / mthong spang sgrib pa dag pas tshe dbang rang
NK076(mu)002:9845: gi rtsa ba'i lus skye 'chi med pa rdo rje
NK076(mu)002:9846: lta bu de rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgya chena por
NK076(mu)002:9847: sngon lam dus kyi yi dam zhi khro rigs lnga
NK076(mu)002:9848: gang bsgoms pa mngon sum du gsal bar gyur pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9849: phyir lha sku'i cha lugs 'dzin pa phyag rgya chen
NK076(mu)002:9851: der bsgom lam de nyid yangas su gyur nas bsgom
NK076(mu)002:9852: spangs kyi sgrib pa dag ste mthar lam lhun gyis
NK076(mu)002:9853: grub pa'i rig 'dzin thoba nasa sangs rgyas kyi sa
NK076(mu)002:9854: la gshegsa pa'o // gnyis pa cig char du bgrod pa thod rgal ba /
NK076(mu)002:9855: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma thod rgal la cig char du sbyor ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:9856: mthong lam gyi rigs mchog lam sbyangs pa'i tshe dbang da nyid nasa /
NK076(mu)002:9857: sngon rim gyis pa'i skabs bzhin du rang gi thos
NK076(mu)002:9858: bsam sgom par gomas pa ye shes rab gsum la
NK076(mu)002:9859: goms par byas pas bsgom lam phyag rgya chen po
NK076(mu)002:9860: dora nas mthong bsgom gyi spang bya rnams ciga chara
NK076(mu)002:9861: du dag nas mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin la
NK076(mu)002:9863: de'i rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:9864: rgyu lta bas chos nyid rtogs tshab che ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9865: rkyen dam tshiga gtsang mar bsrung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9866: smon lam gyi nus mthu btsan pa yang yin pas /
NK076(mu)002:9867: de ni gnas skabs kyi cig char ba'am thod rgal ba zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:9868: gnyis pa sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9869: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan /
NK076(mu)002:9870: zag med kyi lam gsum po de nyid kyi bar
NK076(mu)002:9871: ma bsgom lam rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin bshad par
NK076(mu)002:9872: bya ba la'ang sngon gyi tshe dbang gi lus kyi
NK076(mu)002:9873: mdor bstan bzhin 'dir yang bzhi gnyis brgyad kyis lus
NK076(mu)002:9874: rdzogs par bya ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:9875: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la brgyad de /
NK076(mu)002:9877: tshogs lam rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor dang du ma
NK076(mu)002:9878: spros pa' rnal 'byor pas rang gi 'byung bzhi 'dus
NK076(mu)002:9879: pa'i lus kyang ngo bo sems nyid yin pa'i phyir
NK076(mu)002:9880: rtog tshogs thams cad rang bzhin gyi lhar mngon sum
NK076(mu)002:9881: mthong ba'i don la ting 'dzin goms par byas shing
NK076(mu)002:9882: spyod pa tshogs gnyis basgas pa'i mthar sbyor lam du
NK076(mu)002:9883: tshom bu tshogs bsgrubs pas mthong lam du rnam smin
NK076(mu)002:9885: lta ba chen du 'dzin pa'i kun 'gro'i sgrib pa
NK076(mu)002:9886: mthong lam pa'i rgyud la yod pa dag pa de
NK076(mu)002:9887: nyid bsgom lam rgya chen rig 'dzin gyi ngo bo'i
NK076(mu)002:9888: rgyu yin no // de yang rnam par smin pa'i
NK076(mu)002:9889: rig 'dzin gyis phyag chen la sbyor tshul gyis lus
NK076(mu)002:9890: lha mi'i lus la sems phyag rgya chen por smin
NK076(mu)002:9891: pas phyi'i lus dor nas rgya chen grub para 'dod
NK076(mu)002:9892: rgyu yin no // pa yin / tshe rgya la
NK076(mu)002:9893: sbyor ba la de ltar du 'dod pa med de
NK076(mu)002:9894: rgyu yin no // pa yin / / de ltar
NK076(mu)002:9895: bskyed bya skyed byed kyi snga phyi rgyu 'bras su
NK076(mu)002:9897: lus sems gnyis ka phyag rgya chen por smin pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:9899: rgyu 'bras dus snga phyi rim gyis bsgrubs nas thob
NK076(mu)002:9900: par 'dod pa min te rgyu 'bras dbyer med ngo
NK076(mu)002:9902: rgyu 'bras dbyer med ngo bo gcig pas don de
NK076(mu)002:9903: nyid lam du byas pas tshe dbang thob nas lhag
NK076(mu)002:9904: ma'i lus dang bcas pas lo brgya brgya bsnur zhing
NK076(mu)002:9905: bsgrubsa pa'i mtha' la tshe dbang des phyag rgya chen
NK076(mu)002:9906: po de nyid du gyur pa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:9907: de thob nas lam gong ma la sbyor ba'i dus
NK076(mu)002:9908: la nges pa tshad gcig tu bzung du med do
NK076(mu)002:9909: // gsum po ngo bo la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9910: sems phyag rgya chen po longs sku'i ngo bor snang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:9911: lus phyag rgya chen po longs sku'i cha byad du snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:9913: dang po ngo bor snang ba dngos /
NK076(mu)002:9914: mthong lam pa rang nyid sems lha sku phyag rgya chena pa gyur pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:9915: rgya gcig spros pa gnyis su lha bsgoms pas mthar
NK076(mu)002:9916: yid dam zhi khro gang yin pa de nyid la
NK076(mu)002:9917: mngon sum du gyur pa'i sku la /
NK076(mu)002:9918: thun mong dang mchog gi mtshan bzang so gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9919: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cur ldan pa longs spyod
NK076(mu)002:9920: rdzogs sku dang 'dra bas na longs sku gnyis pa
NK076(mu)002:9921: lta bu bsgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9922: no / gnyis pa rigs lnga so so'i rigs 'dzin pa /
NK076(mu)002:9923: de yang bye brag tu rdo rje rigs kyi phyag chen /
NK076(mu)002:9924: de bzhin du 'khor lo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK076(mu)002:9927: rala gri'i zhes las kyi phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK076(mu)002:9928: phyag mtshan lngas mtshon nas rigs lnga gang yin gyi
NK076(mu)002:9929: sku phyag rgya chen po'i rigas dang cha byad 'dzina
NK076(mu)002:9930: par gyur pas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin no
NK076(mu)002:9931: // gnyis pa longs sku'i cha byad du snang ba la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:9932: dang po cha lugs snang ba dngos /
NK076(mu)002:9933: de yang rang gi lus nyid ye gdod ma nas lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por gnas pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:9935: ting 'dzin gyis yang yang bsgoms pas /
NK076(mu)002:9936: yi dam lha gang yin dbang pos mngon sum du gyur pa'i lha'i sku la /
NK076(mu)002:9937: thun mong dang mchog gi mtshan dang dpe byad dang
NK076(mu)002:9938: cho 'phrul bzhi dang mngon shes drug dang nyer lnga
NK076(mu)002:9939: rdzogs / de ka la phyag rgya chen pa'i rigs
NK076(mu)002:9940: kyi mtshan dpe cho 'phrul mngon shes zhes su gragsa
NK076(mu)002:9941: rdzogs / so // gnyis pa ye shes sku'i cha
NK076(mu)002:9942: lugs 'dzin cing tshe dbang las khyad par du gyur
NK076(mu)002:9943: pas sku tshe'i tshad med pa /
NK076(mu)002:9944: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku longs sku yi cha lugsa can /
NK076(mu)002:9945: skye 'jig med pa 'byung ba rda rje'i lus bgres rgud can las kyang grol lo //
NK076(mu)002:9946: ye shes kyi sku thob pa de yi phyir rgya chen rig 'dzin la /
NK076(mu)002:9947: sku tshe tshad bzung du meda da /
NK076(mu)002:9948: tshe dbang ltar lo brgya brgya dag tu bsnur zhing
NK076(mu)002:9949: 'bras bu mngon du thob par bya ba'i rtsol ba
NK076(mu)002:9950: dang bral nas tshe dbang las spags so //
NK076(mu)002:9951: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:9952: dang po phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi rnam grangs spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:9953: rgya chen rig 'dzin de nyid kyi nang la kri ya rigas gsum gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:9954: u pa ya rigs bzhi yi phyag rgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:9955: yo ga rigs lnga'i phyag rgya dang /
NK076(mu)002:9956: ma h+aa yo ga mchog gi rigs lnga'i phyag rgya
NK076(mu)002:9957: ste lha de rnams kyi rigas dang cha byad 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9958: pas na rgya chen rig 'dzin te /
NK076(mu)002:9960: rigs rnam pa bzhi ru sngona tshe dbang la yang /
NK076(mu)002:9961: ngo bo sman dang thabs rig 'dzin sogs yod pa
NK076(mu)002:9962: bzhin du 'dir yang bzang ngan gyi khyad yod par
NK076(mu)002:9963: 'gyur ro // gnyis pa khyad par ma h+aa'i phyag rgya chen po'i rnam grangs /
NK076(mu)002:9964: de ltar rgya chen nang nas mchog tu gyur pa
NK076(mu)002:9965: ma h+aa'i phyag chen rig 'dzin de dag gi ming
NK076(mu)002:9966: gi rnam grangsa ni gnyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:9969: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yo
NK076(mu)002:9970: zhing gnas pas mi g.yo grub pa'i rnal 'byor zhes
NK076(mu)002:9971: kyang bya / tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i skabs su
NK076(mu)002:9972: lta ba la ched 'dzin kun 'gro'i rtsol ba'i 'adu
NK076(mu)002:9973: byed dang bral bas mthong lam gyi 'du byed dang
NK076(mu)002:9974: bral ba'i lam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK076(mu)002:9975: mthong lam du zag pa med pa chos nyid rang
NK076(mu)002:9976: mtshan mthong ba'i rgyun la gnas pas bsgom pa'i lam
NK076(mu)002:9978: dgongs pa chos nyid las mi g.yo ba grub pa'i rnal 'byor zhes kyang bya /
NK076(mu)002:9979: rgya chen rig 'dzin bya ba nyid du'ang brjod de ming gi rnam grangs lnga'o //
NK076(mu)002:9980: gsum pa lung chen dngos su 'byung bas bdud dang cha dbye mi dgos pa /
NK076(mu)002:9981: de la rgyal bar 'gro bar lung ston pa'i sangs
NK076(mu)002:9982: rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dngos su 'byung bas
NK076(mu)002:9983: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor zhes bya ste /
NK076(mu)002:9984: de la bdud dang cha dbye zhing brtag pa'i bye
NK076(mu)002:9985: braga zag med kyi bsgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i
NK076(mu)002:9986: rig 'dzin 'di la med de mi dgos so //
NK076(mu)002:9988: longs sku ye shes sgyu ma'i sku yi cha lugs
NK076(mu)002:9989: su yod pa'i rnal 'byor pa phyag chen rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:9990: pas / sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi gnyis pa longs
NK076(mu)002:9991: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i shes rab lta ba'i spyan dang
NK076(mu)002:9992: pas / / dgongs pa'i ting 'dzin yod kyang /
NK076(mu)002:9993: de bas dman la rgya chen de mar tshe dbang
NK076(mu)002:9994: dang gnyis lta dgongs kyi rgyud zag med rang mtshan
NK076(mu)002:9995: mthong bar mthun par snang mod kyang khyad yod de
NK076(mu)002:9996: gang zhe na / tshe dbang dgongs pa mi g.yo ba thob pa tsam yin la /
NK076(mu)002:9997: phyag chen mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo bas ting
NK076(mu)002:9998: 'dzin shin tu brtan pasa rig pa'i klong du bab
NK076(mu)002:10000: nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs grangs can gyi lha'i 'khor lo mngon du gsal bar snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10001: bsgom mi dgos pa sangs rgyas longs sku dang khyad
NK076(mu)002:10002: med snyam na 'on kyang da dung lam pa yin
NK076(mu)002:10004: ting 'dzin mthar lam bar mi yeng ba'i rtsol ba cana yin pas khyad par yod do //
NK076(mu)002:10006: rang don du dgongs pa mnyam par bzhag pa'i ngang
NK076(mu)002:10007: las ma g.yos bzhin du gzhan don du stong gsum
NK076(mu)002:10008: gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten khams brgya gcig nas
NK076(mu)002:10009: gnyis su 'brang ba'i stong phrag bcu yi 'jig rten
NK076(mu)002:10010: gyi khams rnams rdul phran du gsil ba'i grangs de
NK076(mu)002:10011: snyed dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten khams kyi gdul bya
NK076(mu)002:10012: dang sangs rgyas sprul pa'i zhing grangsa kyi gnas gzhan
NK076(mu)002:10013: drug cu las 'das pas bgrang du med pas /
NK076(mu)002:10014: grangs med brgya gcig nas gnyis su bgrangs pa'i stong
NK076(mu)002:10015: phrag bcu yi 'jig rten khams rnams rdul de snyed
NK076(mu)002:10016: dang mnyam pa'i zhing khams rnams su /
NK076(mu)002:10017: rtsa ba'i lus las ma g.yos par rngon pa dang
NK076(mu)002:10018: smad 'tshong ma la sogs pa rigs bzang ngan dang
NK076(mu)002:10019: / mtho dman sna tshogs par sprul pa'i lus gang la gang 'tshams kyis 'dul bar byed do //
NK076(mu)002:10020: phrin las sam cho 'phul bzhi dang mngon shes drug
NK076(mu)002:10021: la sogs pas 'gro don byed la gong bstan ltar
NK076(mu)002:10022: de bzhin na // bdun pa mngon shes /
NK076(mu)002:10024: dbang po sgo lnga yi mngon shes re re la
NK076(mu)002:10025: yan lag lnga lnga ste nyer lnga dang bcas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10026: tshul gyis mngon par shes pa'ang tshe dbang dang 'dra
NK076(mu)002:10027: moda / tshe rgya gnyis khyad yod dam zhe na yod de /
NK076(mu)002:10031: zhing grangs med pa sogs de snyed du 'dul zhing /
NK076(mu)002:10032: yul rgya che chung gyi khyad par yod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10033: zag med bsgom lam du mthong lam gyi don rdzogsa pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10034: gzhan don rdzogs pa la nus mathu che chung gi khyad dang /
NK076(mu)002:10035: tshe rgya gnyis gdul bya yul rgya che chung gisa spags pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10036: brgyad pa 'bras bu la sbyor tshul /
NK076(mu)002:10037: phyag rgya chen po rang gi dgongs pa mi g.yo ba'i don lta bas mthong zhing /
NK076(mu)002:10038: ting 'dzin goms par byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10039: 'bras bu don du gnyer ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10040: dkyil 'khor nam mkha' khyab sogs man chad rim par bsgom pa'i brtsam pa yis /
NK076(mu)002:10041: bsgom pa'i lam man chad kun rdzogs pa'i byin rlabs
NK076(mu)002:10042: dang mthu stobs kyis mi g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor bsgom
NK076(mu)002:10043: lam gyi ting 'dzin gyi rtsol ba dang brala nas
NK076(mu)002:10044: mthar lam du lha bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10045: ting 'dzin dbang thob pa'i dus su bsgom lam la
NK076(mu)002:10046: sngar yod pa'i mnyam gzhag gi thog tu lhan cig
NK076(mu)002:10048: bsam yas lhun grub kyi don mi gsal ba ni dri ma'am sgrib pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:10049: sngar bsgoms pa'i 'dzin pa dag nas ched du btsal
NK076(mu)002:10050: ba med par lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob
NK076(mu)002:10051: pa'o // gsum pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10052: dang po lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:10053: thod rgal ba mthong lam tshe dbang de dang /
NK076(mu)002:10054: mthar chags sgom lam rgya chen des mngon du byas pa yi 'bras bu /
NK076(mu)002:10055: rtsa ba'i lus la sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i cha byad dam rig pa 'dzina pas /
NK076(mu)002:10056: lhun grub rig 'dzin zhes kyang bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10057: rang rgyud la lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma cha phra ba dag nas /
NK076(mu)002:10058: ye shes rtsal rdzogs pas rang rgyud dag pa'i sangas rgyas zhes bya ba yin te /
NK076(mu)002:10059: de la yang sngon tshe dbang gi skabs su bstan
NK076(mu)002:10060: pa bzhin du 'di la yang bzhi gnyis brgyad kyi
NK076(mu)002:10061: lus rnam bzhag dagda par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:10062: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas bshad la brgyad /
NK076(mu)002:10064: lam snga ma'i phyag chen riga 'dzin lasa lta sgom
NK076(mu)002:10065: nus pa'i mthu rdzogs pas gong du bshad pa bzhina
NK076(mu)002:10066: du lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma sbyangs nas /
NK076(mu)002:10067: sangs rgyas longs sku'i cha byad can gyi gnyis pa
NK076(mu)002:10068: phyag rgya chen po' thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab
NK076(mu)002:10069: gsum gyis / 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dngos su 'byung ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK076(mu)002:10071: rgya chen mthar phyin nas lhun grub rig 'dzin thob
NK076(mu)002:10072: pa'i gnas skabs der sngon rgya chen thob pa'i skabs
NK076(mu)002:10073: su bstan pa bzhin du thos bsam sgom pa'i shes
NK076(mu)002:10074: rab gsum rdzogs par byed lugs ni /
NK076(mu)002:10075: rgyal ba langas spyod rdzogs sku drug pa las /
NK076(mu)002:10076: mthar thug gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lung yab
NK076(mu)002:10077: kyi dga' ba bcu drug /yum gyi dga' ba bcu
NK076(mu)002:10078: drug /yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug la ye shes
NK076(mu)002:10079: lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pa thos shing bsam pa
NK076(mu)002:10081: rang gi dgongs pa ting 'dzin dang rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK076(mu)002:10082: sbyong ba'i nus pa mthu can du gyur nas yi
NK076(mu)002:10083: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa mthar dbyung ba'i
NK076(mu)002:10084: dus la babs te sangs rgyas so //
NK076(mu)002:10085: de'i tshad la bzung du med do //
NK076(mu)002:10086: gsum pa ngo bo la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10087: dang po sku lnga lhun grub kyi rigs 'dzin cing sgrib pa sbyang tshul /
NK076(mu)002:10088: de ltar kun 'gro dang lhan cig gnas pa'i rang
NK076(mu)002:10089: rgyud kyi dri ma dag pa'i shes pa de nyid
NK076(mu)002:10090: / sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs mi gtong
NK076(mu)002:10091: zhing 'dzin pas rdo rje'i 'dzin pa zhes bya ste
NK076(mu)002:10092: / / dgongs pa lhun grub mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las mi gaya zhing /
NK076(mu)002:10093: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa nyid du mnyam par bzhag nas bzhugs pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:10094: de'nga 'di'i don ni lhun grub de lam la slob
NK076(mu)002:10095: pa'i rtsol ba ni med kyi 'on kyang rnam par
NK076(mu)002:10096: mi rtog pa'i ye shes ngang gis 'byung ba'i mthar
NK076(mu)002:10097: skad cig gis bag la nyal ba bcom ste /
NK076(mu)002:10098: dga' ba so gnyis dang ye shes brgyad cu la
NK076(mu)002:10099: yun se gol gdab tsam du sgrib pa'i nyon mongs
NK076(mu)002:10102: nyin par skar ma lta bu de rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis 'joms par byed cing /
NK076(mu)002:10103: sangs rgyas sa la dus mtha'i skad cig ma tsam
NK076(mu)002:10104: la rag las nas sangs rgyas pa yin pas na
NK076(mu)002:10105: rig 'dzin de ni lam pa rnams kyi mtha' ma
NK076(mu)002:10106: yin pa' //gnyis pa cha lugs dang rgyal tshab kyi
NK076(mu)002:10107: nges tshig mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin de'i sku'i
NK076(mu)002:10108: cha byad lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa
NK076(mu)002:10109: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen nyid kyi cha byad
NK076(mu)002:10111: rigs sam sku lnga pa gcig la dbyer med du lhun gyisa grub pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:10112: rgyal ba drug pa'i sku de nyid 'dra bas na /
NK076(mu)002:10113: drug pa de nyid kyi rgyal tshab mdzad nas 'khor la chos ston pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10114: sku lnga lhun grub kyis drug pa de yi rgyud
NK076(mu)002:10115: mi gtong bas na lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi ming
NK076(mu)002:10116: don dang / nges tshig rnams grub pa yina no //
NK076(mu)002:10117: gsum pa ngo bo'i mdzad pa /
NK076(mu)002:10118: lhun grub rig 'dzin nyid kyi rtsa ba'i lus de la skye shi 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' ba'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:10119: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i sku yin pas de
NK076(mu)002:10120: lta na yang gzhan don du gdul bya yi ngo
NK076(mu)002:10121: la nyid kyi sprul pa'i lus rnams ni mya ngan
NK076(mu)002:10122: las 'das pa'i tshul ston par byed de /
NK076(mu)002:10123: dper na rgyal bu don grub kyis mdzad pa bcu
NK076(mu)002:10124: gnyis kyi sgo nas don mdzad pa la sogas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10125: tshul ji lta bar lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi ston
NK076(mu)002:10126: pa'o // bzhi pa rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10128: bya ba'i rgyud kri ya'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:10129: rnal 'byor yo ga'i rgyud kya lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:10130: rig 'dzin rnal 'byor chen po'i gsang sngags nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i lhun grub rig 'dzin no //
NK076(mu)002:10131: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10132: dang po ma h+aa'i lhun gyi grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi rnams grangs /
NK076(mu)002:10133: de ltar grangs gsum gyi tha ma /
NK076(mu)002:10134: ma h+aa'i lhun grub kyi ming gi rnam grangs la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:10135: lam zad sar skyol pas mthar phyin pa'i lam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK076(mu)002:10136: rang gi rgyud la sgrib pa mngon gyur med pas rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10137: lhun grub rig 'dzin zhes bya ba de nyid dang
NK076(mu)002:10138: ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu la sbyor bas sbyor
NK076(mu)002:10140: yang dag par rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas drug pa rdo
NK076(mu)002:10141: rje 'chang kun tu bzang po'i rgyal tshab ces bya
NK076(mu)002:10143: gnyis pa sngags phyi ba'i rnam grangs /
NK076(mu)002:10144: dkyus kyi snga ma sngags phyi pa la kri ya'i rigs gsum lhun grub dang /
NK076(mu)002:10145: yo ga'i sems dpa' dang po bzhi'am /
NK076(mu)002:10146: rigs bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10147: kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyi cha lugs 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:10148: cing rang rang gi ston pa de gnyis kyi rgyal
NK076(mu)002:10149: tshab dang / de gnyis kyi sdud pa po yang byed do //
NK076(mu)002:10150: lnga pa dgongs pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10151: dang po dgongs pa dang mkhyen pa sangs rgyas dang mnyam la shes sgrib phra mos phye ba /
NK076(mu)002:10152: chos thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor gdul bya'i blos bsam
NK076(mu)002:10153: yas lhun gyis rdzogsa shing grub pa'i ting 'dzin gsal
NK076(mu)002:10154: ba'i phyir / ji lta ji snyed thams cad lta
NK076(mu)002:10155: ba mnyam bzhag la mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi spyan
NK076(mu)002:10156: ba'i phyir / mchog 'chang bas / bcu gsum yi
NK076(mu)002:10157: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis yang rnal 'byor gyis
NK076(mu)002:10159: de ni dgongs pa chos nyid ma gaya ba yi
NK076(mu)002:10160: don la blos gang du yang mi rtog par bsgom
NK076(mu)002:10161: dgos pas na / mnyam rjes kyi cha phra ba
NK076(mu)002:10162: yod pas da dung mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang mi
NK076(mu)002:10163: dgos pas na / rgya ste / dus nam gyi
NK076(mu)002:10164: tshe rgyas na dus mtha' yi skad cig ma gcig
NK076(mu)002:10165: la rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin nyid kyis bag
NK076(mu)002:10166: nyal gyi sgrib pa bcom nas sangs rgyas kyi sa
NK076(mu)002:10167: dgos pas na / rgya ste / la gshegs pa'o
NK076(mu)002:10168: // gnyis pa dgongs pa'i ming gi rnam grangs bstan
NK076(mu)002:10169: dgos pas na / rgya ste / la gshegs pa'o
NK076(mu)002:10170: // pa / lta dgongs sngar bstan ltar la des
NK076(mu)002:10171: na mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi dgongas spyod
NK076(mu)002:10172: rgya mtsho lta bur zab cing rlangs che ba kun
NK076(mu)002:10173: dgos pas na / rgya ste / la gshegs pa'o
NK076(mu)002:10174: // pa / / thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shesa
NK076(mu)002:10175: kyi rtsal rdzogsa pas rtsol ba'i bya ba meda pa'ang
NK076(mu)002:10176: dgos pas na / rgya ste / la gshegs pa'o
NK076(mu)002:10177: // pa / / / mthar phyin pa'i lam gyis
NK076(mu)002:10178: bya byed kyi rtsol ba dang bral bas bya bral
NK076(mu)002:10179: lhun grub kyi spyod pa zhes bya ba la sogas
NK076(mu)002:10180: pa yi minga gi rnam grangs de dag kun longs
NK076(mu)002:10181: spyod yon tan gyi cha las brjod par zad kyis
NK076(mu)002:10182: don la tha dad med pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10183: drug pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10184: dang po bdag don du sgrib pa bcom nas sangs rgyas tshul /
NK076(mu)002:10185: mthar lam bdag nyid kyi don bya ba'i phyir sku
NK076(mu)002:10186: lnga lhun grub drug pa rdo rje 'dzina pa chen
NK076(mu)002:10187: po yang dag par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa la
NK076(mu)002:10188: / lam gyi spangs rtogs kyi bya ba mthar phyin
NK076(mu)002:10189: pa'i dus kyi mtha' skad cig gis tol skyes te
NK076(mu)002:10190: / / skad cig ma'i dus kyi thag lta bas
NK076(mu)002:10191: bcad pa la sogs bslab pa'i mtha' bcu yongs su
NK076(mu)002:10193: lam mthar phyin pa'i tha ma'i lhun grub kyi rgyud
NK076(mu)002:10194: la yod pa'i bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa cha
NK076(mu)002:10195: phra ba de dag pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10196: mnyam par bzhag ma bzhag las 'das te bcom ldan
NK076(mu)002:10197: 'das kun tu bzang po sangs rgyas par gyur pa
NK076(mu)002:10198: yina no // gnyis pa gzhan don thugs rje'i mdzad pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10199: sku'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10200: thugs kyi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul dang /
NK076(mu)002:10201: gsung gi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul lo //
NK076(mu)002:10203: dang po nyid ni bdag don lhun grub thob pa
NK076(mu)002:10204: de tshe de la bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa
NK076(mu)002:10205: cha phra mo tsam yoda kyang lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10206: rig 'dzin gyi sara bzhugs nasa gzhan don du sangs
NK076(mu)002:10207: rgyas kyi 'dul ba'i zhing khams kyi grangs kyi mtha'
NK076(mu)002:10208: thug pa med pa de dag gi gdul bya rnams
NK076(mu)002:10209: 'dul ba'i phyir sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku'i mdzad pa
NK076(mu)002:10210: bcu gnyis ltar du'ang ston par mdzad de don bya
NK076(mu)002:10211: ba'i yul srid gsum gyi 'gro ba rigs drug gi
NK076(mu)002:10213: lhun grub rig 'dzin de'i thugs rje 'dul byed kyi
NK076(mu)002:10214: ston pa sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab par snang
NK076(mu)002:10215: nas / gdul bya lugs 'byung la bsam pa'i don dang mthun pa'i mdzad pa 'ba' zhiga ston la /
NK076(mu)002:10216: gdul bya lugs ldog la drag po'i sgo nas mi
NK076(mu)002:10217: mthun pa'i gdul thabs kyang ston cing thugs rje'i zhags
NK076(mu)002:10218: pa yis 'khor ba yi las rgyun gcod par byed
NK076(mu)002:10219: do // gnyis pa mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyis don mdzad pa /
NK076(mu)002:10220: dus dang gnas skabs la lar dga' ldan la sogs gnas nas 'pho ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10221: yum gyi lhumsa su zhugs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10222: lhums nas sku bltams pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10224: dus dang gnas skabs la lara mchod rten rnam dag
NK076(mu)002:10225: gi drung sogs su nyid las nyid rab tu byung
NK076(mu)002:10226: ba dang / chu bo ne rany+dza nar dka' thub lo drug sogs mdzad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10227: la lara btsun mo brgyad khri bzhi stong sogs khab tu bzhes pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10228: rgyal srid lo nyi shu rtsa dgu sogs skyong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10229: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10233: gdul bya la chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum bskor ba ston pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10234: grong khyer r+ts+wa mchog tu mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10235: sku gdung cha brgyad du bgos pa la sogs ston pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10236: gnyis pa thugs kyi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul /
NK076(mu)002:10237: gnas skabs res 'ga' zhi bas 'dul ba la zhi bar ston pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10238: res 'ga' drag pos 'dul ba la drag po khro bos 'dul ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10239: gdul bya g.yema pa 'dod chags can la g.yem par ston pa /
NK076(mu)002:10240: zhe sdang can la zhe sdang gi tshul du ston pa /
NK076(mu)002:10241: dregsa pa nga rgyal can rnams la nga rgyal ri bo lta bu dang /
NK076(mu)002:10242: mun pa ste gti mug can la gti mug mun pa ltar 'thib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10243: phrag dog rlung ltar 'tshubs pa la yang 'dul thabs
NK076(mu)002:10244: gnyen po de bzhin gdul bya dang mthun pas 'dul
NK076(mu)002:10245: ba / gdul bya dang mi mthun pa'i gnyen po'i
NK076(mu)002:10246: sgo nas kyang 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs mdzad do
NK076(mu)002:10247: ba / // rgya mtsho lta bur thabas zab cing rgya che ba'i spyod pa rlabs po che dang /
NK076(mu)002:10248: mdzad pa'i phrin las gong du bstan pa de bzhin
NK076(mu)002:10249: du mthun pa dang mi mthun pa sna tshogs pa
NK076(mu)002:10250: yi sgo nas 'gro ba 'khor ba las sgrol bar
NK076(mu)002:10251: 'gyur ro // gsum pa gsung gi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul /
NK076(mu)002:10252: lha gnas gsum du sngar gsungs pa'i gsang sngags rdo
NK076(mu)002:10253: rje theg pa'i tan+t+ra ste rgyud 'chad pa'i ston pa
NK076(mu)002:10254: mdzad pa dang / de bzhin du rgyud kyi don rnams kyi bsdu ba po'ang mdzad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10255: dman pa'i lus ngan song gsum dang bsod namas dang
NK076(mu)002:10256: ldan pa lha mi lus khyad par can gyi gnas
NK076(mu)002:10257: su / lha klu la sogs rang rang dang mthun
NK076(mu)002:10258: pa sna tshogas pa'i lus cana dam pa'i rigs can
NK076(mu)002:10259: lnga la sogs pa rnams la /
NK076(mu)002:10260: gsang sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'ang mdzad do //
NK076(mu)002:10262: mngon shes drug dang ldan pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10263: matshana bzang dang dpe byad sogs rgya chen man las 'dir khyad par spagsa te /
NK076(mu)002:10264: drug pa rdo rje 'chang kun tu bzang po'i cha byad 'dzin pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10265: kun mkhyen gyi ye shesa mang'a ba'i phyir rgyal ba drug pa dang mtshungs shing /
NK076(mu)002:10266: mngon shes kyi yul khyon dang gdul bya yang grangs
NK076(mu)002:10267: tshad bzung du med de rgyal ba drug pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:10268: dang gcig go // de yang ji ltar na gsal
NK076(mu)002:10269: la rtog med mkhyen pas na me long lta bu'i
NK076(mu)002:10270: tshul du lhun grub rig 'dzin la mnga' ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10271: brgyad pa 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sbyor tshul la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10272: dang po rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis shes
NK076(mu)002:10273: bya'i sgrib pa dang bdud bcom nas sangs rgyas la
NK076(mu)002:10274: sbyor tshul / rang rgyud la spang bya mi mthun
NK076(mu)002:10275: pa'i phyogs kyi mtshan ma shes sgrib bag la nyal
NK076(mu)002:10276: cha phra ba de gzhom pa'i phyir gnyen por gyur
NK076(mu)002:10277: pa 'bigs shing 'joms pa rdo rje lta bu'i ting
NK076(mu)002:10278: sbyor tshul / 'dzin gyisa / spang byar gyur pa
NK076(mu)002:10279: shes bya la bdag tu rtog pa'i sgrib pa'am nyon
NK076(mu)002:10280: mongs mtshan ma cha phra ba bag nyal de kun
NK076(mu)002:10281: rtsad nas bcom nasa mthar rdo rja lta bu'i ting
NK076(mu)002:10282: 'dzin mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su thim par byed
NK076(mu)002:10283: sbyor tshul / 'dzin gyisa / de / bsgom bya sgom byed las 'das so //
NK076(mu)002:10284: de bas bdag tu 'dzin pa med par rtogs pa ranga riga pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK076(mu)002:10286: dngos med stong par 'dzin pa'i bag chagas thams cad bsregs te /
NK076(mu)002:10287: phyi'i yul la rang gi mtshan nyid dang spyi yi mtshan nyid kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:10288: nang gi sems kya cha phra ba rtog pa bag nyal ba thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:10289: phyogs de'i dngos po med para rang byung gi ye shes mnyam pa nyid du rtogs par byas pasa /
NK076(mu)002:10290: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa phyogs zhen thams cad 'joms
NK076(mu)002:10291: pa'i dpa' bo yin la de'i sar 'gro bar byed
NK076(mu)002:10292: pas na dpa' bar 'gro ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK076(mu)002:10293: mi mthun 'joms pa'i rdo rje ste ye shes mthar
NK076(mu)002:10294: thug pas rtse mo mchog gi ting 'dzin thob pas
NK076(mu)002:10296: 'di'i lam pa man chad kyi yid tshoda du gyur pa yin pas zhen pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10297: bdud bzhi'i sde dang bcas pa rnams tshar bcad cing
NK076(mu)002:10298: gtan nas 'joms pa'i dpa' bas bdud bzhi bcom pa
NK076(mu)002:10299: de rjes la 'bras bu 'grub pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:10300: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad pa
NK076(mu)002:10301: rgyan gya 'khor lo'i man+dala ste yi ge 'khor lo
NK076(mu)002:10302: tshogs chen gyi sa'i dgongs pa bsam yas lhun rdzogsa
NK076(mu)002:10303: shes bya ma lus kun yul med rang gsal mkhyen
NK076(mu)002:10304: pa lta ba'i ngang du mnyam par 'jog go //
NK076(mu)002:10305: gnyis pa de'ang 'bras bu gzhan na med de rang
NK076(mu)002:10306: la gnas pa mngon du gyur tshul de la gsum
NK076(mu)002:10307: / dang po 'bras bu rang la byung ba mngon sum du snang ba'i rkyen /
NK076(mu)002:10308: de mnyam par bzhag nas ting 'dzin mthar phyin rgyal ba rnams kyi ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK076(mu)002:10309: phyag rgya mo la brten nas dbang bsgyur ba'i mthu dang zhing gi 'brel mtshams sbyor ba yin te /
NK076(mu)002:10310: 'bras bu don du gnyer ba'i smon lam rnam par dag pa'i mthusa /
NK076(mu)002:10311: gnyis pa 'bras bu rang las gyur pa mngon du snang ba dngos de la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10313: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las la'ang
NK076(mu)002:10314: lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga lam pa'i rig
NK076(mu)002:10315: pa la rang snang du thon pas gzhan gcig la
NK076(mu)002:10316: yod pa zhig 'dir 'ong nas thob pa min no
NK076(mu)002:10317: // gnyis pa bye brag rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10318: dang po 'bras bu rang gnas mngon gyur /
NK076(mu)002:10319: yon tan thams cad kyi rten byed pas sku lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:10320: brda' sprod pa'i gsung lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:10321: dgongs pa zab pa'i thugs lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:10322: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i yon tana lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:10323: don mdzad pa'i phrin lasa lnga la sogs pa gzhan la ngo mtshar zhing rmada du byung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10324: 'bras bu'i chos kun tu gragsa pa ni gsal ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:10325: rang rig ltun grub las gzhan nas yada pa zhig 'dir bkug nas 'ong ba ni ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:10326: sems nyid rgyu rkyen dang bral bas rang byung gi
NK076(mu)002:10327: ye shesa mtha' gang du yang gnas pa med par
NK076(mu)002:10329: gnyis pa de gzhan nas 'ong ba ma yin par
NK076(mu)002:10330: lam gyis rang gnas mngon du byas par bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:10331: / chos thams cad rang snang ba bde basa na
NK076(mu)002:10332: ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba skye med las skye
NK076(mu)002:10333: ba'i cha 'phrul shar ba 'bras bu'i chos nyer lnga
NK076(mu)002:10334: / po thams cad / sems nyid las ma gtogs
NK076(mu)002:10335: pa gazhana nas yod pa zhig 'dir bkug nas gsar
NK076(mu)002:10337: thabsa snang la ma 'gags pa bde ba'i ye shes
NK076(mu)002:10338: la blo brten pa'i shes raba rang bzhin med pa
NK076(mu)002:10339: dang dbyer med pa nyid du shar ba'i 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:10340: sku dang ye shes sna tshogs snang ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:10341: 'bras chos nyer lnga de lta bu yi nganga du rang snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10342: gsum pa 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar grol nas sangs rgyas par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:10343: de yang dper na mun pa las snang bar 'gyur
NK076(mu)002:10344: ba'am sbrul dug de nyid rtsi ma ki ta sman
NK076(mu)002:10345: du 'gyur ba ji bzhin du rtog tshogs ma spangsa
NK076(mu)002:10346: bar de nyid sku dang ye shes su 'gyura bas
NK076(mu)002:10347: / des na khams gsum 'khor ba yi zhen snang
NK076(mu)002:10348: 'di ma spangs bar 'bras bu myang 'das su rnam
NK076(mu)002:10349: / par daga pas / gsar du mya ngana las
NK076(mu)002:10350: mi 'ad'a ste ye gdod ma nas 'bras bu 'das
NK076(mu)002:10351: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ngo bor gnas pa yin la
NK076(mu)002:10352: / par daga pas / / de bas na 'khor
NK076(mu)002:10353: ba nas 'das pa'i sar 'gro ba dang sa de
NK076(mu)002:10354: la gnas para bya ba yi rtog pa yod pa
NK076(mu)002:10355: / par daga pas / / min te / rtog pa thams cada rang bzhin dbyer med sku dang /
NK076(mu)002:10356: ye shes kyi tshogs su gsal ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10357: gsum pa 'bras bu thob pa'i tshe rig 'dzin gyi tha snyad dang bral bar bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:10358: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mnyam gzhag la dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid yod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10359: ma bzhag na mi mnyam pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:10360: sangs rgyas ni mnyam par bzhag pa dang ma bzhag
NK076(mu)002:10361: pa med par mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos pa'o
NK076(mu)002:10362: // lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mnyam gzhag la gzhan don gyi bya ba lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10363: ma bzhag na gzhan don mi bya ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10364: sangs rgyas kyis mnyam rjes kyi bya ba med par gzhan don lhun grub tu byas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10365: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mnyam gzhag la 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10366: rjes shes la ma grub pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10367: sangs rgyas kyi mnyam rjes med par 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10368: rgyu mtshan gsum po de yi phyir na 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:10369: sangs rgyas thob pa'i tshen rig 'dzin gyi tha snyad
NK076(mu)002:10371: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:10372: lam la mtshan nyid gsum yod pa las mthar phyin
NK076(mu)002:10373: pa'i lam gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid rig
NK076(mu)002:10374: 'dzin rnams kyi don ma nor bar bstan pa'i gzhung
NK076(mu)002:10375: gi tshig don rnams mtshams gcod cing 'dzin pas la'u
NK076(mu)002:10376: ste / yas bgrangs brgyad pa'i don du gda' 'o //
NK076(mu)002:10377: spyi don gsum pa mngon du byas pas 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa bstan pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10378: dang po phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba /
NK076(mu)002:10379: rang bzhin gzhi ji bzhin pa'i chos sku chen po
NK076(mu)002:10380: nyid du ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don ji bzhin
NK076(mu)002:10381: pa lam gyis na mngon sum du stobs rdzogs par
NK076(mu)002:10383: lhun grub rgyal ba rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po
NK076(mu)002:10384: kun tu bzang po nyid la mos shing gus pas
NK076(mu)002:10385: 'dud pa ste / don gyi rtogs pa 'jal ba'i phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10386: dper na srid pa 'khor bar skye ba len lug la mngal skyes rim gyis pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10387: bardzusa skyes rdzogs tshul cig char du smin pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:10388: lam rim dang cig char gnyis kyii sgo nas gzhi don ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:10389: mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag gcig /lam
NK076(mu)002:10390: la don yod bya ba'i phyir mthar thug sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)002:10391: kyi dgongs pa bshad par bya ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10394: spyir lam la mtshan nyid gsum yod pa'i tha ma'i ni /
NK076(mu)002:10395: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid rig 'dzin rnams yin la /
NK076(mu)002:10396: de'i tha ma mthar thug sangs rgyas lugs ni /
NK076(mu)002:10397: 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK076(mu)002:10399: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu'i khyad par bstan
NK076(mu)002:10400: pa gsum gyis 'bras bu'i lus rnam bzhag gsum gyi
NK076(mu)002:10401: don mngon sum gyi tshul du snang ba rnams ni
NK076(mu)002:10402: / yan lag rgyas bshad kyi sgo nas ji lta ba bazhana du shes par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:10403: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10404: rgyal ba drug pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo dang /
NK076(mu)002:10405: 'bras bu thob nas dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:10409: de ltar lus rnam bzhag la don gsum yod pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10410: dkyus kyi snga ma 'bras bu'i ngo bo la brjod
NK076(mu)002:10412: yon tan gyi rten byed pa'i sku dang /
NK076(mu)002:10413: go bar brda sprod pa'i gsung dang /
NK076(mu)002:10414: dgongs pa zab pa'i thugsa nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:10416: bya ba byed pa'i phrin las rnams ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos te /
NK076(mu)002:10417: de ltar lnga po de re re la yang lnga
NK076(mu)002:10418: lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga nyid kyi ngo bar
NK076(mu)002:10419: gnas so // gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:10420: dbyer med lhun grub kyi ngo bo dang /
NK076(mu)002:10421: ma 'dres rnam grangs su snang ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK076(mu)002:10423: dang po yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug
NK076(mu)002:10424: pa ni mtshan gyi rnam grangs kyis 'og ma'i sangs
NK076(mu)002:10425: rgyas las spags tshul ngo bo nyid lhun gyis grub
NK076(mu)002:10427: e ma ho ni lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:10428: khyad par can ye nas gnas pa mngon sum du
NK076(mu)002:10430: dgongs pa de'i ngo bo phyogs re'i nyes skyon dang
NK076(mu)002:10431: bral zhing yang daga par dbyer med du mngon sum
NK076(mu)002:10432: du rdzogs pa'i don la gzhi dang lam gyi nyes
NK076(mu)002:10433: pa gnyis dang bral bas sangs la ye shes mtha'
NK076(mu)002:10434: dbus med par gdal bas rgyas pa ste thun mong
NK076(mu)002:10436: sku gser gyis gtams pa la sogs pa phyi'i bdud las rgyal ba yin la /
NK076(mu)002:10437: de las lhag pa 'di'i rgyal ba ni phung po
NK076(mu)002:10438: lnga rigs lngar shar ba la sogs pa nang gi
NK076(mu)002:10440: thun mong gi lha rgyu ya theg pas ji lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10441: phyi rgyud kyis ji snyed pa'i bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa rnam par dag pa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:10442: de las lhag pa 'di'i lha ni mnyam pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:10443: kyi ngang la bag nyal gyi sgrib pa rnam par
NK076(mu)002:10444: dag pa'o // 'khor ba las 'phags pa'i rgyu'i theg
NK076(mu)002:10445: pas ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa las lhag pa
NK076(mu)002:10446: 'di'i 'aphagas pa dbyer med mnyam pa nyid la spyod
NK076(mu)002:10447: yul yongs su dag pas kun tu bazanga po'o //
NK076(mu)002:10448: thun mong gi de bzhin gshegs pa ni rgyu'i theg pas spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10449: kri yas dag pa mtha' bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)002:10450: yo gas mtshan ma med pa'i de bzhin nyid la sogs pa nar son pas gshegs la /
NK076(mu)002:10451: de las lhag pa 'di'i de bzhin gshegs pa ni
NK076(mu)002:10452: gnyis med lhun grub mnyam pa nyid kyi de bzhin
NK076(mu)002:10453: nyid nar son nas gshegs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10454: thun mong gi bde bar gshegsa pa ni rgyu'i theg
NK076(mu)002:10455: pas nyon mongs pa chos nyid du sbyang ba dang
NK076(mu)002:10456: / phyi rgyud kyis lhar bsgyur nas zug rngu zhi bas bde bar gshegs la /
NK076(mu)002:10457: 'dir de lasa kyang lhag pa bde bar gshegs pa
NK076(mu)002:10458: ni nyon mongs ye shes su rang dbang bsgyur nas
NK076(mu)002:10459: zug rngu zhi bas bde bar gshegs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10460: de mthar phyin nas gshegs pa ni dper na rin
NK076(mu)002:10461: chen nor bu la dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pa
NK076(mu)002:10463: de yang dgong pa tshang ba /
NK076(mu)002:10469: yang na yon tan la zad 'phel dang /
NK076(mu)002:10471: thugs rje la nye ring med pa'i chos drug dang
NK076(mu)002:10472: ldan ba nor busa mtshon pa'i rgyal ba drug pa
NK076(mu)002:10473: de ni / yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs pas dgos pa tshang ba /
NK076(mu)002:10474: gdul bya'i re ba skong ba /
NK076(mu)002:10477: bdag dang gzhan du rtog pa med pa /
NK076(mu)002:10479: 'bras bu'i chos nyer lngar ma 'dres par shar ba'i
NK076(mu)002:10480: ngos nas rigs du mar snang bas gcig pa'i mtha'
NK076(mu)002:10481: dang bral la / yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas rang
NK076(mu)002:10482: byung ye shes su lhun gyis grub pas du ma'i
NK076(mu)002:10483: mtha' kun dang brala zhing des na gcig du ma
NK076(mu)002:10484: gnyis ka'i bdag nyid yin pas ldan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10485: gnyis pa rigs lhun grub de nyid phyogs med du
NK076(mu)002:10486: shar yang rigs phyogs gcig tu chad pa med par
NK076(mu)002:10487: bstan pa / rigs drug pa de nyid de'ii rigas
NK076(mu)002:10488: thams cad kun gyi dngos gzhi yin pas phyogs gcig
NK076(mu)002:10489: pa'i rigs dang bral ba yi phyir /
NK076(mu)002:10490: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lnga ste
NK076(mu)002:10491: nyi shu rtsa lngara ldana pa de zhing khams phyogs
NK076(mu)002:10492: dus kyi rgyal ba kun gyi ngo bo nyid yin
NK076(mu)002:10493: pas / gdul bya rnams la rang rang ci ltar mos bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:10494: gang mos de bzhin du de'i rigs dang mthun par sku lnga la sogs par snang la /
NK076(mu)002:10495: yang dag pa'i don rang bzhin nyid kyi dbang btsan
NK076(mu)002:10496: du byas na rigs rang rgyud pa 'di kho na'o
NK076(mu)002:10497: zhesa phyogs gcig tu grub pa med do //
NK076(mu)002:10498: gsum pa ngo bo lhun grub kyi yon tan phyogs
NK076(mu)002:10499: re nas mtshan gyi rnam grangs su dbye ba sku
NK076(mu)002:10500: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga po nyid re
NK076(mu)002:10501: re la bye brag lnga lnga nyi shu rtsa lngar
NK076(mu)002:10503: rigas thams cad kyi bdag po yanga dag par rdzogs
NK076(mu)002:10504: pa'i sangs rgyas drug pa kun tu bzang po zhes
NK076(mu)002:10505: pa'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:10506: mtshan nyid gsum gyi tha ma 'bras bu bzhi de'
NK076(mu)002:10507: tha ma des mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i skabs su
NK076(mu)002:10508: bag nyal gyi sgrib pa bcom pas phyogs zhena tha
NK076(mu)002:10509: dag phral ba yi phyir sangs la /
NK076(mu)002:10510: rang byung gi ye shes kyis 'gro 'ong meda par
NK076(mu)002:10511: shes bya'i chos kun la khyab pas na rgyas zhes
NK076(mu)002:10512: pa'am / thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis 'gro
NK076(mu)002:10513: 'ong med par shes bya kun la khyab pas na
NK076(mu)002:10514: rgyas pa'i phyir sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:10515: chos nyid snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang byung
NK076(mu)002:10516: gi ye shes ni ma bcos par lhun gyis grub
NK076(mu)002:10518: ci bzhin pa de'i ngang nyid du dgongs pa 'gro
NK076(mu)002:10519: 'ong meda pa nar son par gshegs pas na de
NK076(mu)002:10520: bzhin gshegs pa zhes kyang bya /
NK076(mu)002:10521: de bzhin du chos nyid la spros pa'i zug rngu med pas bde ba chen po'i ngang nyid du /
NK076(mu)002:10522: rtsol rtog gi zug rngu kun dang bral te bdag
NK076(mu)002:10523: gzhan gyi don gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir na
NK076(mu)002:10525: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang khams gsum gyi sems
NK076(mu)002:10526: can thams cad gnyis su med par sems nyid la
NK076(mu)002:10527: nar son pas 'khor 'das thams cad la dbang bsgyur
NK076(mu)002:10528: bas dbang phyug chen po drug pa nyid longs spyod
NK076(mu)002:10529: chen po'i skur bzhugs pas na dbang phyug chen po
NK076(mu)002:10530: zhes bya / gsang ba'i bdag po ye shes dang yul dbyings gnyis 'adu 'brala med pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:10531: gasnga ba'i dbang po rdo rje dang pad+ma gnyis 'adu
NK076(mu)002:10532: 'bral med par kha sbyor gyis bde ba la longs
NK076(mu)002:10533: spyod pas gsang ba'i sku zhes kyang bya /
NK076(mu)002:10534: 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis kyi longs spyod la
NK076(mu)002:10535: nan tar mi 'dzin pas bde ba chen por longs
NK076(mu)002:10536: spyod pas na longs spyod ces so //
NK076(mu)002:10537: de dag ni drug pa kun tu bzang po'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs so //
NK076(mu)002:10538: gnyis pa ma 'dres rnam grangs kyi ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:10539: dang po nye bar bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:10540: rgyal ba rigs drug pa de nyid kyi yon tan
NK076(mu)002:10541: gyi cha las sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK076(mu)002:10542: lnga po cha re re nas phye ste nyi shu
NK076(mu)002:10543: rtsa lnga brjod pa ni gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:10544: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la lnga /
NK076(mu)002:10545: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lnga'o //
NK076(mu)002:10551: 'jig rten las 'das pa rnam par byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10553: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos can ma lus pa
NK076(mu)002:10554: kun chos nyid don dam par dbyer med du gcig
NK076(mu)002:10555: pa yi / rgyal ba chos sku nyid yin pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10556: phyir 'khor 'das sna tshogas pa'i chos su ma 'gags
NK076(mu)002:10557: par kun rdzob tu snang ba'i dus nyid na /
NK076(mu)002:10558: don dam la rang bzhin nam ngo bo rang rgyud du grub pa med pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:10559: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i don mngon du byed
NK076(mu)002:10560: pa de nyid d+harma ni chos k+aa ya sku ste
NK076(mu)002:10561: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i chos skur gnas so
NK076(mu)002:10562: // gnyis pa mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK076(mu)002:10563: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang rig par mngon sum du snang bas mngon par /
NK076(mu)002:10564: de nyid la phyogs 'dzin gyi zhena pa'i mtha' kun
NK076(mu)002:10565: dang bral bas byang rang rig pa'i ye shes su
NK076(mu)002:10566: kun chub pa'i phyir mngon par byang chub pa ste
NK076(mu)002:10567: / rig pa de nyid rgyu rkyen dang byed pa po med par rang byung zhing /
NK076(mu)002:10568: sgrib g.yogs med par rang gsal bas ye shes chen po nyid /
NK076(mu)002:10569: sku bzhi po kun gyi gzhi byed cing gdul bya
NK076(mu)002:10570: ji ltar 'dul ba ltar snang ba'i phyir mngon par
NK076(mu)002:10571: byang chub pa'i sku ste sku bzhi po las mchog
NK076(mu)002:10572: tu gyur pa'o // gsum pa longs sku /
NK076(mu)002:10573: tha ma 'dod pa'i khamas kyi gnas kyi mtha' ma
NK076(mu)002:10574: dmyal ba nas yar yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK076(mu)002:10576: dmyal ba la sogs pa ngan song gsum gyi sdug
NK076(mu)002:10577: bsngal kun dang 'doda khams kyi lha mi'i 'dod yon
NK076(mu)002:10579: gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK076(mu)002:10581: nyan thos 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug dang rang rgyal zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i bde ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10582: byang sems kyi btang snyomsa sa pa /
NK076(mu)002:10583: gsang sngags kyi bde chen dang /
NK076(mu)002:10584: sogs khong nas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad yul
NK076(mu)002:10585: yul can du zhen pa med par kun la rol
NK076(mu)002:10586: bas longs spyod che ba ste longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10587: sku'o // bzhi pa sprul pa'i sku /
NK076(mu)002:10588: rlung gi rta bdun la brten pa'i nyi ma /
NK076(mu)002:10589: ri bong gzugs bris pa can zla ba nyid lha
NK076(mu)002:10590: rnams kyi gzhal yas khang yin pa de las ma
NK076(mu)002:10591: g.yon bzhin du / chu dwangs par kun tu gzugs
NK076(mu)002:10592: brnyan tha dad pa snang ba ltar rgyal ba drug
NK076(mu)002:10593: pa'i sku'i ngo bo'am dgongs par 'gro 'ong med par
NK076(mu)002:10594: gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs la phyogs kun tu thub
NK076(mu)002:10595: pa drug la sogs par snang nas don mdzad pa
NK076(mu)002:10596: ni sprul sku'i mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10598: dpe ji ltar na 'dus ma byas kyi nam mkha' la skye ba dang 'jig pa med pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:10599: sprul sku 'dus byas mi rtag pa chos kun gyi dngosa gzhir snang yang /
NK076(mu)002:10600: ngo bo rang la 'gyur ba med pas rtag pa
NK076(mu)002:10601: chen por bzhugs pa de nyid snang stong gnyis med
NK076(mu)002:10602: rdo rje'i sku mchog tu gyur pa de la skye
NK076(mu)002:10603: 'jiga med pa'o // de ni grangs kyi lnga pa
NK076(mu)002:10604: dbyer med rdo rje sku nyid du le lag la
NK076(mu)002:10605: sogs pa'i rgyud kun la raba tu gragsa so //
NK076(mu)002:10607: de ltar sku lnga pos so sor 'dul ba'i 'khor lnga bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:10608: chos sku'i 'khor ye shes lnga'i gzugs brnyan mchog gi
NK076(mu)002:10609: 'khor rigs lngar shar bas ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshagas
NK076(mu)002:10611: longs sku'i 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho ni /
NK076(mu)002:10612: shesa bya thams cad mkhyen pa yi ye shes la
NK076(mu)002:10613: bsgribs par gyur pa'i sgrib pa mtha' ma shes sgrib
NK076(mu)002:10614: cha phra ba spong ba'i sa bcu la gnas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10615: byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:10616: bsgom lam rgya chen rig 'dzin rnams so //
NK076(mu)002:10618: yo ga 'bras bu'i rgyal po rigs lnga dang /
NK076(mu)002:10621: pha rol tu phyin pa'i kun tu 'od kyi sangs
NK076(mu)002:10622: rgyas la sogs pa'i rgyud mas sbyangsa pa theg pa
NK076(mu)002:10623: 'og ma'i sangs rgyas te rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs
NK076(mu)002:10624: dang / sprul sku'i 'khor mos pa rgya mtsho ni /
NK076(mu)002:10625: rgyu'i mos pa spyod pa'i sa tshogs sbyor dang rgyu'i
NK076(mu)002:10626: sa dang po'ang tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:10627: no // mi 'gyur rdo rje'i 'khor dbyer med rdo
NK076(mu)002:10628: rje tshagas kyi zhal mthong zhing gsung brda' 'jal ba'i
NK076(mu)002:10629: phyir lhun grub rig 'dzin ni rdo rje'i sku'i 'khor
NK076(mu)002:10631: gnyis pa gsung lnga la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10632: dang po gsung lnga so so'i 'khor dang gsang bdag
NK076(mu)002:10633: gis lhun grub tu brda' mjal tshul spyir bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:10634: / 'khor lnga po de dag la ston pa sku
NK076(mu)002:10635: lnga po de yi dgongs pa gsung lnga po bshad
NK076(mu)002:10636: / pa ni / sprul skus tshig tu brjod pas
NK076(mu)002:10637: go ba dang sku bzhis tshig tu ma brjod kyang
NK076(mu)002:10638: brjod pa dang 'dra ba'i phyir don gyi gsung du
NK076(mu)002:10639: / pa ni / nges pas na / tshig dang
NK076(mu)002:10640: yi ge ru brjod pa med par don go zhing
NK076(mu)002:10645: rdo rje sku dang bzhi yi gsung yin la /
NK076(mu)002:10646: sprul sku'i gsung tshig dang yi ga ru brjod pas
NK076(mu)002:10647: ston pa ste de yang 'gro drug gi gnas su
NK076(mu)002:10648: rtsa ba drug po re re la yang /
NK076(mu)002:10649: ring thung 'bring gi chas drug drug go //
NK076(mu)002:10650: de re re la yan lag bcu bcu ste drug
NK076(mu)002:10651: cu pa tshan pa drug la sum bargya drug cus
NK076(mu)002:10652: don go zhing brda' 'jal bar byed pa sprul sku'i
NK076(mu)002:10653: tshig gi gsung dang lnga po nyid kyi tshul gyis
NK076(mu)002:10655: sku lnga po so so rang rang gi 'khor lnga po de dag nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:10656: spyi'i 'khor sdud pa po gsang bdag phyag na rdo
NK076(mu)002:10657: rje de dag gis gsung lnga lhun grub dus gcig
NK076(mu)002:10658: tu thos nus pa'i snyan cha lnga dang ldana pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10659: phyir gsung lnga lhun grub thob pas /
NK076(mu)002:10660: sdud pa pos tshig tshogs dang yi ge bkod pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10661: tshe gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud sde kun
NK076(mu)002:10662: gyi mgo la / sku bzhi'i gsung la bashada ces pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10663: sprul sku'i gsung la thos zhasa gsungs so //
NK076(mu)002:10664: gnyis pa gsung lnga so sor bshad pa la lnga /
NK076(mu)002:10665: dang po chos sku skye med don gyi gsung /
NK076(mu)002:10666: chos sku'i 'khor dang skye med kyi don gnyis rang
NK076(mu)002:10667: bzhin bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel ba yod pa dang
NK076(mu)002:10668: 'khor gyi sgrib pa dag ste shes rab kyi dbang
NK076(mu)002:10669: po dwangs pas / dper na rgya mtsho rnyog ma
NK076(mu)002:10670: dwangs pa'i chu la nya zla skar gsum gyi gzugs
NK076(mu)002:10672: chos thams cad ma skyes shing skye ba med par brda' sprod pas /
NK076(mu)002:10673: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung mchog gis /
NK076(mu)002:10674: sprul sku'i gsung ltar tshig tu smra brjod med par go bar byed pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:10675: de yang chos sku'i dgongs pa skye med de /
NK076(mu)002:10676: 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho'i blo la snang bar mdzad pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10677: gnyis pa mngon par byang chub pa'i gsung rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung /
NK076(mu)002:10678: rang rig pa'i ye shes de stong pa nyid kyi
NK076(mu)002:10679: ye shes la sogs pa ming lnga dang ldan pa
NK076(mu)002:10680: / gong gi chos sku'i gsung de bzhin du rang
NK076(mu)002:10681: bzhin 'brel ba'i rig pa byin rlabsa kyi gsung gis
NK076(mu)002:10682: brjod pa med par brjod bya'i don rang bzhin gsang
NK076(mu)002:10683: ba'i snying po'i rgyud kyi don rnams kun /
NK076(mu)002:10684: dper na nyi ma yi dkyil 'khor 'od kyis thams cad gsal bar byed pa lta bur /
NK076(mu)002:10685: 'khor gyi blo la don gsal bar snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10686: gsum pa longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung /
NK076(mu)002:10687: dper na me long lta bur skyon sel bar byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10690: gzugs brnyan snang bar byed pa /
NK076(mu)002:10694: mi ldan pa ma yin pa dang chos brgyad kyis
NK076(mu)002:10695: mtshon pa'i don dbang phyug chen po'i longs spyod rdzogs
NK076(mu)002:10696: pa'i sku de 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyis
NK076(mu)002:10697: mthong bas 'khor rgyu'i sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK076(mu)002:10698: rnams dang / 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:10699: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi byang chub sems dpa' che'i
NK076(mu)002:10700: zhes rig pa 'dzin chen po'i rgyud la brda'i sgo
NK076(mu)002:10701: nas gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa'i don snang bar
NK076(mu)002:10702: byed do // bzhi pa sprul sku'i gsung tshangs pa dbyangs kyi tshig tu /
NK076(mu)002:10703: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rnam par grol ba myang 'das
NK076(mu)002:10704: thar pa'i gnas su 'grod pa lam gyi chos dang
NK076(mu)002:10705: / kun nyon 'khor ba'i chos su snang ba'i sgra skad thams cad /
NK076(mu)002:10706: sprul sku'i gsung gi dbyangs la sogs pa la drug
NK076(mu)002:10707: gi chos ston pa de rtsa ba tshangs pa'i dbyangs
NK076(mu)002:10708: la sogs pa drug la rigs drug gi yan lag
NK076(mu)002:10709: 'du shes bskyed pa la sogs pa bcu bcu ste
NK076(mu)002:10710: / sum brgya drug cu'i tshul gyis 'jig rten gyi
NK076(mu)002:10711: mes po tshangs pa'i ngag ltara snyan cing yid du
NK076(mu)002:10712: 'ong ba'i gsung gis gdul bya mos pa la spyod
NK076(mu)002:10713: pa'i sa pa las 'phro dang skal ba can rnams
NK076(mu)002:10714: / la / tshig dang sgrar snang ba rang rang gi sha ya rna basa dngos su thos pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10715: lnga pa rdo rje'i gsung grag stong dbyer med /
NK076(mu)002:10716: gdul bya rnams rang rang so sos ji ltar don ga ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10717: 'adul bar snang ba'i 'khor la rdo rje'i gsung rnams /
NK076(mu)002:10718: dper brag gi ngos la sgras rkyen pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:10720: brag gis smra ba med pa ltar /
NK076(mu)002:10721: don grag stong dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung /
NK076(mu)002:10722: ston pas gsungs pa med par 'khor la snang bas na /
NK076(mu)002:10723: dbyer med kyi gsung de yang gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10724: sgra thos par byed pa'ang rdo rje'i gsung de nyid brda 'jal ba'i mthu gzugs snang stong dang /
NK076(mu)002:10725: sgra grag stong du shar ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10726: gsum pa thugs la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:10727: dang po stong pa nyid kyi ye shes bde ba chen po'i thugs /
NK076(mu)002:10728: 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK076(mu)002:10729: phyi nang snod bcud la sogs bye brag gi dbye
NK076(mu)002:10730: ba yan lag dang bcas pa'i chos rnams /
NK076(mu)002:10731: rang rig pa byang chub sems kyi bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:10732: snang ba ma spangs rnam pa kun ldan gyi stong
NK076(mu)002:10733: pa chen po'i don mngon du byas pa'i ye shes
NK076(mu)002:10734: kyis / dngos por snang ba'i zug rngu ma spangs
NK076(mu)002:10735: pas ldan bzhin du rang rgyud du mi dmigs pas
NK076(mu)002:10736: bral bas don de ka bde ba chen po mchog
NK076(mu)002:10738: de yang dper na nam mkha' stong zhing go skabs
NK076(mu)002:10739: 'byed pa lta bur shes bya'i chos thams cad ye
NK076(mu)002:10740: nas sgrib g.yogs med par gsal la ngo bos stong
NK076(mu)002:10741: pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK076(mu)002:10742: gnyis pa me long lta bu'i ye shes rnam par mi rtog /mchog gi don /
NK076(mu)002:10743: chos rnams spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid dbyer med
NK076(mu)002:10744: pa'i chos rnams kun yul dang yul can du rtog
NK076(mu)002:10745: pa med par / dper na me long dwang bar
NK076(mu)002:10746: bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan ji ltar gsal ba bzhin mngon
NK076(mu)002:10747: sum bzhi po kun gyi mchog rang rig pas mngon
NK076(mu)002:10748: sum du rtogs pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:10749: de ka la rnam par mi rtog pa mchog gi thugsa zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:10750: gsum pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes mnyam pa chen po mchog gi thugs /
NK076(mu)002:10751: dper na 'byung ba chen pa lnga gang la bzang
NK076(mu)002:10752: ngan dang yon skyon thams cad mnyam pa lta bur
NK076(mu)002:10753: / 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la tha dad
NK076(mu)002:10754: bzang ngan gyi skyon gang yang mi 'byed cing blang
NK076(mu)002:10755: dara med par mnyam pa nyid kyis mkhyen zhing /
NK076(mu)002:10756: dus thams cad du dgongs pa chos nyid mnyam pa
NK076(mu)002:10757: nyid kyi ngang las dgongs pa mi g.yo ba de
NK076(mu)002:10758: ni mi g.yo ba'i thugs sam /
NK076(mu)002:10759: mnyam pa chen po mchog gi thugsa zhes bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:10760: bzhi pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes 'gro ba sgrol ba ni /
NK076(mu)002:10761: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis su mi 'byed pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10762: thugs rje chen pos 'dul byed kyi ston pa dang
NK076(mu)002:10763: / gdul bya gnyis ngo bo bdag gcig par 'brel pa yod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10764: sangs rgyas de nyid kyi thugs ni mnyam pa nyid
NK076(mu)002:10765: kya dbyings las gdul bya rnams mi gzhan par mkhyen
NK076(mu)002:10766: pa'i phyir lam pa ltar gdul bya'i don bya ba
NK076(mu)002:10767: dang byed pa'i rtsol ba med par phrin las rnam
NK076(mu)002:10768: pa bzhi yis / 'gra ba rnams 'khor ba las
NK076(mu)002:10769: sgrol bar byed pa'i thugs rje chen po dang ldan
NK076(mu)002:10770: pa bzhi yis / pa ni / 'gro ba sgrol ba'i thugs rje yin no //
NK076(mu)002:10771: lnga pa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs /
NK076(mu)002:10772: yul chos nyid spros bral dang /
NK076(mu)002:10773: chos can sems kyi 'dzin pa thams cad kun /
NK076(mu)002:10774: tha dad kyi 'dzin pa dang bral bas /
NK076(mu)002:10775: chos can rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:10776: chos nyid spyi'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:10777: dbyer med dus gcig tu rigs pa la gsal ba'i dpe ni /
NK076(mu)002:10778: dper na nam mkha'a la 'aja'a tshon snang ba ltar
NK076(mu)002:10779: rang spyi gang yang gsal stong dbyer med du ma
NK076(mu)002:10781: gsal stod dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje'i thugsa mchog go //
NK076(mu)002:10782: rgyas par spyi mdo'i le'u sum cu so bzhi par blta bar bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:10783: bzhi pa yon tan la lnga ste /
NK076(mu)002:10784: dang po zhing khams yon tan can /
NK076(mu)002:10785: gnas phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos 'das pa ma lus /
NK076(mu)002:10787: ma 'ongs pa lus pa med pa rnams /
NK076(mu)002:10788: rang rgyud du grub pa med par riga pa rang snang ba nyid kyi phyir /
NK076(mu)002:10789: sems nyid kyi ngo bo yida bzhina nor bu ltar
NK076(mu)002:10790: ji bsam ltar snang ba'i yon tan mang ba ni
NK076(mu)002:10791: sprin phung tsam gyi tshogs kyis phyogsa bcu'i 'jig rten
NK076(mu)002:10792: gyi khams ma lus pa thams cad sangs rgyas kyi
NK076(mu)002:10793: zhing khams rnam par dag par snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10795: 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan thams cad 'bad pa
NK076(mu)002:10796: med par lhun gyis grub cing rdzogs pa'i rig pa
NK076(mu)002:10797: rang snang ba'i rten gzhal yas khang gi gnas kyi
NK076(mu)002:10799: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis
NK076(mu)002:10800: dang bral ba'i rang rig pa nyid la brten pa
NK076(mu)002:10801: lha dang / rten can gzhal yas khang dang gnyis
NK076(mu)002:10802: su med para de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhugs
NK076(mu)002:10803: gnas yin te gnas kyi rang bzhin no //
NK076(mu)002:10805: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa gang yang ma spangs par lhun gyis rdzogsa pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:10806: sna tshogs kyi snang ba ma 'gags pa de ni /
NK076(mu)002:10807: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i rgyan yin no //
NK076(mu)002:10809: sangs rgyas kyi thugs ye shes lnga po nyid kyi
NK076(mu)002:10810: rang bzhin la sgrib pa gsum gyis ma bsgribsa bar
NK076(mu)002:10817: shel lam dngul gyi mdog lta bu drug phyogs bcu 'phro ba drug cu ste /
NK076(mu)002:10818: sna tshogas ba'i 'od zera phyogs bcur 'phro ba'i snang bas khyab cing rang bzhin gsal bar byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10819: lnga pa gdan khri yon tan can /
NK076(mu)002:10824: phrin las bzhi la sogs pa 'bras bu'i chos kun lhun gyis grub cing rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:10825: gdan sems can lnga'i bye brag rang snang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10826: lnga pa phrin las la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10827: dang po gdul bya ngos bzung ba /
NK076(mu)002:10828: gdul bya'i 'gro ba ma lus pa 'dul phyir phrin
NK076(mu)002:10829: las kyi bya ba tha dad pa mang por snang
NK076(mu)002:10831: gdul bya ma zhi ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:10834: tshe bsod nams nyams pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10835: gnyis pa 'dul thabs las bzhi gang 'tshams su don
NK076(mu)002:10836: mdzad cing las bzhi re re'ang bye brag lnga lngar
NK076(mu)002:10838: bzhi yod pa'i phyir 'dul thabs zhi rgyas dbang drag
NK076(mu)002:10839: rnam pa bzhi'i rol ba ste spyod pa rnams gdug
NK076(mu)002:10840: sems zhi ba / ma rung ba bsgral ba /
NK076(mu)002:10841: mos shing dbang du bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:10842: tshe dang bsod nams rgyas par bya'o //
NK076(mu)002:10843: de ltar gang la gang 'tshams pa ltar snang nas gdul bya rnams 'dul bar mdzad de /
NK076(mu)002:10844: phrin las rnam pa bzhi yi bye brag tha dada pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:10845: phrin las bzhi po re re la'ang zhi rgyas dbang
NK076(mu)002:10846: drag lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga ste
NK076(mu)002:10847: / de yang zhi ba'i zhi ba /
NK076(mu)002:10851: zhi ba'i lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las lnga'o //
NK076(mu)002:10852: de'i rigs gzhan bzhi la 'gres pas lnga lnga'i tshul gyis gdul bya'i ngo la snang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:10853: gsum pa 'dul byed rigs lngar snang ba phyogs chad du med par bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:10854: phrin las bzhi pa de la zhi ba'i phrin las de pa'i rigs dang /
NK076(mu)002:10857: drag po rdo rje'i rigs te rigs bzhi yi cha 'dzina par byed pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10858: lnga pa las kyi rigs la phrin las lnga ka lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10859: de ltar rigs rnam pa bzhi yis gdul bya 'dul bar mdzad pa de yang /
NK076(mu)002:10860: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi phyogs kyis gdul bya 'dul
NK076(mu)002:10861: bar byed pa'i cha nas brjod pa yin gyis rigs
NK076(mu)002:10862: phyogs gcig tu chad pa ma yina te /
NK076(mu)002:10863: rigs lnga re res kyang kun 'dul ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10864: gnyis pa 'bras bu thob nas dgongs pa'i gzhugs tshul la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:10865: dang po mthar lam pa las khyad par spags pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10866: 'bras bu drug pa ni theg 'og gi 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:10867: las spags tshul spyir bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:10868: mthar lam man chad de ltar lam gyis rgyud sbyangs pa'i mtha' ma la /
NK076(mu)002:10869: rgyal tshab skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa thob ste sangs rgyas tsan /
NK076(mu)002:10870: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gdul bya'i
NK076(mu)002:10871: snang ngor rigs lnga pa'i cha tsam re 'dzin par
NK076(mu)002:10872: byed kyang / rigs lnga rkyang bkar de dag las
NK076(mu)002:10873: gcig shos te sku lnga lhun grub kyi rgyal ba
NK076(mu)002:10874: byed kyang / drug pa ni / sangs rgyas kun
NK076(mu)002:10875: gyi ngo bo yi spyi gzugs nyid du bzhugs pa'o
NK076(mu)002:10876: byed kyang / drug pa ni / // 'o na
NK076(mu)002:10877: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas su bshad pa ci zhe
NK076(mu)002:10878: byed kyang / drug pa ni / // na / de nyid snga ma 'das pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK076(mu)002:10879: phyi ma ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK076(mu)002:10880: da lta bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas su gsungs pa de
NK076(mu)002:10881: dag gdul bya drang ba yi don ched tsam du
NK076(mu)002:10882: smos pa'o // nges don du sangs rgyas sangs rgyas
NK076(mu)002:10883: zhes brjod pa'i rgyal ba drug pa'i dgongs pa'i bzhugs
NK076(mu)002:10884: tshul ni gcig dang tha dad las grol bas /
NK076(mu)002:10885: tshig tu smra zhing blos bsam pa dang ngag gis brjod pa'i mtha' las 'das par bzhugs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10886: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10888: rang lugs rnam par bzhag pa /
NK076(mu)002:10889: de la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK076(mu)002:10892: de don phyogs gcig tsam brjod par bya ba gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:10893: gdul bya drang pa'i don du snga ma dbu ma dang /
NK076(mu)002:10894: phyi ma phyi rgyud kyi sangs rgyas zhes pa'i don 'di lta ste /
NK076(mu)002:10895: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10896: dang po rgyud gcig par 'dod pa dgag pa /
NK076(mu)002:10897: dbu ma pas don dam gyi bden pa spros bral
NK076(mu)002:10898: stong pa gcig pu mthar phyin nas chos sku thob
NK076(mu)002:10900: de nyid mthar thug gi 'bras bu ma yin pa'i phyir na /
NK076(mu)002:10901: dper na snga ma'i chu la phyi ma'i chu blugs dza gcig tu thim ba ltar /
NK076(mu)002:10902: don dam dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad stong pa rgyu gcig pa kho nar grub pa med pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10903: gnyis pa rgyud tha dad par 'dod pa dgag pa /
NK076(mu)002:10904: dbu ma las dgar ba'i cig shos te /
NK076(mu)002:10905: sems tsam dang sngags phyi rgyud kyi kun rdzob bdena
NK076(mu)002:10906: pa mthar phyin pa'i gzugs sku gcig pur 'bras bur
NK076(mu)002:10907: 'dod na / de nyid ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu ma yin par brjod pas na /
NK076(mu)002:10908: shing gi me dpung bzhin dgongs pa'i rgyud la sbyangs
NK076(mu)002:10909: pa'i ye shes so sa tha dada kyi cha dang
NK076(mu)002:10910: rigsa su grub pa med do //
NK076(mu)002:10911: rigs tha dad las grol ba yin no //
NK076(mu)002:10912: gnyis pa rang lugs la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10913: dang po bden pa gnyis dbyer med la dbang bsgyur ba /
NK076(mu)002:10914: 'dir ma h+aa'i gzhi don bden pa gnyis med rtogs pa'i don la rang dbang du bsgyur ba na /
NK076(mu)002:10915: bdag don chos sku dang gzhan don gzugs sku gnyis kyi bya ba gnyis su med de /
NK076(mu)002:10916: de bas bden gnyis sa sor grub pa med pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:10917: gnyis pa de mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu thob tshul /
NK076(mu)002:10918: gzhi gnyis med kyi don ji bzhin pa der sona pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:10921: stong pa don dam gyi mtha' rnams kyi phyogs su
NK076(mu)002:10922: ma song bas mtha' kun dang brala la gang yang
NK076(mu)002:10923: ma 'gags par snang ba mtha' kun dang ldan par
NK076(mu)002:10924: / ye shes rang gnas nyid zhen pa'i mtha' kun
NK076(mu)002:10925: dang bral bar rang rig pa'i mngon sum du byas
NK076(mu)002:10926: pa la 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa zhen
NK076(mu)002:10927: pa'i ming du brjod kyis sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10928: / ngo bo ni / gcig dang tha dad 'di 'drar gnas pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:10929: zhes smra zhing brjod par dka' 'o //
NK076(mu)002:10930: gsum pa rtsod spang la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10931: dang po bden gnyis tha dad kyi 'bras bu drang
NK076(mu)002:10932: don du bstan pa sems tsam dang sngags phyi rgyud
NK076(mu)002:10933: kyi dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo gcig
NK076(mu)002:10934: pa la sbyangs pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal tha dad
NK076(mu)002:10935: pas rgyud gcig tu 'dres pa min te /
NK076(mu)002:10936: dper na shing ga me dpung gcig la shing so
NK076(mu)002:10937: so'i me tha dad pa ltar du brjod pa ni
NK076(mu)002:10938: / tha dad la mos pa'i gdul bya kun drang
NK076(mu)002:10939: ba tsam du yin ste de nyid don gyi sangs
NK076(mu)002:10940: / rgyas min no // dbu ma pas dus gsum
NK076(mu)002:10941: sangs rgyas rnams chu la chu thim pa ltar du
NK076(mu)002:10942: dgongs rgyud gcig par 'dod pa'ang gong gi don de
NK076(mu)002:10943: / rgyas min no // dang 'dra'o // gnyis pa
NK076(mu)002:10944: bden gnyis lhun grub kyi 'bras bu nges don du
NK076(mu)002:10945: / rgyas min no // dang 'dra'o // bstan pa
NK076(mu)002:10946: / de ltar gcig dang tha dad 'dod pa ni
NK076(mu)002:10948: 'o na nges pa'i don ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:10949: 'dir bden pa gnyis su med par gnas pa'i tshul
NK076(mu)002:10950: gyis gong gi rgyud 'dres ma 'dres phyogs re re
NK076(mu)002:10951: 'dod pa rnams la skyon brjod pa yin pas /
NK076(mu)002:10952: skyon de dag gam gzung 'dzin gnyis su 'dzin pa
NK076(mu)002:10953: ngang gis dag pa'i gnyis med rang byung ye shes
NK076(mu)002:10954: de nyid de bzhen gshegs pa sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK076(mu)002:10956: tan+t+ra ste rgyas pa'i rgyud nyid las grags pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10957: gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa'i zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK076(mu)002:10958: de'i don mngon sum du byas pas gshegs pa ste /
NK076(mu)002:10959: de'ang mtha' gnyis gang la'ang mi gnas par /
NK076(mu)002:10960: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK076(mu)002:10961: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK076(mu)002:10964: mnyam pa chen po pa yi nganga nyid du spyod
NK076(mu)002:10965: yul dang bral bas byon zhes rgyud le'u lag las
NK076(mu)002:10966: gsungs shing tshig tu brjod pa yang /
NK076(mu)002:10967: shes bya'i chos kun don dam dang kun rdzob dbyer
NK076(mu)002:10968: med mnyam pa nyid kyi bden pa gsum pa yin
NK076(mu)002:10969: pa'i phyir yang dag ngesa par na rgyal ba rnams
NK076(mu)002:10970: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid yin te rgyud 'dres te
