NK076(mu)002:10971: gcig pa dang / ma 'dres te tha dad pa'i tha snyad dang bral ba'i tshul du gnas pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:10972: gsum pa 'bras bu'i khyad par la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10973: dang po ming grangs kyi khyad par du dbye na bsam yas pa /
NK076(mu)002:10974: gsang ba'i theg pa thun mong min pa'i sku lnga
NK076(mu)002:10975: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa de'i minga
NK076(mu)002:10977: gong ltar bde bar gshegs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:10980: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK076(mu)002:10981: dgyes pa chen po zhes brjod pa la sogs ming gi rnam grangs mtha' yas pa zhig yod kyang /
NK076(mu)002:10982: gnyis pa 'dir bsdus te bstan pa la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:10985: ngo bo tshul grangs khyad par gsum yod pa'i grangs kyis phye bas ngo bo'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:10987: ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par tsam zhig brjod na /
NK076(mu)002:10988: 'dir mdo ru bsdus te brjod pa'i theg pa so
NK076(mu)002:10989: so'i 'bras bu'i khyad par gyi don khong du chub
NK076(mu)002:10991: gnyis pa rgyas pa de la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:10992: dang po 'bras bu'i ngo bo'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:10993: ma h+aa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo ni sku gsung thugs
NK076(mu)002:10994: yon tan phrin las lnga dang de re re la'ang
NK076(mu)002:10995: lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lngar lhun gyis grub
NK076(mu)002:10997: 'og ma dbu ma kri yog gis rgyal ba sku
NK076(mu)002:10998: gsum rdzogsa par 'dod pas so so yi grub pa'i
NK076(mu)002:10999: mtha' rang sa yi sangs rgyas dang ma h+aa'i sangs
NK076(mu)002:11000: rgyas gnyis la / grangsa rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad
NK076(mu)002:11001: par dbu ma pas kun tu 'od chos sku gcig
NK076(mu)002:11002: rgyas gnyis la / bu dang / kri yas rigs gsum dang /
NK076(mu)002:11004: ma h+aas ni nyer lnga lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11005: ngo ba 'dus ma byas ma byas kyi khyad par ni gzugs sku ste /
NK076(mu)002:11006: dbu ma pas gzugs sku gdul bya'i ngor snang tsam du 'dod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11008: yo gas rnam snang brgya byin lha'i bla ma yang skye 'jig yod pas 'dus byas yin /
NK076(mu)002:11009: ma h+aa'i drug pa spyi gzugs can ni 'dus ma byas kyi gzugs sku'o //
NK076(mu)002:11010: byin rlabs las mngon du snang ba dang mi snang ba'i khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)002:11011: gsum pos ni rang sa rang sa'i 'bras bu'i sa las mi drong la /
NK076(mu)002:11012: ma h+aas ni yi ge 'khor lo'i sar drong bar snang ngo //
NK076(mu)002:11013: don byed rgya che chung ga khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:11014: dbu mas nyan rang man chad /
NK076(mu)002:11015: kri yas dbu ma man chad /
NK076(mu)002:11016: yo gas u pa man chad /
NK076(mu)002:11017: ma h+aas yo ga man chad la lugs 'byung ldog gi sgo nas don byed pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11018: de ltar khyad par bzhi las spags pa'i don gyis na /
NK076(mu)002:11019: 'bras bu rang gi ngo ba nyid kyis khyad par yod pa gsal lo //
NK076(mu)002:11020: gnyis pa 'bras bu thob nas dgongs rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul gyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:11021: sangs rgyas de dag gi dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:11024: yo ga ma h+aa dang rang sa bzhi'i rgyal ba kun tu 'od /
NK076(mu)002:11027: sku lnga lhun grub dang bzhi po de dag gi khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)002:11028: dbu mas rgyud gcig tu 'dres par 'dod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11029: phyi rgyud kyis de las grol te tha dad par smra ba rnams /
NK076(mu)002:11030: ma h+aa'i sa 'dir drang ba'i thabs tsam du bstan
NK076(mu)002:11031: pa yin la ma h+aa ni gong du bshad pa
NK076(mu)002:11033: de bas na dgongs pa rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul gyi
NK076(mu)002:11034: khyad par ni blos bsam pa'i tshad las 'das pa'o
NK076(mu)002:11035: // gsum pa 'bras bu'i ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par la bzhi ste /
NK076(mu)002:11036: bde gshegs de bzhin gshegs pa'i khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:11037: rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das kyi khyad par gtan tshigs dang bcas pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11038: dgyes pa longs spyod kyi khyad par dang /
NK076(mu)002:11039: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu'i khyad par ro //
NK076(mu)002:11041: thun mong gi theg pa'i bde gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11042: de las ma h+aa'i bde gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs pas spags pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11044: grol lam gyi bde gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs tshul dang /
NK076(mu)002:11045: thabs lam gyi khyad par dang /
NK076(mu)002:11046: sh+aakya thub pa gshegs tshul lo //
NK076(mu)002:11048: dang po byang chub sems pa'i gshegs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:11049: 'bras bu'i ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par ni nyan rang la ltos na theg chen /
NK076(mu)002:11050: gsang sngags la ltos na lta spyod dman pa byang
NK076(mu)002:11051: chub sems dpa'i theg pa bas rgyu thun mong gi
NK076(mu)002:11052: tshogs gnyis bsags pa'i stobs kyis 'bras bu kun tu
NK076(mu)002:11053: 'od kyis sa la bde bar gshegs shinga /
NK076(mu)002:11054: don dam pa skye ba med par 'bras bu chos
NK076(mu)002:11055: nyid stong pa de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gshegs
NK076(mu)002:11056: pa de yang / dus bskal pa grangs med gsum
NK076(mu)002:11057: gyi dbang du lam bgrod pa'i phyir du dus der
NK076(mu)002:11058: snga ma bzhin du thun mong gi tshogs gnyis bsags
NK076(mu)002:11059: pa la brten nas gnas lugs chos nyid kyi de
NK076(mu)002:11060: bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gshegs pa nyid dang /
NK076(mu)002:11061: gnyis pa bya ba'i lugs kyi gshegs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:11062: gsang sngags phyi rgyud kyi theg pa la'ang /
NK076(mu)002:11063: khrus dang gtsang sbra'i bya ba byed pa kri ya'i lugs kyis shes rab lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11064: 'bras bu 'grub pa'i yan lag cha ga'i dkyil 'khor
NK076(mu)002:11065: bcu gcig gi lha bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor ting 'dzin
NK076(mu)002:11066: gsal zhing / sngags bzlas pa'i grangs rdzogsa par byas pas /
NK076(mu)002:11067: de yang 'bras bu rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK076(mu)002:11068: ye nas sangs rgyas pa de la lam du byas
NK076(mu)002:11069: pas dgongs pa bde bar gshegsa pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:11070: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sar rang sems dag
NK076(mu)002:11071: pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma dang bral ba'i de bzhin
NK076(mu)002:11072: nyid mngon du gyur pas gshegsa pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11073: gnyis pa thabs lam gyi gshegs tshul la gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:11074: dang po mtshan nyid lugs kyi gshegs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:11075: grol lam du gshegs pa las dgar bas yang na thabs lam dbang gis gshegs pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:11076: dbang gnas gang du bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11077: spyi'i gnas rgya gar gyi yul bya rgod phung po'i
NK076(mu)002:11078: ri 'dabs logs kyi bye brag tu bsod nams dang
NK076(mu)002:11079: las skal ldan pa'i gnas dgon phug bye ma 'dabs
NK076(mu)002:11080: sna zhes bya ba de ru bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11082: dgra bcom stong dang lnga brgya 'dus nas bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11084: dge slong 'di ni bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal mthong gi 'khor te zhes bden pa'i tshig gis bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11085: gang la bskur na bram ze la bza' rgan mo'i
NK076(mu)002:11086: bu dge slong sa ri zhes bya ba la bskur
NK076(mu)002:11087: / dgos ched ci'i phyir bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11088: rgyal tshab tu dbyung ba'i phyir bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11089: tshig dang yi ge la brten nas dbang bskur ji bzhin nama /
NK076(mu)002:11090: zhes dge slong sa ri la dbang bskur dgra bcom thob pa ci bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:11091: da lta lam pa la yang dbang bskur pas sangs rgyas so //
NK076(mu)002:11092: gnyis pa kri ya'i lugs kyi gshegs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:11094: spyi'i gnas w+aa ra na si'i bye brag sme khrod
NK076(mu)002:11095: brtsegs pa mi gtsang ba'i dri ma med cing bsil
NK076(mu)002:11098: dam pa'i rigas cana zhes kri ya'i rnal 'byor si r+au pra ta ba /
NK076(mu)002:11099: bram ze khyim bdag /ku ku r+aa tsa gsum la dbang bskur nas /
NK076(mu)002:11101: gtsang ma phyag na rdo rjes bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11102: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11103: rdo rje rgya gram la sogs pa lha'i mngon rtags brgyad dam dgus bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11104: dgos ched ci'i phyir bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11105: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la dgod pa'i
NK076(mu)002:11106: ched du dbang bskur nas 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo
NK076(mu)002:11107: rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob pa'i tshul ji bazhana du
NK076(mu)002:11108: rjes 'jug rnams kyang de bzhin du mthun no //
NK076(mu)002:11109: gsum pa sh+aaka thub gshegs tshul la gnyis te /
NK076(mu)002:11110: dang po theg pa gsum gyis 'dod pa'i thub pa gshegs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:11111: sngon byung du sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang pa yang /
NK076(mu)002:11112: gong gi thun mong gi lam gyi gshegs tshul de ji lta ba bzhin du kun tu 'od /
NK076(mu)002:11114: rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs pa'am /
NK076(mu)002:11116: bya ba kri ya'i rgyud dang /
NK076(mu)002:11117: gnyis ka spyod pa u pa ya'i rgyud la sogs
NK076(mu)002:11118: par rang rang so so'i gzhung las ji ltar grags
NK076(mu)002:11119: pa bzhin du gshegs pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:11120: gnyis pa yo ga'i gzhung ltar gshegs tshul /
NK076(mu)002:11121: rnam 'byor yo ga'i gzhung gi dbang gang la bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11122: rgyal bu don grub de nyid la /
NK076(mu)002:11124: chu bo nee r+aa ny+dza na'i 'gram logs su bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11125: dus nam gyi tshe bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11128: 'bras nyag ma re re gsol ba'i dka' thub kyis dka' ba spyod pa'i tsha bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11130: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sprul pa sku'i rnam pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11131: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rigs lnga'i skus bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11132: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11133: rin chen sna bdun la brten nas bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11139: sku yongs rdzogs dang mngon par byang chub pa dang rnam pa lnga'i stobs kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK076(mu)002:11140: dgos chad ni 'di ltar du snang ba 'og min
NK076(mu)002:11141: stug po bkod pa'i gnas nyid du rang gzhan gyi
NK076(mu)002:11142: don grub de / de'i sgra don grub pa'i tshul ni /
NK076(mu)002:11143: sprul pa'i lus kyis dka' thub mdzad pa'i khog pa nas /
NK076(mu)002:11144: sems nyid ye shes lngar rtogs pa'i rang gzugs la
NK076(mu)002:11145: longs sku rnam par snang mdzad kyi lugs su gshegs
NK076(mu)002:11147: ri rab kyi rtse mo rin po che'i khang bzang
NK076(mu)002:11148: brtsegs par yo ga dum bu bzhi pa'i chos kyi
NK076(mu)002:11149: 'khor losa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la bskor
NK076(mu)002:11151: de yang ma h+aa la ltos na 'khor gyi rtog pa'i gzugsa sku yin no //
NK076(mu)002:11152: gnyis pa ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid gshegs lugs spags pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:11153: dang po thabs lam dang grol lam gnyis med kyi sgo nas gshegs lugs kyi spags pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:11154: ma h+aa rang gi bde gshegs de bzhin nyid du gshegs lugs gang zhe na /
NK076(mu)002:11155: thabs lam dang shes rab grol lam gnyis med mnyam
NK076(mu)002:11156: pa nyid kyi don nyams su blangs pa'i sgo nas
NK076(mu)002:11157: snying po byang chub kyis 'gro 'ong gi rtog pa
NK076(mu)002:11158: meda par bde bar gshegs te /
NK076(mu)002:11159: gzhi gnas lugs ci bzhin pa 'khor 'das lhun grub
NK076(mu)002:11160: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang nas nar son pa yis
NK076(mu)002:11161: gshegs pa ste / 'og ma'i bde gshegs de bzhin
NK076(mu)002:11162: gshegs pa bas dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul dang ngo bos
NK076(mu)002:11163: dang rnam grangs kyi khyad par dang gsum gyis cha
NK076(mu)002:11164: gshegs pa ste / ba'o // gnyis pa sh+aaka thub gshegs lugs spags so //
NK076(mu)002:11165: deng dbang gang du bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11166: chu bo nee r+aany+dza na'i 'gram du /
NK076(mu)002:11167: gang la bskur na rgyal bu don grub dka' thub kyi lus cana de la /
NK076(mu)002:11169: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad dbyar gyi sprin phung bzhin du 'dus pa yi cha lugs ni /
NK076(mu)002:11170: gsang ba'i ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rnams kyis bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11171: dus nam gyi tshe na srod la rtog pa nub pa'i tshe gsang dbang dang /
NK076(mu)002:11172: tho rangs ye shes skye ba'i dus nyid du shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur /
NK076(mu)002:11173: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK076(mu)002:11174: ston pa yab yum gyi nyi zla byang sems lce
NK076(mu)002:11175: thog tu bzhag pa khara bza' ba'i dbang rdzas byin
NK076(mu)002:11178: mchan /ra ste sbyor thabs kyi bstan chos bstan te sbyor du bcug pa yis /
NK076(mu)002:11179: thig le lugs su song ba'i yas bab kyi dga'
NK076(mu)002:11180: ba bzhi la shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang
NK076(mu)002:11181: / thig le de nyid lugs su zlog pa mas
NK076(mu)002:11182: brtan gyi dga' ba bzhi la shin tu brtan pa
NK076(mu)002:11183: bde ba chen po rdzogs pa'i dbang thob pasa gzhi
NK076(mu)002:11184: don ji lta ba de bzhin du 'bras bu mngon
NK076(mu)002:11186: rjes 'jug rnams kyang de bzhin du gshegs pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11187: gsum pa des ni theg pa 'og ma las spags tshul gtan tshigs dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:11188: gshegs lugs la khyad par yod pa de yi phyir
NK076(mu)002:11189: thun mong gi theg pa byang sems kri yog rnam
NK076(mu)002:11190: pa gsum dang ma h+aa dang bzhi las /
NK076(mu)002:11191: byang ba bzhi yi khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)002:11192: rgyu'i theg pa bcu gcig kun du 'od kyi sa mngon du byas tsam na /
NK076(mu)002:11193: rnam par mi rtog pa'i rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11194: shes bya sa bcu'i sgrib pa thams cad byang ba /
NK076(mu)002:11195: kri yas rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11196: rigs gsum stobs su byas pa'i rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis /
NK076(mu)002:11197: nyon shes kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11198: bcu gcig kun tu 'od man chad kyi sgrib pa byang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:11199: yo gas stug po bkod pa'i sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11200: mtshan bcas dang mtshan ma med pa rdo rje lta
NK076(mu)002:11201: bu'i ting 'dzin gyis nyon shes kyi sgrib pa dang
NK076(mu)002:11202: / u pa man chad kyi lta sgrib byang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:11203: ma h+aa yo gas pad+ma spyan gyi sa mngon du byas tsam na /
NK076(mu)002:11205: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis /
NK076(mu)002:11206: nyon shes kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11207: yo ga man chad kyi lta sgrib byang ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:11208: chub pa bzhi ni rgyu'i kun tu 'od sku gsum gyi ngo bor chub /
NK076(mu)002:11209: kri ya rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa rigs gsum gyi ngo bor chub /
NK076(mu)002:11210: yo ga rigs lnga'i ngo bor chub /
NK076(mu)002:11211: ma h+aa yo ga sku lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor chub pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11212: bde bar gshegs pa bzhi ni /
NK076(mu)002:11213: rgyu'i theg pas bcu gcig kun du 'od kyi sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11214: sa bcu pa man chad kyi nyon mongs rnam rtog gi zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK076(mu)002:11215: bdag gzhan gyi don gyi phyir gshegs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11216: kri yas rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11217: kun tu 'od man chad kyi nyon mongs rnam rtog zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK076(mu)002:11218: bdag gzhan gyi don phyir gshegs pa /
NK076(mu)002:11219: yo gas stug po bkod pa'i sa mngon du byas tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11220: kri ya man chad kyi nyon mongs rnam rtog gi zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK076(mu)002:11221: bdag gzhan gyi don phyir gshegs pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11222: ma h+aa yo gas pad+ma spyan gyis mngon du byas tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11223: yo ga man chad kyi nyon mongs dang rnam rtog gi zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK076(mu)002:11224: bdag gzhan gyi don phyir gshegs pa /
NK076(mu)002:11225: de bzhin gshegas pa bzhi'i khyad par ni /
NK076(mu)002:11226: dbu mas don dam pa'i bden pa stong zhing spros pa dang bral ba de bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:11227: de'i don nar son pas gshegs /
NK076(mu)002:11228: kri yas sems dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba de bzhin /
NK076(mu)002:11229: yo gas chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba de bzhin /
NK076(mu)002:11230: ma h+aa yo gas snang ba dang stong pa gnyis su med pas de bzhin /
NK076(mu)002:11231: de dag gi don nar son pas gshegs pa dang brgyad do //
NK076(mu)002:11235: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen sku gsung thugs yon
NK076(mu)002:11236: tan phrin las nyer lnga'i grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi
NK076(mu)002:11237: khyad par dang / 'bras bu'i nga bo gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:11238: byin rlabs dang rtsal la sogs pa'i yon tan gyis khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11239: gnyis pa rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das kyi khyad par gtan tshigs dang bcas pa /
NK076(mu)002:11240: des na theg pa so so'i rgyal ba dang bcom ldan 'das la yang /
NK076(mu)002:11241: theg pa thun mong gi dang /
NK076(mu)002:11242: mchog ma h+aa'i bcom ldan 'das dang lugsa gnyis ni snga ma bzhina du yod pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:11243: de dag gi don rgyas par bshad na theg pa
NK076(mu)002:11244: bzhi so so'i lam thabs dang shes rab grol lam
NK076(mu)002:11245: gnyis kyis rgyu'i theg pa'i kun tu 'od kyi skabs
NK076(mu)002:11246: su rnam par mi rtog pa stobs su byas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:11247: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin dang /
NK076(mu)002:11248: kri yas rigs gsum stobs su gyur pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11249: yo gas mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi stobs dang /
NK076(mu)002:11250: ma h+aa yo gas dbyer med stobs su byas pa'i
NK076(mu)002:11251: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin bzhi rgyud la bskyed
NK076(mu)002:11255: lha'i bu'i bdud dang bzhi ngasa par bcom zhing rang rang gi 'bras bu'i yon tan dang ldan te /
NK076(mu)002:11256: rang rang gi sdug bsngal gyi mya ngan bzhi las
NK076(mu)002:11257: 'das shing yod med rtag chad kyi mtha' bzhi las
NK076(mu)002:11258: 'das pa dang / de ltar theg pa gong 'og mi mthun pa tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:11259: rang rang gi gzhung ga rang rang gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa de yang /
NK076(mu)002:11260: theg pa de dag rang rang gi rtog pa'i lta ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:11261: rjes mthun gyi spyod pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11262: nyams len ting 'dzin gyi lam rnams la gong 'og gi rima pa'am khyad par yod pa bzhin du /
NK076(mu)002:11263: mthar thug grub pa'i mtha' 'bras bu sangs rgyas rnams
NK076(mu)002:11264: la yang rim pa bzhin du khyad para yoda pa
NK076(mu)002:11265: ste / de'i rgyu mtshan lta ba'i mtho dman gyi
NK076(mu)002:11266: chas 'og mas gong ma'i don la sgrib pas na
NK076(mu)002:11267: khyad par phye ba yin no //
NK076(mu)002:11268: gsum pa dgyes pa longs spyod kyi khyad par /
NK076(mu)002:11269: de ltar theg pa so so'i bcom ldan 'das la khyad par yod pa des na /
NK076(mu)002:11270: dgyes pa chen po la yang khyad par yod pa yin te /
NK076(mu)002:11271: dgyes pa'i longs spyod chen po'i khyad par kyang /
NK076(mu)002:11272: mdo sde ste rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11274: rnal 'byora rgyud kyi yo ga gnyis kyi rgyud gzhung
NK076(mu)002:11275: so so las ji ltar grags pa bzhin du longs
NK076(mu)002:11277: gong gi ma h+aa'i dgyes pa chen po ni 'og ma'i yid tshoda du gyur pa min no //
NK076(mu)002:11278: bzhi pa 'bras bu'i khyad par la bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:11279: dang po sangs rgyas pa'i khyad par bstan pa dngos /
NK076(mu)002:11280: snga ma'i gtan tshigs de yi phyir theg pa gong
NK076(mu)002:11281: 'og gi dgyes pa'i rim pa che chung yod pas
NK076(mu)002:11282: / theg pa so so'i rang sa yi 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:11283: sangs rgyas rnams la khyad par gyi rim pa yod
NK076(mu)002:11284: / pa'i phyir na / ming gi rnam grangs sam
NK076(mu)002:11285: yon tan gyi cha shas tsam gyis khyad par phye
NK076(mu)002:11286: / pa'i phyir na / ba min te / theg
NK076(mu)002:11287: pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu ngo bo nyid kyis
NK076(mu)002:11289: 'og ma'i 'bras bu bas ma h+aa'i 'bras bu rnam par 'phags pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11290: gnyis pa thun mong gi sa gsum drang don du bstan pa'i dgos ched /
NK076(mu)002:11291: de yang theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu bshad pa la dgos ched ci yod ce na /
NK076(mu)002:11292: theg pa 'og ma so so'i lam gya rtsol bas shes rgyud ngal ba rnams /
NK076(mu)002:11293: 'bras bu la blo brod pa bskyed pa'i phyir byang sems la kun tu 'od kyi sa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11294: kri ya la rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11295: yo ga la stug po bkod pa zhes par bstan pa yin la /
NK076(mu)002:11296: gsum pa mtha' thug gi sa gsum yon tan gyi cha las btags pa /
NK076(mu)002:11297: theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu'i mthar thug ma h+aa'i 'bras bu'i su ni pad+ma spyan dang /
NK076(mu)002:11298: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen dang /
NK076(mu)002:11299: ye shes bla ma'i sa dang gsum bzang ngan dang mtho dman khyad par med de /
NK076(mu)002:11300: yon tan gyi cha las brjod do //
NK076(mu)002:11301: bzhi pa gong 'og gi rim pa dpe'i sgo nas bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:11302: theg pa la khyad par yod pa de yi phyir
NK076(mu)002:11303: theg pa gong 'og gi so so'i 'bras bu'i khyad
NK076(mu)002:11304: par skas kyi gdang bu lta bura mtho dman yod
NK076(mu)002:11305: pa ste / de yang gdul bya 'dren pa'i thabs
NK076(mu)002:11306: la mkhas pa nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i theg
NK076(mu)002:11307: pa 'di yis mthar thug gi 'bras bu dngos su
NK076(mu)002:11308: 'thob par byed pa 'di la dngos su 'jug ma
NK076(mu)002:11309: nus pa rnams thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa
NK076(mu)002:11310: las gzhan pa yi thun mong lam stegs kyi theg
NK076(mu)002:11311: pa'i thabs la brten nas gang mos su 'jug bcuga
NK076(mu)002:11312: pa ste / cing / de nas theg pa 'og
NK076(mu)002:11313: ma nas gong ma nyid du 'du shes bsgyur nas
NK076(mu)002:11314: mthar thug ma h+aa yo ga 'di yis 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:11316: thun mong gi theg pa rang gi lam gyi thabs
NK076(mu)002:11317: sna tshogs kyisa theg pa rang sa yi 'bras bu
NK076(mu)002:11318: thaba pa las / theg 'og thun mong dang mchog
NK076(mu)002:11319: gi theg pa'i 'bras bu gnyis ngo bo nyid gcig
NK076(mu)002:11320: cing khyad par med par smra ba yi gang zag
NK076(mu)002:11321: thaba pa las / rnams ni / ma h+aa' don
NK076(mu)002:11322: ma mthong ba'i mun sprul gyi blo can yin pa'o
NK076(mu)002:11323: thaba pa las / rnams ni / // theg pa
NK076(mu)002:11324: gong 'og gi 'bras bu la khyad par yod pa'i
NK076(mu)002:11325: thaba pa las / rnams ni / // rgyu mtshan
NK076(mu)002:11326: ni / gsang sngags bla med kyi gzhung zab mo
NK076(mu)002:11328: de nyid kyi dgongs pa'i bcud phyung pa'i man ngag gi bdag po /
NK076(mu)002:11329: rgya gar gyi mkhas grub chen po in+t+ra b+ho d+hi /
NK076(mu)002:11334: sgeg pa rdo rje la sogs pa'i rgya gzhung thams cad nas gsungs la /
NK076(mu)002:11335: bod kyi so zur gnubs gsum /
NK076(mu)002:11336: rong klong yab sras la sogs pas dgongs pa mthun par gsungs so //
NK076(mu)002:11337: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa /
NK076(mu)002:11338: mtshan nyid gsum mam lam lnga'i gzhi'i don ji lta
NK076(mu)002:11339: ba mthar phyin pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs
NK076(mu)002:11340: rgyas kyi sa'i rnam bzhag bstan pa'i gzhung don mtshams
NK076(mu)002:11341: dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK076(mu)002:11342: tshig don gyis na le'u zhes bya ba ste /
NK076(mu)002:11343: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK076(mu)002:11344: yas bgrangs dgu pa'i don du gda' 'o ////spyi don gsum pa 'jug gi don la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:11345: brtsams pa'i dge ba 'gro ba yongs la bsngo ba /
NK076(mu)002:11346: snod ngan dang ma 'phrad par smon lam btab pa /
NK076(mu)002:11347: brtsams pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK076(mu)002:11349: dang po gang phyir brtsams pa /
NK076(mu)002:11350: 'gro ba lam lag pa ni mu stegs yin la de' nga rtag lta bzhi /
NK076(mu)002:11355: chad lta rgyang 'phen pa dang lnga yin /
NK076(mu)002:11356: lam stor ba lha mi gnyis /
NK076(mu)002:11357: ngan song gsum ste lnga dang lnga tshan gnyis po'i sems can rnams /
NK076(mu)002:11360: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sa la bkra ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir /
NK076(mu)002:11361: gnyis pa gang brtsams pa'i ngo bo 'khor 'das tha
NK076(mu)002:11362: dad du mi gnyis te gnyis su med par ston
NK076(mu)002:11365: rdzogs pa'i lam mchog rnam par bkod pa 'di ni sangs rgyas gsang ba bdag gis bgyisa pa'i /
NK076(mu)002:11366: gsum pa de ltar brtsams pa'i dge ba /
NK076(mu)002:11367: sgo gsum ngal ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba gang yin
NK076(mu)002:11368: pa des 'gro ba sems can kun kyang yang dag
NK076(mu)002:11369: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sar grol bar shog
NK076(mu)002:11370: cig ces bsngo ba yin no //
NK076(mu)002:11371: gnyis pa snod ngan dang ma 'phrad par smon lam btab pa la gsum /
NK076(mu)002:11372: dang po snod ngan gyi mtshan nyid /
NK076(mu)002:11373: bla na med pa byang chub gtso bor mi gnyer
NK076(mu)002:11374: bar kha na ma tho ba zhor tsam la byed
NK076(mu)002:11375: cing 'jig rten tshe 'di'i khe dang grags pa ched
NK076(mu)002:11377: gsang sngags kyi bcud chen po'i man ngag lta stom
NK076(mu)002:11378: gsang mi thub nas snod med rnams la 'dzag canga
NK076(mu)002:11379: / man ngag zab mo gzhan la gzhogs ngoma can gyi gang zag dang /
NK076(mu)002:11380: gnyis pa snod ngan gyi dpe /
NK076(mu)002:11381: sngon rgyal bu mu tig 'bebs zhes bya ba gad mo bzhad tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11382: kha nas mu tig mang po sha ra ra skyugs pa zhig yod pa /
NK076(mu)002:11383: rgyal po stobs bzang zhes bya ba zhig yod pas /
NK076(mu)002:11384: mu tig 'dod pa'i ched du rgyal bu bos nas
NK076(mu)002:11385: snang g.yel che ba zhig tu bzhag nas gad mo
NK076(mu)002:11386: bsgug pas / rgyal po de'i btsun mo gtsug rgyal
NK076(mu)002:11387: sgeg mo zhes bya ba gcig 'khor rnams kyis rin
NK076(mu)002:11388: po che'i khri la bzhag ste /
NK076(mu)002:11389: rgyal pos rin po che'i sor gdub chung ngu brgyab pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11390: 'khor rnams kyis me tog phog tsam na a na na zer zhing ngu /
NK076(mu)002:11391: bram ze lkog nag ces bya ba zhig dang dus
NK076(mu)002:11392: btab byas shing dus bcag pa las khos ber rgas
NK076(mu)002:11393: brdung tsa na / he he zer ba zhig mthong ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:11394: 'jag skyil ste bram ze'i drang srong me len spur skyel zhes bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:11395: de'i mchod gnas shig 'dug pa des /
NK076(mu)002:11396: ngas ma sbyin pa len pa spang ba yin zer zhing gzhan la me bslang tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11397: chos gos la rdul 'byang ba ba skyal du 'ong /
NK076(mu)002:11398: phags su nor thob tshad rku ba zhig yod pas /
NK076(mu)002:11399: mgar ba'i khyim na gser gyi sgrom bu zhig yod
NK076(mu)002:11400: pa mthong nas mkhar gsil gyi gsham du gar sbyin
NK076(mu)002:11401: bskus nas / mgar ba'i khyim gyi gser gyi sgrom bu la mkhar gsil mi tshor bar btsugs te /
NK076(mu)002:11402: sga sgar med par gser brkus pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11404: ne tsho kha na gshog pa'i sgro bcug nas chu 'thung zhing 'dug pa mthong ba las /
NK076(mu)002:11406: chu la srog chags 'dug pa shi yis dogs pa yin zer /
NK076(mu)002:11407: mi mi 'dug tshe na srog chags mthong tshad btu zhing za ba mthong /
NK076(mu)002:11409: khro mo ku ma ra'i a ma yin te /
NK076(mu)002:11410: mo khyo la ma dga' nas /
NK076(mu)002:11411: ngas skyes pa pho dang reg pa spangs pa yin zer zhing /
NK076(mu)002:11412: bu la nu ma blud tsa na /
NK076(mu)002:11413: gos la bug pa phug nas blug /phags su skyes
NK076(mu)002:11414: pa pho dang 'khrig pa spyod pa log g.yem gsog
NK076(mu)002:11415: pa mthong ngo // de sogs kyis dgod bro ba ma byung /
NK076(mu)002:11416: yi mug pa zhig byung gsung /
NK076(mu)002:11417: ji ltar yi mug gsungs pas /
NK076(mu)002:11418: rgyal bus de'i don tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
NK076(mu)002:11419: rgyal mo me tog 'thor bshum dang /
NK076(mu)002:11420: drang srong me len spur bskyal dang /
NK076(mu)002:11421: ne tso kha nas gshog thogs dang /
NK076(mu)002:11422: ku ma ra yi a ma sogs /
NK076(mu)002:11423: mi dge bcu la 'chol nyog spyod /
NK076(mu)002:11424: mu tig 'bebs las ma gtogs pa /
NK076(mu)002:11425: bden par smra ba ngas ma mthong /
NK076(mu)002:11426: ha ha nga ni dgod re bro /
NK076(mu)002:11428: mu tig 'khyor ba gang tsam lhur gyis byung skad do //
NK076(mu)002:11429: gsum pa snod ngan gyi dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:11430: de lta bu'i gang zag gis /
NK076(mu)002:11431: dam tshig dang sdom pa rnams tshul 'chos tsam du
NK076(mu)002:11432: bsrung bar byed cing yang dag pa'i dam tshig la
NK076(mu)002:11434: gsang ba'i gzhung zab mo'i don nyams su blang ba
NK076(mu)002:11435: la shes rab gsum gyis bsran mi tshugsa shing brtson
NK076(mu)002:11437: gzhung dang man ngag sna mang du grub cing don
NK076(mu)002:11438: du gnyer bar byed pa la de dag gang la
NK076(mu)002:11439: yang yid ches par dka' ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:11440: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon nyid spyi bos gus par mi len cing bkur sti chung ba dang /
NK076(mu)002:11441: bla ma dang mched lca ma la zhe nas skur pa 'debs shing /
NK076(mu)002:11442: rnal 'byor pa dang sems can yongs la'ang skur pa
NK076(mu)002:11443: 'debs shing gnod par byed pa'i gang zag de lta
NK076(mu)002:11444: bu snod min pa rnams dang /
NK076(mu)002:11445: man ngag zab mo 'di dang ma 'phrad par gyur cig /ces gsungs pa yin no //
NK076(mu)002:11446: gsum pa brtsams pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK076(mu)002:11447: chos 'di bsgyur ba spyi'i gnas ni mang yula /
NK076(mu)002:11448: bye brag tu khri babs zhes bya ba'i gnas su /
NK076(mu)002:11449: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku
NK076(mu)002:11450: m+aa ra ste ye shes gzhon nu zhes bya bas
NK076(mu)002:11453: bye brag tu brjod bya'i gtso bo ni /
NK076(mu)002:11454: lam rgyas par ston pas lam rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba /
NK076(mu)002:11455: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob
NK076(mu)002:11456: dpon mkhas pa chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad
NK076(mu)002:11457: pa tshegs chung la don che ba'i man ngag /rdzogs
NK076(mu)002:11458: so zhes pas tshig don ma lus pa'i tha tshig
NK076(mu)002:11459: gam / gnas skabs re zhig bshad du ma mchis nas rdzogs so //
NK076(mu)002:11460: rigs kun spyi dpal rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:11461: mkhas grub chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba nas //
NK076(mu)002:11462: ring brgyud zam ma chad pa'i bka' lung thob //
NK076(mu)002:11463: 'di tsam ma yin tshe rabs du ma ru //
NK076(mu)002:11464: gsang chen chos la bzang 'brel bag chags bzhag /rig 'dzin smon lam gtad rgya'i mthu byin gyis /
NK076(mu)002:11465: khams dbus mkhas grub du ma'i 'grel pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:11466: mchan dang bsdus don spyi bshad bcu phrag brgal //
NK076(mu)002:11467: 'jal ba'i skal pa bzang pos lam 'di la //
NK076(mu)002:11468: 'bru 'brel nyung bsdus bkod 'dir sdang zhen gyis //
NK076(mu)002:11469: mthong ma thag tu snga rgol ma bzhag par //
NK076(mu)002:11470: tshig don dpyod dang las skal ldan rnams kyi //
NK076(mu)002:11471: dam pa'i gsung las rang bzos dben snyam yang //
NK076(mu)002:11472: kho bo skyes spyangs shes rab blo dman pas //
NK076(mu)002:11473: gzhung dang tshig don mthun min rang skyon nges //
NK076(mu)002:11474: snying nas bshags so dag tshangs dngos grub stsol //
NK076(mu)002:11475: ye nas snod bcud dag mnyam rang bzhin gyi //
NK076(mu)002:11476: gsang chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK076(mu)002:11477: 'bras chos mngon gyur mkha' khyab sems can kun //
NK076(mu)002:11478: gdod ma'i mgon po'i go 'phang thob phyir bsngo //
NK076(mu)002:11479: zhes pa'ang sgyu 'phrul stong phrag brgya pa'i bcud bsdus lam mchog 'di la /
NK076(mu)002:11480: sngar nas rang 'dra'i blo dman gyis go bde ba'i tshig 'grel zhig bri bdun yod pas /
NK076(mu)002:11481: nye char mkhas btsun bzang po'i yon tan mchog mnga' mkhan las rab rdo rje'i yang srid /
NK076(mu)002:11482: pad+ma kun grol bzang pos legs pa'i rten 'brel bzang po'i gnang skyes bcas nan bskul mdzad pa dang /
NK076(mu)002:11483: gzhan dam pa du mas bskul ngor rang gis chos
NK076(mu)002:11484: la 'brel pa tsam zhog phyir bkra shis khrom gyi
NK076(mu)002:11485: ljongs yul gyi dge bcu tshang zhing zab gsang snying
NK076(mu)002:11486: po'i bstan pa 'phela ba'i gling nas /
NK076(mu)002:11487: 70rdo rje snying po rtsal lam 7rig 'dzin 'gyur med
NK076(mu)002:11488: rdo rjes pas bskal pa lcags stag lo'i sbo zla'i
NK076(mu)002:11489: tshes nyer bzhi nas dbu bzung /
NK076(mu)002:11490: dbyar ra ba nag zla'i tshes bcu'i dus chen la
NK076(mu)002:11491: rdzogs par grub par bgyis pas bstan 'gror sman pa'i
NK076(mu)002:11493: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim 'bru 'brel gyi //
NK076(mu)002:11494: yi ge phyi mo spar du bskrun pa po //
NK076(mu)002:11495: rang slog dge slong bstan 'dzin bkra shis kyis //
NK076(mu)002:11496: zho bdun gor mo brgya sogs zhal theb byas //
NK076(mu)002:11497: yi ge mthun sbyor dkon mchog 'od zer bgyis //
NK076(mu)002:11498: dge des 'brel thogs sems can thams cad kun //
NK076(mu)002:11499: gdod ma'i mgon po'i go 'phang thob pa dang //
NK076(mu)002:11500: zab chos 'di yang mi nub dar rgyas shog //
